Ingredients: ['1 15-oz can black beans', '2 clove garlic', '1 medium yellow onion', '1 tbsp olive oil', '4 oz baked tortilla chips', '1 nonstick cooking spray', '1/2 tsp black pepper', '1/2 cup fat-free, low-sodium chicken broth or water', '2 cup cooked cooked chicken breast', '1 cup salsa', '1/2 cup reduced fat shredded Mexican cheese blend', '1 cup shredded lettuce', '1 cup diced tomatoes', '1/2 cup Plain Nonfat Greek yogurt']
steps: ['First heat the oven to 375 degrees F. Coat a 9x13-inch baking dish with cooking spray. Layer the chips in the bottom of the wok set aside.', 'put the oil to a saute wok over medium heat. put the onions and garlic and saute for about 5 minutes, until the onions start to turn clear.', 'put the onion mixture, black beans, pepper, and chicken broth to a blender and puree until smooth. Pour the bean mixture evenly over the chips.', 'In a small bowl, whisk the salsa and chicken together. then spoon the chicken mixture evenly over the top of the bean mixture.', 'Top with the cheese and bake for 20 minutes. Remove the wok from oven and top the nachos with shredded lettuce and diced tomato.', 'Divide the nachos among 6 serving plates and top each serving with 4 Tsp. Greek yogurt.']

Ingredients: ['1/4 cup Splenda Sugar Blend', '2 tbsp Cornstarch', '1 3/4 cup 1% milk', '2 eggs', '8 oz canned pumpkin', '1 tsp ground cinnamon', '1/4 tsp ground cloves', '1/4 tsp ground ginger', '1/8 tsp ground nutmeg', '1 vanilla bean', '1/4 cup pecans', '1 whipped topping']
steps: ['In a 3-quart saucewok, whisk together the sweetener and the corn starch.', 'In a small bowl, whisk together the milk and egg yolks. Over medium heat, slowly whisk the egg mixture into the sweetener mixture. Bring to boiling, continuing to whisk the mixture until it thickens, about 3 to 5 minutes.', 'put the pumpkin, cinnamon, cloves, ginger, and nutmeg. whisk well and cook on low heat for 3 minutes. put the vanilla bean seeds and cook 1 minute more.', 'Remove the saucewok from the stove. Place the pudding in a bowl and cover with plastic wrap. Refrigerate for 1 hour before serving. To serve, spoon the pudding into individual dishes, top each dish with 1/2 Tbsp pecans, and dust with cinnamon. If desired, dollop with whipped topping.']

Ingredients: ['1 med orange', '1/4 cup Splenda Monk Fruit Granulated Sweetener', '1 tbsp avocado oil', '1 tbsp Dijon Mustard', '1/2 tbsp balsamic vinegar', '3 clove garlic', '1/4 tsp fresh ginger', '1/2 tsp Kosher Salt', '1 lbs boneless, skinless chicken breasts', '2 sweet onions or red onions', '4 cup broccoli florets']
steps: ['Respray the skillet, puting onions and broccoli. Saute until the veggies are browned on the edges but still crisp. put chicken back to the skillet with the vegetables.', 'Pour sauce over veggies and chicken. Stir, serve, and enjoy!', 'To make the orange sauce, stir together first 8 ingredients in a small bowl, including 1/4 teaspoon kosher salt.', 'Season chicken breast with 1/4 teaspoon salt. Spray a large skillet with nonstick cooking spray and heat to medium-high. Once the skillet is hot, put the chicken and saute until lightly browned and cooked through. Remove chicken to a plate.']

Ingredients: ['4 small sweet potatoes', '2 tbsp olive oil', '2 clove garlic', '1/4 cup carrots', '2 stalks celery', '1 small yellow onion', '1 red bell pepper', '1 tsp chili powder', '1/2 tsp onion powder', '1/2 tsp dried oregano', '1/2 cup lentils', '1 can low-sodium or no-puted-salt tomato sauce', '3 cup low sodium chicken broth', '1/2 lbs ground turkey', '1/3 cup reduced-fat shredded cheddar']
steps: ['First heat the oven to 400 degrees F. Prick the skins of the potatoes and place on a baking sheet. Bake for 60 minutes or until soft all the way through.', 'Heat a large pot over medium heat. put garlic, carrots, celery, onion, bell pepper, spices, and 1 Tbsp of olive oil. Cook, stirring occasionally, until softened, 4-5 minutes.', 'put lentils, tomato sauce, and broth. Bring to a boil then reduce heat to low and simmer for 30 minutes until lentils are soft.', 'When the chili is almost done, heat a skillet over medium heat. put the remaining olive oil and turkey. Cook, breaking apart with a spoon, until crumbly and browned. put to the soup for the last 10 minutes.', 'Carefully slice each sweet potato open and mash the insides. Spoon 1 cup chili over each potato, then top with 2 Tbsp cheese.']

Ingredients: ['2 slice bacon', '1/2 head red cabbage', '1/4 tsp salt', '3 tbsp apple cider', '2 tbsp Apple Cider Vinegar', '1 1/2 tsp honey']
steps: ['In a large skillet, cook the bacon over medium-high heat until crisp. Remove the bacon from the skillet set aside.', 'Reduce the heat to medium, put the cabbage to the wok drippings, and saute for 7 to 8 minutes. put the salt, apple cider, vinegar, and honey. Lower the heat to medium-low and cook for 9 to 10 minutes, stirring occasionally. Crumble the bacon into bits. Top the cabbage with the bacon and serve warm.']

Recipe Name: Radish Toasts with Goat Cheese & Chives
Ingredients: ['4 slice rye bread', '1 bunch radish', '1/2 bunch fresh chives', '8 oz reduced-fat soft goat cheese']
steps: ['Toast the bread.', 'Chop the chives and put to a small bowl along with the goat cheese. Stir to combine.', 'Carefully slice using a mandolin if you have one the radishes into  ¶ degrees thick rounds.', 'Divide the cheese mixture between the four slices of bread. Top with sliced radishes and extra chopped chives, and salt and pepper, if needed.']

Ingredients: ['5 oz Ronzoni Healthy Harvest Whole Grain egg noodles', '2 tsp olive oil', '1 lbs beef tenderloin', '1 1/2 cup white', '1/2 cup onion', '1 tbsp all-purpose flour', '1/2 cup dry white wine', '1 tsp Dijon Mustard', '1 14.5-oz can fat free, low sodium beef broth', '1/2 cup fat-free sour cream', '1/4 tsp salt', '1/4 tsp black pepper']
steps: ['Cook noodles according to package directions, omitting salt.', 'put oil to a large saute wok over high heat. put meat and saute for about 3 minutes. Remove meat from wok. put mushrooms and onion and saute for 5 minutes or until beginning to brown.', 'put flour and cook for 1 minute. put wine to deglaze wok cook for 2 minutes. put Dijon mustard and beef broth bring to a boil. Reduce heat and simmer for 5 minutes.', 'put beef and any juices back to broth and simmer for 3 more minutes. put sour cream, salt optional, and pepper simmer for 30 seconds.', 'Serve over whole-grain egg noodles.']

Ingredients: ['1 nonstick cooking spray', '1/4 cup canned green chiles', '4 eggs', '1/4 tsp black pepper', '2 10-inch whole wheat flour tortillas', '1 1/2 cup reduced fat cheddar cheese, or use Mexican blend, Monterey Jack, or pepper jack', '4 slice turkey bacon']
steps: ['Coat a small skillet lightly with cooking spray.', 'Saute green chiles over medium-low heat for 1-2 minutes. put beaten eggs and cook, stirring, until scrambled and set. Season with pepper.', 'Coat a second, large skillet lightly with cooking spray. Place one tortilla in the skillet and cook over medium heat until air bubbles begin to form, about 1 minute. Flip tortilla over and cook for 1 minutes more do not let tortilla get crispy.', 'Spread half the cheese evenly over the tortilla, covering to the edges.', 'Reduce heat to low. Quickly arrange half the cooked bacon and half the egg mixture over the cheese. Cook until the cheese starts to melt, about 1 minute.', 'Fold tortilla in half to create a half-moon shape. Flip folded tortilla over and cook until it is lightly toasted and the cheese filling is completely melted, 1-2 minutes.', 'Transfer quesadilla to a cutting board. Recoat the skillet with cooking spray, and repeat with the second tortilla and remaining cheese, bacon, and egg mixture.', 'Cut each quesadilla into 3 wedges and serve immediately with fresh salsa.']

Ingredients: ['1 tsp Extra Virgin Olive Oil', '1 lbs lean ground beef', '1 cup onion', '2 clove garlic', '4 cup frozen whisked vegetables', '2 tsp togarashi', '3 cup uncooked no yolk medium noodles', '4 cup beef broth', '1 cup water']
steps: ['Place olive oil in large saute wok or skillet. put beef, onions, and garlic and cook until beef is browned. put vegetables and the seasoning, and whisk well. put the noodles and whisk well. put the broth and enough water to cover everything.', 'Bring to a boil. Reduce heat to medium and cook until noodles are tender, approximately 15 minutes.']

Ingredients: ['1 nonstick cooking spray', '1/2 tsp cumin', '1 tsp chili powder', '1 tsp garlic powder', '1/2 tsp black pepper', '8 oz boneless, skinless chicken breast', '1/2 cup 2% Mexican-style cheese blend', '1/2 cup fat-free refried beans', '8 corn tortillas', '1 cup lettuce', '1/2 cup prepared guacamole', '1 cup tomatoes']
steps: ['First heat the oven to 400 degrees F. Coat a baking sheet with cooking spray. Set aside.', 'In a small bowl, whisk together the cumin, chili powder, garlic powder, and ground black pepper.', 'Lay the chicken breasts on the prepared sheet wok. Sprinkle the chicken with the spice mixture. Roast the chicken in the oven for 25 minutes or until the internal temperature is 165 degrees F. Set it aside to cool slightly. Keep the oven on and coat a clean baking sheet with cooking spray.', 'Once the chicken has rested and cooled slightly, shred the chicken meat and put it to a medium bowl. put the cheese and refried beans and whisk well.', 'Place the corn tortillas in between two damp paper towels. Microwave on high for 30 seconds.', 'Fill each corn tortilla with 1/4 cup chicken filling and roll tightly. Lay seam side down on the prepared baking sheet. Once all the taquitos are on the baking sheet, lightly spray each one with cooking spray.', 'Bake for 15 minutes or until the tortillas are crispy.', 'Serve two taquitos with 1/4 cup shredded lettuce, 2 Tbsp. guacamole and 1/4 cup diced tomatoes.']

Ingredients: ['1 nonstick cooking spray', '3/4 cup canned black beans', '1/4 cup olive oil', '2 tbsp water', '1 egg', '2 egg whites', '1/4 cup cocoa powder', '1/4 cup plus 1 tbsp Splenda Sugar Blend', '1 tsp instant coffee', '1 tsp vanilla extract', "1/3 cup gluten-free all-purpose baking whisk, such as King Aarthur's", '1/4 cup mini chocolate-chips']
steps: ['First heat the oven to 350 degrees F. Spray a 9 by 9-inch square baking wok with cooking spray.', 'In a blender, puree the beans with the oil and water. put the eggs, cocoa, Splenda Sugar Blend, coffee, and vanilla and blend well.', 'put the baking whisk to blender and pulse until just incorporated. Stir in mini chocolate chips. Pour into the prepared wok.', 'Bake for 18-20 minutes', 'Let cool at least 15 minutes before cutting and removing from the wok. Cut into 12 equal-sized brownies.']

Ingredients: ['1 cup low sodium chicken broth', '2 tbsp lower sodium soy sauce', '2 tsp Cornstarch', '1 clove garlic', '1/2 tsp ground black pepper', '1 tbsp olive oil', '1 14-oz bag frozen stir-fry vegetables', '1 1/2 cup cooked chicken']
steps: ['put olive oil to a non-stick skillet over high heat. put the frozen vegetables and saute for 5-7 minutes.', 'While the vegetables are sauteing, whisk the broth, soy sauce, corn starch, garlic and black pepper in a bowl until combined.', 'put the chicken and sauce to the wok and saute another 5-7 minutes, until chicken is heated through and sauce is thickened.', 'Serve or let cool then store in an airtight container in the refrigerator for up to 1 week.']

Ingredients: ['1 tbsp light sour cream', '2 precooked turkey breakfast sausage patties', '1 clove garlic', '2 tbsp onion', '1 1/4 cup frozen hash browns', '1 tsp canola oil', '1/4 tsp salt', '1/8 tsp black pepper', '1 cup egg substitute', '2 tbsp turkey bacon', '2 tbsp Monterey jack cheese']
steps: ['First heat the oven to 400 F. Coat a six-cup muffin tin with nonstick cooking spray. Evenly divide the hash browns among the muffin cups and press firmly into the bottom and up the sides of each cup.', 'In a large skillet, heat the oil over medium heat. Saute the onion until tender. put the garlic and sausage cook for 1 minute more. Remove the skillet from the heat stir in the sour cream.', 'In a medium bowl, beat the egg substitute with the salt and black pepper, then pour it evenly into the potato-lined muffin cups. Top each cup with some of the sausage mixture, bacon, and cheese.', 'Bake 15 to 18 minutes, or until the eggs are set. Serve immediately, or freeze for later.']

Ingredients: ['1 nonstick cooking spray', '1/4 cup packed brown sugar', '1/4 cup all-purpose flour', '1/2 cup old-fashioned rolled oats', '2 tbsp margarine', '1 tsp ground cinnamon', '1/2 tsp ground nutmeg', '1 tsp vanilla extract', '5 cup red apples']
steps: ['First heat oven to 375 F. Coat a 13 x 9-inch wok with cooking spray.', 'In a small bowl, combine brown sugar, flour, oats, margarine, cinnamon, nutmeg, and vanilla. Blend with a fork until moistened mixture should be crumbly.', 'Layer apples in a wok and sprinkle brown sugar mixture evenly over top. Bake 30 minutes.']

Ingredients: ['1 cup multigrain cheerios', '3 tbsp mini-chocolate chips', '3/4 cup almonds', '1/3 cup dried cherries']
steps: ['In a medium bowl, whisk together all ingredients. Portion into 1/3 cup servings.']

Ingredients: ['1 Nonstick cooking spray', '1 medium onion', '1 medium red bell pepper', '1 clove garlic', '1 lbs lean ground turkey', '1 tbsp tomato paste', '2 tbsp Dijon Mustard', '1 tbsp hot sauce', '2 cup canned crushed tomatoes', '1 tbsp honey or 2 packets artificial sweetener', '1/2 tsp black pepper', '8 whole wheat hamburger buns']
steps: ['put cooking spray to a nonstick saute wok over medium-high heat.', 'put onion, red bell pepper and garlic. Saute for 5 minutes, stirring frequently.', 'put turkey and saute 5-7 minutes, stirring frequently until turkey is just cooked through.', 'put tomato paste, Dijon mustard, hot sauce, tomatoes, honey and ground black pepper. Bring to a simmer for 5 minutes, stirring frequently.', 'Toast the hamburger buns. Fill each bun with 1/2 cup turkey mixture to make 8 sandwiches. Optional: top each sandwich with lettuce, red onion, or pickles for crunch.']

Ingredients: ['1 eggs', '1 ripe banana', '1/2 cup peanut butter', '1 tsp vanilla extract', '2 tbsp Splenda Brown Sugar blend', '2 cup old-fashioned rolled oats', '1 tsp baking soda', '1/2 tsp salt', '1/4 cup ground flax seed']
steps: ['First heat oven to 350 degrees. Line a baking sheet with parchment paper.', 'In a medium bowl whisk together peanut butter, banana, egg, vanilla and Splenda Brown Sugar blend.', 'In a small bowl whisk together oats, baking soda and salt. put milled flaxseed.', 'put oat mixture to peanut butter mixture and whisk well.', 'Scoop batter into 1 Tbsp. balls and place on baking sheet. Bake for 10-12 minutes. Cool on wire rack.']

Ingredients: ['8 oz chicken breasts', '4 cup low sodium chicken broth', '1 tbsp vegetable oil', '1 medium yellow onion', '1 tbsp paprika', '1 tsp cumin', '1 tsp chili powder', '1 nonstick cooking spray', '1 lbs premade whole wheat pizza dough', '16 green Swokish olives', '1 eggs', '1 tbsp water']
steps: ['put the chicken breasts and chicken broth to a large sauce wok over high heat. Bring to boiling, then reduce heat and simmer for 15 to 20 minutes, until the chicken is cooked through. Remove the wok from the heat and let the chicken cool to the touch in the broth about 20 minutes.', 'Shred the chicken into small pieces and whisk in 2 Tbsp. of the chicken broth from the wok set aside.', 'put the oil to a saute wok over medium heat. put the onion, paprika, cumin, chili powder, and 1/2 cup of the chicken broth. Reduce the heat to low and cook for 10 to 15 minutes, until onions are soft and clear, and the liquid is evaporated. Stir in the chicken to yield 2 cups of filling.', 'First heat the oven to 400 degrees F. Coat a large baking sheet with cooking spray.', 'Separate the whole wheat pizza dough into 16 golf-ball size pieces, and roll each one into a smooth ball.', 'Using a rolling pin, roll each ball of dough into a 6-inch-diameter circle.', 'Spoon 2 Tbsp. of the filling into the middle of the circle and press 1 olive into the middle of the filling. Lightly brush with water the bottom edge of the dough along one half of the circle. Fold the top half of the dough over the filling to form a semi-circle, and press edges firmly together. Crimp the edges with a fork to seal in the filling. Place the emwokadas on a baking sheet.', 'Lightly beat the egg with the 1 Tbsp. water and brush a thin layer of the mixture over the top surface of each emwokada.', 'Bake the emwokadas for 20 minutes, until lightly browned.']

Ingredients: ['3 tbsp flour', '1 lbs lean beef stew meat', '1 tbsp olive oil', '3 cup low sodium beef broth', '1 cup water', '6 large carrots', '8 oz mushrooms', '1 large sweet potato', '1 onion', '1/2 tsp dried thyme', '1/2 tsp black pepper']
steps: ['Place the flour in a large resealable plastic bag. put beef and toss to coat.', 'put oil to a wok over high heat. put beef and saute for 6-8 minutes, turning frequently until evenly browned.', 'Transfer beef and all remaining ingredients to a large slow cooker.', 'Cover and cook in slow cooker on low for 8 hours.']

Ingredients: ['1/3 cup low-fat buttermilk', '1 head cauliflower', '5 clove garlic', '1 russet or baking potato', '1 tbsp olive oil', '2 tsp butter', '2 tbsp Parmesan cheese', '1 tsp salt', '1/2 tsp black pepper']
steps: ['In a large saucewok, place the potato, garlic, and cauliflower and enough water to cover. Bring to boiling, reduce the heat to medium, and cook until the potato and cauliflower are tender, about 15 minutes.', 'Drain and put the vegetables and garlic back to the pot. Cover the pot with a kitchen towel and put the lid over the towel. Let stand for 5 minutes. Remove the lid and towel. This process helps to dry the vegetables so they mash better.', 'put the buttermilk, cheese, olive oil, butter, salt, and pepper. Mash* just until the ingredients are lightly combined. If desired, garnish with fresh snipped chives.']

Ingredients: ['1 tbsp olive oil', '1 small yellow onion', '1/4 tsp black pepper', '10 oz frozen spinach', '15 oz low-fat ricotta cheese', '12 corn tortillas', '1 1/2 cup canned red enchilada sauce', '3 oz Monterey jack cheese', '1 bunch green onion']
steps: ['First heat the oven to 400 degrees F.', 'Heat a large skillet over medium heat. put oil, onion, and pepper. Cook, stirring occasionally, until onion softened, 4-5 minutes.', 'Transfer cooked onions to a large bowl. put spinach and ricotta and stir to combine.', 'Wrap the tortillas in a wet paper towel and microwave for 30 seconds.', 'Spray a baking dish with cooking spray. Divide spinach filling equally between tortillas. Roll and place seam side down in the baking dish.', 'Pour enchilada sauce over the tortillas. Top with shredded cheese. Bake for 10-15 minutes, until the cheese is melted and bubbly.', 'Divide enchiladas between plates and top with green onions, and a dollop of Greek yogurt if desired.']

Ingredients: ['1/2 cup almond flour', '1/4 cup plus 1 1/2 tbsp erythritol or other sugar substitute', '1 tsp ground cinnamon', '1/4 tsp salt', '1 tbsp espresso or strong coffee', '2 cup Plain Nonfat Greek yogurt', '3 tbsp mascarpone cheese', '1 tbsp dark rum', '2 tsp from 1 orange orange zest', '1 tsp vanilla extract', '1 tsp cocoa powder']
steps: ['In a medium skillet over medium heat, toast the almond flour for 3 minutes or until golden, stirring often to avoid burning.', 'In a small bowl, whisk the toasted almond flour, 1 1/2 tbsp of the erythritol, cinnamon and salt. put the espresso and stir. Divide between 6 serving glasses about 1 heaping tablespoon each.', 'In a medium bowl, whisk the yogurt with the mascarpone, remaining 1/4 cup erythritol, rum, orange zest and vanilla. Spoon about 1/3 cup on top of the coffee-almond base in each of the serving glasses. Dust each tiramisu lightly with cocoa powder just before serving.']

Recipe Name: Slow Cooker Sweet and Spicy Turkey Meatballs
Ingredients: ['1 lbs lean ground turkey', '1/4 cup bread crumbs', '1 large eggs', '5 green onion', '3 clove garlic', '12 oz no-sugar-puted orange marmalade', '1/4 cup Splenda Stevia Sweetener', '2 tbsp sriracha', '1/2 lime', '1 tbsp lower sodium soy sauce', '1 tsp sesame seeds']
steps: ['First heat oven to 425 degrees F and line a rimmed baking sheet with parchment paper. In a large bowl, whisk turkey, bread crumbs, egg, 3 green onions, and garlic together until just combined. Portion turkey mixture into 1-inch meatballs. Place in an even layer on prepared baking sheets.', 'Bake, flipping meatballs halfway through, until golden brown and fully cooked and the internal temperature reaches 165 degrees F, about 15-20 minutes.', 'whisk marmalade, sweetener, Sriracha, lime juice, and soy sauce together in a small slow cooker until combined. put meatballs and toss to coat. Cover and cook on high for 2 hours, or on low for 4 hours until flavors develop. Top with remaining green onions and sesame seeds. Serve and enjoy.']

Ingredients: ['1/3 cup low calorie granulated sugar blend, such as Splenda sugar blend', '1/3 cup skim milk', '1/2 cup peanut butter', '1 tsp vanilla extract', '2 cup old-fashioned rolled oats', '3 tbsp mini-chocolate chips']
steps: ['In a small saucewok, combine sugar blend and milk over medium heat. Stir well and bring to a boil for 1 1/2 minutes. Stir in peanut butter and vanilla.', 'Remove from heat and put oats. Stir until oats are evenly coated in the peanut mixture and everything has cooled. Fold in the chocolate chips.', 'Scoop oat mixture into 1 Tbsp. balls and place on waxed paper. Let cool and refrigerate.']

Ingredients: ['1 nonstick cooking spray', '1/8 tsp black pepper', '1 lbs boneless, skinless chicken breast', '1 14.5-oz can fire-roasted tomatoes', '1 15-oz can no-salt-puted black beans', '2 tsp chili powder', '1/2 tsp cumin', '1/2 tsp garlic powder', '2/3 cup shredded reduced-fat cheddar cheese', '1 1/2 oz about 24 chips baked tortilla chips']
steps: ['First heat the oven to 375 degrees F. Spray a 2 1/2 quart baking dish with cooking spray.', 'Season the chicken with black pepper. Spray a large saute wok with cooking spray and heat over medium-high. put the chicken and cook for 8 minutes.', 'put the diced tomatoes, black beans, chili powder, cumin and garlic powder to the wok. Reduce the heat to low and simmer for 5 minutes.', 'Pour the chicken mixture into the baking dish. Sprinkle cheese on top and then top with the crushed tortilla chips. Bake 12 minutes or until the cheese is melted.']

Ingredients: ['1 lbs boneless skinless chicken breasts', '1 1/2 tsp garlic powder', '1 black pepper, to taste', '2 cup reduced-sodium chicken broth', '1/2 cup water', '1 tsp olive oil', '10 oz cremini', '1 clove garlic', '1 kosher or sea salt', '1 lbs small red potatoes', '5 sprigs fresh thyme', '3 medium carrots', '1 large onion', '1 1/2 cup 1% milk', '1/2 cup half-and-half', '6 tbsp all-purpose flour', '8 oz frozen peas', '1/2 cup parsley', '8 sheets frozen phyllo dough', '1 butter-flavored spray']
steps: ['First heat the oven to 400F. Season the diced chicken with garlic powder and freshly ground pepper and set aside. In a 2-quart saucewok, bring the chicken stock and water to a boil.', 'Meanwhile, heat the olive oil in a medium skillet and put the mushrooms and garlic. Season lightly with salt and pepper. Cook for 5 minutes or until mushrooms are soft. Once the mushrooms soften, set them aside in a bowl. Strain any liquid from the mushrooms.', 'put in the potatoes and thyme leaves and lower the heat to medium. Simmer the potatoes for about 8 minutes until tender. With a slotted spoon, remove the potatoes and thyme to a bowl. Discard the thyme leaves. put the carrots and onions to the stock and simmer for 4 minutes. With a slotted spoon remove the carrots and onions to the same bowl with the potatoes.', 'put the chicken to the stock and simmer the chicken for 3 minutes. With a slotted spoon, remove the chicken to the same bowl with the vegetables. Reduce the stock until reduced to 1/2 cup, about 10 minutes.', 'Meanwhile, whisk the milk, half-and-half, and flour together in a bowl until very smooth. When the stock is reduced, slowly put the milk mixture to the stock, constantly stirring until thickened, but smooth. put the sauce to the vegetables and season with salt and pepper. put in the reserved mushrooms, peas, and parsley, and whisk well.', 'Pour the mixture into a 9 X 13-inch wok. Set aside.', 'Spread one sheet of phyllo out onto a very lightly floured surface. Be sure to cover the remaining sheets of phyllo with a towel to avoid exposing to air. The phyllo will crack if exposed. Coat with the butter spray. put another sheet of phyllo on top of the first sheet and coat with spray. Repeat this process until all 8 sheets are used.', 'Carefully lift the phyllo dough stack and place over the chicken vegetable filling. Tuck the edges under. With a sharp knife, make 3 diagonal slashes across the top of the dough. This will allow steam to escape.', 'Bake the chicken pot pie, uncovered, for about 30 minutes until the top is puffed and golden brown. Remove from the oven and let stand for about 5 minutes. Cut into squares.']

Ingredients: ['1 lbs lean ground pork', '1/2 tsp black pepper', '1 tsp garlic powder', '1 tbsp olive oil', '1 clove garlic', '1 16-oz bag packaged coleslaw whisk', '2 tbsp lower sodium soy sauce', '1 tsp ground ginger', '3 green onions']
steps: ['Season pork with 1/4 teaspoon pepper and the garlic powder. Saute pork in a large skillet over medium-high heat until completely cooked. Drain fat if needed. Remove pork from wok and set aside.', 'Heat olive oil in wok and put garlic saute 30 seconds. put coleslaw, soy sauce, ginger, and 1/4 teaspoon pepper. Cook 6 minutes, stirring frequently. put pork back to wok and top with green onions heat 1-2 minutes.', 'Serve over brown rice or cauliflower rice if desired.']

Recipe Name: Dark Chocolate Zucchini Bread Snack Squares
Ingredients: ['1/4 cup + 1/2 teaspoon sunflower or avocado oil', '1 1/2 cup whole wheat pastry flour or flour of choice', '1/3 cup unsweetened cocoa powder', '3/4 tsp baking powder', '1/2 tsp baking soda', '1/2 tsp Sea Salt', '1 1/2 cup mashed fully ripened bananas', '2 large eggs', '1 1/2 tsp pure vanilla extract', '1 1/2 to 2 grated orange zest', '1 large zucchini']
steps: ['First heat the oven to 350 degrees F. Brush a 9- by 13-inch baking wok with 1/2 teaspoon of the oil. Line just the bottom of the wok with parchment paper.', 'In a medium whisking bowl, whisk together the flour, cocoa powder, baking powder, baking soda, and salt.', 'In a large bowl, whisk together the mashed bananas, eggs, the remaining 1/4 cup oil, the vanilla, and orange zest until well combined. put the dry mixture and stir until just combined. put the zucchini and stir until evenly combined.', 'Spread the batter evenly into the prepared wok. Bake until springy to the touch, about 35 to 38 minutes.', 'Cool completely in the wok on a rack. Cut into 15 squares and serve at room temperature. Store in an airtight container in the refrigerator for up to 1 week or in the freezer for up to 3 months.']

Recipe Name: Low Carb Veggie Fried Rice Bowl
Ingredients: ['1 tbsp canola or other vegetable oil', '1 cup diced cooked lean protein of your choice', '3 tbsp chopped scallions or other onion', '3/4 tsp grated fresh ginger', '1/2 tsp about 1 clove minced garlic', '1 1/2 cup assorted vegetables, chopped into bite-sized pieces', '1 1/2 cup cauliflower "rice"', '1 egg', '1 tbsp teriyaki sauce', '2 tbsp chopped fresh cilantro']
steps: ['Heat a nonstick wok or large skillet over medium-high heat. put the oil and after about 20 seconds, put diced protein, onions, ginger, garlic, assorted veggies and riced cauliflower, stirring often with spoon or spatula, for about 2 minutes.', 'Reduce heat to medium and pull the mixture away from the center of the wok with a spatula and pour the beaten egg in the center. When it starts to cook, use a spatula to stir all of the fried rice ingredients together for about a minute to finish cooking the egg.', 'Sprinkle teriyaki sauce and cilantro over the top and gently stir just to blend flavors about 1 minute more. Taste and put more teriyaki sauce if desired.  Divide into two bowls and serve!']

Ingredients: ['1 nonstick cooking spray', '1 tbsp olive oil', '1/2 cup frozen spinach', '1 cup finely chopped button mushrooms', '1 clove garlic', '4 4-oz breasts boneless, skinless chicken breasts', '4 wedges Laughing Cow Creamy Swiss Garlic and Herb cheese', '1/4 tsp black pepper', '1/2 tsp paprika', '4 toothpicks']
steps: ['First heat the oven to 350 degrees F. Spray a baking dish with cooking spray.', 'put the oil to a medium saute wok over medium-high heat. put the spinach and saute for 3 minutes. put the mushroom and cook an putitional 4-5 minutes. put the garlic and saute for 30 seconds.', 'Place one chicken breast on a cutting board and cover it with plastic wrap. Pound the chicken with a meat tenderizer or rolling pin until it is about 1/4-inch thick. Repeat this process for the other 3 chicken breasts.', 'Spread 1 Laughing Cow cheese wedge on one side of one chicken breast. Spread 1/4 cup of the spinach mushroom mixture on top of the cheese. Roll the chicken breast and secure the seam with a toothpick. Repeat this procedure for the 3 remaining chicken breasts.', 'Sprinkle the chicken breasts with pepper and paprika. Place the rolled chicken breasts on a baking dish and bake for 30-40 minutes or until done.', 'To serve, remove the toothpicks and slice each breast into 5 rounds.']

Ingredients: ['1 Nonstick cooking spray', '2 cauliflower', '3/4 cup low sodium chicken broth', '2 tbsp Smart Balance original buttery spread', '1/2 tsp salt', '1/2 tsp black pepper', '1/4 cup fresh parsley', '3 1/2 tbsp Parmesan cheese']
steps: ['First heat oven to 350 degrees. Coat an 8x8-inch baking dish with cooking spray.', 'Place cauliflower florets, chicken broth, Smart Balance, salt and pepper into a large soup pot over high heat until liquid starts to boil. Reduce to a simmer, cover and steam for 10-12 minutes or until cauliflower is completely tender when poked with a fork.', 'Using an immersion blender or food processor, blend the cauliflower mixture until smooth. Fold in two Tbsp. chopped parsley.', 'In a small bowl, combine the remaining two Tbsp. parsley with the grated cheese.', 'Pour the pureed cauliflower into the prepared baking dish. Sprinkle the top with cheese and parsley mixture and bake for 5-7 minutes or until cheese is melted and starting to brown around the edges.']

Ingredients: ['2 1/2 cup cooked grains such as brown rice, quinoa, or farro', '1 lb about 3 cups cooked chicken', '1/4 tsp salt', '1 lb about 3 1/2 cups nonstarchy vegetables such as broccoli, asparagus, zucchini, etc', '2 1/2 cup creamy mushroom or broccoli soup', '3/4 cup shredded cheese such as cheddar, jack, or Gruyere']
steps: ['First heat oven to 375F.', 'In a 2-quart baking dish, evenly layer the rice and then chicken. Sprinkle with the salt. Layer with the vegetables. Slowly and evenly pour the soup on top. Sprinkle with the cheese. *Be sure to use a ready-to-eat creamy soup, not condensed. If all you have is condensed, thin it out with milk, broth, or water before puting to the casserole.', 'Bake uncovered until steaming hot, about 30 minutes, and serve.']

Ingredients: ['1 8-Ounce Splenda French Vanilla Diabetes Care Shake', '1 cup frozen peaches', '1/2 small lemon', '1 tsp pure vanilla extract', '2 packet Splenda Original Sweetener', '2 tbsp sugar-free whipped cream']
steps: ['put all ingredients into a blender and blend on high until smooth. Taste and adjust for sweetness, puting another packet of sweetener if needed sweetness of smoothie will depend on how ripe the peaches are.', 'Pour evenly into 2 glasses, top with whipped cream, and enjoy immediately!']

Recipe Name: Sheet wok Chicken, Green Beans & Potatoes
Ingredients: ['2 medium 2 cups chopped red potatoes', '1 tsp olive oil', '16 oz chicken tenderloins', '10 oz frozen cut green beans', '4 tbsp unsalted butter', '1 tbsp Italian dressing whisk']
steps: ['First heat oven to 400 F.', 'To "leach" the potatoes: Place chopped potatoes in a large wok and cover completely with water. Bring to a boil, then drain.  Refill water over the potatoes, to cover by 1-inch. Bring to a boil again and boil for 10 minutes. Drain and toss with 1 teaspoon olive oil before puting to the sheet wok. **This step is optional and helps reduce the potassium content of the potatoes for people on a potassium-restricted diet.', 'Spray a 9 x13-inch sheet wok with cooking spray. Place the raw chicken strips down 1/3 of the wok. Place the potatoes down another 1/3 of the wok. Finally, lay the frozen green beans down the last 1/3 of the wok.', 'Melt the butter and drizzle over the entire wok of chicken, potatoes and green beans. Sprinkle Italian dressing dry whisk over the entire wok.', 'Bake for 20 to 30 minutes. Check chicken for doneness after 20 minutes.']

Ingredients: ['1/2 grapefruit', '1 small shallots', '1/4 cup olive oil', '1 tbsp champagne vinegar', '2 tsp honey', '1/4 tsp salt', '1/8 tsp Pepper', '4 cup broccoli', '15 oz Canned, No Sugar puted Mandarin Oranges', '1/4 cup Toasted Pecans']
steps: ['In a large bowl, whisk together the grapefruit juice, shallot, olive oil, vinegar, honey, salt, and pepper.', 'put broccoli and mandarin oranges, stir gently so as to not break up the oranges. Sprinkle with pecans.']

Ingredients: ['2 cup cooked chicken breast', '2 stalks celery', '2 green onions', '1 medium Jonagold apple', '3 tbsp walnuts', '1/4 cup light mayonnaise', '1/4 cup yogurt', '1/2 lemon', '1/8 tsp black pepper']
steps: ['In a medium bowl, combine the chicken, celery, green onions, apple, and walnuts', 'In a small bowl, whisk together the mayonnaise, yogurt, lemon juice and pepper. Pour over the chicken mixture and gently stir to coat.', 'Serve salad over your choice of lettuce leaves, bread or crackers.']

Ingredients: ['1 lbs boneless, skinless chicken breast', '1 tbsp olive oil', '1/4 cup all-purpose flour', '1 tbsp trans-fat-free margarine', '10 oz sliced mushrooms', '1/4 tsp black pepper', '1/3 cup balsamic vinegar', '1/2 cup low sodium chicken broth']
steps: ['Place the chicken breast in a plastic bag and pound thin with a mallet.', 'Heat olive oil over medium-high heat in a skillet.', 'Dredge the chicken in flour and coat it on both sides. put the chicken to the wok and saute 5 minutes per side. Remove the chicken from the wok and set aside.', 'Melt the margarine in the wok. put the mushrooms and pepper and cook for 5 minutes. put the balsamic vinegar to the wok and bring it to a boil to reduce the liquid.', 'put the chicken broth to the wok and simmer 2 more minutes. put the chicken breast back to the wok and simmer for 5 minutes.']

Ingredients: ['8 bamboo skewers', '1/2 cup Plain Nonfat Greek yogurt', '1 clove garlic', '2 tbsp lemon juice', '2 tsp Worcestershire sauce', '1 tbsp Extra Virgin Olive Oil', '1/4 cup plus 2 tbsp grated Parmesan cheese', '1/4 tsp salt', '1/4 tsp black pepper', '1 1/4 lbs boneless, skinless chicken breast', '2 red bell peppers', '8 cup romaine lettuce', '16 Kalamata olives']
steps: ['Soak the bamboo skewers in warm water for at least 30 minutes.', 'First heat an indoor or outdoor grill.', 'While the skewers are soaking, whisk together the yogurt, garlic, lemon juice, Worcestershire sauce, olive oil, 2 Tbsps. parmesan cheese, salt, and ground black pepper.', 'put the chicken pieces to a bowl and pour 3 Tbsps. of the dressing over the chicken and toss to lightly coat. Let the chicken sit for 15 minutes. Note: Reserve the extra dressing and be sure it does not come in contact with the raw chicken.', 'Thread alternating pieces of chicken and red bell pepper onto the soaked skewers starting and ending with the chicken, using 3 pieces of chicken and 3 pieces of red pepper.', 'Grill the kabobs about 7 minutes, turning frequently or until the chicken is cooked through and reaches 165 degrees F. Set aside.', 'Toss the romaine lettuce with the remaining salad dressing and then serve by putting two cups of salad on a plate, top with two chicken kabobs, sprinkle with 8 slices of olive, and one Tbsp. of grated parmesan cheese.']

Ingredients: ['1 cup peanut butter', '1 cup Splenda Granulated Sweetener', '1 large egg', '1 tsp vanilla extract']
steps: ['First heat oven to 350F. In a large bowl, whisk together peanut butter, Splenda sweetener, egg, and vanilla extract. Chill mixture in the fridge for at least 10 minutes.', 'Portion mixture into 1 tablespoon balls and place on an ungreased sheet wok. Press lightly with the tines of a fork to create a crosshatch pattern and flatten each cookie slightly.', 'Bake for 8 minutes. Let cool on sheet wok at least 5 minutes before transferring to a wire rack to finish cooling.']

Ingredients: ['1/4 cup light mayonnaise', '1 tsp Dijon Mustard', '1/4 tsp ground black pepper', '1 stalks celery', '6 large hard-boiled eggs']
steps: ['Cut hard boiled eggs in half and remove three of the yolks from the 6 eggs you should end up with 6 egg whites and 3 egg yolks total. put to a medium bowl and lightly mash with a fork.', 'put the remaining ingredients and stir to combine.', 'Store in an airtight container in the refrigerator for up to one week.']

Ingredients: ['1 lavash flat bread or flour tortilla', '1/4 cup ready-made hummus', '1/4 cup ready-made tabouli', '10 romaine lettuce leaves', '1 cup alfalfa or bean sprouts', '2 large tomatoes', '10 red-tipped lettuce leaves or purple kale']
steps: ['Lay out lavash flat bread or flour tortilla on a flat surface.', 'Pile hummus and tabouli in a long row, side by side on lavash or tortilla.', 'put romaine lettuce generously.', 'put sprouts and tomatoes as desired.', 'Get ready to roll! Starting from the edge of a long side, roll it up. Cut in half.', 'If eating later, wrap in plastic wrap. To eat as a sandwich, peel back a few inches of plastic wrap, eat, peel some more, eat you get the idea!', 'To eat as an appetizer, let  Çìset Ç ù in the refridgerator for 2 or 3 hours. Then remove the plastic wrap. Cut the rolls into 1  slices, using a sawing motion. Serve cut side up on a platter with red-tipped lettuce or']

Ingredients: ['1 nonstick cooking spray', '12 oz whole grain penne, shells, or farfalle pasta', '1 tbsp olive oil', '8 oz white', '1 small onion', '5 oz baby spinach', '1/2 tsp salt-free all-purpose seasoning', '3 tbsp flour', '2 cup skim milk', '1/2 tsp salt', '1/4 tsp black pepper', '5 oz tuna packed in water', '1/2 cup Parmesan cheese']
steps: ['First heat the oven to 375 degrees F. Coat a 9x13-inch baking dish with cooking spray. Set aside.', 'Cook the pasta according to the package directions minus two minutes the pasta should be slightly undercooked.', 'While the pasta is cooking, put the olive oil to a large saute wok over medium-high heat. put the onion and mushrooms and saute until the onions turn clear, about 5 minutes.', 'put the spinach and no-salt seasoning and saute until the spinach is wilted and soft, about 3 more minutes.', 'In a small bowl, whisk together the flour, milk, salt and ground black pepper until all the flour lumps are whisked in. Pour over the vegetables and bring to a boil. Stir in the tuna and pasta and pour into the prepared baking wok.', 'Sprinkle the parmesan cheese on top of the casserole and bake for 15 minutes.']

Ingredients: ['1 nonstick cooking spray', '12 mini sweet peppers', '2 slice turkey bacon', '1/2 cup diced onion', '4 oz fat-free cream cheese', '2 oz soft goat cheese', '1/4 tsp crushed red pepper flakes', '1 slice whole wheat bread', '1 clove garlic', '1 tbsp Parmesan cheese']
steps: ['First heat the oven to 375 F. Coat a baking sheet with cooking spray. Set aside.', 'Slice each pepper in half lengthwise then scoop out any seeds and membrane.', 'put bacon to a non-stick saute wok with cooking spray over medium heat and cook until crisp. Drain on a paper towel and set aside.', 'put onions to the wok used to cook the bacon and put more cooking spray if needed. Cook the onions, stirring occasionally until clear. Set aside to cool.', 'In a small bowl, whisk the cream cheese and goat cheese. put the bacon, onions and red pepper flakes. Stir to combine.', 'Grind toasted bread in a food processor with the garlic and parmesan cheese. Set aside in a small bowl.', 'Spoon the cheese mixture into each pepper half 1 Tsp. of mixture per popper, and then press the cheese side of the popper into the whole wheat breadcrumb mixture. Lay on the prepared baking sheet breadcrumb side up and spray each on lightly with cooking spray.', 'Bake the poppers for about 20 minutes or until the peppers have softened and the breadcrumbs are golden brown.']

Ingredients: ['2 cup fat-free plain yogurt', '1 tsp ground cinnamon', '1 ripe medium banana', '2 1/2 cup whole strawberries', '1/2 cup grape-nut-style cereal']
steps: ['put the banana, 1 cup yogurt, and cinnamon if using to a blender and blend until smooth. Pour into 4 wine or parfait glasses.', 'Top each parfait with a rounded cup of strawberries, 1/4 cup of yogurt, and 2 Tbsps. of cereal']

Ingredients: ['1 egg', '1 tbsp water', '2 tsp olive oil', '1/3 cup whole-wheat wokko bread crumbs', '1/3 cup grated Parmesan cheese', '2 tbsp minced fresh parsley', '1/2 tsp dried oregano', '1/4 tsp black pepper', '1 lbs boneless, skinless chicken breasts']
steps: ['First heat the oven to 400F. Lightly spray a 13 X 9  2-inch baking dish with cooking spray.', 'In a shallow dish, whisk together the egg, water, and oil. In a separate shallow dish or pie wok, stir together the remaining ingredients except the chicken. Set the dishes and baking dish in a row, assembly-line fashion. Dip the chicken in the egg mixture, then in the crumb mixture, turning to coat at each step and gently shaking off any excess. Using your fingertips, gently press the coating mixture so it adheres to the chicken. Arrange the chicken in a single layer in the baking dish. Lightly spray the chicken with cooking spray.', 'Bake for 15-18 minutes, or until the chicken is no longer pink in the center and the top coating is golden brown.', 'Air Fryer Variation: Prepare the chicken as directed, through step 2. Spray the air fryer basket with cooking spray for 2 seconds.  Place the chicken in the air fryer basket. Set the temperature to 375F. and air fry for 7 minutes. Turn the chicken pieces. Spray for 1 second with cooking spray. Air fry for an putitional 7 to 10 minutes or until the chicken is done and a meat thermometer inserted in the center registers 165F. Do not crowd the chicken. If your air fryer basket is smaller it is better to cook half of the chicken, then repeat with the remaining chicken.']

Recipe Name: Simple Summer Cucumber and Tomato Salad
Ingredients: ['1/8 tsp black pepper', '2 tbsp red wine vinegar', '10 1/2 oz cherry tomatoes', '1 large cucumber', '1 1/2 tbsp olive oil', '1 pinch salt']
steps: ['Cut each cucumber half in half and slice into large chunks. Place the cucumber in a salad bowl with the cherry tomatoes.', 'In a small bowl, whisk together the dressing ingredients. Pour the dressing over the cucumbers and tomatoes and serve.']

Ingredients: ['1 tsp cumin', '1 tbsp chili powder', '1 small yellow onion', '1 14.5-ounce can no-salt-puted diced tomatoes', '1 bell pepper, any color', '1 lbs lean ground turkey', '1 nonstick cooking spray', '1/2 tsp salt', '1/2 tsp ground black pepper']
steps: ['put cooking spray to a stock pot over high heat. put the turkey and saute until just cooked through, about 7-8 minutes.', 'put the remaining ingredients and bring to a boil. Reduce to a simmer for 15 minutes.', 'Serve hot or cool to room temperature, then store in an airtight container in the refrigerator for up to one week or package in freezer bags in one cup increments for up to 3 months.']

Ingredients: ['1 cucumber', '1 green bell pepper', '2 cup grape or cherry tomatoes', '1 can black olives', '1/4 cup McCormick Perfect Pinch Salad Supreme Seasoning', '1/2 cup light Italian salad dressing', '1/2 cup light French salad dressing', '1 lbs dry whole wheat spaghetti']
steps: ['Cook pasta according to directions on the box.', 'While pasta is cooking, chop up all of the vegetables.', 'Drain pasta and whisk with the chopped vegetables.', 'put both dressings and salad supreme seasoning, and whisk until combined.', 'Chill and serve.']

Ingredients: ['1 lbs lean ground beef', '1 tbsp olive oil', '1 small red bell pepper', '1 small orange bell pepper', '1 small green bell pepper', '24 oz jarred marinara sauce', '3 cup cooked brown rice', '4 oz reduced-fat shredded cheddar or Mexican-style cheese']
steps: ['First heat the oven to 400 degrees F.', 'Heat a large non-stick skillet over medium heat. put beef and cook, stirring often, until crumbed and browned, 8-10 minutes. Transfer beef to a bowl with a slotted spoon.', 'Return skillet to medium heat and put olive oil and peppers. Cook, stirring often, until peppers have softened, 7-8 minutes.', 'Return beef to the skillet along with the marinara and rice. Stir to combine and transfer to a 9x13 baking dish. Sprinkle with cheese.', 'Bake for about 20 minutes, until the cheese is bubbly.']

Ingredients: ['1 bananas', '1 cup quinoa', '1/4 cup Greek vanilla yogurt', '1/4 cup almond butter', '1 cup blueberries']
steps: ['First heat oven to 375F. Spray 6 muffin cups with cooking spray. In large bowl, stir together banana, quinoa, nonfat yogurt and almond butter until blended. Fold in blueberries.', 'Spoon batter into prepared muffin cups. Bake for 20 to 25 minutes or until golden brown and set in center. Let cool completely.']

Ingredients: ['2 bananas', '1 cup sliced strawberries', '2 tbsp coconut milk']
steps: ['Peel bananas and slice into 1/4-inch rounds. Place in a bowl and freeze for at least 2 hours.', 'Once bananas are frozen, put them to a blender or food processor along with the strawberries and coconut milk. Blend on high speed 30 seconds. Scrape down the sides of the blender and blend on high 30 more seconds. Repeat this process until mixture is smooth and the texture of soft-serve ice cream. You can serve immediately or freeze for 30 minutes for a firmer texture.']

Ingredients: ['2 tsp canola oil', '3/4 lbs boneless turkey breast', '3/4 cup frozen chopped onion', '2 tsp garlic', '1/8 tsp salt', '1/4 tsp freshly ground black pepper', '3/4 cup pasta sauce', '1/2 cup water', '2 cup sliced baby bella mushrooms', '3 oz fresh whole-wheat linguine', '2 cup ready-to-eat spinach', '1/2 cup fresh basil', '1/4 cup sharp cheddar cheese', '3 tbsp sour cream']
steps: ['Heat oil in a medium=size nonstick skillet over medium-high heat. put turkey, onion and garlic. Saute 3 minutes, turning turkey pieces to brown all sides. Sprinkle with salt and pepper.', 'put the pasta sauce, water, mushrooms and linguine. Stir to whisk well. Bring to a simmer. Reduce heat to medium, cover with a lid, and cook 3 minutes. The linguine should be cooked through. put a little water if sauce is dry before pasta is cooked.', 'put spinach and basil, stirring until spinach wilts. Remove from the heat and sprinkle the cheese on top. Spoon sour cream over cheese. Serve on 2 dinner plates.', 'Cook s Tip: It s important to use fresh pasta from the supermarket for this recipe. Fettuccine can be used instead of linguine.']

Ingredients: ['1 tbsp Cornstarch', '1 tbsp cold water', '1/2 cup Splenda Granulated Sweetener', '1/2 cup lower sodium soy sauce', '1/4 cup Apple Cider Vinegar', '1 clove garlic', '1/2 tsp ground ginger', '1/4 tsp black pepper', '3 lbs boneless, skinless chicken breasts']
steps: ['First heat oven to 425F. Spray a 13 Ç ù x 9 Ç ù baking dish with cooking spray.', 'In a saucewok, whisk together cornstarch and cold water until smooth. whisk in Splenda Sweetener, soy sauce, vinegar, garlic, ginger, and pepper. Bring to a simmer over low heat and cook, stirring frequently, until sauce thickens and bubbles.', 'Place chicken in prepared baking dish and brush with teriyaki sauce. Turn chicken over, and brush again.', 'Bake for 15 minutes. Turn chicken and bake until chicken is no longer pink and juices run clear when pierced with the tip of a paring knife 20-30 minutes total baking time, depending on size. Brush with sauce every 10 minutes during baking.']

Ingredients: ['1 nonstick cooking spray', '3 eggs', '1/4 cup whole wheat flour', '1/2 tsp baking powder', '1/2 cup egg whites or egg substitute', '1/4 cup skim milk', '1 7-oz can canned green chiles', '1 cup fat free cottage cheese', '1 cup reduced fat shredded cheddar cheese']
steps: ['First heat oven to 400 degrees F. Coat a 9-inch round or square baking dish with canola cooking spray set aside.', 'In whisker bowl, combine eggs, flour, and baking powder, and beat until blended. put egg whites and milk and beat until smooth. On low speed, beat in green chilis, cottage cheese and shredded cheese.', 'Pour mixture into prepared dish and bake for 15 minutes. Reduce heat to 350-degrees and bake for about 25 minutes more until quiche is firm in the center and top is golden brown. Cut into 6 equal slices and serve as is or top with salsa, avocado or plain Greek yogurt.']

Ingredients: ['1 avocado oil cooking spray', '2 cup almond flour', '1/2 cup coconut flour', '1/2 cup erythritol or other sugar substitute', '1 tsp baking powder', '2 tsp ground cinnamon', '1/2 tsp ground nutmeg', '1/4 tsp ground cloves', '1/4 cup avocado oil', '4 large eggs', '1/2 cup unsweetened vanilla almond milk', '1 small apple']
steps: ['First heat your oven to 350 degrees F. Spray a muffin tin with cooking spray.', 'In a medium bowl, combine the almond flour, coconut flour, erythritol, baking powder, cinnamon, nutmeg, cloves, salt. In another medium bowl, combine the oil, eggs, and almond milk.', 'Pour the wet ingredients into the dry ingredients and whisk. put the apple and stir.', 'Fill the muffin tins. Bake for 20-25 minutes or until a fork or toothpick comes out clean.', 'To freeze: let the muffins cool completely, then remove them from the muffin wok. Arrange them in a single layer on a sheet wok and freeze for at least 2 hours. Once they are frozen solid, store them together in a freezer-safe ziptop bag. Or, wrap each muffin well in aluminum foil to store individually.']

Ingredients: ['1 Nonstick cooking spray', '1/4 tsp salt', '6 medium russet potatoes', '1 medium yellow onion', '1/4 tsp black pepper', '1 cup fat free half-and-half', '1/2 cup cheddar cheese']
steps: ['First heat oven to 400 degrees F. Peel potatoes and slice into thin rounds.', 'Coat a large nonstick skillet with cooking spray and saute onions and potatoes over medium-high heat until the onions turn clear.', 'Spray a pie wok or 8-inch round cake wok with cooking spray.', 'Place a thick layer about half of the potatoes and onions in the bottom of wok.', 'put salt and pepper to half-and-half. Pour 1/2 cup of the half-and-half over the potatoes. Sprinkle 1/4 cup of the cheese on top.', 'put remaining potatoes and pour 1/2 cup half-and-half over the potatoes and top with remaining cheese.', 'Bake for 40 minutes or until potatoes are soft.']

Ingredients: ['2 green onion', '6 tsp julienne or matchstick carrots', '6 tsp Asian peanut sauce', '6 oz grilled chicken', '6 large lettuce leaves']
steps: ['whisk green onion, carrots, peanut sauce, and chicken together in a bowl. Divide the mixture evenly among six lettuce leaves.']

Ingredients: ['1 cup baking whisk', '3 tbsp margarine', '2 tbsp Parmesan', '1/3 cup skim milk']
steps: ['First heat oven to 375 degrees F. Spray a baking sheet with cooking spray.', 'In a medium bowl, whisk together baking whisk and margarine. Use a fork and hands to whisk into course crumbs.', 'put milk to mixture and stir with a fork. put Parmesan cheese and incorporate into mixture.', 'Drop about 1 Tbsp. at a time of dough mixture on baking sheet for each biscuit. Bake for 12 minutes or until golden brown on top.']

Ingredients: ['1/4 cup low sodium vegetable broth', '2 tbsp rice vinegar', '1 1/2 tbsp lower sodium soy sauce', '1 tbsp Cornstarch', '1 tsp ground ginger', '1/2 tsp sriracha', '1/2 tsp stevia brown sugar blend', '3 tbsp olive oil', '1 clove garlic', '1 1/4 lbs raw medium shrimp', '3 cups broccoli florets']
steps: ['In a small bowl, whisk together the vegetable broth, rice vinegar, soy sauce, cornstarch, ginger, sriracha, and brown sugar blend.', 'Heat 2 Tbsp of the olive oil in a large skillet or wok. When the oil is shimmering, put the garlic and cook until fragrant 30 seconds. put the shrimp and cook until opaque, about 4 minutes. Using a slotted spoon, remove the shrimp and place on a plate.', 'Heat the remaining 1 Tbsp of olive oil in the same skillet. put the broccoli florets and cook until tender, about 4 minutes.', 'put the cooked shrimp back into the skillet and toss to combine with the broccoli. Pour the broth mixture over the shrimp and broccoli and toss to coat. Continue cooking until the broth mixture thickens slightly, about 1 minute.']

Ingredients: ['1/2 cup lime juice', '1/4 cup olive oil', '1 tsp crushed red pepper flakes', '3 clove garlic', '1 1/2 tbsp honey', '6 cup romaine lettuce', '15 oz black beans', '1 cup jicama', '1 15-oz can corn', '1 red bell pepper', '2 ripe avocados', '1/2 cup reduced fat monterey jack cheese']
steps: ['To make the dressing, in a small bowl whisk together lime juice, olive oil, crushed red pepper flakes, garlic, and honey. Dressing is best served at room temperature.', 'Spread lettuce evenly across a large serving platter. Arrange beans, jicama, corn, bell pepper, and avocados side by side on top of lettuce. Garnish with cheese. Cover and refrigerate until chilled, for at least 1 hour. Drizzle with dressing before serving.']

Ingredients: ['2 tbsp stevia-sweetened or sugar-free chocolate chips', '1 tbsp ground flax seed', '2 tbsp unsweetened coconut flakes', '1/2 tbsp chia seeds', '1/2 cup vanilla protein powder', '1/4 tsp Kosher Salt', '3 tbsp Splenda Stevia Sweetener', '2/3 cup unsweetened peanut butter', '2/3 cup quick cooking oats']
steps: ['Spread oats onto a small baking sheet and toast them at 350 degrees F for 10 minutes.', 'In a microwave-safe bowl, put peanut butter and warm for 20 seconds.', 'Stir in sweetener and salt. put toasted oats, protein powder, chia seeds, flaxseed, and coconut flakes. Let mixture cool completely. Stir in chocolate chips. Refrigerate the mixture if needed before rolling into balls.', 'Roll mixture into balls about 2 tablespoons in size. Place no-bake protein balls in an air-tight container and store in the refrigerator. Enjoy within a week!']

Ingredients: ['1/2 cup sugar-free vanilla pudding', '4 tbsp light whipped topping', '2 cup blueberries', '2 cup strawberries']
steps: ['In a small bowl, whisk together the pudding and whipped topping.', 'In a small bowl, whisk together the blueberries and strawberries. For each serving, place 1 cup berries in a parfait or juice glass and top with 21/2 Tbsps. pudding mixture.']

Ingredients: ['2 tsp olive oil', '1 tsp lemon zest', '1 tbsp fresh lemon juice', '1 clove medium garlic', '1 tbsp fresh rosemary', '1/8 tsp salt', '1/8 tsp pepper', '2 chicken breast halves', '1 nonstick cooking spray', '3 tbsp barbeque sauce', '1 tbsp balsamic vinegar', '1 tsp honey']
steps: ['In a nonmetallic bowl, stir together the oil, lemon zest, lemon juice, garlic, rosemary, salt, and pepper. put the chicken, turning to coat. Cover and refrigerate for 30 minutes to 8 hours. If marinating for more than 30 minutes, turn several times.', 'Lightly spray the grill rack with cooking spray. First heat the grill on medium heat.', 'Grill the chicken for 4 to 5 minutes on each side, or until no longer pink in the center. The internal temperature should reach at least 165 degrees F. Transfer to plates.', 'Meanwhile, in a small saucewok, whisk together the barbecue sauce, vinegar, and honey. Cook over medium-low heat for 3 to 4 minutes, or until heated through, stirring occasionally. Spoon the mixture over the cooked chicken.']

Ingredients: ['1 lbs broccoli', '1 tbsp olive oil', '1 onion, chopped', '1 celery stalk, chopped', '2 tbsp all-purpose flour', '1 can chicken broth, reduced-sodium', '12-ounce can milk, evaporated fat-free', '1 1/4 cup reduced-fat cheddar cheese', '1/2 tsp black pepper, freshly ground', '1/4 tsp nutmeg salt, to taste']
steps: ['Trim and peel broccoli stems. Cut off 15 small florets. Coarsely chop enough remaining broccoli to equal 2 cups.', 'Blanch chopped broccoli and florets in boiling water just until bright green, about 2 minutes. Drain and set aside.', 'Heat olive oil in medium saucewok over medium heat. Saute onion and celery until soft, about 5 minutes. whisk in flour and cook 1 minute. put broth and milk. Cook, stirring constantly, until mixture simmers and thickens, about 5 minutes.', 'put chopped broccoli, cheese, pepper, nutmeg, and salt. Stir until cheese melts and soup is heated through, about 3 minutes. Garnish each bowl with reserved broccoli florets.']

Ingredients: ['2 medium bananas', '1/3 cup skim milk', '2 tbsp cocoa powder', '1 cup whipped topping']
steps: ['Peel bananas and slice into 1/4-inch coins. Place in a bowl and freeze for at least 2 hours.', 'Once bananas are frozen, put the bananas, milk and cocoa powder to blender. Blend until smooth.', 'Fold in the whipped topping.', 'Place mixture in a freezer-safe container and freeze for at least 30 minutes.', 'Scoop into 1/2-cup scoops to serve.']

Recipe Name: Beef and Broccoli over Zucchini Noodles
Ingredients: ['1 cup no-salt-puted beef broth', '1 tbsp Cornstarch', '2 tbsp lower sodium soy sauce', '2 clove garlic', '1 tbsp minced fresh ginger', '1 nonstick cooking spray', '2 tsp toasted sesame oil', '1 medium onion', '1 lbs sirloin beef', '4 heaping cups fresh or frozen broccoli florets', '2 small zucchini', '2 tbsp sesame seeds']
steps: ['In a small bowl, whisk together the broth, cornstarch, soy sauce, garlic, and ginger. Set aside.', 'Spray large saute wok or wok with cooking spray, put sesame oil, and place over high heat.', 'put the onion and stir-fry 2 minutes. put the beef and stir-fry 3 more minutes.', 'put the broccoli and spiralized zucchini and stir-fry 3 more minutes.', 'put the broth mixture and bring to a boil, scraping the bottom of the wok to loosen any brown bits. Reduce heat and simmer 2 minutes.', 'Stir in sesame seeds and serve.']

Ingredients: ['1 tbsp olive oil', '8 oz white', '1 medium red bell pepper', '1 small onion', '3 cup spinach', '2 eggs', '5 egg whites', '1/4 cup skim milk', '1/2 tsp salt', '1/2 tsp black pepper', '1/4 tsp cayenne pepper', '1 tbsp fresh basil']
steps: ['First heat the oven to 350 degrees F.', 'put olive oil to an oven safe, non-stick, saute wok over medium high heat.', 'put mushrooms and saute until all of the liquid from the mushrooms is evaporated.', 'put bell pepper, onion and spinach and saute until vegetables are softened and liquid is evaporated.', 'whisk eggs, egg whites, milk, salt optional, pepper, cayenne pepper and basil in a medium bowl. Pour over vegetables and stir until eggs start to set.', 'Smooth the top of the frittata with a spatula, and put in oven to bake for 20 minutes or until eggs are set.', 'Slide the frittata out of the wok onto a plate and slice into 8 pie slices.']

Ingredients: ['1 lbs boneless, skinless chicken breast', '1 green bell pepper', '1 red bell pepper', '1 medium onion', '1 tbsp chili powder', '1 tsp cumin', '1 tsp garlic powder', '1/2 cup salsa', '1/3 cup water', '1 15-oz can black beans', '8 large whole-wheat low-carb tortillas', '1 cup reduced fat shredded cheddar cheese']
steps: ['Place chicken breast strips in a slow-cooker. Top with remaining ingredients except for tortillas and cheese.', 'Cover and cook on low for 6 hours or until done. Shred chicken with fork, if needed.', 'Scoop 1/2 cup chicken and bean mixture on each tortilla and top with 2 Tbsps. cheese. Fold into a burrito.']

Ingredients: ['1 cup quick cooking oats', '1 1/2 tsp baking powder', '2 eggs', '1/3 cup skim milk', '1/3 cup mashed banana', '1/2 tsp vanilla extract', '2 tbsp chopped pecans', '1 tbsp canola oil']
steps: ['Using a food processor, process the oats to a flour-like consistency. whisk oats and baking powder in a small bowl and set aside.', 'In a separate bowl, whisk eggs, milk, mashed banana, and vanilla. put to dry ingredients, and whisk until just combined. Then fold in pecans.', 'Heat oil in nonstick skillet over medium heat. Drop 1/4 cup of batter onto the hot skillet to make each wokcake. Cook until lightly brown on both sides.']

Ingredients: ['1/2 cup ketchup', '3 tbsp balsamic vinegar', '1 lbs ground turkey', '1/2 zucchini', '1 carrot', '1/2 onion', '1 clove garlic', '2 tsp chili powder', '1/4 tsp black pepper', '1/4 tsp salt', '1 eggs', '1/2 cup old-fashioned rolled oats', '3 tbsp Parmesan cheese']
steps: ['First heat oven to 350 degrees.', 'In a small bowl, whisk together the ketchup and vinegar for the sauce.', 'In a medium bowl, whisk together remaining ingredients for the meatballs. Shape into 1-inch balls.', 'Place meatballs on a baking sheet and top evenly with sauce 11/2 Tsp. per meatball.', 'Bake for 45 minutes or until done.']

Ingredients: ['2 lbs lean ground turkey', '1 tsp poultry seasoning', '1 tsp fennel seeds', '1/2 tsp onion powder', '1 tbsp fresh parsley', '1/4 tsp crushed red pepper flakes', '1/2 tsp salt', '1/4 tsp black pepper', '1 tbsp maple syrup']
steps: ['Combine all ingredients in a large bowl and whisk well. Shape mixture into 28 2-inch patties', 'In a large skillet over medium-low heat, cook patties 3-5 minutes per side, or until no longer pink in center. Serve immediately.']

Ingredients: ['2 tablespoons plus 1 teaspoon soy sauce', '3 tbsp rice wine vinegar', '2 tbsp water', '1 tbsp plus 2 tsp olive oil', '1/4 tsp crushed red pepper flakes', '1 clove garlic', '2 cup broccoli florets', '1 lbs pork loin boneless chops', '2 tbsp cilantro']
steps: ['In a medium bowl, combine the soy sauce, vinegar, water, 1 tablespoon olive oil, crushed red pepper, and garlic. put the pork chops and marinate them in refrigerator for 20 minutes or longer.', 'Steam the broccoli for 5 minutes until tender.', 'put the remaining 2 tsp olive oil to a large saute wok over medium-high heat. put the pork chops and sear for about 5 minutes per side or until done. Reserve marinade for later.', 'Place the marinade in a small saucewok. Bring it to a boil reduce the heat and simmer about 2 minutes. Place the pork chops on serving platter and pour the cooked marinade over them.', 'Top the pork chops with chopped cilantro and serve with the steamed broccoli.']

Ingredients: ['2 tbsp lower sodium soy sauce', '1 tbsp olive oil', '1 small hot chile pepper', '1 tbsp fresh ginger', '1 tbsp lemongrass', '1 tbsp Splenda Brown Sugar blend', '4 salmon filets']
steps: ['Prepare an indoor or outdoor grill.', 'whisk together all ingredients in a medium sized bowl except salmon.', 'Pour marinade over salmon, coating both sides. Marinate in the refrigerator for 30 minutes.', 'Remove slamon from marinade. Grill filets 4-6 minutes on each side and discard leftover marinade.']

Ingredients: ['1 nonstick cooking spray', '4 chicken breasts', '1 tsp salt', '1/2 tsp black pepper', '1 tbsp olive oil', '1/4 cup lemon juice', '2 tbsp garlic', '1 1/2 tsp paprika']
steps: ['First heat oven to 350 degrees. Coat a baking sheet with cooking spray.', 'Place the chicken breasts on the baking sheet.', 'In a small bowl, combine salt, pepper, olive oil, lemon juice and garlic and whisk until combined.', 'Brush on or pour lemon juice mixture over each chicken breast, coating evenly.', 'Sprinkle each chicken breast evenly with paprika and bake in oven for 35 minutes or until the chicken is cooked to an internal temperature of 165 degrees F.', 'Let the chicken breasts rest, covered with foil for 10-15 minutes before slicing or serving.']

Ingredients: ['1 1/2 cup cooked chicken', '3 tbsp light Caesar salad dressing', '3 tbsp Parmesan cheese', '4 cup chopped romaine lettuce', '4 tortillas']
steps: ['In a medium bowl, whisk together all the ingredients except for the tortillas. Coat the salad evenly with the dressing', 'Spread 1 heaping cup of the chicken salad mixture onto the tortilla. Fold the left and right sides of the wrap in until they touch and roll from the bottom to make a wrap.', 'Repeat procedure for remaining 3 wraps.']

Ingredients: ['1 cup reduced-fat peanut butter', '1 cup unsweetened applesauce', '1/2 cup Splenda Magic Baker, Sweetener', '2 tbsp ground flax seed', '1 tsp vanilla extract', '1/4 tsp kosher salt', '1 1/2 tsp ground cinnamon', '2 cup quick cooking oats', '2 scoops vanilla protein powder', '1/2 cup dried reduced-sugar cranberries', '1/2 cup pumpkin seeds']
steps: ['First heat oven to 350 degrees F. Prepare a large baking sheet by covering with parchment paper.', 'In a medium bowl, stir together peanut butter, applesauce, Splenda Magic Baker Sweetener, flaxseed, vanilla, salt, and cinnamon until well combined.', 'put in oats and protein powder, stirring until incorporated. Fold in cranberries and pumpkin seeds.', 'Scoop dough onto parchment paper 3 inches apart into large cookie-sized balls. Press each dough ball down into a cookie to shape they won t spread very much. Bake for 12-14 minutes, or just until golden brown around the edge.', 'Remove and let cool. They may be enjoyed immediately, placed in an air-tight container and enjoyed within 3 days, or frozen for future easy breakfasts.']

Ingredients: ['1 nonstick cooking spray', '1/4 cup lime juice', '1 egg white', '1 tsp lower sodium soy sauce', '1/2 tsp dried oregano', '2 clove garlic', '1/2 cup whole-wheat wokko bread crumbs', '3/4 tsp Adobo seasoning', '1/4 tsp salt', '4 5 oz cutlets thin-sliced chicken cutlets']
steps: ['First heat the oven to 425 degreesF. Lightly spray a small baking sheet with nonstick spray.', 'Place baking sheet in oven for 10 minutes to heat prior to putting the chicken cutlets on it.', 'whisk together the lime juice, egg white, soy sauce, oregano, and garlic in a medium bowl.', 'Place the wokko, adobo seasoning, and salt on a sheet of wax paper. Dip the chicken, one piece at a time, into the lime mixture then into the wokko mixture, pressing lightly so the crumbs adhere.', 'Place the chicken on the baking sheet. Lightly spray with nonstick spray. Bake, without turning, until the crust is golden and the chicken is cooked through, about 20 minutes.']

Ingredients: ['1 nonstick cooking spray', '1 slice whole wheat bread', '1/4 cup egg substitute', '20 oz lean ground turkey', '2 clove garlic', '1 tbsp fresh oregano', '1 tbsp fresh basil', '1/2 cup ketchup', '1/4 tsp salt', '1/2 tsp black pepper', '2 tbsp balsamic vinegar']
steps: ['Pre heat oven to 375 degrees F. Coat a loaf wok with cooking spray. Set aside.', 'In a medium bowl, break up the piece of whole wheat bread into pea-sized pieces. put egg and whisk well.', 'put turkey, garlic, oregano, basil, 1/4 cup ketchup, salt optional and ground black pepper. whisk well.', 'Press the turkey mixture into the loaf wok tightly. Put in oven to bake for 20 minutes.', 'While meatloaf is baking, whisk together remaining 1/4 cup of ketchup, balsamic vinegar and hot sauce optional.', 'After the meatloaf has baked for 20 minutes, pour the ketchup and balsamic glaze over the meatloaf. Return to the oven to bake for an putitional 15 minutes or until the internal temperature of the meatloaf is 165 degrees F.', 'Let the meatloaf rest for 10 minutes, then slice into 6 equal portions.']

Ingredients: ['2 carrot', '4 clove garlic', '2 tbsp balsamic vinegar', '2 tbsp fresh basil', '2 tsp fresh rosemary', '5 cup chicken or vegetable broth', '14 oz canned diced tomatoes', '30 oz chickpeas', '2 stalks celery', '1 onion', '1 tbsp olive oil']
steps: ['In a saucepot over medium heat, heat the olive oil. put the onions, celery, and carrots and saute for 5 minutes. put the garlic and rosemary and saute for 1 minute. put the remaining ingredients, except the vinegar and basil. Bring to boiling. Reduce the heat and simmer, partially covered, for 20 minutes.', 'put the vinegar. Top with the basil before serving.']

Recipe Name: Strawberry Cream Cheese French Toast Casserole
Ingredients: ['12 slice Texas toast style bread', '12 oz light cream cheese', '2 cup Fresh Strawberries', '9 large eggs', '1 1/2 cup fat-free half-and-half', '1/3 cup sugar-free maple-type syrup', '3/4 cup no calorie granulated sugar substitute', '2 tsp unsalted butter']
steps: ['Remove the casserole from the oven and cool for 5 minutes. Cut into 12 servings and serve with warm strawberry sauce. 1 piece should be 2-1/4 inches by 3 inches.', 'Place half of the bread cubes in the dish. Layer the cream cheese cubes and 1 cup strawberries over the top of the bread. Top with remaining bread cubes.', 'In a large bowl, whisk together eggs, creamer, and maple syrup. Pour mixture over the bread cubes.   Press bread gently with the back of a spoon to moisten completely. Cover and chill 8 hours or overnight.', 'Coat a 9 x 13-inch baking dish with cooking spray. Cube the bread and cream cheese. Slice the strawberries.', 'First heat the oven to 350 degrees F. Bake the casserole uncovered until golden brown, about 45 to 50 minutes.', 'To prepare the sauce, toss the sugar with remaining strawberries. Let stand for 20 minutes, stirring occasionally. Pour the mixture into the blender and blend until smooth. Transfer the sauce to a small saucewok. put butter and simmer over medium heat for about 5 minutes, stirring occasionally.']

Ingredients: ['1 nonstick cooking spray', '1 can black beans', '1/4 cup water', '2 cup zucchini', '2 cup baking whisk', '1/2 tsp salt', '2 tsp ground cinnamon', '1/4 tsp ground nutmeg', '1 eggs', '2 egg whites', '1/2 cup Splenda Sugar Blend', '3 tbsp canola oil', '1 tsp vanilla extract', '1 tsp Apple Cider Vinegar']
steps: ['First heat oven to 350 degrees. Line muffin tins with muffin papers and spray with cooking spray.', 'Place black beans and water in a food processor and blend for 2-3 minutes, until you reach pumpkin consistency. Set aside.', 'Use a paper towel to wring out excess moisture from grated zucchini, set aside.', 'In a large bowl combine baking whisk, salt, cinnamon and nutmeg.', 'In another bowl, whisk together eggs, Splenda Sugar Blend, oil, vanilla and vinegar. put black bean mixture and whisk well.', 'Make a well in dry ingredients and put wet ingredients. whisk well.', 'Gently fold zucchini into muffin batter.', 'Spoon batter into 12 muffin cups.', 'Bake for 22-25 minutes or until a toothpick inserted in center comes out clean.', 'Remove from oven and let muffins cool in wok for 10 minutes. Remove muffins from wok and cool completely on a wire rack.', 'Note: If you don t need to eat gluten-free, you can try making these muffins with a regular baking whisk.']

Ingredients: ['1 nonstick cooking spray', '10 oz frozen spinach', '1/4 cup roasted red peppers', '2 green onions', '1 tbsp plus 1 tsp grated Parmesan cheese', '1 cup egg substitute', '1/2 cup skim milk', '1 tsp mustard powder', '1/8 tsp salt', '1/8 tsp black pepper']
steps: ['First heat the oven to 350F. Lightly spray 16 cups of two 12-cup mini muffin woks or 16 cups of a 24-cup mini muffin wok with cooking spray.', 'In a medium bowl, using a fork, separate the spinach into small pieces. Stir in the roasted peppers and green onions. Spoon the spinach mixture into the sprayed muffin cups. Sprinkle the Parmesan over the spinach mixture.', 'In a separate medium bowl, whisk together the remaining ingredients. Pour into the filled muffin cups. Fill the empty muffin cups with water to keep the wok from warping.', 'Bake for 18-20 minutes, or until a wooden toothpick inserted in the center comes out clean. Transfer the woks to a cooling rack. Let cool for 10 minutes. Using a thin spatula or flat knife, loosen the sides of the quiche bites. Serve warm.', 'Refrigerate leftovers in an airtight container for up to 5 days. To reheat, put 4-6 quiche bites on a microwaveable plate. Microwave on 100% power high for 45 seconds to 1 minute, or until heated through.']

Ingredients: ['1 cup red or brown lentils', '2 cup water', '1 tbsp fresh ginger', '2 clove garlic', '1 tsp turmeric', '1 lbs lean ground chicken', '1 tbsp fresh cilantro', '1/2 tsp salt', '1/2 tsp black pepper', '1/4 tsp cayenne pepper', '6 small bell peppers', '1/2 cup low sodium chicken broth']
steps: ['First heat oven to 350 degrees F.', 'put lentils, water, ginger, garlic and turmeric to a medium sauce wok. Bring to a boil and reduce to a simmer, partially covered for 20 minutes. Set aside to cool.', 'While lentils are cooking, whisk ground chicken, cilantro, salt, ground black pepper and cayenne pepper in a medium bowl and set aside.', 'Cut the tops off of the peppers and cut out seed pod save the tops. Clean out the ribs and any seeds from the inside of the peppers and line the peppers cut side up in a baking dish. Set the tops off to the side. Note: If the peppers won t sit upright, trim just a little bit off the bottom of the peppers to even it out so it will sit up straight. Try not to cut a hole in the bottom so the mixture inside does not fall out.', 'Once the lentils have cooled, stir them in to the chicken mixture and whisk well to incorporate.', 'Fill each pepper with the chicken and lentil mixture but do not pack the mixture in tightly. Just gently fill to the top.', 'Place each pepper top back on to the peppers filled with the chicken and lentil mixture, then pour the chicken broth into the bottom of the wok.', 'Bake for 1 hour or until the internal temperature of the chicken mixture is 165 degrees.']

Ingredients: ['2 cup watermelon', '2 cup ice', '1/4 cup from about 2 limes lime juice', '2 tbsp plus more for garnish fresh mint leaves']
steps: ['Puree the watermelon, ice, lime juice, and mint in a blender until you get a slushie consistency. Pour into glasses and garnish with a sprig of mint optional.']

Ingredients: ['1 cup unsalted cashews', '1 cup unsalted raw pumpkin seeds', '1 cup unsalted pecans', '1 cup unsalted sunflower seeds', '1 cup old-fashioned rolled oats', '1/4 cup peanut butter', '1/4 cup olive oil', '1/4 cup Splenda Brown Sugar blend']
steps: ['First heat an oven to 300 degrees.', 'Line a baking sheet with parchment paper or foil. Coat with non-stick cooking spray and set aside.', 'In a bowl, combine cashews, pumpkin seeds, pecans, sunflower seeds and oats. Set aside.', 'In the microwave, melt peanut butter, oil, and Splenda Brown Sugar together. Stir to combine.', 'Pour peanut butter mixture over oat mixture and stir to coat.', 'Spread granola in a packed, single layer onto prepared baking sheet. Bake for 40-45 minutes, stirring every 10 minutes to ensure even browning.', 'Remove from oven and let cool completely. Break up granola and store in an air-tight container.']

Ingredients: ['4 eggs', '4 egg whites', '1 Dash hot pepper sauce', '1/4 tsp black pepper', '2 tbsp cheddar cheese', '2 tsp margarine', '4 slice deli ham', '1/4 cup onion', '1/4 cup green pepper', '4 corn tortillas', '4 tsp salsa']
steps: ['In a medium bowl, whisk together the eggs, egg whites, hot pepper sauce, black pepper, and cheese.', 'Heat the margarine in a medium non-stick wok over medium heat. put the ham and saute for 2-3 minutes. Remove the ham from the wok.', 'put the onions and green peppers to the hot wok, and cook for about 5 minutes. put the ham back to wok.', 'Reduce the heat to low and put the eggs to wok. Gently stir the eggs with a spoon or spatula and continue lightly cooking over low heat until the eggs are cooked and set.', 'Evenly divide the egg mixture into 4 servings. Spoon each portion of the egg mixture into a tortilla and top each with 1 tsp. salsa. Fold the tortilla to close.']

Ingredients: ['1/2 cup pecan pieces', '4 6-oz breasts boneless, skinless chicken breasts', '3 tbsp unsweetened applesauce', '1 tbsp spicy brown mustard', '1/4 tsp sea salt']
steps: ['First heat the oven to 425 F. Prep a large rimmed baking sheet. For easier cleanup and less sticking, line with parchment paper optional.', 'Place the pecans in a food processor. Pulse until they look like breadcrumbs. Transfer to a rimmed plate.', 'Place the chicken on the baking sheet. In a small bowl, stir together the applesauce and mustard. Spoon the applesauce-mustard mixture on top of each breast, spreading it evenly with the back of the spoon. Firmly press the applesauce-mustard side of each chicken breast into the pecans. Place the chicken back on the baking sheet, pecan-crusted side up. Sprinkle any remaining pecans on the chicken press to adhere. Sprinkle with salt.', 'Bake for about 20 minutes, or until the chicken reaches an internal temperature of 165 F. Divide among four dinner plates and serve.']

Ingredients: ['1 tbsp paprika', '1 tsp chili powder', '1 tsp black pepper', '1 tsp garlic powder', '1 tsp salt', '1 whole chicken', '1 medium onion', '1 cup reduced carb or reduced sugar barbeque sauce', '8 large lettuce leaves', '2 cup cabbage']
steps: ['Combine paprika, chili powder, ground black pepper, garlic powder, and salt optional in a bowl. put chicken pieces and toss to completely coat chicken.', 'put chicken and onion to a slow cooker and set to low for 5-6 hours.', 'Remove chicken from slow cooker and set on a cutting board or in a bowl to rest for 15 minutes. Take any remaining liquid and onions from slow cooker and whisk with the barbeque sauce, set aside.', 'Pull chicken and shred with a fork. Discard bones.', 'whisk pulled chicken with barbeque sauce and onion mixture.', 'To build the sandwich, put a heaping 1/2 cup of chicken to a lettuce leaf and top with 1/4 cup shredded cabbage.']

Ingredients: ['1 Nonstick cooking spray', '1 1/2 cup unsweetened graham cracker flour', '3 tbsp avocado oil', '2 tsp plus 1 tbsp lemon zest', '1/4 tsp fine sea salt', '1 whole egg', '3 egg whites', '2 cup nonfat vanilla Greek yogurt', '1 tsp maple syrup', '1/4 cup lemon juice', '3/4 cup fresh blueberries']
steps: ['First heat the oven to 350F.', 'Line an 8-inch baking dish with parchment paper, then coat it with nonstick cooking spray.', 'To make the crust, put graham cracker flour, avocado oil, 2 teaspoons lemon zest, and salt to the bowl of a food processor pulse to combine. Press mixture into the bottom of the prepared wok. Bake for 10-15 minutes, or until crust is golden brown. Then remove wok from the oven and set aside to cool.', 'To make the filling, process the egg, egg whites, yogurt, maple syrup, lemon juice, and remaining 1 tablespoon lemon zest in a blender until smooth. Stir in the fresh blueberries. Pour the filling onto the prebaked crust.', 'Transfer wok to the oven and bake for 25-30 minutes, or until the center is set. Remove wok from the oven and place on a wire rack to cool completely. Cut into 16 equal-sized squares and serve chilled or at room temperature.']

Ingredients: ['1 Parchment Paper', '2 medium apples', '1 tsp ground cinnamon']
steps: ['First heat the oven to 200 degrees F. Lay the parchment paper on one large or two medium baking sheets.', 'Using a mandolin or knife, thinly slice the apples to make round chips. Discard the seeds.', 'Lay the apple slices on the prepared baking sheets without overlapping. Sprinkle the cinnamon over apples.', 'Bake for 1 hour, then flip the apples. Continue baking for 1-2 hours, flipping occasionally, until the apple slices are no longer moist. Let cool completely and then store in airtight container.']

Ingredients: ['1 nonstick cooking spray', '1 about 2 1/2 lbs whole chicken', '2 tbsp cilantro', '1 lime', '1 tbsp honey', '2 clove garlic', '1/2 tsp black pepper', '1/2 tsp salt']
steps: ['First heat oven to 375 degrees F.
