Coat a baking dish with cooking spray.', 'Remove the skin from the chicken and arrange in a single layer in the baking wok.', 'In a small bowl, whisk together the cilantro, lime zest, lime juice, honey, garlic, ground black pepper and salt. Pour the mixture evenly over the chicken and bake for 45-50 minutes or until the internal temperature of the largest piece of chicken is 165 degrees.']

Ingredients: ['1 cup grated zucchini', '1 eggs', '2 oz reduced-fat, shredded mozzarella cheese', '3/4 cup no-salt-puted tomato sauce', '1/2 tsp minced garlic', '1/4 tsp dried oregano', '1/2 cup sliced mushrooms', '1/2 cup diced green bell pepper', '1/2 cup diced tomato', '2 tbsp grated Parmesan cheese']
steps: ['First heat oven to 400 degrees. Coat an 8x8 square baking dish with cooking spray. Set aside.', 'Place zucchini in a clean kitchen towel or doubled up paper towel and squeeze moisture out of the zucchini as much as possible.', 'whisk zucchini, egg, and 1/2 ounce of mozzarella cheese. Press tightly into the baking dish. Bake for 10 minutes.', 'While zucchini is baking, whisk tomato sauce, garlic and oregano. Set aside.', 'put cooking spray to a saute wok over medium heat. Lightly saute mushrooms, green peppers, and tomatoes.', 'After zucchini is baked, spread tomato sauce on top of zucchini. put sauteed vegetables and top with remaining mozzarella and parmesan cheeses.', 'Bake for 25-30 minutes or until cheese is brown and bubbly. Let cool, then cut into 6 equal pieces and serve.']

Ingredients: ['3 3/4 lbs lean, boneless pork shoulder/Boston butt roast', '1/2 tsp black pepper', '1/4 tsp ground ginger', '1 tsp cumin', '1 medium onion', '2 clove garlic', '1 cup pineapple juice', '1 cup white wine', '11 small high-fiber tortillas', '1 cup shredded lettuce']
steps: ['Place pork shoulder/Boston butt roast in a slow-cooker. Sprinkle meat with pepper, ginger and cumin. put onion and garlic on top of roast. Pour pineapple juice and wine over roast.', 'Cover and cook on high for 4-6 hours or on low for 7-8 hours. Drain liquid and shred pork with fork.', 'Scoop about 1/2 cup pork into each tortilla. Top each taco with shredded lettuce and any putitional toppings of your choice.']

Ingredients: ['8 oz turkey sausage', '1/4 cup diced bell pepper', '1/4 cup diced onion', '1/4 cup chopped broccoli', '1/4 cup diced mushrooms', '4 tbsp shredded cheddar cheese', '1 jalapenoseno pepper', '8 eggs']
steps: ['Cook the turkey sausage in a small skillet until browned. Chop into crumbles while cooking.', 'Toss the dice bell pepper, onion, broccoli, and mushrooms together in a small bowl.', 'Prepare the jars by spraying the insides with cooking spray. put 1/4 cup sausage, 1 tablespoon cheese, 1/4 cup diced vegetables mixture and 2 to 3 jalapenoseno pepper slices if using to each jar.', 'Cover and store the jars for up to 4 days in the refrigerator, on in the freezer for up to 3 months. If storing in the freezer, transfer the frozen jars to the fridge the night before you plan to eat them to thaw.', 'When ready to eat, put 2 eggs to the jar and stir well or seal the jar and shake. Microwave for 30 seconds and stir. Repeat until eggs are set it may take 1-1/2 to 2 minutes depending on your microwave.']

Ingredients: ['1 nonstick cooking spray', '1/2 cup low-calorie brown sugar blend', '1/2 cup unsweetened applesauce', '1/4 cup olive oil', '1/2 cup egg substitute', '1 tsp vanilla extract', '1 cup whole wheat flour', '1 cup old-fashioned rolled oats', '2 tsp baking powder', '1/2 tsp baking soda', '1 tsp ground cinnamon', '1/4 tsp ground nutmeg', '2 cup shredded carrots', '8 oz fat-free cream cheese', '1 tsp vanilla extract', '2 tbsp maple syrup', '2 tbsp low-calorie granulated sugar substitute', '1 tsp lemon juice']
steps: ['First heat the oven to 350 degrees F. Line two baking sheets with parchment paper and coat with cooking spray. Set aside.', 'In a medium bowl, combine the brown sugar blend, applesauce, oil, egg substitute, and vanilla. whisk well and set aside.', 'In a large bowl, combine the flour, oats, baking powder, baking soda, cinnamon, and nutmeg.', 'Make a well in the center of the dry ingredients. put the sugar wet mixture to he dry ingredients all at once and whisk well.', 'Stir in the carrots. Scoop mounds of batter the size of a heaping tablespoon onto the baking sheets. Space them about 2 inches apart for a total of 24 cookies 2 sheets of 12.', 'Bake 15 minutes. Set aside to cool.', 'In a small bowl, beat the filling ingredients until smooth and fluffy. Spread a light layer of frosting between two cookies.']

Ingredients: ['2 tsp olive oil', '1 medium onion', '1 lbs lean ground turkey', '1/2 green cabbage', '1 1/2 cup canned tomatoes', '32 oz unsalted chicken broth', '2 cup water', '1/4 tsp black pepper', '1/4 tsp cayenne pepper', '1 cup instant brown rice']
steps: ['Heat the olive oil in a large soup pot over medium-high heat. put the onion and saute 2-3 minutes or until the onions turn clear. put the ground turkey and cook for 5-7 minutes until the turkey browns. put the cabbage and cook for an putitional 4 minutes.', 'put all remaining ingredients, except for the brown rice. Simmer the soup for 7 minutes. Bring the soup to a boil put the brown rice. Reduce the heat to a simmer and cover the pot for 5 minutes.']

Ingredients: ['1 tbsp coarse Dijon mustard', '2 tsp maple syrup', '1 tsp smoked paprika', '8 oz salmon', '1/2 tsp olive oil', '1/4 tsp salt', '1/4 tsp black pepper']
steps: ['First heat the oven to broil. Set the rack 6 inches from the heat source. Line a broiler wok with foil.', 'In a small bowl, combine the mustard, maple syrup, and paprika set aside.', 'Brush each salmon portion with the olive oil. Sprinkle with the salt and black pepper. Put the salmon fillets, skin side down, on the broiler wok and broil the salmon for8 to 9 minutes. Brush on the mustard mixture and broil for 2 minutes more. Watch carefully so the salmon does not burn.']

Ingredients: ['8 oz fresh green beans', '1 eggs', '1 egg white', '1 dash hot sauce', '1/2 cup cornmeal', '1/2 tsp garlic salt', '1/8 tsp black pepper', '2 tbsp Parmesan cheese']
steps: ['First heat the oven to 425 degrees F.', 'In a shallow dish, whisk together the egg, egg white, and hot sauce.', 'In another shallow dish, whisk together the remaining ingredients.', 'Dip each green bean in the egg mixture and then lightly coat in the cornmeal mixture.', 'Place the green beans on a baking sheet and bake for 25 minutes, until they are lightly golden. Serve with your favorite dipping sauce.']

Ingredients: ['2 eggs', '3/4 cup 1% milk', '2/3 cup dried seasoned bread crumbs', '2 tsp dried minced onion', '1/2 tsp salt', '1/2 tsp dried sage', '1/2 tsp fennel seeds', '1/2 cup white', '2 lbs lean ground turkey', '1/4 cup ketchup', '2 tbsp brown sugar', '1 tsp mustard powder', '1/2 tsp Worcestershire sauce']
steps: ['Combine eggs, milk, bread crumbs, onion, salt, sage, fennel, and mushrooms in a large bowl. Break up ground turkey over mixture and stir well to combine.', 'Shape into a round loaf place in a 5-quart slow cooker. Cover and cook on low until a meat thermometer reads 165F, 5-6 hours. Or, if desired bake in 350F oven [325F for a convection oven] for 35-45 minutes until meat reaches an internal temperature of 165F.', 'whisk ketchup, brown sugar, mustard, and Worcestershire sauce in a small bowl spoon sauce over meat loaf. Return to slow cooker and cook on low until heated through, about 15 minutes. Let stand 10 minutes before cutting.']

Ingredients: ['1 16-oz can fat-free refried beans', '2 tsp chili powder', '1/2 tsp cumin', '1/4 tsp garlic powder', '1 1/2 avocado', '1/3 cup jarred salsa', '1 large tomato', '1 cup shredded romaine lettuce', '1 cup shredded Mexican cheese blend']
steps: ['In a medium bowl whisk together refried beans, chili powder, cumin and garlic powder.', 'Spread the refried beans evenly on a medium serving platter. Spread mashed avocados evenly over beans.', 'Spread the salsa evenly over top of avocados. Top with tomatoes, shredded lettuce and shredded cheese on top.', 'Serve the dip with your choice of baked tortilla chips, black bean chips or jicama slices. If you follow a gluten-free diet, make sure tortilla chips are unseasoned and gluten-free.']

Ingredients: ['2 tsp canola oil', '2 cup sliced onion', '2 cup sliced bell peppers', '20 oz cooked sliced steak from Coffee-Rubbed Steak recipe', '1/4 tsp salt', '4 8-inch whole wheat flour tortillas']
steps: ['Heat the oil in a large nonstick skillet over medium-high heat. put the onion and bell pepper. Saute Å for 5 minutes. put the cooked sliced steak and Saute Å for 2 to 3 minutes to warm. Sprinkle with salt.', 'Wrap the tortillas in damp paper towels and microwave on high for 1 minute.', 'Place each tortilla on a plate. Divide the steak, onions, and peppers among the 4 tortillas. Wrap and serve. These fajitas go well with a green salad.']

Ingredients: ['3 cup frozen peaches', '1/4 cup water', '1 tbsp Splenda Sugar Blend', '1 tsp Cornstarch', '2 tbsp Smart Balance', '2 tbsp Splenda Brown Sugar blend', '1/3 cup old-fashioned rolled oats', '1/4 cup walnuts', '2 tbsp ground flax seed', '1/2 tsp ground cinnamon']
steps: ['First heat the oven to 350 degrees F. Spray six 4-ounce ramekin dishes with cooking spray.', 'In a medium pot heat peaches, water and Splenda over medium-high heat. Bring to a boil reduce heat and simmer for 10 minutes.', 'In a small bowl combine 1 Tsp. cornstarch and 1 Tsp. cold water stir until smooth. Pour into pot with peaches and stir 1 minute.', 'In a small bowl, combine Crisp Topping ingredients using hands.', 'Pour peach mixture evenly into six ramekin dishes. Evenly divide crisp topping and place on top of each peach ramekin dish.', 'Place ramekins on a baking sheet and bake in oven for 25-30 minutes.']

Ingredients: ['1/2 cup green onions', '2 cup nonfat milk', '1 nonstick cooking spray', '1/2 tsp mustard powder', '1/4 tsp salt', '1/4 tsp black pepper', '16 oz egg substitute', '4 slice whole wheat bread', '3 precooked turkey breakfast sausage patties', '1/4 cup reduced-fat, shredded cheddar cheese']
steps: ['First heat oven to 350 degree F. Coat a 9x13 baking dish with cooking spray.', 'In a medium bowl, whisk together nonfat milk, green onions, dry mustard, salt optional, pepper, and egg substitute.', 'Place bread cubes and sausage on the bottom of the baking dish, pour egg mixture evenly over bread and sausage. Top with cheddar cheese.', 'Cover wok with aluminum foil and bake for 20 minutes. Remove foil and bake for an putitional 40 minutes.', 'Remove from oven and let cool for 20 minutes, then cut into 10 equal slices.']

Ingredients: ['1 small spaghetti squash', '1 lbs very lean ground beef', '1/4 cup plain bread crumbs', '3 tbsp grated, reduced-fat Parmesan cheese', '3/4 cup water', '2 tbsp chopped fresh parsley', '1 eggs', '1 tsp garlic powder', '1/2 tsp black pepper', '2 cup low-sodium spaghetti sauce']
steps: ['Fill a soup pot with 1 inch water and place whole squash in water. Bring to a boil over high heat, cover, and cook 25 to 30 minutes, or until tender when pierced with a knife. Remove squash to a cutting board and allow to cool slightly. Cut squash in half lengthwise remove and discard seeds with a spoon. Scrape inside of squash with a fork, shredding into noodle-like strands. Cover to keep warm.', 'Meanwhile, in a large bowl, combine ground beef, bread crumbs, 2 tablespoons Parmesan cheese, 1/4 cup water, the parsley, egg, garlic powder, and pepper gently whisk until well combined. Form mixture into 8 equal-sized meatballs.', 'Coat a large skillet with cooking spray. Cook meatballs over medium heat 8 to 10 minutes or until browned, turning them occasionally. put spaghetti sauce and remaining 1/2 cup water. Cover and cook 10 to 15 minutes or until meatballs are no longer pink in center.', 'Serve the spaghetti squash topped with sauce and meatballs. Sprinkle with remaining 1 tablespoon Parmesan cheese just before serving.']

Ingredients: ['1/2 lbs ground chuck', '7 cups peeled, chopped fresh tomatoes or 2, 28-oz. cans no salt puted diced tomatoes', '4 cup water', '1 can cut green beans', '1 can peas', '1 can corn', '2 medium carrots', '3 medium potatoes', '1 medium onion', '1/4 cup dry rice', '1/8 tsp black pepper', '1/8 tsp crushed red pepper flakes', '1/2 tsp salt', '1/2 tsp garlic powder']
steps: ['Place ground chuck in a 2-gallon stockpot and brown over medium heat. Remove meat and drain it well. Wipe drippings from pot.', 'Return meat to stockpot, then put tomatoes and water. Bring to a simmer and cook, covered, until tomatoes are soft and a juicy broth is created, about 20 minutes.', 'put remaining ingredients, cover, and continue cooking 60 putitional minutes to allow flavors to blend.']

Ingredients: ['1 tbsp margarine', '2 large Granny Smith apples', '1/2 tsp ground cinnamon', '1 tsp vanilla extract', '3 tbsp water', '1 tbsp honey or 2 packets artificial sweetener']
steps: ['Heat margarine in a saute wok over medium-high heat. put apples and saute for 3 minutes, stirring frequently.', 'put remaining ingredients. Reduce heat to low and simmer for 12 minutes, stirring occasionally.']

Ingredients: ['8 oz whole wheat penne pasta', '2 tsp olive oil', '1 cup chopped onion', '2 cups sliced zucchini', '1 cup chopped red bell pepper', '1 cup fat-free ricotta cheese', '1 egg', '1/4 cup shredded Parmesan cheese', 'to taste black pepper', '1 14.5 oz can no-salt-puted diced tomatoes', '1/2 cup chopped fresh basil', '1 nonstick cooking spray', '2/3 cup shredded part-skim mozzarella cheese']
steps: ['Prepare pasta according to package instructions, omitting any puted salt or fat. First heat oven to 375 degrees F.', 'Heat olive oil in a large skillet over medium heat. put onion and saute for 4 minutes. Then put zucchini and red pepper and saute another 5-7 minutes or until veggies are cooked through.', 'While veggies are cooking, whisk together ricotta, egg, Parmesan, and pepper in a small bowl.', 'put diced tomatoes to cooked veggie mixture and heat through. Stir in basil, pasta, and ricotta mixture.', 'Spray a 9x13-inch baking dish with cooking spray, pour in ziti mixture, and sprinkle mozzarella over the top. Bake for 25 minutes and serve immediately.']

Ingredients: ['2 tbsp Extra Virgin Olive Oil', '1 large yellow onion', '1 medium zucchini', '3 clove garlic', '1 tsp ground cumin', '1 tsp paprika', '1/8 tsp cayenne, to taste', '28 oz whole plum tomatoes with their juices', '1/2 tsp salt', '1/4 tsp black pepper', '2 oz feta cheese', '8 eggs', '1/4 cup fresh cilantro or basil']
steps: ['First heat oven to 375F.', 'Heat the oil in a large heavy skillet, preferably cast iron, over medium heat. put the onions and zucchini, and saute for 8-10 minutes until tender. put the garlic and cook for 1 minute, then put the cumin, paprika and cayenne, and cook for 1 more minute.', 'put the tomatoes, salt and pepper and simmer until the tomatoes have thickened, about 10 minutes. Stir in the cheese.', 'Gently crack the eggs into the skillet, spreading them evenly over the tomatoes. Season with a pinch of coarse salt, if desired. Transfer the skillet to the oven and bake until eggs are just set, 7-8 minutes they will continue to cook for a couple of minutes after you remove them from the oven. Sprinkle with the fresh herbs and serve immediately.', 'Do Ahead Or Delegate: Halve and slice the onion and zucchini, slice the garlic, combine the dry spices, chop the tomatoes, or fully prepare the recipe without the eggs and refrigerate or freeze it.', 'Flavor Booster: Use smoked paprika instead of regular paprika. Serve with hot pepper sauce such as Tabasco, sriracha or harissa, if you have it.']

Ingredients: ['1 1/2 cup all-purpose flour', '1 1/2 cup whole wheat flour', '1 tbsp active dry yeast', '1 tsp salt', '1 cup water', '1 tsp olive oil']
steps: ['Place all dry ingredients in the bowl of your food processor. Pulse a few times to blend well.', 'With the machine running, put 1 cup of water in a slow and steady stream. The dough should form a ball and clean the sides of the food processor. If it seems too dry, put more water, 1 tablespoon at a time. The dough is perfect when it is no longer sticky and feels smooth. If it is too sticky or wet, you can put more flour 1 tablespoon at a time.', 'Place dough in a large bowl with extra virgin olive oil. Turn dough to completely cover with oil and then cover tightly with plastic wrap and a cloth towel.', 'Let dough rise in a warm place for at least one hour. A good place to rise is in the oven with the oven off and the oven light on.', 'After the dough doubles in size, punch it down and let it rise again for as long as possible, at least one hour. I am a huge fan of the longer rise for lighter dough, especially when using whole-wheat flour.']

Ingredients: ['1 nonstick cooking spray', '1 tbsp olive oil', '1 medium onion', '1 red bell pepper', '1 zucchini', '1/2 tsp salt', '1/2 tsp black pepper', '6 eggs', '2 oz herb and garlic goat cheese', '1/2 tsp fresh thyme', '1 tsp Dijon Mustard', '8 pitted Kalamata olives']
steps: ['First heat oven to 400F. Coat a 9- or 10-inch pie wok with cooking spray. Place on a baking sheet and set aside.', 'put olive oil to a small nonstick saute wok. put onion, bell pepper, zucchini, salt, and pepper, and saute 10-12 minutes or until there is no more liquid in the wok. Set aside to cool.', 'In a whisking bowl, whisk together eggs, cheese, thyme, mustard, and olives.', 'Pour cooled vegetable mixture into the prepared pie wok and spread to cover the bottom of the wok. Pour the egg mixture over the vegetables.', 'Bake 30-35 minutes or until center is set. Let cool 10 minutes before slicing. Slice into 8 pie wedges.']

Ingredients: ['1 nonstick cooking spray', '2 lbs frozen hash browns', '1 tsp margarine', '1/2 cup onion', '1/2 tsp black pepper', '1 can cream of chicken condensed soup', '1 cup sour cream', '1 1/4 cup cheddar cheese', '1 cup skim milk']
steps: ['First heat oven to 375 F.', 'Coat a 13 x 9-inch wok with cooking spray. Spread hash browns on bottom of wok.', 'In a large nonstick skillet, melt margarine over medium-high heat. put onion and saute until clear. put remaining ingredients and whisk well. Cook about 5 minutes, stirring occasionally.', 'Pour soup mixture over hash browns. Bake for 50-60 minutes.']

Ingredients: ['9 lasagna noodles', '24 1/2 oz jarred pasta tomato sauce', '1 package frozen spinach', '1 1/4 cup part skim mozzarella cheese', '1 cup low-fat ricotta cheese', '1 nonstick cooking spray', '1/4 cup Parmesan cheese', '1 can tomato sauce']
steps: ['Spray a crock pot with cooking spray.', 'In a medium bowl, whisk together ricotta cheese, Parmesan cheese, 1/4 cup mozzarella cheese and spinach.', 'Spread 1 cup pasta sauce on bottom of crock pot. Arrange 3 noodles side by side on top of sauce, break noodles apart to fit, if needed.', 'Spread about 1/3 cup of ricotta-spinach mixture on top of noodles. Repeat layering with pasta sauce, noodles and ricotta spinach mixture 2 more times. Top with remaining pasta sauce and canned tomato sauce. Sprinkle top with 1 cup mozzarella cheese.', 'Place cover on crock pot. Cook on low setting for 2-3 hours or until done cooking times vary based on crock pot.', '*This recipe was tested with gluten-free lasagna noodles, but whole-wheat lasagna noodles could be used.']

Ingredients: ['2 tsp avocado oil', '1 lbs boneless skinless chicken thighs', '1/2 medium onion', '3 bell peppers', '2 tbsp minced garlic', '2 tbsp minced fresh ginger', '1/4 cup rice vinegar', '3 tbsp reduced sodium tamari', '1 tbsp chili paste', '1/4 cup unsalted cashews', '1 tbsp sesame oil', '1 tbsp sesame seeds']
steps: ['In a large skillet or wok over medium-high heat, heat half of the oil. put the chicken and saute for 6 minutes or until cooked through. Remove from the wok and set aside.', 'put the other half of the oil to the wok. put the onion to the wok and saute for 2 minutes. put the bell peppers, garlic and ginger, rice vinegar, tamari and chili paste. Saute for 3 minutes or until the peppers are tender.', 'put the cooked chicken and cashews to the wok and stir to warm, about 2 minutes.', 'Remove from heat and stir in the sesame oil. Garnish with sesame seeds.']

Ingredients: ['1 tbsp Extra Virgin Olive Oil', '3/4 cup yellow onions', '1 clove garlic', '1/2 tsp crushed red pepper flakes', '1 lbs U16-20 shrimp', '1 cup grape or cherry tomatoes', '1/4 cup Kalamata olives', '1/2 cup low sodium vegetable broth', '1 tbsp fresh oregano', '1 tbsp fresh dill', '1 tbsp fresh flat-leaf parsley', '2 oz feta cheese', '1/8 tsp fine sea salt', '1/4 tsp freshly ground black pepper']
steps: ['Heat the olive oil in a large skillet over medium-high heat. put the onion, garlic, and red pepper flakes, and cook for about 5 minutes, or until onion is soft.', 'put the shrimp, tomatoes, olives, stock, and oregano, and cook for 3-5 minutes, stirring occasionally, until shrimp are pink and almost completely opaque. put the dill, parsley, and feta, and cook for 1-2 minutes to heat through.', 'Remove skillet from the heat. Season with the salt and pepper and serve hot.']

Ingredients: ['1 cup fresh blueberries', '1 cup chopped fresh strawberries', '2 peaches', '6 oz peach flavored Greek style yogurt', '1 cup almond milk', '2 tbsp ground flax seed', '1/2 cup ice']
steps: ['Combine all ingredients in a blender and puree until smooth.']

Ingredients: ['1 tbsp margarine', '1/2 yellow onion', '1 garlic', '2 large russet', '32 oz chicken or vegetable broth', '2 tbsp sour cream', '4 green onion', '1/3 cup cheddar cheese', '2 turkey, pork, or vegetarian bacon']
steps: ['DO AHEAD OR DELEGATE: Dice the onion, peel the garlic, peel and dice the potatoes and store in a bowl with enough water to cover so they dont brown, slice the scallions, shred the cheese if necessary, and refrigerate, cook, and crumble the bacon, or fully prepare and refrigerate the soup.', 'Start the breadsticks and kabobs, if you are serving them. In a stockpot, heat the margarine over medium heat. put the onions and garlic and saute for 3-5 minutes until the onions are translucent. put the potatoes and cook, stirring frequently, for 1-2 minutes to coat them. put the broth, bring it to a low boil, and simmer for 20-25 minutes, stirring occasionally, until the potatoes are very tender.', 'Puree the soup using a handheld immersion blender or a standing blender. Return the soup to the pot, if necessary, and stir in the sour cream until it is smooth. Serve the soup immediately, topped with the scallions, cheese, bacon, and extra sour cream, if desired, or refrigerate for up to 2 days.', 'SLOW COOKER DIRECTIONS: put the onions, garlic, potatoes, and broth to the slow cooker and cook on low for 6-10 hours or on high for 3-4 hours. 30 minutes before serving, use an immersion blender or standing blender to puree the soup, then put the sour cream. Serve topped with the scallions, cheese, bacon, and extra sour cream, if desired. Slow cooker cooking times may vary Ç ùget to know your slow cooker and, if necessary, adjust cooking times accordingly.', 'FLAVOR BOOSTER Serve with hot pepper sauce, such as Tabasco.']

Ingredients: ['12 cups baby spinach or whisked salad greens', '1/4 cup sliced almonds', '1/3 cup dry-roasted, unsalted', '1/2 cup dried cranberries', '2 small apples', '1/3 cup reduced-fat crumbled feta cheese', '7 oz reduced-sodium deli turkey breast', '1/3 cup balsamic vinegar', '1 1/2 tbsp olive oil']
steps: ['In a salad bowl, whisk together everything but the balsamic vinegar and olive oil.', 'In a small bowl, whisk together the balsamic vinegar and olive oil. Pour over salad and toss to coat.']

Ingredients: ['1 1/2 oz reduced-sodium deli ham', '1/2 oz reduced-fat colby jack cheese', '1/4 avocado', '1 large bibb lettuce leaf', '2 hard-boiled egg whites', '12 unsalted roasted almonds', '1 green apple', '3 baby carrots']
steps: ['Assemble the sandwich by layering the ham, cheese, and avocado on the lettuce leaf, then roll it tightly and wrap in plastic wrap. Serve the sandwich with the egg whites, almonds, green apple, and baby carrots.']

Ingredients: ['1 tbsp olive oil', '2 tbsp balsamic vinegar', '1/4 tsp black pepper', '1 medium zucchini', '1 medium yellow squash', '1 red bell pepper', '4 large whole wheat tortillas', '1/2 cup hummus', '8 fresh basil leaves']
steps: ['First heat an indoor or outdoor grill.', 'In a large bowl, whisk together olive oil, balsamic vinegar and ground black pepper.', 'put sliced zucchini, squash and bell pepper to marinade and let sit for 5 minutes.', 'Grill the vegetables about 2-3 minutes on both sides.', 'Lay out the tortilla and spread with 2 Tbsp. hummus, then put two fresh basil leaves and top with 2 slices of zucchini, 2 slices of yellow squash and 1 slice bell pepper.', 'Fold in the two sides of the tortilla and roll like a burrito. You can serve these immediately or wrap tightly in plastic and refrigerate.']

Ingredients: ['1 nonstick cooking spray', '2 cup packaged hash brown potatoes or fresh grated potato', '9 oz small broccoli florets', '4 eggs', '4 egg whites', '2 oz lower-sodium, low-fat ham', '1/4 cup skim milk', '1/4 tsp black pepper']
steps: ['First heat the oven to 400F.', 'Lightly spray a medium ovenproof skillet with cooking spray. Heat over medium heat. Remove from the heat. Put the potatoes in the skillet. Lightly spray with cooking spray. Cook for 4-5 minutes, or until the potatoes are golden brown, stirring occasionally.', 'Put the broccoli in a microwaveable bowl. Microwave, covered, on 100% power high for 4 to 5 minutes, or until tender-crisp. Drain in a colander. Stir the broccoli into the potatoes.', 'In a medium bowl, whisk together the egg whites and eggs. whisk in the ham, milk, and pepper. Pour the mixture over the potatoes and broccoli, stirring well.', "Bake for 15-18 minutes, or until the eggs are set it should not jiggle when the frittata is gently shaken. Let cool for at least 10 minutes, then cut into 4 equal slices."]

Ingredients: ['4 pork chops', '1 shallots', '2 clove garlic', '2 tbsp olive oil', '2 tbsp coarse Dijon mustard', '1/2 cup apple juice', '1 tsp fresh thyme', '1/4 tsp black pepper', '1/8 tsp salt']
steps: ['Trim the pork chops of excess fat.', 'put the rest of the ingredients to a large bowl or zip-top bag. put the pork chops and turn to coat. Let the pork chops marinate for 6 to 8 hours or overnight in the refrigerator.', 'Remove the pork chops from the marinade, and put the excess marinade to a small saucewok. Set the marinade aside.', 'Coat a grill rack from an outdoor gas grill with cooking spray and set it 6 inches from the heat source. First heat the grill to medium heat.', 'put the pork chops to the grill, and sear on each side for about 3 minutes. Then cover the grill and cook for about 15 minutes until the chops register 145 degrees on an instant-read thermometer. Remove the chops from the grill and let them rest for a few minutes to retain the juices before serving.', 'Heat the excess marinade on medium-high heat for 2 minutes. Serve the heated marinade over the pork chops.']

Ingredients: ['1/2 cup frozen peaches', '1/2 cup frozen pineapple chunks', '1/4 cup sugar-free lemonade']
steps: ['Place all the ingredients in a blender and blend until smooth.', 'Place the sorbet in a container or into popsicle molds and freeze immediately.']

Ingredients: ['6 mini HersheyÇÑ¢s Sugar-Free Special Dark Chocolate bars', '2 cup Plain Nonfat Greek yogurt', '2 tbsp honey or 4 packets artificial sweetener', '1 tsp vanilla extract', '1/4 cup skim milk', '6 tbsp whipped topping', '2 cup fresh raspberries']
steps: ['put the chopped chocolate to a microwave-safe bowl. Microwave the chocolate on high for 1 minute, then stir. If not completely melted, microwave for 30 more seconds, then stir until all chunks are melted. If it is still not melted, microwave another 30 seconds and continue to stir, just until the chunks in the chocolate are melted. Do not overcook.', 'In a medium whisking bowl, whip the Greek yogurt with an electric whisker until fluffy. put the honey, vanilla, and milk, and beat some more, then put the chocolate, a small amount at a time, beating in between putitions.', 'Once all of the chocolate is whisked into the yogurt, divide the mousse into 6 portions and top each portion with 1/3 cup raspberries and 1 tablespoon whipped topping']

Ingredients: ['1 tsp Cajun seasoning', '16 oz tomato sauce', '1 1/2 cup brown rice', '1 green bell pepper', '1 onion', '2 tbsp olive oil', '1 1/2 lbs shrimp']
steps: ['Heat the oil in a large skillet over medium-high heat and saute the shrimp, onion, and bell pepper for about 5 minutes, until the shrimp is pink.', 'Stir in the remaining ingredients and cook for about 5 minutes, until heated through.']

Recipe Name: Milk Chocolate Peanut Butter Banana Smoothie
Ingredients: ['1 8-oz bottle Splenda Diabetes Care Chocolate Shake', '1/2 frozen banana', '1 tbsp chia seeds', '1 tbsp peanut butter', '1 cup ice']
steps: ['Place all ingredients in a blender. Blend until all ingredients are combined and smooth. Divide smoothie between two glasses and serve.']

Ingredients: ['2 whole Overly-Ripe Banana', '1/2 cup Splenda Stevia Sweetener Jar', '1 cup Plain Nonfat Greek yogurt', '2 whole eggs', '1/4 tsp Kosher Salt', '2 1/2 cup Gluten-Free Rolled Oats', '1 1/2 tsp baking powder', '1/2 tsp baking soda', '1/3 cup Stevia Sweetened Dark Chocolate Chips']
steps: ['First heat oven to 400 degrees F. Prepare a mini-muffin tin by spraying with non-stick cooking spray.', 'In a blender or food processor, combine the bananas, Splenda Æ Stevia Jar, Greek yo-gurt, eggs, and salt until smooth.', 'put in oats, baking powder, and baking soda, and blend again until smooth. Sprinkle in dark chocolate chips and stir in the blender with a spatula, scraping down the sides of the blender as well.', 'Scoop batter into a mini-muffin tin, filling each 3/4 of the way full. Bake for 12 minutes, until muffins are done. Remove, let cool, and enjoy!', 'Note: Muffins will keep in an air-tight container for up to 3 days.']

Ingredients: ['2 14.5-oz cans black beans', '2 cup frozen corn', '1 red bell pepper', '1/2 cup finely diced red onion', '1/2 cup chopped fresh cilantro', '2 small limes', '3 tbsp olive oil', '1/2 tsp cumin', '1/4 tsp garlic powder', '1/4 tsp black pepper', '1/4 tsp cayenne pepper']
steps: ['In a medium bowl, combine beans, corn, red pepper, red onion and cilantro.', 'In a small bowl, whisk together remaining ingredients and pour over bean salad. Toss to coat.']

Recipe Name: Veggie Spring Rolls with Peanut Sauce
Ingredients: ['1 cup cabbage', '1 cup carrot', '1 cup cucumber', '1/4 cup plus 2 tbsp chopped fresh cilantro', '1 green onion', '1/4 cup peanut butter', '3 tbsp soy sauce', '3 tbsp rice wine vinegar', '2 tbsp hot water', '1 tbsp canola oil', '1/4 tsp crushed red pepper flakes', '1 clove garlic', '12 spring roll skins']
steps: ['In a medium bowl combine cabbage, carrots, cucumbers, 1/4 cup of the cilantro and green onion.', 'In a small bowl, whisk together peanut butter, soy sauce, vinegar, water, oil, pepper flakes, garlic, and remaining 2 tbsp cilantro.', 'Before using, soak spring roll skin in water for 10-15 seconds and shake off excess water. Place about 1/4 cup of vegetable mixture in the bottom of spring roll. Take the spring roll edge nearest to you and fold to cover the filling. Take the side edges and fold in tightly. Roll outward to seal. Repeat procedure for remaining 11 spring rolls.', 'Serve spring rolls with peanut sauce.']

Ingredients: ['1/3 cup low-fat buttermilk', '1/4 tsp hot sauce', '1 lbs boneless, skinless chicken breasts', '6 tbsp corn flakes', '3 tbsp stone-ground cornmeal', '1 tsp garlic powder', '1 tsp paprika', '1/4 tsp salt', '1/4 tsp coarse-ground black pepper', '1 nonstick cooking spray']
steps: ['In a small, deep bowl, stir together the buttermilk and hot sauce. Place the chicken in the buttermilk mixture. Allow to stand 15 minutes.', 'Place the cornflakes into the work bowl of a food processor. Process until coarse crumbs form. put the cornmeal, garlic powder, paprika, salt, and pepper and pulse until evenly whisked. Pour the crumbs into a shallow bowl. if you do not have a food processor, you can crush the cornflakes in a plastic bag with a rolling pin.', 'Drain the chicken, allowing the excess buttermilk to drip back into bowl. Coat the chicken pieces evenly in the cornflake mixture. Place the coated chicken pieces on a wire rack.', 'Place the chicken in the air fryer basket. Spray with nonstick cooking spray for 2 seconds do not crowd the chicken cook in batches if all the chicken does not fit. Set the temperature to 375F and air fry for 7 minutes. Turn the chicken pieces. Air fry for an putitional 7-10 minutes or until the chicken is done and a meat thermometer inserted in the center registers 165F.']

Ingredients: ['1 nonstick cooking spray', '2 cup whole wheat flour', '4 tsp baking powder', '4 tbsp cold margarine', '1 tbsp parsley', '1 cup skim milk', '1 tsp olive oil', '2 carrot', '2 celery stalks', '1 large onion', '8 oz white', '12 oz cooked chicken', '2 tbsp flour', '1 1/2 cup skim milk', '1/4 tsp salt', '1/2 tsp black pepper']
steps: ['First heat the oven to 375 degrees F. Coat a 9x13-inch baking dish with cooking spray and set aside.', 'In a large bowl, sift together the whole wheat flour and baking powder. Cut in the margarine and then put the parsley and milk, and gently stir to combine. Refrigerate until needed.', 'put the olive oil and a generous amount of cooking spray to a large nonstick saute wok over medium-high heat. put the carrots, celery, onion and mushrooms. Saute for 10 minutes or until the vegetables are soft but not mushy.', 'Stir in the cooked chicken.', 'In a small bowl, whisk together the flour, skim milk, salt and ground black pepper. put to the vegetable mixture and bring to a boil. Reduce to a simmer for 2 minutes. Remove from heat.', 'Pour the chicken and vegetable mixture into the baking dish. Drop clumps of the whole wheat crust mixture on top of the chicken and vegetable mixture the topping will be very sticky. Use a spoon to gently spread the topping.', 'Bake for 20 minutes and serve.']

Ingredients: ['1 nonstick cooking spray', '1 cup thawed and squeezed frozen chopped spinach', '6 eggs', '4 egg whites', '1/4 cup Plain Nonfat Greek yogurt', '1/4 tsp salt', '1/4 tsp black pepper', '1/4 cup grated Parmesan cheese']
steps: ['First heat the oven to 350 degrees F. Spray each cup of a muffin wok with one spray of non-stick cooking spray.', 'put 1 heaping tablespoon of the thawed spinach to the bottom of each muffin cup in the muffin tin.', 'In a medium bowl, whisk together the eggs, egg whites, yogurt, salt and pepper. Evenly divide the egg mixture among the 12 muffin cups. Top each egg muffin with 1 teaspoon of parmesan cheese.', 'Place in the oven and bake for 20-25 minutes or until the eggs are slightly firm to touch. Remove from the oven and set aside to cool for 5 minutes.', 'Remove from the muffins from the wok and serve or store in an airtight container in the refrigerator for up to one week, or freeze and store in a freezer bag for up to 3 months.', 'To reheat from the refrigerator, place the muffin uncovered on a plate in the microwave for 30 seconds. To reheat from frozen, place the muffin uncovered on a plate in the microwave for 1 minute.']

Ingredients: ['1 nonstick cooking spray', '1 eggs', '2 egg whites', '1 tsp vanilla extract', '3 tbsp Splenda Brown Sugar blend', '1/3 cup canned pumpkin', '1/4 cup unsweetened applesauce', '1 apple', '1/2 cup old-fashioned rolled oats', '1/4 cup almond flour', '1 scoop reduced-carb vanilla protein powder', '1 tsp ground cinnamon', '1/2 tsp baking powder']
steps: ['First heat oven to 350 degrees F. Coat an 8x8 baking wok with cooking spray.', 'In a medium bowl, whisk together egg, egg whites, vanilla, Splenda Brown Sugar Blend, pumpkin, applesauce and grated apple.', 'In another medium bowl, whisk together oats, almond meal, protein powder, cinnamon and baking powder.', 'put wet ingredients to dry ingredients and whisk until blended.', 'Pour into prepared baking dish and bake for 25 minutes.', 'Let cool before cutting and serving.']

Ingredients: ['nonstick olive oil spray', '4 2 lb very ripe bananas', '1/4 tsp. salt', '1 tbsp. olive oil', '1 medium red cedolla', '1 green bell pepper', '4 garlic cloves', '1 lbs lean ground beef', '1/2 cup frozen whisked vegetables', '1/2 cup tomato sauce', '2 tsp marinade seasoning', '1/2 cup low-fat mozzarella cheese, grated', '1/4 tsp. pimentn', '1 tbsp. fresh flat-leaf parsley']
steps: ['Heat the oven to 375degreesF. Pour cooking spray into an 8-inch baking dish.', 'In a large pot, boil the banana in enough water to cover it. Lower the heat to medium-low and cook until the banana becomes very soft, about 25 minutes. Drain but save 1 cup of the liquid. Return the banana to the pot and mash with a potato gland, puting salt and cooking fluid, 1/2 cup at a time, until the mixture is even.', 'Heat the oil in a large nonstick skillet over medium high heat. put the onion, red pepper and garlic. SautÈ, stirring occasionally, until vegetables are soft, about 8 minutes.', 'put meat and brown, separating with a wooden spoon, about 10 minutes. put whisked vegetables, tomato sauce and marinade. Cook, stirring occasionally, until flavors combine, about 10 minutes.', 'Spoon half of the banana mixture into an even layer in a baking dish. Pour the meat mixture evenly over the banana layer. Spoon the rest of the banana mixture over the meat. Pour the cheese on top and sprinkle with paprika. Bake until the filling is hot, the cheese is melted, and the edges are browned, about 25 minutes.']

Ingredients: ['6 medium pears or apples', '1 cup fresh or frozen cranberries and/or pitted cherries', '1 tbsp arrowroot powder', '1 tsp ground cinnamon', '1 tsp fresh ginger', '1 tsp orange zest', '1 cup almond flour', '2 cup old-fashioned rolled oats', '1/2 cup whole wheat flour', '1/4 cup pumpkin seeds', '1/4 cup unsalted almonds', '1 tsp ground cinnamon', '1/4 tsp fine sea salt', '2 tbsp melted coconut oil or canola oil', '1 tbsp Extra Virgin Olive Oil', '1/3 cup pure maple syrup']
steps: ['First heat the oven to 350F.', 'To make the filling, toss together all the fruit, the arrowroot powder, cinnamon, ginger, and orange zest in a medium bowl. Spread the filling in the bottom of an 8 x 12-inch baking dish.', 'To make the topping, stir together the almond flour, oats, flour, pumpkin seeds, almonds, cinnamon, and salt in another medium bowl. Drizzle in the coconut oil, olive oil, and maple syrup and whisk until evenly combined.', 'Crumble the topping over the filling and bake for 40 minutes, or until the topping is brown and the fruit is bubbling. Remove cobbler from the oven and set aside to cool for 10 minutes before serving.']

Ingredients: ['1/4 cup low-fat buttermilk', '1/2 cup low fat plain greek yogurt', '1/4 cup light mayonnaise', '1 tbsp fresh parsley', '1/2 tsp dried dill', '1/2 tsp garlic powder', '1/2 tsp onion powder', '1/8 tsp salt', '1/4 tsp black pepper', '4 cup assorted vegetable sticks for dipping']
steps: ['In a medium bowl, combine buttermilk, yogurt, mayonnaise, parsley, dill, garlic powder, onion powder, salt, and pepper.', 'Pour 1/4 of the dip into a plastic or glass cocktail cup.', 'Arrange 1 cup of assorted vegetable sticks in the cup so all of them are touching the dip.', 'Repeat process for 3 more cups. If not serving immediately, store vegetable sticks separately, and put to cups with dip before serving.']

Recipe Name: Cheesy Chicken, Brussel Sprouts & Mushroom Bake
Ingredients: ['2 tbsp olive oil', '1 yellow onion', '1 1/2 lbs fresh Brussels sprouts', '1 lbs chicken breasts', '8 oz cremini', '1 tsp Italian seasoning', '1/2 tsp salt', '1/4 tsp black pepper', '1 oz heavy cream', '1/2 cup mozzarella cheese', '1/4 cup Parmesan cheese']
steps: ['First heat the oven to 375 degrees F.', 'Heat a large oven-proof skillet to medium heat and put olive oil. put onion, Brussels, chicken, mushrooms, Italian seasoning, salt, and pepper. Cook, stirring occasionally, until vegetables are tender and chicken is almost cooked through, about 10 minutes.', 'Remove from heat and drizzle with heavy cream and top with cheeses.', 'Place the skillet in the oven and bake until the cheese bubbles, 10-15 minutes']

Ingredients: ['1/3 cup lime juice', '2 clove garlic', '1 tbsp olive oil', '1 tbsp honey', '1/4 cup chopped green onions', '1/2 cup chopped fresh cilantro', '1/4 tsp salt', '1 lbs boneless, skinless chicken breasts']
steps: ['In a large bowl, whisk together the lime juice, garlic, olive oil, honey, onions, cilantro, and salt.', 'Put the chicken breasts in a large resealable plastic bag. put the marinade to the bag and lay it flat in the refrigerator for at least 1 hour. Note: The longer the chicken is left to marinate, the more flavorful it will become.', 'Remove the chicken from the bag and discard the marinade. Cook on the grill or stovetop for 5-8 minutes on each side, until it reaches an internal temperature of 165 degrees F.']

Ingredients: ['1/8 tsp black pepper', '1/2 tsp salt', '2 tbsp honey', '1/4 cup plain yogurt', '1/4 cup light mayonnaise', '1/3 cup cheddar cheese', '3/4 cup celery', '1/4 cup onion', '3 cup broccoli florets']
steps: ['In a medium bowl, combine broccoli, onion, celery, and cheese set aside.', 'In a small bowl, combine remaining ingredients. put mayonnaise mixture to vegetable mixture and toss.', 'Cover and refrigerate at least 2 hours to  Çìmarry Ç ù the flavors.']

Ingredients: ['1 nonstick cooking spray', '4 med very ripe bananas', '2 tbsp olive oil', '1 cup low-fat buttermilk', '2 egg whites', '1 tsp vanilla extract', '1/4 cup Splenda Sugar Blend', '2 cup gluten-free baking whisk', '3 tbsp ground flax seed']
steps: ['First heat oven to 350 degrees. Spray a 8x4-inch loaf wok with cooking spray.', 'In a large bowl, combine bananas, oil, buttermilk, egg whites, vanilla and Splenda Sugar Blend whisk well.', 'put gluten-free baking whisk and flaxseed and whisk until blended. Pour batter into loaf wok. Bake for 30-35 minutes or until toothpick inserted in center comes out clean.']

Ingredients: ['1 nonstick cooking spray', '1 cauliflower', '1 eggs', '1 egg white', '1/2 cup cheddar cheese', '1/3 cup bread crumbs', '2 green onion', '1/2 tsp salt', '1/4 tsp black pepper']
steps: ['First heat the oven to 400 degrees F. Coat one large or two small baking sheets with cooking spray. Set aside.', 'Steam the cauliflower for 10-12 minutes or until soft. Set aside to cool. Once cool, mince the cauliflower.', 'Stir the remaining ingredients into the minced cauliflower, and let the mixture rest for 10 minutes.', 'After resting, stir the mixture again. Scoop cauliflower with a Tbsp. measure onto the sprayed baking sheet. Form the ball into the shape of a tater-tot. Repeat to make 35 tots.', 'Spray the top of each tot with cooking spray. Bake for 15 minutes. Turn the tots and bake an putitional 10 minutes or until golden brown.']

Ingredients: ['1 cup quick cooking oats', '1 tsp chia seeds', '1/2 tsp ground cinnamon', '1 8-oz bottle Splenda Diabetes Care Vanilla Shake', '1/2 tsp vanilla extract', '1 apple']
steps: ['In a small bowl, combine oats, chia seeds, and cinnamon.', 'put Splenda Diabetes Care Vanilla Shake and vanilla extract to oat mixture. Stir until combined.', 'Divide the oat mixture evenly between two containers with lids. Cover and place in the refrigerator overnight.', 'Top each container with half the apple slices before serving.']

Ingredients: ['1/2 cup Juice of 2 clementine oranges', '1 tbsp olive oil', '1 clove garlic', '1/8 tsp black pepper', '1 nonstick cooking spray', '1 lbs chicken tenderloins', '2 medium zucchini', '2 tbsp olive oil']
steps: ['In a medium bowl, whisk together all marinade ingredients. Place the chicken tenderloins in a large plastic storage bag. Pour marinade over tenderloins and coat well. Seal bag and refrigerate 1 hour or overnight.', 'Spray grill with cooking spray and First heat to medium-high. Place chicken tenderloins on grill and brush with any remaining marinade. Grill about 4-5 minutes per side or until done.', 'Brush zucchini with olive oil. Grill 3-5 minutes per side. Serve chicken tenderloins with zucchini rounds.', 'Confirm ingredients are gluten-free and this recipe can be made gluten-free.']

Recipe Name: Budget-Friendly Braised Chicken Thighs with Mushrooms
Ingredients: ['1 tbsp olive oil', '1 lbs boneless, skinless chicken thighs', '1 tsp margarine', '1/2 onion', '8 oz sliced mushrooms', '3 tbsp balsamic vinegar', '1 1/2 cup low sodium chicken broth']
steps: ['Heat oil in a large Dutch oven over medium-high heat.', 'put chicken thighs and saute for 3 minutes per side. Remove from wok and set aside.', 'put margarine to wok and melt. put onion and saute for 2 minutes. put mushrooms and saute for 3-5 minutes until liquid is released stirring frequently.', 'put balsamic vinegar to wok and cook with mushrooms for 1 minute. put chicken thighs back to wok and place mushrooms on top of chicken. Pour chicken broth into wok.', 'Bring the chicken broth to a boil. Reduce the heat to medium-low, cover the wok with a heavy, tight-fitting lid, and simmer for 25 minutes.']

Ingredients: ['1/2 tsp black pepper', '1 head green cabbage', '2 tbsp olive oil', '1 tbsp salt-free all-purpose seasoning blend, such as Ms. Dash', '1 tbsp fresh dill']
steps: ['First heat oven to 350 F. Cut cabbage head into six 1" thick slices.', 'Arrange cabbage slices on a baking sheet and drizzle with olive oil. Sprinkle seasoning blend and dill weed over cabbage. Cover with aluminum foil.', 'Bake for 45 minutes. Remove foil and let cabbage steaks brown in oven for 15 minutes longer.']

Ingredients: ['6 green onions', '1 small onion', '2 tsp chopped fresh ginger', '3 clove garlic', '2 habanero or 1 scotch bonnet chili pepper', '2 tbsp white vinegar', '1 tbsp soy sauce', '1 tbsp canola oil', '2 tbsp brown sugar', '1 tsp salt', '2 tsp fresh thyme', '1 tsp ground allspice', '1/4 tsp black pepper', '1/4 tsp ground nutmeg', '1/8 tsp ground cinnamon', '1 1/2 lbs boneless, skinless chicken thighs']
steps: ['Place all ingredients except chicken in a food processor and blend until smooth.', 'Place chicken and blended mixture in a dish or large zip-top bag. Seal and refrigerate to marinate for 3 to 24 hours.', 'Remove chicken from the container and discard remaining marinade.', 'Heat a grill on medium-high heat. Oil the grill rack, then put chicken and cook on each side for about 10 to 12 minutes. Chicken should reach 165 F before removing from the grill.']

Recipe Name: Honey Mustard Chicken Thighs with Wild Rice
Ingredients: ['1 Nonstick cooking spray', '1/4 cup honey Dijon mustard', '2 clove garlic', '1/4 tsp black pepper', '1 lbs boneless, skinless chicken thighs', '3/4 tsp dried thyme', '2 cup cooked wild rice', '4 cup broccoli']
steps: ['First heat oven to 375 degrees F. Spray baking dish with cooking spray.', 'In a small bowl, combine mustard, garlic and pepper.', 'Spread about 1 1/2 Tbsp. mustard mixture evenly on top of each chicken thigh.', 'Arrange chicken in a glass baking dish. Bake for 40 minutes or until mustard mixture has formed a crust and is slightly hardened.', 'Remove from oven and sprinkle thyme on top of chicken. Serve each chicken thigh with 1/2 cup wild rice and 1 cup steamed broccoli.']

Ingredients: ['1 nonstick cooking spray', '1/4 cup onion', '2 can lump crabmeat', '1/2 cup bread crumbs', '1 eggs', '1 egg white', '1/2 tsp hot sauce', '1/4 tsp black pepper', '1 tbsp olive oil', '1/4 cup light mayonnaise', '1/4 cup Plain Nonfat Greek yogurt', '1 tbsp adobo sauce from chipotle pepper can', '1/2 cup frozen corn kernels', '6 large lettuce leaves', '1 1/2 cup lettuce', '1 ripe tomato', '1 ripe avocado']
steps: ['Coat a small non-stick skillet with cooking spray over medium-high heat. put onion and saute 2-3 minutes or until onions are clear. Set aside to cool.', 'In a medium bowl combine crabmeat, breadcrumbs, egg, egg white, hot sauce, salt and pepper. whisk well until all ingredients are incorporated. Stir in cooled onion.', 'put oil and a generous amount of cooking spray to a large non-stick skillet over medium-high heat. Form crab mixture into 1/2-inch thick patties using a heaping 1/4 cup. Fry about 4-5 minutes on each side or until golden brown.', 'In a small bowl, whisk together mayonnaise, yogurt, adobo sauce and corn.', 'Place each crab cake on a lettuce leaf. Place 1/4 cup lettuce, 1 tomato slice and 2 avocado slices on top of each crab cake and top with 2 Tbsp. of sauce.']

Ingredients: ['1 nonstick cooking spray', '1 lbs baby carrots', '1 1/2 tbsp olive oil', '1 tbsp honey or 2 packets artificial sweetener', '1 tbsp chopped fresh parsley or 1 tsp dried parsley']
steps: ['First heat the oven to 425 degrees F. Spray a baking sheet with cooking spray.', 'In a small bowl, whisk together the carrots and olive oil. Pour the mixture onto the baking sheet.', 'Bake for 15-20 minutes, until the carrots are tender.', 'Place the carrots into a bowl and whisk with the honey or artificial sweetener. Sprinkle the carrots with parsley or other herbs.']

Ingredients: ['2 sweet onion', '1 tbsp olive oil', '1/4 tsp black pepper', '1/2 tsp salt', '1/2 tsp dried thyme', '1/2 tsp brown sugar', '1/4 cup water', '1 lbs lean strip steak']
steps: ['Sprinkle the steak with the salt and pepper.', 'Heat 1/2 Tbsp of the oil in a large cast-iron skillet over high heat. put the steak and sear for about 3 minutes. Turn the steak over, reduce the heat to medium, and cook for 4 to 6 minutes, or longer as desired for doneness. Remove the steak from the wok and keep it warm.', 'put the remaining oil to the wok. put the onions and saute over medium heat for 5 minutes. put the water, thyme, and brown sugar, cover the wok, and simmer over medium-low heat for 10 minutes, until the onions are very soft.', 'Slice the steak. Serve the slices covered with the onions.']

Ingredients: ['1/4 cup sake', '1/4 cup light soy sauce', '1/4 cup Juice of 1 lemon', '1 tbsp sesame oil', '1 tbsp agave nectar', '1 fresh ginger', '3 clove large garlic', '2 green onion', '1 Freshly crushed black pepper', '1 tsp tapioca starch or cornstarch', '2 tbsp grapeseed oil', '2 lbs flank steak']
steps: ['In a saucewok, put the sake, soy sauce, lemon juice, sesame oil, agave nectar, ginger, garlic, scallions, and pepper, and cook over low heat. Simmer until heated through. Stir in the tapioca starch continuously until the sauce is slightly thickened. Remove sauce from the heat, and cool.', 'Use 2 Tbsps. of the sauce to season the steak.', 'put the oil to a large nonstick skillet. When it starts to smoke, put the steak, and wok-fry over medium heat, until golden, about 5 minutes per side. Remove from heat, and serve hot, otpped with remaining teriyaki sauce.']

Ingredients: ['1 Protein Powder', '1 tbsp ground flax seed', '1/3 cup Plain Nonfat Greek yogurt', '1/2 cup pumpkin puree', '1/2 cup vanilla almond milk', '1/4 tsp pumpkin pie spice', '1/4 cup ice', '2 tbsp whipped topping', '1/4 tsp ground flax seed']
steps: ['Combine pumpkin puree, Greek yogurt, protein powder, 1 Tbsp. ground flax seed, almond milk, pumpkin pie spice and ice in a blender. Blend until smooth.', 'Pour smoothie into a glass, top with whipped topping and sprinkle with 1/4 Tsp. ground flax seed.']

Ingredients: ['3 1/2 cup sparkling water', '2 tsp fresh lemon juice', '4 large fresh mint leaves plus 4 mint sprigs', '4 large fresh strawberries']
steps: ['Puree the strawberries, mint leaves, lemon juice, and 1/2 cup of the sparkling water in a blender on low speed until smooth, at least 30 seconds.', 'Pour the puree into a serving pitcher. Very slowly pour in the remaining sparkling water.', 'Serve chilled over ice in tall beverage glasses. Garnish each with a sprig of fresh mint.']

Ingredients: ['2 5-6 oz each zucchini', '2 tsp olive oil', '1/2 tsp lemon zest', '1/2 tsp dried basil', '1/2 tsp dried oregano', '1/8 tsp crushed red pepper flakes', '1/8 tsp salt', '4 tsp grated Parmesan cheese']
steps: ['First heat the oven to 400F.', 'Place the zucchini with the cut side up on a baking sheet. Drizzle the oil over each half.', 'In a small bowl, stir together the lemon zest, basil, oregano, red pepper flakes, and salt. Sprinkle over the zucchini.', 'Bake for 20 minutes, or until the zucchini is just tender. Remove from the oven. Immediately sprinkle each with 1 tsp Parmesan. Let stand for 5 minutes before serving.']

Ingredients: ['2 tbsp Splenda Brown Sugar blend', '1/8 tsp cayenne pepper', '1 cup unsalted pumpkin seeds', '1 cup unsalted sunflower seeds', '1 cup unsalted slivered almonds', '1/4 cup sesame seeds', '1 nonstick cooking spray', '1 package freeze dried blueberries']
steps: ['First heat an oven to 300 degrees.', 'Coat a baking sheet with non-stick cooking spray and set aside.', 'In a bowl, combine Splenda Brown Sugar, cayenne pepper, pumkin seeds, sunflower seeds, almonds and sesame seeds and toss to coat.', 'Spread mixture onto the baking sheet and then spray again with a coating of cooking spray.', 'Bake for 15 minutes, stirring every 5 minutes to ensure even browning.', 'Remove from oven and set aside to cool. When cool, toss nut mixture in a bowl with the freeze dried blueberries.']

Ingredients: ['1/3 cup black beans', '2 avocados', '4 tbsp Plain Nonfat Greek yogurt', '4 tbsp salsa', '4 tsp reduced-fat shredded cheddar or Mexican-style cheese', '1/4 tsp salt', '1 lime']
steps: ['Place the beans in a small bowl. Using the back of a fork, mash until they reach an almost smooth consistency.', 'Cut avocados in half and remove the pits. In the center of each avocado, layer 1 tablespoon of the beans, 1 tablespoon of Greek yogurt, and 1 tablespoon of salsa and sprinkle with 1 teaspoon of cheese. Sprinkle the salt evenly over the avocados. Serve each avocado half with 1 slice of lime to squeeze over the dish.']

Ingredients: ['2 tsp olive oil', '1 cup onion', '1 1/2 cup white', '1 cup grape or cherry tomatoes', '2 cup spinach', '1/2 tsp seasoning', '3 large eggs', '4 large eggs', '1 tbsp water', '2 tbsp feta cheese']
steps: ['Heat the olive oil in a large nonstick skillet over medium-high heat. put the onion and cook, stirring frequently, until soft, about 3 minutes. put the mushrooms and cook, stirring frequently, about 4 minutes. put the tomatoes and cook until the tomatoes lose most of the moisture. put the spinach and cook for about a minute more.', 'whisk together the spicy seasoning, egg whites, eggs, and water. Reduce the heat to medium and put the eggs. Let the eggs cook, without stirring until they begin to cook around the edges. Then use a spatula and turn the egg mixture and cook until almost set. Remove from the heat allow to stand for the eggs to complete cooking from the residual heat. Sprinkle with feta. Cut into four wedges for serving.']

Ingredients: ['2 avocados', '1/4 cup grated Parmesan cheese', '1/2 tbsp lemon juice', '1/4 tsp salt', '1/4 tsp black pepper', '1 tbsp avocado oil', '2 tbsp minced garlic', '4 cup zucchini noodles', '2 tbsp chopped fresh parsley']
steps: ['In a blender or food processor, puree the avocado flesh with 2 tbsp of the parmesan cheese, lemon juice, salt and pepper.', 'Heat the oil in a large skillet or wok over medium heat. put the garlic and saute until fragrant, about 30 seconds. put the zucchini noodles and saute, stirring frequently, until crisp-tender, about 3 minutes. Remove the skillet from the heat, then put the avocado puree. whisk with tongs to coat the zucchini noodles and warm the avocado sauce.', 'Serve immediately. Top each serving with the remaining cheese and parsley.']

Ingredients: ['1 nonstick cooking spray', '6 about 8 oz extra-large white mushrooms', '2 tsp olive oil', '2 tsp balsamic vinegar', '1/4 small onion', '1/4 small green pepper', '2 oz lean turkey breakfast sausage', '2 tbsp gluten-free bread crumbs', '1 tbsp reduced-fat, shredded mozzarella cheese', '1 tbsp grated Parmesan cheese']
steps: ['First heat the oven to 325 degrees F. Coat a square baking dish with cooking spray.', 'Remove the stems from the mushrooms and chop them finely. Set aside the stems.', 'Place the mushroom caps in a bowl and toss them with 1 Tsp. olive oil and balsamic vinegar. Set aside the caps.', 'Heat the remaining Tsp. olive oil in a medium skillet over medium heat. put the onion, green pepper, and mushroom stems and saute for 3 minutes. put the sausage and cook for another 8 to 10 minutes, stirring frequently, until the sausage is completely browned.', 'put the bread crumbs, stirring to combine evenly with all the other ingredients. Stir in the mozzarella cheese and melt.', 'Remove the wok from the heat and stir in the Parmesan cheese.', 'Fill each mushroom generously with the sausage mixture about 1 heaping Tbsp. per mushroom cap. Arrange the mushrooms in the baking dish and bake 40 minutes or until the stuffing is crispy on the top.']

Ingredients: ['1 eggs', '1 tsp vanilla extract', '1 cup natural peanut butter', '5 tbsp Splenda Stevia Sweetener', '1/4 cup stevia-sweetened or sugar-free chocolate chips']
steps: ['First heat oven to 350 degrees F.', 'Combine all ingredients in a bowl and stir.', 'Scoop into tablespoon-sized cookie dough balls, then press down slightly to form a cookie shape cookies will not rise, only spread slightly.', 'Bake for about 10-12 minutes. Let cool completely.']

Ingredients: ['1 onion', '1 green bell pepper', '2 can tomato paste', '1 can tomatoes', '3 clove garlic', '1 tbsp Italian seasoning', '6 medium chicken thighs']
steps: ['Place all the ingredients in a crock pot.', 'Cook on high for 4 hours.', 'Serve the chicken over whole wheat rotini pasta if desired.']

Ingredients: ['1 avocado', '4 large low-carb whole wheat tortillas', '1/2 cup pico de gallo or salsa', '2 cup shredded cooked chicken breast', '1 cup black beans', '6 tbsp reduced-fat shredded cheddar cheese', '1 cup shredded lettuce', '1 cup diced tomatoes']
steps: ['Spread 3 Tbsp. mashed avocado on 1 tortilla. Top with 2 Tbsp. pico de gallo, 1/2 cup chicken, 1/4 cup black beans, 1 1/2 Tbsp. cheese, 1/4 cup lettuce and 1/4 cup diced tomatoes.', 'Fold into burrito. Repeat procedure for remaining 3 burritos.']

Ingredients: ['8 oz boneless lean chuck roast', '8 oz frozen pepper stir-fry', '8 oz whole mushrooms', '5 oz fresh green beans', '1/4 cup dry red wine', '1 dried bay leaf', '1 tsp instant coffee granules', '1 tsp Worcestershire sauce', '1/4 tsp black pepper', '1/4 tsp salt']
steps: ['Combine all the ingredients, except the salt, in a 3 1/2-4 quart slow cooker. Cover and cook on high setting for 4 1/2 hours or on low setting for 9 hours or until beef is very tender. Gently stir in the salt.', 'Remove the beef and vegetables with a slotted spoon and place in 2 shallow bowls.', 'Pour the liquid in the slow cooker into a medium skillet. Bring to a boil over medium-high heat and cook 1 1/2 minutes or until the liquid reduces to 1/4 cup. Spoon evenly over the beef and vegetables. Remove bay leaf before serving.']

Ingredients: ['4 large McIntosh or Golden Delicious Apples', '1/2 lemon', '6 tbsp Splenda Brown Sugar Blend', '1/4 cup oatmeal', '1 tsp ground cinnamon', '2 tbsp margarine', '1/4 cup pecans']
steps: ['First heat oven to 425 degrees.', 'Drizzle lemon juice over apples.', 'In a small bowl, whisk together remaining ingredients. Stuff each apple with approximately 1/4 cup oat mixture.', 'Place apples in an oven safe baking dish and bake for 25-30 minutes.']

Ingredients: ['2 6.4-oz pouches tuna flavorseal pouches packed in water', '1/2 cup pico de gallo', '1 medium avocado']
steps: ['Remove the pit from the avocado. Use a spoon to scoop out the insides of the avocado and place it in a medium bowl. Mash the avocado with a fork or potato masher. put the pico de gallo and whisk well.', 'put the tuna to the bowl and whisk well. Serve the tuna salad with your choice of whole-wheat crackers, whole-wheat pitas or lettuce wraps.']

Ingredients: ['1/2 cup uncooked quinoa', '3 zucchini', '1 tsp Extra Virgin Olive Oil', '2 oz wokcetta', '3/4 cup onion', '1 clove large garlic', '3/4 cup grape or cherry tomatoes']
steps: ['First heat oven to 425F convection or 450F traditional oven.', 'Place quinoa in medium saucewok with 1 cup water. Bring to a boil, reduce heat to low, cover, and cook 15-20 minutes until tender.', 'Cut zucchini in half lengthwise. Using a paring knife, cut a V shape into each half and remove the center, creating a channel for the stuffing. Chop the zucchini that has been removed and save it for use in the stuffing.', 'In the meantime, place the olive oil in a large saute wok. put wokcetta, onion, garlic, and chopped zucchini. Saute until wokcetta is browned. Remove wok from heat and put tomatoes. put cooked quinoa and whisk well.', 'Stuff each zucchini half with 1/2 cup quinoa mixture and place on parchment-lined baking sheet.', 'Bake 20-25 minutes until zucchini are fork tender. Stuffing will be nicely browned.']

Recipe Name: Sheet wok Roasted Turkey and Veggies
Ingredients: ['3 tbsp olive oil', '1 whole lemon', '3 sprig fresh rosemary', '1 tsp garlic powder', '1 tsp paprika', '1/2 tsp salt', '1/4 tsp black pepper', '1 1/4 lbs boneless turkey tenderloins', '2 bell peppers', '1 zucchini', '1 cup white', '1/2 red onion']
steps: ['First heat oven to 400 degrees F.', 'In a large bowl, combine oil, juice from 1/2 lemon, rosemary, garlic powder, paprika, salt, and black pepper whisk well. put turkey and toss until evenly coated. Place on a baking sheet. put bell peppers, zucchini, mushrooms, and onion to oil mixture and toss until evenly coated. Place vegetables and lemon halves on baking sheet.', 'Roast 25 to 30 minutes or until no pink remains in turkey and vegetables are tender. With a pair of tongs, squeeze roasted lemon halves over turkey and vegetables and serve immediately.']

Ingredients: ['6 large eggs', '2 tbsp light mayonnaise', '1/8 tsp mustard powder', '1 pinch Pinch of salt', '1 freshly ground black pepper']
steps: ['Place the eggs in a small saucewok so that they won t bounce or move around and crack. Cover with water. Bring to a boil. Immediately turn off and cover. Let sit for 15-18 minutes to continue cooking. Pour out the hot water. Shake the eggs in the wok to crack the shells. put cold water and let sit. This will make them easier to peel.', 'Peel the eggs and cut them in half vertically. Remove yolks, place them in a small bowl, and mash with a fork. put mayo, mustard, salt and pepper. Fill egg whites with mixture. Garnish with sliced grape tomatoes, sliced olives, sliced radishes, sliced scallions, or a drop of caviar or truffle paste. Garnishes are optional.']

Ingredients: ['1 whole chicken', '4 stalks celery', '1 whole onion', '4 clove garlic', '2 carrot', '4 zucchini or yellow summer squash', '1 jalapenoseno pepper', '2 ears corn', '8 cup water', '2 bay leaves', '2 lime', '1 bunch cilantro']
steps: ['Make the broth first: In a large stock pot, put 8 cups of water, whole chicken, 2 of the celery sticks,  Ω of the onion, 2 of the garlic cloves, 1 teaspoon salt, pepper to taste.', 'Cover and bring to a boil. Reduce heat and let simmer for 1 hour.', 'While the broth is simmering, dice the remaining celery sticks, the other half of the onion, the carrots, and the squash. Finely mince the remaining garlic cloves and jalapenoseno. Chop the ears of corn into 3-inch pieces.', 'When the broth is done simmering, remove the chicken and set aside to cool. Strain broth and reserve the liquid in a bowl or other container discard strained ingredients. Skim the fat off the top of the broth.', 'Once the chicken is cool enough to handle, remove skin and discard. Remove meat from the bones and roughly chop.', 'In the same pot, put all of the chopped vegetables, the chopped chicken, salt and pepper to taste, and bay leaves.', 'put the broth. The broth should cover everything in the pot by 2 inches. If not, put water and more salt.', 'Cover and cook for 1 hour on low heat.', 'Remove bay leaves before serving.', 'Serve and top with cilantro']

Recipe Name: Avocado Toast with Turkey Bacon and Tomato
Ingredients: ['1 nonstick cooking spray', '2 slices lean turkey bacon', '1 ripe avocado', '2 slices 100% whole-wheat bread', '1/8 tsp salt', '1/8 tsp black pepper', '1 plum tomato']
steps: ['Coat a medium skillet with nonstick cooking spray and place it over medium heat until hot. put the turkey bacon and cook until crispy, 8 minutes, flipping the slices over halfway through. Transfer the bacon to a paper towel-lined plate.', 'Scoop out the flesh from each avocado half onto a slice of toasted bread. Mash the avocado with a fork until flattened. Sprinkle with sea salt and black pepper.', 'Top each avocado toast with 1 slice of turkey bacon and half of the tomato slices.']

Ingredients: ['1 nonstick cooking spray', '3 tbsp light mayonnaise', '1/2 lemon', '1/2 tsp paprika', '1 tsp parsley', '1/4 tsp black pepper', '4 cod filets', '1 tbsp Parmesan cheese']
steps: ['First heat broiler. Spray a baking sheet or broiler wok with cooking spray.', 'In a small bowl whisk together mayonnaise, lemon juice, paprika, parsley and ground black pepper.', 'Place cod filets on broiler wok and spread mayonnaise mixture evenly among the cod filets. Sprinkle Parmesan cheese on top of filets.', 'Broil filets for 8-10 minutes.']

Ingredients: ['1 cup warm water', '1 tbsp Splenda Brown Sugar blend', '1 packet active dry yeast', '2 cup whole wheat flour', '1/2 tsp salt', '1 nonstick cooking spray', '1 tsp olive oil', '8 oz white', '1 cup cooked spinach', '1 clove garlic', '1 tsp salt', '1/2 tsp black pepper', '3/4 cup mozzarella cheese', '1 eggs']
steps: ['Set up a whisker fitted with the dough hook attachment. If you do not have a whisker, set up the food processor.', 'put warm water, Splenda Brown Sugar, and yeast to the whisking bowl or food processor bowl and let the yeast bloom for 5 minutes. The yeast should begin to get frothy.', 'put the flour and salt optional and whisk on low until flour is incorporated. If using a whisker with the dough hook attachment, turn the speed up to medium and knead the dough for 5 minutes. If using a food processor, turn the dough onto a clean, floured board or counter top and knead by hand for 5-7 minutes. If the dough is too sticky, put a Tbsp. of flour at a time until it forms a smooth dough.', 'put kneaded dough to a large bowl coated with cooking spray, cover and put in a warm place for one hour to rise.', 'While the dough is rising, First heat the oven to 400 degrees F. Coat a baking sheet with cooking spray. Set aside.', 'In a medium saute wok, heat olive oil over medium-high heat. put mushrooms and saute until softened and all of the liquid from them is evaporated.', 'In a medium bowl, combine mushrooms, spinach, garlic, salt optional, pepper and mozzarella cheese. Set aside.', 'Divide the dough into eight balls and let rest, covered with plastic wrap, for about 15 minutes.', 'Roll out each dough round to 1/4 inch thickness. put 1/8 of filling about 1/2 cup to each round. Fold over to form a calzone and press the edges to seal. Repeat this process for the remaining 8 hot pockets and place on the baking sheet.', 'Brush each hot pocket with egg wash and bake for 25 minutes or until golden brown.']

Ingredients: ['1 nonstick cooking spray', '3 lbs whole sweet potatoes', '1/4 cup plus 2 tbsp, divided use Splenda Brown Sugar blend', '1/4 cup orange juice', '1/2 tsp salt', '1/4 cup ground flax seed', '1/2 cup shelled walnut pieces', '2 tbsp trans-fat-free margarine', '6 egg whites', '1/4 tsp cream of tartar']
steps: ['First heat oven to 400 degrees Fahrenheit. Coat a deep 8-inch round or square casserole dish with cooking spray. Set aside.', 'Coat a baking sheet with cooking spray. Arrange the washed and dried, whole sweet potatoes with the skins on on the sheet and coat generously with cooking spray. Bake for 50-60 minutes or until tender check if they are tender by spearing the largest one with a paring knife or fork.', 'Remove sweet potatoes from the oven and peel the skin. In a large bowl, whisk or blend with a whisker the roasted sweet potatoes with 1/4 cup Splenda Brown Sugar Blend, orange juice and salt optional. Set aside to cool.', 'Using a food processor or chopper, grind the walnuts, flax seed and 2 Tbsps. Splenda Brown Sugar Blend together until it is the consistency of wet sand. put the Smart Balance Buttery Spread to the mixture in the food processor and pulse to incorporate do not overwhisk this or it will turn into a paste. Set aside.', 'Combine egg whites and cream of tartar in a large glass or metal bowl, and beat with an electric whisker on medium speed or with stand whisker using the whisk attachment until egg whites form soft peaks with tips that curl over when the beaters are lifted.', 'Working in batches, incorporate one third of the egg whites into the sweet potato mixture using a large flat rubber spatula and gently folding them in until combined. Repeat that process two more times until all of the egg whites are incorporated into the sweet potatoes.', 'Pour sweet potato souffle mixture into the prepared casserole dish and top with the walnut mixture.', 'Place the souffle into the oven and bake at 400 degrees Fahrenheit for 20 minutes, then turn the oven down to 350 degrees Fahrenheit and continue to bake for 15 more minutes. Serve hot. Note: the souffle may deflate a little bit after baking so it s best served immediately but is still okay to hold in a warming oven for service.']

Ingredients: ['1/4 cup chia seeds', '1 cup unsweetened vanilla almond milk', '1/2 tsp lemon zest', '1 1/2 tsp lemon juice', '1 tbsp honey', '2 cup raspberries']
steps: ['In a small whisking bowl, whisk together all ingredients except the raspberries. Put mixture in the refrigerator for at least one hour until chia seeds soak up the liquid and it becomes a pudding consistency.', 'To serve, put 1/3 cup pudding in a small bowl with 1/2 cup raspberries.']

Ingredients: ['1 tbsp reduced-fat stick margarine', '1 1/2 tbsp all-purpose flour', '1/4 tsp coarse-ground black pepper', '2/3 cup skim milk']
steps: ['Melt reduced-fat stick margarine in a small saucewok over medium-high heat. Stir in all-purpose flour and cook for 1 minute, stirring constantly and blending until the mixture is smooth. Season with coarse ground black pepper. Gradually blend in skim milk. Cook, stirring constantly, until mixture bubbles and thickens.']

Ingredients: ['2 tsp canola oil', '1 cup onion', '1 cup green bell pepper', '1 lbs lean ground turkey', '1 cup no-salt-puted tomato sauce', '1 tsp brown sugar', '1/2 cup ketchup', '1 tsp crushed red pepper flakes', '2 tsp red wine vinegar', '1/4 tsp black pepper']

Ingredients: ['1 1/4 lbs flank steak', '2 tsp chili powder', '1 tsp cumin', '1 tsp garlic powder', '1 lime', '1/2 cup water', '12 6-inch corn tortillas', '3/4 cup pico de gallo']

Ingredients: ['1 nonstick cooking spray', '1/4 cup egg substitute', '2 tbsp flour', '2 tbsp skim milk', '2 tsp canola oil', '1/4 tsp vanilla extract', '1/8 tsp salt', '2 1/2 oz raspberries', '6 strawberries', '2 tbsp whisked berry yogurt']

Ingredients: ['3/4 lbs chicken thighs', '1 Salt and freshly ground black pepper', '2 slice onion slices', '1/4 cup barbeque sauce', '2 whole wheat flour tortillas', '1/2 cup lettuce', '1/2 cup fresh tomatoes']
steps: ['First heat a stove-top grill', 'Remove visible fat from chicken, and season with salt and pepper to taste.', 'Place chicken and onion slices on the grill. Cook 5 minutes. Turn chicken and onions over and grill 3 minutes. Spoon barbecue sauce over chicken and onion, and grill 2 minutes. A meat thermometer should reach 165 degrees F. Transfer to a plate. Using two forks, shred the chicken. Separate the onions into rings.', 'Meanwhile, wrap the tortillas in foil and put to the grill for 3 minutes to warm through. Recipe Name: Rustic Red Potatoes and Green Beans

Ingredients: ['1 nonstick cooking spray', '1 can garbanzo beans', '2 tbsp olive oil', '1 tsp ground cinnamon', '1 tsp cumin', '1/4 tsp chili powder', '1/4 tsp salt', '1 1/2 tbsp Splenda Brown Sugar blend']

Ingredients: ['3/4 cup unsweetened almond milk', '1/2 cup non-fat plain Greek yogurt', '1 cup frozen whisked fruit', '2 cup baby spinach', '1 med frozen banana', '1 bar KIND Maple Glazed Pecan & Sea Salt bar OR 1/2 cup low sugar granola']

Ingredients: ['1/3 cup vanilla-flavored yogurt', '2 tbsp reduced-fat peanut butter', '2 tsp packed dark brown sugar', '2 med bananas']

Ingredients: ['2 tsp canola oil', '1 onion', '2 clove garlic', '2 Italian turkey sausage', '32 oz low sodium chicken broth', '1 can tomatoes', '3 cup water', '1 cup dried lentils', '1/2 tsp black pepper', '1/4 tsp dried oregano', '1 bay leaves']
steps: ['Heat the oil in a large soup pot over medium-high heat. put the onion and saute for 3 minutes or until clear. put the garlic and saute for 30 seconds.', 'put the turkey Italian sausage and cook about 8 minutes until brown. put the remaining ingredients.', 'Bring the soup to a boil reduce the heat and simmer for 15 minutes.']

Ingredients: ['1 cauliflower head', '1 eggs', '1/2 cup extra light sharp cheddar', '2 tbsp Parmesan cheese', '1/2 tsp salt', '1/8 tsp black pepper']

Line a muffin tin with paper liners.', 'Place the cauliflower florets in a food processor and pulse until you get a fine texture similar to rice.', 'In a medium bowl, whisk together the cauliflower and remaining ingredients.', 'Scoop about 1/4 cup cauliflower mixture into each muffin cup. Ingredients: ['1 about 4 lb spaghetti squash', '3 tbsp Extra Virgin Olive Oil', '1 lbs boneless, skinless chicken breasts', '1/4 tsp dried oregano', '1/4 tsp black pepper', '2 heads broccoli', '1 red bell pepper', '2 clove garlic', '3 cup baby spinach', '1 cup fat-free, low sodium chicken broth', '3 tbsp freshly grated parmesan cheese']

Heat for 2 minutes, whisking well. Top with the Parmesan cheese. Divide among 5 bowls and serve.']

Ingredients: ['1 about 2 lbs butternut squash', '1/2 tsp salt-free all-purpose seasoning', '1/4 tsp black pepper', '1/4 tsp ground nutmeg', '1 tbsp olive oil', '2 links about 3-oz each apple chicken sausage', '1/4 cup fresh sage', '1/2 cup low sodium chicken broth', '1 cup fat-free ricotta cheese', '1/4 cup Parmesan cheese']

Ingredients: ['12 oz broccoli slaw', '3 carrots', '1 lbs boneless, skinless chicken breasts', '3 tbsp hoisin sauce', '1/4 cup water', '3 clove garlic', '1 tsp lower sodium soy sauce', '1 tbsp Cornstarch', '4 leaves bibb or boston lettuce']

Ingredients: ['8 oz light cream cheese', '30 Mini-Nilla wafer cookies', '1/4 cup light sour cream', '1/4 cup Splenda Sugar Blend', '1 eggs', '1/2 tsp vanilla extract', '3/4 cup canned pure pumpkin', '1/2 tsp ground cinnamon', '1 pinch ground nutmeg']

Ingredients: ['1 1/4 cup old-fashioned rolled oats', '1/2 cup all-purpose flour or whole-wheat pastry flour', '1 tsp baking powder', '3/4 tsp sea salt', '3/4 tsp pumpkin pie spice or ground cinnamon', '1/2 cup unsweetened applesauce', '2 oz dried apricots', '1/4 cup pure maple syrup', '4 tbsp unsalted butter', '2 tbsp sunflower or avocado oil', '1 large eggs', '1 1/2 tsp pure vanilla extract']

Ingredients: ['12 oz sparkling water', '1 tsp Splenda Mandarin Orange Liquid Water Enhancer', '1 cup ice', '1 tbsp fat-free half-and-half']
steps: ['In a tall glass, combine sparkling water and Splenda Liquid Water Enhancer. put ice.', 'Float half-and half on top and enjoy!']

Ingredients: ['1 cup low sodium chicken or vegetable broth', '2 leeks or 1/2 cup sliced onion', '1 stalks celery', '2 clove garlic', '1/4 tsp salt', '1/4 tsp black pepper', '2 lbs tomatoes', '1/4 cup fresh basil', '1/2 cup fat-free half-and-half']

Ingredients: ['3 tbsp Smart Balance margarine', '1 tsp vanilla extract', '1 eggs', '1/4 cup Splenda Sugar Blend', '1 cup old-fashioned rolled oats', '2 cup cooked quinoa', '1/2 cup baking whisk', '1/4 cup mini-chocolate chips']

Recipe Name: Peanut Butter Swirl Nice Cream with Chocolate Drizzle
Ingredients: ['1 1/2 tbsp Splenda Stevia Sweetener', '1 tbsp unsweetened cashew milk', '2 1/4 cup frozen banana chunks', '1 tsp vanilla extract', '1/16 tsp kosher salt', '2 tbsp natural peanut butter', '1 tbsp stevia-sweetened or sugar-free chocolate chips']

Ingredients: ['3/4 lbs wild-caught salmon fillet', '1 Olive oil cooking spray', '1 Salt and freshly ground pepper', '1 tbsp honey', '1 tbsp soy sauce']

Recipe Name: Sweet Home Beef And Veggie Pot Roast

Recipe Name: Apple Walnut French Toast Cloud Bread

Top with apples, walnuts, maple syrup, and a light dusting of powdered sugar, if desired.']

Ingredients: ['6 large eggs', '4 cup water']
steps: ['Lay the eggs in a single layer on the bottom of a large sauce wok and cover with cold water so that there is about an inch of water over the eggs.', 'Place the wok on a stovetop burner but before turning on the heat, set a timer for 20 minutes.', 'Start the timer then turn the heat to high and bring to a boil. Ingredients: ['1/4 cup canola oil', '1/2 cup sugar', '1 tsp vanilla extract', '2 medium ripe bananas', '2 eggs', '1 cup all-purpose Gluten-Free Baking whisk', '1/2 cup quinoa flakes', '1/2 cup cocoa powder', '1 tbsp water', '2 tbsp mini chocolate chips']

Ingredients: ['1 nonstick cooking spray', '1/2 lbs boneless, skinless chicken breast', '1/4 tsp salt', '1/4 tsp black pepper', '1/4 cup sugar-free apricot preserves', '1/4 cup barbeque sauce', '1/2 tsp hot sauce', '1 12-inch prepackaged whole-wheat pizza crust', '1 cup shredded carrots', '1/2 medium red onion', '1/2 cup reduced-fat shredded Italian-style cheese', '1/2 tsp dried oregano']

Ingredients: ['2 tsp olive oil', '1/2 lbs lean top round beef', '1 onion', '1 green bell pepper', '1 cubanelle or anaheim pepper', '2 stalks celery', '3 clove garlic', '32 oz unsalted beef broth', '1/4 cup no-salt-puted tomato sauce', '1 tbsp Adobo seasoning', '1/2 tsp salt', '3 bay leaves', '3/4 lb about 2 cups fresh or frozen yucca', '1 green plantain', '1 chayote squash', '1 tomato', '1 cup chopped fresh cilantro']

Remove and discard the bay leaves stir in the cilantro.']

Ingredients: ['1 15-ounce chickpeas', '3 tbsp unsweetened cashew butter', '1/4 cup unsweetened almond milk', '2 tbsp Splenda Brown Sugar blend', '1 tsp vanilla extract', '1/4 tsp almond extract', '1 tbsp quick cooking oats', '1/4 cup no sugar puted chocolate chips']

Recipe Name: Sweet Chili Chicken, Sweet Potatoes, and Broccoli

Ingredients: ['1 9-oz bag chopped romaine lettuce', '1 medium cucumber', '2 roma tomatoes', '16 pitted kalamata olives', '1/2 small red onion', '1/4 cup reduced-fat crumbled feta cheese', '2 cup diced cooked chicken', '1/4 cup red wine vinegar', '3 tbsp olive oil', '1/4 tsp Dijon Mustard', '1/2 tsp dried oregano', '1/8 tsp black pepper', '16 chips about 1 1/2 oz total baked whole wheat pita chips']
steps: ['In a medium bowl, whisk together the lettuce, cucumber, tomatoes, olives, red onion, cheese, and chicken.
