Or, store the dressing separately, and drizzle over the salad just before serving.', 'Enjoy the pita chips on the side or break into bits and sprinkle over your salad for puted crunch.', 'DIY: Try making your own pita chips! Use 1 whole wheat pita 6 1/2" diameter or about 2 oz.. Cut the pita in half and cut then each half into quarters. Separate each piece for a total of 16. Place on rimmed baking sheet and spray lightly with olive oil nonstick spray. Turn over each piece and spray the other side. Bake at 375 degrees F for about 10 minutes or until crisp.']

Ingredients: ['1 nonstick cooking spray', '4 wedges Laughing Cow Light Creamy Swiss Cheese Wedges', '1 tbsp canola oil', '1/2 onion', '1 tsp Smart Balance margarine', '8 oz white', '1/8 tsp salt', '1/4 tsp black pepper', '1/2 cup low sodium vegetable broth', '2 tsp Cornstarch', '2 tsp cold water', '1/4 cup 1% milk', '2 14.5-oz cans no-salt-puted canned cut green beans', '1 cup corn flakes', '1 Smart Balance margarine']

Cook putitional 2-3 minutes until thick.', 'Remove from heat and stir in green beans. Ingredients: ['1 cup frozen strawberries and peaches', '1/2 cup Plain Nonfat Greek yogurt', '1 cup unsweetened almond milk']
steps: ['Combine all ingredients in a blender and puree until smooth and thick.']

Ingredients: ['1 tbsp olive oil', '1 tsp sesame oil', '3 green onion', '1 1/2 tbsp soy sauce', '1/4 cup low sodium chicken broth', '1/8 tsp ground ginger', '2 large carrots', '3 cup cauliflower florets', '1/8 tsp black pepper']
steps: ['Cut the cauliflower into small chunks and process in a food processor until rice consistency, or grate the head of cauliflower with a grater set aside.', 'Heat 1/2 Tbsp. olive oil in a nonstick wok over medium-high heat. put carrots and scallions and saute for 5 minutes.', 'put remaining 1/2 Tbsp. olive oil and sesame oil to wok. put cauliflower  Çìrice Ç ù and remaining ingredients and lower heat to medium-low. Cook cauliflower mixture for 6-8 minutes, stirring frequently. Cauliflower should be tender, but not mushy.']

Recipe Name: Instant Pot Vegetarian Thai Mushroom Soup
Ingredients: ['8 oz sliced mushrooms, preferably cremini', '2 cup frozen pepper-and-onion blend', '1 15-oz can no-salt-puted chickpeas', '1 14.5-oz can no-salt-puted diced tomatoes', '1/2 cup water', '1 tbsp sriracha', '1/2 tsp ground cumin', '1 1/2 cup lite coconut milk', '1/2 cup chopped fresh cilantro', '1 tbsp sugar', '1 tbsp grated fresh ginger', '1/2 tsp salt']
steps: ['Combine the mushrooms, frozen vegetables, chickpeas, tomatoes, water, sriracha, and cumin in the multicooker pot.', 'Seal the lid and close the valve. Select Manual and cook for 8 minutes. Use a quick pressure release.', 'When the valve drops, carefully remove the lid and stir in the remaining ingredients. Let sit for 5 minutes to allow the flavors to blend. Serve warm.']

Ingredients: ['1 lbs chicken breasts', '1/2 tsp garlic powder', '1/4 tsp black pepper', '1 small onion', '1 cup water', '1/3 cup barbeque sauce', '8 mini whole wheat buns']
steps: ['Place the chicken breasts in a slow cooker. Sprinkle with the garlic powder and pepper. Place the sliced onion on top of the chicken. Pour in 1 cup water. Cover and cook on low for 6 hours, or until done.', 'Drain the cooking water from the slow cooker. Shred the chicken with two forks. whisk in the barbeque sauce and stir to coat the chicken. Heat through for an putitional 15 minutes.', 'Assemble the sandwiches, using 1/3 cup BBQ chicken for each bun.']

Ingredients: ['1 cup whole wheat flour', '1/2 cup all-purpose flour', '1 tsp baking soda', '1/2 tsp baking powder', '1/2 tsp ground sage', '1/2 tsp salt', '1/4 tsp black pepper', '1/2 cup Plain Nonfat Greek yogurt', '1 eggs', '1 tbsp cold water', '1 nonstick cooking spray', '1 tsp olive oil', '1 medium onion', '2 carrot', '2 stalks celery', '8 oz white', '1 1/2 lbs chicken breasts', '8 cup low sodium chicken broth']
steps: ['whisk the flours, baking soda, baking powder, sage, salt optional, and pepper in a medium bowl. put yogurt, egg, and water and knead to make a slightly sticky dough. Cover the bowl and set aside.', 'put cooking spray and olive oil to a large soup pot over medium high heat. put the onion, carrots, celery, and mushrooms. Saute for 5-7 minutes or until the vegetables are softened.', 'put the chicken and broth, and bring to a boil. Reduce to a simmer for 5 minutes.', 'Roll the dough out into an 8 inch disk that is 1/2-inch thick. Cut the dough into 1 inch pieces and drop the dumplings into the simmering broth. Stir frequently until all the dumplings are puted.', 'Simmer the dumplings for 10 minutes and serve.']

Recipe Name: Chicken Fried Rice with Cabbage, Zucchini, and Carrots
Ingredients: ['1/2 cup brown rice', '1 zucchini', '6 oz about 3 whole carrots carrots', '1/2 lbs red cabbage', '2 scallions', '3 tbsp peanuts', '1 tbsp mirin', '1 tbsp rice vinegar', '3 tbsp sichuan sauce', '1/2 lbs chicken tenders', '2 tsp olive oil', '1 tbsp toasted sesame oil', '1 tsp sesame seeds']
steps: ['Cook the rice: Fill a medium pot 3/4 of the way up with water. Heat to boiling on high. Once boiling, put the rice and cook, uncovered, 16 to 18 minutes, or until tender. Turn off the heat. Drain thoroughly and return to the pot.', 'Prepare the ingredients & make the sauce: Meanwhile, wash and dry the fresh produce. Medium dice the zucchini. Peel the carrots and thinly slice on an angle. Cut out and discard the core of the cabbage thinly slice the leaves. Thinly slice the scallions on an angle, separating the white bottoms and hollow green tops. Roughly chop the peanuts. In a bowl, combine the mirin, vinegar, and cumin-Sichuan sauce.', 'Cook & chop the chicken: Pat the chicken dry with paper towels season with salt optional and pepper on both sides. In a large wok nonstick, if you have one, heat 1 teaspoon of olive oil on medium-high until hot. put the seasoned chicken and cook 3 to 5 minutes per side, or until browned and cooked through. Leaving any browned bits or fond in the wok, transfer to a cutting board. When cool enough to handle, cut into bite-sized pieces. Transfer to a large bowl and cover with foil to keep warm.', 'Cook the vegetables: In the wok of reserved fond, heat 1 teaspoon of olive oil on medium-high until hot. put the diced zucchini and sliced carrots in an even layer. Cook, without stirring, 3 to 4 minutes, or until browned. put the sliced cabbage and sliced white bottoms of the scallions. Cook, stirring occasionally, 3 to 4 minutes, or until browned and softened. Transfer to the bowl of chopped chicken and cover with the foil to keep warm. Wipe out the wok.', 'Make the fried rice & serve your dish: In the same wok, heat the sesame oil on medium-high until hot. put the cooked rice in an even layer. Cook, without stirring, 3 to 4 minutes, or until slightly crispy. Transfer to the bowl of chopped chicken and vegetables put the sauce and stir to thoroughly combine. Serve the fried rice garnished with the sliced green tops of the scallions, chopped peanuts, and sesame seeds. Enjoy!']

Ingredients: ['3/4 cup unsalted pecan halves', '3/4 cup unsalted walnut halves', '1/2 cup unsalted whole blanched almonds', '2 egg whites', '16 packet Splenda Stevia Sweetener Jar', '1 tsp ground cinnamon', '1/2 tsp salt']
steps: ['First heat oven to 300F. Spray a baking sheet with cooking spray.', 'In a bowl, combine pecans, walnuts, and almonds. put beaten egg whites, tossing to coat.', 'In another bowl, combine Splenda Sweetener, cinnamon, and salt. Sprinkle over nuts toss to coat. Spread mixture evenly in prepared wok.', 'Bake for 30-40 minutes, stirring every 10 minutes, until nuts are toasted. Cool completely.']

Ingredients: ['1 nonstick cooking spray', '1 medium onion', '20 oz lean ground turkey', '2 1/2 tsp ground cinnamon', '1 tsp ground oregano', '1/2 tsp salt', '1/2 tsp black pepper', '2 15-oz cans low sodium tomato sauce', '1 tbsp fresh parsley', '1 lbs whole-grain penne pasta', '1 tbsp olive oil', '2 tbsp whole wheat flour', '2 cup skim milk', '1/8 tsp ground nutmeg', '1/3 cup Parmesan cheese', '1 eggs']
steps: ['First heat the oven to 350 degrees F. Coat a 9x13-inch baking sheet with cooking spray. Set aside.', 'put cooking spray to a large nonstick saute wok. Saute onions for 4-5 minutes or until translucent. put in ground turkey and saute for 8-10 minutes, or until turkey is cooked through.', 'put cinnamon, oregano, salt optional, ground black pepper, and tomato sauce. Stir to combine and bring to a simmer for 5-7 minutes or until just starting to thicken.', 'Stir in parsley and set aside.', 'Cook pasta according to package directions, omitting salt. Drain and stir immediately into turkey mixture. Pour the pasta and turkey mixture into the baking sheet and press down so it is evenly spread in the wok.', 'put the olive oil to a small sauce wok over medium heat. Stir in flour and cook the flour for 1-2 minutes, taking care not to brown it. Stir constantly.', 'Slowly whisk in the skim milk and bring to a boil, whisking constantly. whisk in the nutmeg and parmesan cheese.', 'In a small bowl, whisk the egg and then slowly whisk in the hot milk mixture to temper the egg. put the rest of the milk mixture to the egg and then pour over the top of the pasta, spreading to coat the entire thing.', 'Bake on the middle rack of the oven for 30 minutes or until bubbly and top is golden brown. Let cool for 15-20 minutes, the cut into 12 equal slices.']

Ingredients: ['1 tbsp Extra Virgin Olive Oil', '1 lbs shrimp, peeled and deveined', '1/2 tsp Kosher Salt', '1/4 tsp freshly ground black pepper', '1 Crushed red chile flakes, to taste', '1 Juice and zest from 1 lemon']
steps: ['Heat olive oil in a large skillet over medium-high heat.', 'When olive oil begins to release its aroma, put shrimp, salt, black pepper, and crushed red chile flakes. Cook shrimp on one side just until the tail of the shrimp is bright pink, approximately 1-2 minutes.', 'Turn shrimp over and squeeze lemon juice over top. Cook shrimp until all gray color is gone and they are pink and cooked through, approximately 1-2 more minutes. At this point, shrimp should be coiled slightly tighter than when they were raw. Shrimp will continue to sizzle in the wok.', 'When they are cooked completely through, transfer shrimp to a serving platter, garnish with lemon zest, and serve immediately.']

Ingredients: ['2 tbsp unsweetened cocoa powder', '2 tbsp white whole-wheat flour', '1 Nonstick cooking spray', '1/4 tsp baking powder', '1 pinch pinch salt', '1 1/2 tsp stevia powder', '1 1/2 tsp canola oil', '2 tbsp skim milk', '1/4 tsp vanilla extract', '3/4 tbsp walnuts']

Place on baking sheet and bake in oven for 20 minutes.', 'Safety Tip: Be careful when opening the foil packets because the steam can burn you.']

Ingredients: ['12 oz fresh green beans', '1 tbsp olive oil', '1 tsp Thai-style chili garlic paste', '1 tbsp whole-wheat wokko bread crumbs', '1/4 tsp salt']

Ingredients: ['1/2 cup roasted red peppers', '4 oz cream cheese', '1 cup reduced-fat sour cream', '2 tsp hot sauce', '2 cup cooked shredded chicken']
steps: ['Puree drained red peppers in a blender or food processor to make red pepper sauce.', 'In a medium bowl whisk cream cheese and sour cream together until smooth. put pureed peppers and 2 teaspoons of Tabasco sauce. Taste and put putitional hot sauce if desired.', 'Place mixture in a slow cooker for 2 to 3 hours on low heat, or bake in the oven at 350 F for 30 minutes.', 'Serve warm dip with carrots, celery, cucumber, cauliflower for dipping, or make mini roll-ups by wrapping dip inside lettuce or cabbage leaves.']

Ingredients: ['1 14.5-oz can no-salt-puted pinto beans', '1/4 cup water', '2 tsp chili powder', '1 tsp ground cumin', '1 clove garlic', '1/4 tsp hot sauce', '4 6-inch corn tortillas', '1/2 cup reduced-fat shredded cheddar or Mexican-style cheese', '2 cup shredded romaine lettuce', '4 oz grape or cherry tomatoes', '1/3 cup finely chopped red onion', '1/4 cup chopped fresh cilantro', '1 tbsp lime juice', '2 tsp olive oil', '1/4 tsp salt']

Serve immediately.']

Recipe Name: Spinach, Avocado, and Summer Berry Salad
Ingredients: ['10 oz fresh baby spinach', '1 cup diced or sliced strawberries', '1/2 cup blueberries', '1 avocado', '1/3 cup finely diced or sliced red onion', '2 tbsp olive oil', '2 tbsp white balsamic or champagne vinegar', '1 tsp honey', '1/2 large lime', '1 clove garlic', '1/4 tsp black pepper']

Ingredients: ['1 1/2 cup white whole wheat flour', '1/3 cup brown sugar', '1 tsp baking soda', '1/2 tsp salt', '2 tsp pumpkin pie spice', '2 eggs', '1 cup pumpkin puree', '3 tbsp canola oil', '1 small bananas', '1 tsp vanilla extract', '1/4 cup walnuts']
steps: ['whisk flour, sugar, baking soda, salt, pumpkin pie spice in a large bowl.', 'First heat the oven to 350 degrees F and line a muffin tin with liners.', 'In a small bowl, whisk together the eggs, pumpkin puree, melted butter, banana, and vanilla.', 'Pour the wet ingredients into the dry ingredients and stir to combine. Gently fold in the walnuts.', 'Scoop the batter into muffin tins and bake for 18-20 minutes, until a toothpick comes out clean.']

Ingredients: ['1 nonstick cooking spray', '12 oz lean ground beef', '3 1/2 oz sweet Italian turkey breakfast sausage links', '1 15-oz can no-salt-puted pinto or kidney beans', '8 oz frozen pepper stir-fry', '2 14.5-oz cans no-salt-puted stewed tomatoes', '2 tsp sugar', '1 tbsp chili powder', '1 tbsp cumin', '1/2 cup reduced-fat shredded cheddar or Mexican-style cheese']
steps: ['Lightly coat a 3 1/2- to 4-quart slow cooker with cooking spray.', 'Lightly coat a large skillet with cooking spray and place over medium-high heat until hot. Cover and cook on high for 3 1/2 hours or on low for 7 hours.', 'Stir in the remaining ingredients. Cover and let stand on low for 15 minutes to absorb flavors. Flavor improves overnight.']

Ingredients: ['1/3 cup fresh lemon juice', '1/2 cup granulated Splenda', '4 large eggs', '3 cup fresh berries']
steps: ['Place lemon juice and Splenda in saucewok. Heat and stir until sugar dissolves. Remove from heat.', 'Crack eggs into the bowl and whisk well. Slowly pour the lemon sugar whisk into the eggs while whisking. whisk for 1 minute, then return the egg mixture to the saucewok. whisk and cook on low to medium for several minutes until the egg mixture thickens. The more you whisk, the lighter the mixture will be. This will take 2-5 minutes depending on your equipment. The mixture is ready to be removed from heat when it coats the back of a spoon. Refrigerate for one hour or more. It will thicken more as it cools.', 'Place some of the lemon chiffon in a dessert glass or bowl and spoon berries over or layer lemon cream and berries. Top with berries.']

Raise the heat to high and bring the mixture to a boil. Then lower the heat to medium low and simmer, covered, until the beef is cooked through and the flavors combine, 30 minutes. Stir occasionally during cooking time.', 'Remove the chili from the heat and allow to cool for 10 minutes before serving.']

Ingredients: ['4 oz Bow-tie pasta', '2 tbsp red bell pepper', '2 tbsp orange bell pepper', '3 tbsp cucumber', '3 tbsp carrots', '3 tbsp red onion', '1/8 tsp black pepper', '2/3 cup light mayonnaise', '1/2 tsp sugar', '1 tbsp lemon juice']

Ingredients: ['1 cup unsweetened almond milk', '1 cup frozen blueberries', '2 cup baby spinach', '1 banana']
steps: ['Combine all ingredients in a blender and puree until smooth and thick.']

Ingredients: ['1 tsp dried rosemary', '1 tsp dried oregano', '1/2 tsp dried thyme', '1/2 tsp garlic powder', '1/2 tsp chili powder', '1/4 tsp black pepper', '1 tbsp olive oil', '1 1/2 lbs pork loin boneless chops']
steps: ['In a small bowl, combine rosemary, oregano, thyme, garlic powder, chili powder, and black pepper. whisk well.', 'put olive oil to a large saute wok and heat over medium-high heat. Season pork chops on both sides with herb blend.', 'Saute pork chops for about 5 minutes per side or until done.']

Ingredients: ['2 apple', '3 tbsp zero-calorie granulated sweetener, such as splenda', '1/2 tsp ground cinnamon', '1/4 cup water', '4 8-inch whole wheat flour tortillas', '1 nonstick cooking spray']
steps: ['First heat oven to 400 degrees F', 'In a medium-sized saucewok, combine apples, 2 tbsp Splenda, cinnamon, and water. Bring to a boil, and cook until apples are soft. Remove from heat. Bake for 5 minutes, then turn over and bake 5 minutes more.', 'Remove chimichangas from the baking sheet and place on individual plates. If desired, garnish with a scoop of ice cream or a dollop of whipped cream.']

Recipe Name: Light And Fluffy Spinach And Cheese Strata
Ingredients: ['10 oz frozen chopped spinach', '6 eggs', '1 1/2 cup milk', '1 cup cheddar cheese', '1/2 cup Swiss cheese', '1 tsp herbes de Provence or thyme, or other Italian herbs', '1/2 tsp garlic powder', '1/4 tsp salt', '3 slice bacon', '6 slice ciabatta bread']
steps: ['DO AHEAD OR DELEGATE: Defrost the spinach, combine and refrigerate the eggs and the milk, shred the cheese, if necessary, and refrigerate, combine the dry seasonings, cube the bread, or fully assemble and refrigerate the strata.', 'Defrost the spinach in the microwave or on the stovetop. Spray a 9 X 13-inch glass or ceramic baking dish with nonstick cooking spray. Cook the bacon, if necessary.', 'In a large bowl, whisk together the eggs and the milk. whisk in the cheeses, herbs, garlic powder, and salt. Stir in the spinach, bacon optional, and bread cubes until the bread is completely moistened. Pour the egg mixture into the baking dish, smoothing it with the back of a spoon, if necessary. Refrigerate, covered, for at least 4 hours and up to 24 hours.', 'When you are ready to bake it, remove the strata from the refrigerator and First heat the oven to 350F. Bake it in the center of the oven, uncovered, for 45-50 minutes until it is browned on the edges and cooked through in the center. Cut into squares to serve.', 'SLOW COOKER DIRECTIONS: In the slow cooker, whisk together the eggs and the milk, then whisk in the cheeses, herbs, garlic powder, and salt. Stir in the spinach, bacon, and bread cubes until the bread is completely moistened. Cook on low for 4-5 hours or on high for 2-3 hours. Slow cooker cooking times may vary Ç ùget to know your slow cooker and, if necessary, adjust cooking times accordingly.']

Ingredients: ['9 oz romaine lettuce', '1 cup cabbage', '1 cup shredded carrots', '1/4 cup slivered almonds', '1 tbsp plus 1 tsp Toasted sesame seeds', '2 cup cooked chicken breast', '2 tbsp rice vinegar', '2 tbsp lower sodium soy sauce', '2 tbsp olive oil', '1/4 tsp crushed red pepper flakes']

Ingredients: ['1 14-oz can low sodium chicken broth', '1 14.5-oz can canned diced tomatoes', '2 oz whole grain or multigrain pasta', '2 cups diced cooked chicken breast', '1 cup packed baby spinach', '1/4 cup chopped fresh basil', '1 tbsp extra virgin olive oil', '1/4 tsp salt', '2 tbsp grated parmesan cheese']
steps: ['In a medium saucewok, combine the broth and tomatoes and their liquid and bring to a boil over high heat. Stir in the pasta, return to a boil, reduce heat, cover, and simmer 6 minutes or until pasta is just tender.', 'Remove from heat and stir in the remaining ingredients, except the cheese. Let stand, covered, 5 minutes to absorb flavors and heat through. Serve topped with cheese.']

Ingredients: ['1/3 cup sugar', '1/4 cup water', '2 cups skim milk', '1 12 oz can evaporated skim milk', '3 tbsp granulated sugar substitute baking blend', '1/4 tsp ground cinnamon', '2 cinnamon sticks', '2 tsp vanilla extract', '5 large eggs', '2 2/3 cups raspberries']
steps: ['First heat the oven to 350 degreesF.', 'Combine the sugar and water in a small heavy-bottomed saucewok. Bring to a boil over medium-high heat and cook, swirling the wok occasionally, until the caramel is lightly browned, about 12 minutes. Immediately pour the caramel into a 2-quart round baking dish, tilting the dish to evenly coat. Set aside until the caramel is cool and hardened, about 10 minutes.', 'Meanwhile, combine the milk, evaporated milk, sugar substitute, cinnamon powder, and cinnamon sticks in a medium saucewok. Bring to a simmer over medium-low heat and cook, stirring occasionally, for 6 minutes. Remove from the heat. Stir in the vanilla and let stand 15 minutes. Remove the cinnamon sticks.', 'Beat the eggs in a medium bowl. Slowly whisk into the milk mixture until well blended. Pour into the baking dish.', 'Place the baking dish with the flan mixture into a 9 by 13 inch roasting wok and fill the roasting wok with enough hot water to come one-third of the way up the sides of the baking dish. Bake until the custard is set but jiggles slightly in the center, 50-55 minutes.', 'Transfer the wok to a rack let cool 1 hour. Refrigerate until well chilled, about 3 hours or overnight. To unmold, run the tip of a small knife around the edge of the flan. Place a large flat plate on top of the flan and flip it over. Cut the flan into wedges and serve each wedge with 1/3 cup raspberries.']

Ingredients: ['1 1/2 cup cottage cheese', '1 cup sour cream', '3 green onions', '2 tsp hot sauce', '1 tsp fresh or dried dill', '1/2 tsp garlic powder', '1/3 cup crumbled blue cheese']
steps: ['whisk all ingredients together in a medium bowl. Serve immediately, or cover and refrigerate until chilled. OPTIONAL: For a creamier dip, blend everything together in a food processor or blender.']

Ingredients: ['1 cup brown rice', '12 oz frozen broccoli stir fry vegetable blend', '2 tbsp peanut oil', '2 clove garlic', '8 oz lean sirloin beef', '1/4 cup low sodium chicken broth', '1 tbsp Cornstarch', '2 tbsp lower sodium soy sauce']
steps: ['Prepare rice according to package directions or start with 2 cups cooked rice.', 'Microwave frozen stir-fry vegetable blend on defrost setting for 3-4 minutes to thaw.', 'In a fry wok or wok heat oil and saute the garlic until fragrant. put vegetable blend and cook over high heat, stirring constantly, for about 5 minutes. Remove from wok and set aside.', 'put the beef to the wok and cook until beef is done to your likeness, or about 7 minutes.', 'Prepare the sauce by combining chicken broth, cornstarch and soy sauce in a bowl.', 'put cooked vegetables, sauce and tomato to the wok with the beef. Heat and stir until sauce is thick. Serve stir fry with 1/2 cup cooked rice.']

Ingredients: ['2 ripe medium-size bananas', '2 medium-size avocados', '1/3 cup lite coconut milk', '1/3 cup cocoa powder', '1/4 cup Splenda Sugar Blend']
steps: ['put all of the ingredients to a food processor or blender and blend until completely smooth, stopping occasionally to scrap the sides of the food processor.', 'If you have a homemade ice cream maker, blend the mixture in the ice cream maker for 10 minutes, then pack into a container and freeze. If you do not have an ice cream maker, just pack and freeze.', 'To serve, bring the ice cream out of the freezer about 20 minutes before serving to slightly thaw so it s easier to scoop.']

Recipe Name: Sugar Free Yogurt Parfait with Fresh Berries
Ingredients: ['1 cup Plain Fat-Free Greek Yogurt', '1/2 cup Fresh Blueberries', '5 drops SweetLeaf Sweet Drops Clear']
steps: ['In a bowl, whisk Greek yogurt and SweetLeaf Sweet Drops Clear with a spoon until the mixture is a creamy consistency.', 'Take a tall glass or small bowl for your parfait and put a layer of yogurt to the bottom. put berries and nuts optional between layers of yogurt until you reach the top. Enjoy!', 'Tip: A finished parfait stores great in the fridge for easy meal prep on the go!']

Recipe Name: Chicken Stir-Fry with Snow Peas and Bell Pepper
Ingredients: ['1/2 cup low sodium chicken broth', '2 tbsp rice vinegar', '1 1/2 tbsp lower sodium soy sauce', '1 tsp grated fresh ginger', '2 clove garlic', '1/4 tsp black pepper', '1 nonstick cooking spray', '2 cup fresh or frozen snow peas', '1/3 cup chopped green onions', '2 whisked color bell peppers', '2 tsp canola or corn oil', '1 lbs boneless, skinless chicken breasts', '2 tsp Cornstarch', '1/4 cup water']
steps: ['In a small bowl, whisk together the broth, vinegar, soy sauce, gingerroot, garlic, and pepper. Set aside.', 'Lightly spray a large skillet or wok with cooking spray. Cook the snow peas, green onions, and all the bell peppers over medium-high heat for 4-5 minutes, or until tender-crisp, stirring occasionally. Transfer to a plate.', 'In the same skillet, heat the oil, swirling to coat the bottom. Cook the chicken for 4-5 minutes, or until no longer pink in the center, stirring frequently.', 'Return the snow pea mixture to the skillet. Stir in the broth mixture. Bring to a boil, still over mediumhigh heat. Boil for 1 minute, stirring occasionally.', 'Put the cornstarch in a small bowl. put the water, stirring to dissolve the cornstarch. Stir into the chicken mixture. Cook for 45 seconds to 1 minute, or until thickened, stirring occasionally.']

Ingredients: ['2 cup cubed cooked chicken', '1/2 cup low-fat tzatziki sauce or nonfat plain Greek yogurt', '2 whole grain pocket style pitas', '1 cup diced cucumber', '1 cup diced tomato', '1/2 cup unsalted, sliced dry-roasted almonds']
steps: ['In a medium whisking bowl, whisk together the chicken and tzatziki sauce. Stuff  Ω cup of the chicken mixture into each pita pocket.', 'Top each filled pita pocket with  º cup cucumbers,  º cup tomatoes, and 2 Tbsp sliced almonds.']

Recipe Name: Baked Fish Fillets with Thyme-Dijon Topping
Ingredients: ['1 nonstick cooking spray', '4 grouper or other mild fish fillets', '3 tbsp light tub margarine', '2 tbsp fresh parsley', '1 tsp Dijon Mustard', '1/4 tsp dried thyme', '1/4 tsp red hot-pepper sauce', '1/8 tsp salt']
steps: ['First heat the oven to 350 degrees F. Lightly spray a baking sheet with cooking spray.', 'Place the fish on the baking sheet. Bake for 18-20 minutes, or until the fish flakes easily when tested with a fork.', 'Meanwhile, in a small bowl, stir together the remaining ingredients.', 'Spread the margarine mixture over the fish.']

Ingredients: ['3/4 lbs ground beef', '1 package frozen vegetable and grain protein blends', '1 diced tomatoes', '1 tbsp cumin']
steps: ['Heat a Dutch oven over medium-high heat. put beef and cook until browned, stirring frequently. Stir in the frozen vegetable mixture, tomatoes, and 1 cup water. Bring to a boil. Reduce heat to medium-low, cover, and cook 10 minutes.', 'Remove from heat. Stir in the cumin, 1/4 teaspoon salt, and 1/4 teaspoon pepper, if desired.', 'Spoon equal amounts into 4 bowls.']

Ingredients: ['4 large red or green bell peppers, or a combination', '1 nonstick cooking spray', '1/2 cup onion', '3 clove medium garlic', '8 oz ground beef', '2 tsp chili powder', '1 tsp ground cumin', '1/8 tsp salt', '3/4 cup low-sodium salsa', '1 cup no-salt-puted canned black beans', '1/2 cup plus 2 tbsp fresh cilantro', '1/4 cup shredded cheddar cheese, or use Mexican blend, Monterey Jack, or pepper jack', '1/4 cup light sour cream']
steps: ['First heat the oven to 375F.', 'In a microwave oven, place the bell peppers with the cut side up on a paper towel. Microwave on 100% power high for 4-5 minutes, or until tender-crisp. Transfer with the cut side up to a 9-inch square baking dish or shallow casserole dish.', 'Meanwhile, lightly spray a large skillet with cooking spray. Heat over medium heat. Cook the chopped bell pepper tops, onion, and garlic for 5 minutes, stirring occasionally.', 'Stir in the beef. Cook for 5 minutes, stirring occasionally to turn and break up the beef. Discard any drippings.', 'Sprinkle the beef mixture with the chili powder, cumin, and salt. Cook for 1 minute. Stir in the salsa. Remove from the heat.', 'Gently stir in the beans and 1/2 cup cilantro. Spoon the beef mixture into the peppers. Cover the baking dish with aluminum foil.', 'Bake for 30 minutes, or until heated through. Remove from the oven. Sprinkle the Mexican blend cheese over the beef mixture. Let stand for 5 minutes.', 'Top the peppers with the sour cream. Sprinkle with the remaining 2 tablespoons cilantro.']

Ingredients: ['2 lbs red potatoes', '1/2 cup 1% milk', '1 tbsp unsalted butter', '1/4 tsp salt', '1/8 tsp black pepper']
steps: ['Pour 1/4 cup of water into a medium pot fitted with a steamer basket and bring to a boil over high heat. put the red potatoes, cover, and reduce the heat to medium. Cook until the potatoes are tender, 25-30 minutes. Set aside to cool.', 'In a small saucewok, heat the milk and butter over medium heat until the butter melts, 2 minutes. Remove the saucewok from the heat and set aside to slightly cool.', 'put the potatoes to a large bowl and, using a potato masher, mash until almost smooth. put the milk mixture, salt, and black pepper and whisk until well combined.']

Ingredients: ['1/4 lbs Italian turkey sausage', '2 tsp olive oil', '1/2 lbs russet or baking potatoes', '2 cup onion', '2 cup ready-to-eat spinach', '2 cup sliced baby bella mushrooms', '2 tsp garlic', '2 large eggs', '5 large egg whites', '1/4 cup milk', '1/2 cup fresh basil', '1/4 tsp freshly ground black pepper']
steps: ['First heat the broiler. Cut the sausage into 1/2-inch slices.', 'Heat the oil in a medium, ovenproof, nonstick skillet over medium-high heat. put the potatoes and saute 3 minutes. put the sausage, onion, and spinach and saute 3 minutes, stirring several times. put the mushrooms and garlic. Continue to cook 1 to 2 minutes.', 'Meanwhile, whish the whole eggs, egg whites, and milk together. Tear the basil into small pieces and put to the egg mixture along with the black pepper.', 'Pour egg mixture into the skillet and gently stir vegetables to make sure the egg mixture spreads throughout the wok. Press the sausage and vegetables into the egg mixture. Turn the heat to low and cook 10 minutes. Frittata will be mostly cooked through.', 'Place the frittata under the broiler for 1 to 2 minutes to brown. Watch to make sure the top doesn t brown too much.', 'To serve, loosen frittata around edges, cut in half, and slip each half onto an individual plate.']

Ingredients: ['1 nonstick cooking spray', '20 oz lean ground turkey', '1 eggs', '1/2 cup old fashioned rolled oats', '1 clove garlic', '1 tbsp Dijon Mustard', '1 tsp hot sauce', '1 tsp steak seasoning', '1/2 tsp black pepper', '1/4 cup barbecue sauce', '1/4 cup whole berry cranberry sauce', '1/4 cup low sodium chicken broth', '1 tbsp hot sauce']
steps: ['First heat the oven to 400 degrees F. Coat a baking sheet with cooking spray. Set aside.', 'In a large bowl, whisk together the turkey, egg, oats, garlic, mustard, hot sauce, steak seasoning, and black pepper. whisk well.', 'Scoop meatballs the size of a heaping Tbsp. on to the baking sheet, setting them side by side so they are touching, to make 25 meatballs. Spray the tops of the meatballs with cooking spray and bake for 20 minutes or until the internal temperature is 165 degrees F.', 'While the meatballs are baking, whisk together the BBQ sauce, cranberry sauce, chicken broth, and hot sauce optional. Bring to a boil. Reduce heat and simmer until thickened.', 'When the meatballs are done, toss them in the BBQ sauce to coat.']

Recipe Name: Grilled Angel Food Cake With Melted Berries
Ingredients: ['3 cup whisked berries', '1 tsp Splenda', '1 tbsp maple syrup', '1/4 tsp cardamom', '4 tsp balsamic vinegar', '1 angel food cake, cut into eight', '1 vegetable oil']
steps: ['Line a medium bowl with a large piece of aluminum foil, pressing the foil into the sides of the bowl well.', 'put the berries, Splenda, maple syrup, cardamom, and balsamic vinegar over all.', 'Wrap the foil up, forming a package, and twist the top so the liquid doesn t escape.', 'First heat the grill over medium-high heat and place the berry package on the grill.', 'Grill for 5-6 minutes, turning and shaking the package occasionally. Spray the cake slices lightly with vegetable oil to prevent sticking and put the cake slices to the grill to mark. Grill gently for 2-3 minutes, place on a serving dish and pour the melted berries over the cake.', 'If desired, serve with sugar-free whipped cream or low- or no-fat Greek yogurt.']

Ingredients: ['4 eggs', '4 slice hearty whole grain bread', '1 avocado', '1/2 tsp salt', '1/4 tsp black pepper', '1/4 cup Plain Nonfat Greek yogurt']
steps: ['To poach each egg, fill a 1-cup microwaveable bowl or teacup with 1/2 cup water. Gently crack an egg into the water, making sure it s completely submerged. Cover with a saucer and microwave on high for about 1 minute, or until the white is set and the yolk is starting to set but still soft not runny.', 'Toast the bread and spread each piece with 1/4 of the mashed avocado.', 'Sprinkle avocado with the salt optional and pepper. Top each piece with a poached egg. Top the egg with 1 Tbsp. Greek yogurt.']

Recipe Name: Greek Orzo Salad with Peas, Lemon and Kalamata Olives
Ingredients: ['8 oz whole-wheat orzo', '1 cup English cucumber', '1 cup tomatoes', '1/2 cup red onion', '1/4 cup Kalamata olives', '2 tbsp fresh dill', '6 oz feta cheese', '1/2 cup frozen peas', '1 tbsp lemon juice', '2 1/2 tbsp Extra Virgin Olive Oil', '1 tsp dried oregano', '1 cup baby spinach leaves']
steps: ['Combine all ingredients except spinach leaves in a large bowl. Marinate at least one hour in refrigerator, covered, before serving. put spinach leaves just before serving.']

Ingredients: ['2 cup cooked chicken', '1 cup Gala apples', '1/2 cup celery', '2 tbsp scallions', '1/4 cup raisins', '1/3 cup light mayonnaise', '1 tbsp light sour cream', '1 tbsp lemon juice', '1/4 tsp ground cinnamon', '1/4 tsp black pepper']
steps: ['Cube cooked chicken. Dice apple and celery. Chop scallions', 'Combine chicken, apple, celery, scallions, and raisins in a large salad bowl.', 'whisk together mayonnaise, sour cream, lemon juice, cinnamon, and black pepper. Pour over the chicken-apple mixture and toss.', 'Refrigerate to chill prior to serving.']

Ingredients: ['1 Nonstick cooking spray', '4 slice turkey bacon', '1 medium onion', '2 clove garlic', '2 medium celery stalks', '2 medium carrots', '2 can low sodium chicken broth', '2 can cannellini beans', '1 can tomatoes', '1 tsp parsley', '1 tsp basil', '1/4 tsp black pepper', '1 cup small shell quinoa pasta', '1/4 cup Parmesan cheese']
steps: ['Coat a large soup pot with cooking spray over high heat. put bacon and saute until crisp.', 'Reduce heat to medium and put onion, garlic, celery, and carrots. Saute about 5-7 minutes or until vegetables begin to brown. put broth and simmer for 5 minutes.', 'Stir in beans, tomatoes, parsley, basil, and pepper and simmer for 10 minutes. put the pasta and continue to simmer for 10-15 minutes or until pasta is al dente.', 'Serve soup in a bowl sprinkled with Parmesan cheese.']

Ingredients: ['1 about 4 lbs whole chicken', '2 tsp salt-free herb seasoning, such as Ms. Dash', '1 tsp black pepper', '1 tsp garlic powder']
steps: ['Remove inside giblets from the chicken if they are included save them for making chicken broth. Pat the chicken dry with paper towels.', 'In a small bowl combine seasoning blend, pepper and garlic powder. Sprinkle half the seasonings inside the chicken. Rub the remaining seasoning on the outside of the chicken.', 'Place the chicken breast-side-up in an oval slow cooker or neck-up in a round slow cooker. Cover and cook on low setting for 8 hours.', 'Remove chicken from bones and discard the skin. Serve now, or store cooked chicken in the fridge for 3-5 days.']

Ingredients: ['1/2 14-oz can artichoke hearts', '4 oz button mushrooms', '1 small tomato', '1/4 cup finely chopped green onion', '1/4 cup chopped fresh parsley', '1 1/2 tsp dried basil', '3/4 tsp dried oregano', '1/2 oz reduced-fat feta cheese']
steps: ['In a medium bowl, toss together all the ingredients except the feta.', 'put the feta and toss gently. This salad is best if served within 1 hour.']

Ingredients: ['1/2 lbs ground chicken breast', '1/2 lbs ground chicken', '1/4 cup sun-dried tomatoes', '1/4 cup onion', '1/4 cup fresh basil', '1/4 cup fresh flat Italian parsley', '4 clove garlic', '1/2 tsp fine sea salt', '1/2 tsp black pepper']
steps: ['whisk all ingredients together and form 4 patties. Grill 3-4 minutes on each side and serve with guacamole.']

Ingredients: ['2 Splenda Diabetes Care Vanilla Shake', '1 1-ounce box sugar-free instant butterscotch pudding whisk', '1 premade pecan pie crust']
steps: ['In a medium bowl, combine cold Splenda French Vanilla Diabetes Care Shakes and sugar-free butterscotch pudding whisk, whisking for about two minutes. Place in the fridge and let cool for about 1 hour.', 'Once cooled, spread pudding into premade pecan pie crust. Top with stevia-sweetened chocolate shavings or chopped pecans if desired.']

Recipe Name: Herbed Soft Scrambled Eggs on Toast
Ingredients: ['2 slices sprouted whole-grain or whole-wheat bread', '1 tsp olive oil', '2 eggs', '1/8 tsp salt', '1/4 cup loosely packed chopped fresh herbs']
steps: ['Toast the bread in a toaster or toaster oven to desired doneness.', 'While the bread is toasting, prepare the eggs: fully heat the oil in a medium stick-resistant skillet over medium-low heat. Pour the eggs into the hot skillet and cook while gently stirring or folding the mixture until the eggs are no longer runny, yet are still moist, about 1 1/2-2 minutes. Remove the skillet from the heat, sprinkle with the salt, and gently stir or fold in the herbs.', 'Transfer the toasts to plates. Top each toast with half the herbed eggs. If desired, sprinkle with freshly ground black pepper to taste. Serve.']

Ingredients: ['20 oz boneless skinless chicken breasts', '1/4 tsp salt', '1/2 tsp black pepper', '1/4 cup whole wheat flour', '1 eggs', '1 juice of 1 lemon', '1/2 cup bread crumbs', '1 tsp Italian seasoning', '1 tsp olive oil', '2 tbsp capers', '1/2 cup low sodium chicken broth', '1/4 cup chopped fresh parsley']
steps: ['First heat the oven to 475 degrees F. Coat a baking sheet with cooking spray and set aside.', 'Slice the chicken breast in half lengthwise and then pound to 1/4-inch thickness. Season each chicken breast with salt and ground black pepper.', 'Set up three wide bowls or flat-bottom containers. Fill the first bowl with the whole wheat flour, the second bowl with the egg and 1 tsp lemon juice, and the third bowl with the breadcrumbs and Italian seasoning. whisk the egg and lemon juice together. Combine the breadcrumbs and Italian seasoning and whisk well.', 'Dredge one chicken breast in the flour and shake off the excess. Then dip the chicken breast in the egg, and then coat in the breadcrumb mixture. Place on the baking sheet. Repeat this process for the remaining three chicken breasts.', 'Spray the top of each chicken breast with cooking spray and bake for 8 minutes. Turn the chicken breasts over and bake for 5 more minutes. Ensure that the chicken is cooked to an internal temperature of 165 degrees F.', 'While the chicken is baking, heat the oil and a generous amount of cooking spray over medium heat in a small nonstick skillet. put the capers and saute for 2-3 minutes.', 'put about 1 tbsp lemon juice and cook until the lemon juice is completely reduced. put the chicken broth and simmer until reduced by half. Stir in the parsley.', 'Remove the chicken from the oven and serve with 1 Tbsp. of sauce drizzled over the chicken.']

Ingredients: ['12 hard-boiled eggs', '4 Laughing Cow Light Creamy Swiss Cheese Wedges', '1 tbsp Dijon Mustard', '1 tsp horseradish', '1/2 tsp salt', '1/4 tsp black pepper', '4 cup arugula']
steps: ['In a medium bowl, mash together egg whites, cheese wedges, mustard, horseradish, salt optional and ground black pepper using a potato masher or sturdy whisk. You can also use a food processor but take care not to over process the egg salad. Pulse until combined but still slightly chunky.', 'Serve 1/2 cup egg salad mixture on top of 1 cup arugula. You could also serve with arugula on toasted whole wheat bread for an open-face sandwich.', 'Crack and peel the hard-boiled eggs. Slice the eggs in half and discard the yolks.']

Recipe Name: Roast Beef with Creamy Horseradish Sauce
Ingredients: ['1/2 cup horseradish', '3 lbs sirloin tip roast or bottom round roast', '2 cup sour cream', '5 clove garlic', '2 tsp Kosher Salt', '1 1/2 tbsp black pepper', '1/4 cup Dijon Mustard']
steps: ['First heat the oven to 400 degrees F. Combine the black pepper, salt, and garlic, and rub all over the roast. Place the meat in a large roasting wok. Roast the meat for about 20 minutes.', 'Reduce the heat to 325 degrees F, and bake for about 50 putitional minutes or until a meat thermometer inserted in the roast registers 140 degrees F for medium rare. Cook longer if desired.', 'Remove the roast from the oven. Cover loosely with foil, and let stand for 15-20 minutes. Cut the meat across the grain into thin slices.', 'Combine the ingredients for the horseradish sauce, and serve with the sliced beef.']

Ingredients: ['2 cup plain non-fat yogurt', '1/2 cucumber', '2 clove garlic', '1/2 tsp dried dill', '1/4 tsp salt', '2 tsp lemon juice', '1 tsp olive oil', '6 cup fresh vegetables']
steps: ['12-24 hours before serving, line a strainer with a paper coffee filter or cheesecake cloth. Place over a bowl. Spoon yogurt into coffee filter, cover, and refrigerate for 12-14 hours.', 'Yogurt will now be thick. Discard the collected liquid beneath or use it in soups or breads. Remove yogurt from the filter and place in a small bowl.', 'whisk cucumber, garlic, dill weed, salt, lemon juice, and olive oil into yogurt. Refrigerate for one hour before serving.', 'Serve with a variety of vegetables like: fresh green beans lightly steamed, green, red, or yellow bell peppers, carrots, celery, zucchini, yellow squash, tomatoes, cucumbers, radishes, broccoli, and cauliflower.']

Ingredients: ['1 tbsp olive oil', '1 nonstick cooking spray', '1 onion', '1 cup sliced mushrooms', '1 medium red bell pepper', '1/2 tsp dried thyme', '1/4 tsp crushed red pepper flakes', '1/4 tsp black pepper', '1 clove garlic', '3 links apple chicken sausage', '1/4 cup water', '1 lbs sweet potatoes']
steps: ['put olive oil and a generous amount of cooking spray to a large saute wok over medium high heat.', 'Saute the onions, mushrooms and red bell pepper for 6-7 minutes or until starting to caramelize.', 'put the thyme, crushed red pepper flakes, ground black pepper and garlic. whisk well and saute 1-2 more minutes.', 'Stir in the chicken sausage and water and saute for 3-4 more minutes, scraping the bottom of the wok to whisk in any brown bits on the bottom.', 'Gently stir in diced, cooked sweet potatoes and serve.']

Ingredients: ['1/2 cup salsa or pico de gallo', '1 lime', '1 tbsp chopped fresh cilantro', '1 tsp chili powder', '1 nonstick cooking spray', '1 1/4 lbs firm white fish such as tilapia or halibut', '1/2 cup Greek plain yogurt', '1 tbsp hot sauce', '8 6-inch corn tortillas']
steps: ['In a medium bowl whisk together the salsa, lime juice, cilantro, chili powder, salt, and pepper. Set aside.', 'Coat a large saute wok with cooking spray. Saute fish over medium heat for 2 minutes on each side. Pour salsa mixture over fix and saute an putitional 3 minutes.', 'Remove the fish from the wok and flake with a fork, whisking in the salsa mixture.', 'In a small bowl combine the yogurt and hot sauce. Evenly divide the fish among 8 tortillas and top each with a dollop of the yogurt sauce.']

Ingredients: ['1/8 tsp ground nutmeg', '3/4 tsp ground cinnamon', '1 tbsp brown sugar', '3 tbsp buttery spread', '1 nonstick cooking spray', '1/4 tsp ground cloves', '2 carrot', '1 sweet potatoes', '1/3 cup pecans']
steps: ['First heat the oven to 350 degrees. Coat a 1 1/2- to 2-quart casserole dish with nonstick cooking spray set aside. put water to a large saucepot until it s 2/3 full. put the sweet potato to the pot and bring to boiling over medium heat. Cook the sweet potato for 20 minutes. put the carrots to the pot and continue to cook for 15 to 20 minutes, until vegetables are tender. Drain, reserving 1/4 cup of the cooking water, and put the vegetables to a bowl.', 'Mash the sweet potato and carrots and the 1/4 cup reserved cooking water with a potato masher. put 2 Tbsp. of the buttery spread, the brown sugar, cinnamon, cloves, and nutmeg, and whisk well. put the mixture to the prepared casserole dish. Top with the pecans and the remaining melted buttery spread.', 'Bake the casserole, covered, for 15 minutes. Uncover and bake 10 minutes more, until the top is lightly browned.']

Ingredients: ['15 oz chickpeas', '1 1/2 cup chicken or vegetable broth', '1 tbsp olive oil', '1 onion', '2 stalks celery', '1 carrot', '1 leeks', '3 clove garlic', '1/2 cup white wine', '28 oz diced tomatoes', '1 lemon', '15 oz cannellini beans', '1/3 cup fresh oregano', '1/2 tsp salt']
steps: ['In a large saucewok, heat the oil over medium heat. put the onion and celery and saute for 4 minutes. put the carrot and leek and saute for 6 to 7 minutes, until the vegetables are soft. put the garlic and saute for 1 minute.', 'put the wine and cook for 3 to 4 minutes, until the wine evaporates. put the tomatoes and lemon zest and cook for 1 minute. Pour in the broth and bring it to boiling. Lower the heat, cover, and simmer for 20 minutes, until the mixture has thickened.', 'put the beans and simmer, uncovered, for 5 minutes. Stir in the lemon juice, oregano, salt, and pepper and simmer for 1 minute.']

Recipe Name: Baked Hot Wings with Cilantro Lime Dip
Ingredients: ['2 lbs whole chicken wings', '1/2 cup no-sugar-puted apricot preserves', '1 tbsp garlic', '1 tbsp reduced sodium soy sauce', '1 tsp Thai style chili garlic sauce', '2 tbsp lime juice', '1/2 tsp black pepper', '1 cup Plain Nonfat Greek yogurt', '1/4 cup fresh cilantro']
steps: ['First heat oven to 375 degrees.', 'Coat a baking sheet with cooking spray. Remove skin from wings. Lay chicken wings in a single layer on the baking sheet and spray again with cooking spray.', 'Bake for 10 minutes. While the chicken is baking, whisk apricot preserves, 2.5 Tsps.. of garlic, soy sauce, chili garlic sauce, lime juice and 1/4 Tsp. ground black pepper together and set aside.', 'After the wings have been in the oven for 10 minutes, coat them generously with the apricot preserve mixture. Return to the oven for another 15 minutes or until wings are cooked through and glazed is caramelized.', 'In a small bowl, whisk together Greek yogurt, 1 Tbsp. lime juice, cilantro and 1/4 Tsp. ground black pepper. Serve dipping sauce with hot wings.']

Ingredients: ['1/3 cup rolled oats', '15 oz Can Chickpeas', '2 tbsp Splenda Granulated Sweetener', '1/3 cup almond butter', '1 1/2 tsp vanilla extract', '1/4 cup mini chocolate chips']
steps: ['In a food processor, pulse rolled oats until ground into a fine powder.', 'put chickpeas, Splenda sweetener, almond butter, and vanilla extract. Process until mixture comes together into a dough. put chocolate chips and pulse until just combined.', 'Divide into 24 portions and roll into balls. Chill until ready to serve.']

Recipe Name: Maryland's Eastern Shore Cream of Crab Soup
Ingredients: ['1 tbsp unsalted butter', '1 medium onion', '1/2 lbs lump crabmeat', '4 cup low sodium seafood or chicken broth', '1 cup half-and-half', '2 tbsp Cornstarch', '1/4 tsp Old Bay seasoning', '1/8 tsp dried dill', '1/8 tsp black pepper']
steps: ['Melt butter in a large pot over moderate heat. put onion and cook for a few minutes, until the onion become soft and transparent.', 'put crab meat. Cook 2 to 3 minutes, stirring constantly.', 'put chicken broth and bring mixture to a boil. Reduce heat to low.', 'Combine half & half creamer and cornstarch in a small bowl. whisk until smooth. put to soup and increase heat slightly, stirring constantly until mixture thickens and comes to a boil.', 'put dill weed, Old Bay seasoning and pepper to soup. Cook for 5-10 minutes longer. Serve warm.']

Ingredients: ['2 med fully ripened bananas', '3 tbsp unsweetened cocoa powder', '1/2 tsp vanilla extract', '1/4 tsp peppermint extract', '1 tbsp cacao nibs']
steps: ['put the frozen banana coins, cocoa powder, and extracts to a food processor. Cover and pulse 10 times to chop the bananas.', 'Process the banana mixture on high speed until creamy, about 2 Ω minutes. Every 30 seconds, stop and scrape down the inside of the food processor.', 'put the cacao nibs and pulse 3 times to combine.', 'Enjoy immediately, soft-serve style. Or freeze until solid at serving time, set it out for 15 minutes, scoop, and serve.']

Ingredients: ['1/2 cup frozen chopped veggie whisk, such as broccoli, cauliflower, and carrots', '1/2 cup cooked brown rice', '1/2 cup shredded cabbage', '1 tbsp shredded carrot', '1 tsp coconut aminos', '1 tsp sesame oil', '1/2 tsp fresh grated ginger', '1/2 tsp garlic powder', '1 pinch crushed red pepper flakes', '1 hard-boiled egg']
steps: ['Layer rice, frozen vegetables, cabbage, and carrot in a 16 oz glass jar with lid.', 'In a small bowl whisk coconut aminos, sesame oil, ginger, garlic powder and red pepper flakes. Pour over rice and vegetables. Top with a lid and refrigerate.', 'Remove jar from refrigerator at least 15 minutes before you are ready to eat.', 'Pour 5 ounces boiling water into the jar, close the lid and shake to combine. Let ingredients steep in unopened jar for 2 minutes.', 'Peel and slice the hard-boiled egg, and put to the soup. Pour contents from jar into a bowl, or enjoy straight from the jar!']

Ingredients: ['1 avocado', '1/4 cup Plain Nonfat Greek yogurt', '1/2 cup water', '1/4 cup fresh cilantro', '3 tbsp lime juice', '1 tbsp garlic', '1/4 tsp salt']
steps: ['In a blender or food processor, puree all ingredients until smooth. put more water if you would like a thinner dressing.', 'Store in a jar with a tight fitting lid or other airtight container in the fridge for up to 7 days.']

Ingredients: ['1 tbsp olive oil', '2 15-oz cans low-sodium great northern or cannellini beans', '1 14.5-oz can no-puted-salt fire-roasted diced tomatoes', '1 cup low-sodium tomato sauce', '1 1/2 cup low sodium vegetable broth', '1/2 med eggplant', '2 cup shredded green cabbage', '1 red bell pepper', '3 clove garlic', '2 tbsp Apple Cider Vinegar', '1 tsp dried oregano', '3 bay leaves', '1/4 tsp plus 1/8 tsp salt', '1/4 tsp black pepper']
steps: ['Brush the inside of the slow cooker with the olive oil. put the remaining ingredients to the slow cooker stir to combine.', 'Cover and cook on low for 6 hours, until the vegetables and beans soften. Remove and discard the bay leaves before serving.']

Ingredients: ['4 oz low sodium turkey breast', '12 small skewers or toothpicks', '1/4 English cucumber', '12 cherry tomatoes', '24 about 2 ounces fresh mozzarella balls', '1 tbsp olive oil', '1 tbsp balsamic vinegar', '1/8 tsp salt', '1/8 tsp black pepper']
steps: ['Cut the turkey into 12 1-inch cubes.', 'Thread each skewer with 1 slice of cucumber, 1 turkey cube, 1 tomato, and 2 mozzarella pearls.', 'Place the skewers in a single layer on a large plate. Drizzle with the olive oil and balsamic vinegar and sprinkle with the salt and black pepper.']

Ingredients: ['12 oz lean boneless beef tenderloin', '3 green onion', '2 clove garlic', '2 tsp rice wine vinegar', '2 tbsp water', '3 tbsp lower sodium soy sauce', '1 tbsp honey or 2 packets artificial sweetener', '1/2 tsp black pepper', '1 16-oz bag frozen stir-fry vegetables']
steps: ['Wrap the beef in plastic wrap and freeze until firm but not rock hard. Once firm, slice the beef thinly into long strips. Place in a baking dish.', 'In a small bowl, whisk together the scallions, garlic, rice wine vinegar, water, soy sauce, Splenda, and pepper. Pour the mixture over the beef and let it marinate in the refrigerator for at least 30 minutes, up to 2 hours. While the beef is marinating, First heat an indoor or outdoor grill.', 'Remove the beef from the marinade and shake off any excess marinade. Grill beef for 2-3 minutes on each side or until it is cooked to a medium-well doneness.', 'Steam the vegetables and serve the beef over the steamed vegetables.']

Ingredients: ['4 chicken breast cutlets', '2 tbsp mango chutney or mango salsa', '2 tbsp fresh lime juice', '2 tsp grated fresh ginger, or 1/2 Tsp. ground ginger', '1 tbsp olive oil', '1/4 cup orange juice', '1 tsp minced fresh oregano or 1/4 to 1/2 Tsp. dried oregano', '1/2 tsp hot pepper sauce', '2 clove garlic']
steps: ['In a large resealable plastic storage bag, combine chicken with remaining ingredients. Place in refrigerator and marinate 8 hours or overnight, turning halfway during marinating time.', 'First heat grill to medium-high heat. Place chicken on grill, discarding excess marinade. Grill chicken 4 to 6 minutes per side, or until cooked through.']

Ingredients: ['1 Nonstick cooking spray', '1 large onion', '1 3-oz link fully cooked adouille or chorizo chicken sausage', '1 red bell pepper', '2 clove garlic', '1/2 tsp turmeric', '1/2 tsp paprika', '3 cup low sodium chicken broth', '1/2 tsp salt', '6 cup fresh or frozen cauliflower rice', '1/2 tsp black pepper', '12 oz raw shrimp']
steps: ['put cooking spray to a large skillet over medium-high heat. put sausage, onion, bell pepper and garlic. Saute until onions are starting to caramelize, about 8 minutes.', 'Stir in turmeric and paprika. put the broth, cauliflower rice, salt and pepper. Bring to boil then reduce heat to low, cover and simmer about 5 minutes.', 'put the shrimp to the wok, then cover and cook until shrimp are just opaque in center, about 6 minutes.']

Ingredients: ['1 nonstick cooking spray', '1 3/4 cup whole wheat flour', '6 egg whites', '1 tbsp hot sauce', '1/2 cup cornmeal', '1/2 tsp salt', '1/2 tsp black pepper', '1 lbs boneless, skinless chicken breasts', '1 large egg', '1 cup skim milk', '1/2 cup Plain Nonfat Greek yogurt', '2 tbsp olive oil', '1/2 tsp baking soda', '1 1/2 tsp baking powder']
steps: ['First heat the oven to 375 degrees F. Coat a baking sheet with cooking spray. Set aside.', 'In a small bowl, put 1/4 cup of the whole wheat flour. In a second small bowl, whisk together 3 of the egg whites and hot sauce. In a third small bowl, whisk together the corn meal, salt, and pepper.', 'Slice chicken breasts lengthwise into 1-inch thick strips this should make 15 strips. Dredge each strip in the flour and shake off the excess, then dip in the egg white, then coat in the corn meal, and lay on the prepared baking sheet.', 'Once all of the chicken strips are coated, spray each strip with cooking spray on both sides. Bake for 20 minutes.', 'While the chicken is cooking, First heat a waffle iron according to manufacturer directions set it to high. In a small bowl, whisk together the egg, milk, yogurt, and oil.', 'In a large bowl, sift together the baking soda, remaining 1 1/2 cup whole wheat flour and baking powder.', 'In another bowl, whip the remaining 3 egg whites to stiff peaks.', 'whisk the wet ingredients into dry ingredients until combined. Gently fold in the whipped egg whites until combined. Cook the waffles according to your waffle iron instructions. For 4-inch square waffles, each waffle uses 1/2 cup batter. Cook the waffles until they are dark golden brown.', 'Serve two waffles with 3 strips of chicken.']

Recipe Name: Herbs de Provence Roasted Chicken Breasts
Ingredients: ['2 10-oz breasts bone-in, skin on chicken breasts', '1 tsp olive oil', '1 1/2 tsp dried herbs de Provence or crushed rosemary', '1/4 tsp salt']
steps: ['First heat oven to 425F.', 'Place the chicken in a baking wok. Brush the chicken skin with the oil. Sprinkle with the herbs de Provence and salt.', 'Roast until the chicken is well done internal temperature of at least 165F and skin is crisped and browned, about 40-45 minutes.', 'Let stand for at least 5 minutes. If desired, drizzle the chicken with any wok juices. Serve.']

Ingredients: ['1/4 cup white vinegar', '1/4 cup water', '1 tbsp corn oil', '1/2 cup ketchup', '3 tbsp Worcestershire sauce', '2 tbsp onion', '2 tbsp brown sugar', '1/8 tsp garlic powder', '2 tsp mustard powder', '1/4 tsp salt', '1/8 tsp coarse ground black pepper', '4 chicken breasts', '1 nonstick cooking spray']
steps: ['First heat oven to 350 F. Combine all sauce ingredients in a small saucewok and simmer for 15 minutes over medium-low heat, stirring occasionally.', 'Place chicken in a 9x13-inch baking dish coated with cooking spray. Cover chicken evenly with 1 cup barbecue sauce.', 'Back for 20-25 minutes, baste with remaining sauce, and cook another 5-10 minutes or until chicken is tender and no longer pink.']

Ingredients: ['4 oz deli ham', '1 cup sweet onion', '1 1/2 cup egg substitute', '1/2 cup cheddar cheese']
steps: ['Place a medium nonstick skillet over medium-high heat until hot. Coat the skillet with nonstick cooking spray, put ham, and cook until beginning to lightly brown, about 2-3 minutes, stirring frequently. Remove from skillet and set aside on separate plate.', 'Reduce the heat to medium, coat the skillet with nonstick cooking spray, put onions, and cook 4 minutes or until beginning to turn golden, stirring frequently.', 'Reduce the heat to medium low, put ham to the onions, and cook 1 minute this allows the flavors to blend and the skillet to cool slightly before the eggs are puted. Pour egg substitute evenly over all, cover and cook 8 minutes or until puffy and set.', 'Remove the skillet from the heat, sprinkle cheese evenly over all, cover and let stand 3 minutes to melt the cheese and develop flavors.']

Ingredients: ['1 15.5-oz can cannellini beans', '1 cup grape tomatoes', '1/4 cup diced red onion', '1/4 cup diced green bell pepper', '1/4 cup crumbled reduced-fat feta cheese', '6 Kalamata olives', '1/4 cup red wine vinegar', '1/4 cup olive oil', '1/2 tsp dried oregano', '1/4 tsp black pepper']
steps: ['In a medium salad bowl, combine the beans, tomatoes, onion, bell pepper, feta cheese, and olives.', 'In a small bowl, whisk together the vinegar, olive oil, oregano, and black pepper. Pour the dressing over the salad ingredients and whisk to coat. Serve cold.']

Ingredients: ['6 cup cauliflower florets', '1 tbsp or 1 tsp dried rosemary fresh rosemary', '1 1/2 tbsp olive oil', '1/4 tsp salt', '1/4 tsp black pepper']
steps: ['Roast for 15 minutes remove from oven and stir. Continue roasting for 10 minutes or until cauliflower is tender and lightly browned.', 'First heat oven to 450 F.', 'In a large bowl, toss cauliflower with rosemary, olive oil, salt, and pepper. Spread seasoned cauliflower on a large baking sheet use two sheets if they are crowded on one.']

Ingredients: ['1 lbs flank steak', '1 medium onion', '1 bay leaf', '4 cup water', '1 tbsp plus 1 tsp olive oil', '1 large onion', '1/4 cup lime juice', '2 clove garlic', '1/4 tsp salt', '1/4 tsp black pepper', '1 nonstick cooking spray', 'for garnish lime wedges', 'for garnish chopped fresh cilantro']
steps: ['In a large saucewok, combine the beef, quartered onion, bay leaf, and water. Bring to a simmer. Reduce the heat to medium low. Cover and simmer until the beef is tender, about 1 hour 10 minutes. Transfer the beef to a cutting board and let cool. To save the broth for another use, skim any fat and strain the broth, discarding the bay leaf. Refrigerate for up to 1 week or freeze for up to 1 month.', 'Heat 1 Tbsp oil in a large skillet over medium heat put the sliced onion and cook, over medium heat, stirring occasionally, until the onion is very tender and begins to caramelize, about 10 minutes.', 'Meanwhile, with two forks, shred the beef and transfer to a large bowl. put the lime juice, garlic, remaining 1 tsp oil, salt, and pepper. Let stand 20 minutes.', 'Spray a griddle or nonstick skillet with nonstick spray and heat over mediumhigh heat. put the beef and caramelized onion and cook, turning occasionally, until the beef and onions are browned, about 8 minutes. Serve garnished with lime wedges and cilantro.']

Ingredients: ['1 cup quinoa', '1 1/2 cup water', '1 tbsp Extra Virgin Olive Oil', '1 lemon', '1 tomatoes', '1 cucumber', '1 cup fresh parsley', '1/2 cup fresh mint', '1/2 tsp salt', '1/4 tsp black pepper']
steps: ['Rinse quinoa and then combine with 11/2 cups water. Bring to a boil then reduce to simmer. Cover and cook for 15 minutes or until all liquid is absorbed. Fluff with a fork and then cool completely.', 'Combine cooled quinoa with olive oil, lemon zest, lemon juice, tomato, cucumber, parsley, mint, salt optional, and ground black pepper. Refrigerate or serve.']

Ingredients: ['6 tbsp light mayonnaise', '1/4 cup fat-free plain yogurt', '2 limes', '2 tbsp olive oil', '1 tbsp salt-free cajun seasoning', '3 clove garlic', '1/4 tsp salt', '32 about 1 lb shrimp', '8 6-inch corn tortillas', '2 cup chopped whisked greens', '1 tbsp chopped fresh cilantro']
steps: ['First heat the broiler. Set the broiler rack 3-4 inches from the heat.', 'In a small bowl, stir together the mayonnaise, yogurt, and 1 tbsp lime juice. Set aside.', 'In a large bowl, whisk together the oil, remaining lime juicee, Creole seasoning, garlic, and salt. put the shrimp to the mixture, tossing gently until well coated.', 'Spread the shrimp in a single layer on a large baking sheet. Broil the shrimp for 2-3 minutes. Using tongs, turn over the shrimp. Broil for 2-3 minutes, or until the shrimp turn pink on the outside.', 'Divide the shrimp equally among the tortillas. Top each with the greens and cilantro. Drizzle with the white sauce.']

Ingredients: ['2 Granny Smith or other tart apple', '1 tbsp lemon juice', '1 tsp canola oil', '1/4 cup apple cider', '1 tbsp sugar-free maple-type syrup', '1/4 tsp ground cloves', '1/4 tsp ground cinnamon', '1 tbsp slivered almonds']
steps: ['Toss the apple slices with the lemon juice.', 'In a large skillet, heat the oil over medium heat. put the apples and saute for 3 minutes. Reduce the heat to low, cover, and simmer for about 6 to 7 minutes, stirring occasionally. Remove the apples from the wok and set aside.', 'In the same skillet put all the remaining ingredients except the almonds. Bring to a boil and cook over medium-high heat until syrupy, scraping up any bits of apple remaining in the wok. put back the apples and sprinkle with the sliced almonds.']

Ingredients: ['8 bamboo skewers', '1 lbs boneless, skinless chicken breasts', '2 tbsp Splenda Brown Sugar blend', '2 tbsp lower sodium soy sauce', '2 clove garlic', '1 tsp minced fresh ginger', '2 tbsp lime juice', '1/2 tsp Asian-style hot sauce, such as sriracha', '2 tbsp creamy peanut butter', '1/4 cup unsweetened coconut milk beverage']
steps: ['Soak bamboo skewers in warm water for at least 30 minutes. While skewers are soaking, slice chicken breasts into eight strips lengthwise.', 'In a medium bowl, whisk together 1 tbsp Splenda Brown Sugar, 1 tbsp soy sauce, half the minced garlic, ginger, lime juice and hot sauce. put chicken to the marinade and marinate chicken strips in the refrigerator for 1 hour.', 'Prepare an indoor or outdoor grill.', 'While the chicken is marinating, whisk together the remaining tbsp Splenda brown sugar blend, remaining tbsp soy sauce, remaining minced garlic, peanut butter, and coconut milk in a microwave safe bowl. Set aside.', 'Thread chicken strips lengthwise onto the soaked bamboo skewers. Grill chicken for 4-5 minutes one each side.', 'Right before serving, microwave sauce for 30 seconds. Remove from microwave and whisk again to combine. Serve two skewers with 2 Tbsps. of sauce.']

Ingredients: ['1 whole 8-Ounce Splenda French Vanilla Diabetes Care Shake', '3 ice cubes', '2 oz espresso']
steps: ['Pour a Splenda French Vanilla Diabetes Care Shake into a glass.', 'put ice until the glass is  æ full.', 'Fill the rest of the glass with espresso or coffee then stir until whisked. Enjoy!']

Ingredients: ['2 stalks celery', '1 nonstick cooking spray', '14 oz spicy chicken sausage', '1 medium onion', '2 carrot', '1 red bell pepper', '3 cup water', '1 can low sodium chicken broth', '1 cup lentils', '1/2 tsp salt', '1 tsp black pepper', '1 bay leaves', '1/4 cup fresh parsley']
steps: ['Coat a large soup pot with cooking spray. Over medium-high heat saute sausage until lightly brown.', 'put celery, onions, carrots and red bell pepper to pot and saute over medium-high heat for approximately 4 minutes or until onions begin to turn clear.', 'put the water, broth, lentils, salt, pepper and bay leaf. Bring to a boil reduce heat and low simmer for 1 hour.', 'Remove bay leaf, put parsley and serve.']

Ingredients: ['1/2 cup water', '1 1/2 package unflavored gelatin', '1/2 cup water', '4 tsp Splenda Strawberry Watermelon Liquid Water Enhancer', '1 cup water', '1 cup Plain Nonfat Greek yogurt', '1 cup Fresh Strawberries', '4 tbsp sugar-free whipped cream']
steps: ['In a medium bowl, stir unflavored gelatin into cold water. Let stand for 3 minutes.', 'Stir in boiling water and whisk until gelatin has fully dissolved.', 'Stir in Splenda Liquid Water Enhancer.', 'Fill a 1-cup measuring cup to the top with ice. Fill remainder of the cup with cold water. put to gelatin mixture and stir until ice is melted.', 'In a high-powered blender, combine gelatin mixture and Greek yogurt and blend on high for about 1 minute.', 'Stir in diced strawberries.', 'Spoon mixture evenly into four large custard cups and chill for 1 hour until set.', 'Store in refrigerator until ready to be served. Top each yogurt whip with a tablespoon of sugar-free whipped cream.']

Ingredients: ['1 nonstick cooking spray', '2 medium zucchini', '10 oz grape tomatoes', '1 tbsp olive oil', '1/4 tsp black pepper', '1/2 lemon', '2 tbsp Dijon Mustard', '4 chicken breasts', '1/2 tsp salt', '1/2 tsp garlic powder', '1 tsp dried oregano', '1 tbsp Parmesan cheese']
steps: ['First heat oven to 350 degrees. Coat a large baking dish with cooking spray. In a small bowl combine zucchini, tomatoes, olive oil, 1/8 Tsp. black pepper and toss to coat. Set aside.', 'In another small bowl whisk together lemon juice and Dijon mustard. Set aside', 'Season chicken breasts on both sides with 1/8 Tsp. pepper, garlic powder and oregano. Place chicken breasts in baking dish and brush top with mustard mixture. Sprinkle with Parmesan cheese.', 'Pour zucchini and tomatoes around chicken in baking dish. Bake for 30 minutes or until done.']

Recipe Name: Holiday Pumpkin Pie With Maple-Ginger Crust
Ingredients: ['1 1/2 cup graham cracker crumbs', '3 tbsp maple syrup', '1 tsp canola oil', '1 egg white', '1 tsp finely minced crystallized ginger', '1 tsp ground ginger', '1/2 cup Splenda Sugar Blend', '2 tsp ground cinnamon', '1/4 tsp ground cloves', '1/4 tsp salt', '2 eggs', '1 tsp vanilla extract', '1 15-oz can pumpkin puree', '1 tsp Cornstarch', '1 12-oz can evaporated skim milk', '1/2 cup light whipped topping']
steps: ['First heat the oven to 425 F.', 'Make the crust: in a bowl, combine the graham-cracker crumbs, maple syrup, oil, egg white, crystallized ginger, and 1/2 tsp of the ground ginger. Press into a 9-inch, nonstick pie wok, to form an even crust. Set aside.', 'In a small bowl, whisk together the Splenda, cinnamon, the other 1/2 tsp of ground ginger, cloves, and salt.', 'In another bowl, beat the eggs and vanilla together. put in the Splenda mixture and stir to combine.', 'put in the pumpkin and stir until the mixture is well blended. Dissolve the corn starch in about 2 to 3 Tbsp. of the evaporated milk. put the corn starch mixture and the remaining evaporated milk to the pumpkin mixture, and whisk until smooth. The mixture will be thin.', 'Pour the pumpkin pie filling into the prepared crust. Place the pie on a baking sheet. Bake for 15 minutes at 425F. Lower the heat to 350F, and bake an putitional 40 minutes, or until the filling is set when a knife inserted comes out clean.', 'Remove the pie from the oven, and let cool for 2 hours before serving. Cut into 8 wedges. Top each slice with 1 tbsp whipped topping right before serving.']

Ingredients: ['6 oz canned tuna or salmon, packed in water', '2 tbsp Plain Nonfat Greek yogurt', '1 tsp olive oil', '2 tbsp chopped scallions or other onion', '1 tbsp chopped green olives', '1 tsp lemon zest', '2 tbsp chopped toasted walnuts or other nuts', '1 large avocado']
steps: ['In medium bowl, toss together salmon or tuna, yogurt, olive oil, green onion, green olives, lemon zest and toasted nuts. Stir the mixture to blend everything well. Spoon about half of the mixture into each of the avocado halves and serve.']

Ingredients: ['1 nonstick cooking spray', '8 oz cooked chicken breast', '9 oz frozen spinach', '1 clove garlic', '1/2 tsp cumin', '1 tbsp fresh cilantro', '1/4 tsp black pepper', '1/2 cup cheddar cheese', '3 tbsp Parmesan cheese', '10 corn tortillas', '8 oz canned green chile enchilada sauce']
steps: ['First heat oven to 350 degrees F. Spray a large metal or glass baking dish with cooking spray.', 'In a small bowl, combine spinach, garlic, cumin, cilantro, pepper, cheddar cheese, and parmesan cheese whisk to incorporate. put shredded chicken whisk to incorporate.', 'Scoop 1/4 cup chicken-spinach mixture into a tortilla. Roll tortilla and place seam side down in a baking dish. Repeat process for remaining 9 tortillas.', 'Pour enchilada sauce over tortillas. Bake 25 minutes.']

Recipe Name: Chickpea Pasta & Calabrian Tomato Sauce with Mushrooms, Spinach, and Peppers
Ingredients: ['4 oz cremini mushrooms', '4 oz mini sweet peppers', '1 shallot', '2 clove garlic', '6 oz chickpea rotini pasta', '2 tsp olive oil', '1 tbsp capers', '2 tbsp tomato paste', '1 1/2 tsp calabrian chili paste', '1/4 cup water', '3 oz baby spinach', '2 tbsp mascarpone cheese']
steps: ['Prepare the ingredients: Fill a medium pot 3/4 of the way up with salted water cover and heat to boiling on high. Wash and dry the fresh produce. Cut the mushrooms into bite-sized pieces. Cut off and discard the stems of the peppers remove the cores, then thinly slice lengthwise. Peel and thinly slice the shallot. Peel and roughly chop 2 cloves of garlic.', 'Cook the pasta: put the pasta to the pot of boiling water. Cook, stirring occasionally, 4 to 6 minutes, or until al dente still slightly firm to the bite. Turn off the heat. Reserving 1 cup of the pasta cooking water, drain thoroughly and rinse under cold water to prevent sticking. Return to the pot.', 'Cook the vegetables & make the sauce: Meanwhile, in a medium wok nonstick, if you have one, heat 2 teaspoons of olive oil on medium-high until hot. put the mushroom pieces in an even layer. Cook, without stirring, 3 to 4 minutes, or until lightly browned. put the sliced peppers, sliced shallot, capers, and chopped garlic season with salt optional and pepper. Cook, stirring occasionally, 2 to 3 minutes, or until slightly softened. put the tomato paste and chile paste. Cook, stirring frequently, 1 to 2 minutes, or until thoroughly combined. put 1/4 cup of water carefully, as the liquid may splatter. Cook, stirring occasionally, 1 to 2 minutes, or until the liquid is slightly reduced in volume. Turn off the heat. Stir in the spinach until wilted and combined.', 'Finish & serve your dish: To the pot of cooked pasta, put the cooked vegetables and sauce and half the reserved pasta cooking water. Cook on medium-high, stirring gently, 1 to 2 minutes, or until the pasta is coated if necessary, gradually put the remaining cooking water to ensure the pasta is thoroughly coated. Turn off the heat. Stir in the mascarpone until combined. Taste, then season with salt and pepper if desired. Enjoy!']

Recipe Name: Grilled Fish Tacos With Strawberry-Mango Salsa
Ingredients: ['1 tbsp Extra Virgin Olive Oil', '2 tbsp lime juice', '1 tsp lime zest', '1/4 tsp chipotle chili powder', '1/2 tsp ground cumin', '1/4 tsp fine sea salt', '1/4 tsp freshly ground black pepper', '1 lbs cod filets', '8 corn tortillas', '1/2 cup strawberries', '1/2 cup mango', '1 small shallot', '1/4 tsp lime zest', '2 tbsp lime juice', '1/4 cup fresh cilantro']
steps: ['In a medium bowl, whisk together the oil, lime juice, lime zest, chili powder, cumin, salt, and pepper. put the cod and marinate in the refrigerator for 15-20 minutes.', 'While fish is marinating, stir together all the salsa ingredients in a medium bowl.', 'First heat an outdoor grill or grill wok to medium-high heat.', 'Remove the cod from the marinade and grill for 3-4 minutes on one side. Then flip and grill 1-2 minutes on the other side, or until fish flakes easily with a fork.', 'Transfer the cod to a plate and let it rest for 5 minutes, then use a fork to flake it into bite-size pieces.', 'Working in batches if necessary, grill the tortillas for 20 seconds each. Divide the fish evenly among the tortillas, garnish with the salsa about 2 tablespoons per taco, and serve.']

Ingredients: ['1/8 tsp salt', '1/2 tsp black pepper', '1 lbs boneless sirloin steak', '1 large onion', '1/2 cup water', '8 oz French bread', '1 1/2 tbsp prepared mustard']
steps: ['First heat the oven to 350F.', 'Sprinkle 1/16 teaspoon salt and the pepper evenly over both sides of the steak. Place a large nonstick skillet over medium-high heat until hot. Coat with nonstick cooking spray, put the steak, and cook 5 minutes.', 'Turn and cook another 4 minutes or until the beef is done as desired. Place the beef on a cutting board and set aside.', 'Coat the wok drippings with nonstick cooking spray, reduce the heat to medium, and put the onions. Coat the onions with nonstick cooking spray and cook 6-7 minutes or until they are richly browned, stirring frequently.', 'put water to the onions and cook 1 minute or until most of the moisture has evaporated, stirring constantly. Remove from heat.', 'Wrap the bread in foil, place in the oven, and bake 5 minutes or until hot. Meanwhile, thinly slice the beef diagonally.', 'Using a serrated knife, cut the bread in half lengthwise and spread a thin layer of mustard on each side. Top with beef, then onions and any juices. Sprinkle with the remaining salt, top with the other bread half, and cut in fourths crosswise.']

Ingredients: ['4 cup unsweetened almond milk', '1/4 cup almonds', '1/4 cup cocoa powder', '1/4 cup Splenda Sugar Blend', '1/2 tsp coconut extract', '1/2 cup whipped topping']
steps: ['put almonds to a dry saute wok over medium-high heat and saute until lightly toasted. Set aside to cool.', 'put almond milk, cocoa powder, Splenda, and coconut extract to a blender and blend until incorporated and slightly foamy.', 'put hot chocolate mixture to a saucewok over medium heat and bring to a simmer.', 'put one cup of hot chocolate to a coffee mug, top with 2 Tbsps. whipped topping and sprinkle with 1 Tbsp. cooled, toasted almonds.', 'Repeat for three remaining coffee mugs.']

Ingredients: ['2 tbsp Extra Virgin Olive Oil', '1/2 cup onion', '1 clove garlic', '1 cup celery', '1 cup carrot', '1 tbsp butter', '1/4 cup all-purpose flour', '2 cup chicken stock, plus putitional, if desired', '3 cup chicken or turkey, or leftover chicken or turkey', '1 cup baby peas', '2 tbsp Italian parsley', '1/2 tsp sea salt', '1/2 tsp pepper', '5 sheets frozen phyllo dough']
steps: ['First heat oven to 375F.', 'Place 1 tablespoon olive oil in saucewok. put onion and garlic and cook 2-3 minutes until it begins to soften. put celery and carrot and cook 5 minutes to soften. Set aside.', 'Place 1 tablespoon of olive oil and butter in 4-quart saucewok. Melt butter. whisk in flour and whisk well. mixture will be dry. Gradually put 1 cup stock to saucewok. Cook 2-3 minutes until mixture begins to thicken and takes on a golden color.', 'put chicken, peas, parsley, and putitional stock to achieve desired consistency some like it soupy, some like it thick. Season with salt and pepper to taste. Place mixture in baking dish.', 'Spray each sheet of phyllo with olive oil mister and place on top of baking dish. Trim edges.', 'Bake for approximately 25 minutes or until crust is golden and pie is bubbly.']

Ingredients: ['1 nonstick cooking spray', '1 lbs strawberries', '1 pints blueberries', '1 tsp lemon zest', '2 tbsp lemon juice', '3 tbsp Splenda Sugar Blend', '1 1/2 tbsp Cornstarch', '1 tsp ground cinnamon', '1 cup old-fashioned rolled oats', '3 tbsp Splenda Brown Sugar Blend', '1/2 cup pecans', '4 tbsp trans-fat-free margarine']
steps: ['First heat oven to 350 degrees F. Spray a 9-inch pie wok with cooking spray.', 'In a medium bowl combine the berries, lemon zest, lemon juice, 2 Tbsps. Splenda Æ Sugar blend, corn starch and cinnamon. whisk well and pour into pie wok.', 'In another medium bowl, combine the oats, remaining 1 tbsp Splenda sugar blend, brown sugar blend, pecans, and margarine. Work the margarine into the dry ingredients with your hands until it is crumbly.', 'Sprinkle the crisp topping mixture evenly over the berries. Bake for 55 minutes or until the top is brown and the fruit is bubbly. Serve warm.']

Ingredients: ['2 eggs', '2 egg whites', '3/4 cup light ricotta cheese', '1/2 tsp vanilla extract', '1/4 cup unsweetened vanilla almond milk', '1 large ripe banana', '1 lemon', '1 cup almond flour', '1/2 cup ground flax seed', '1 tsp baking powder', '1 nonstick cooking spray', '1/2 cup blueberries']
steps: ['put the eggs, egg whites, ricotta cheese, vanilla, almond milk, banana, lemon juice, and lemon zest to a blender. Blend until smooth.', 'In a small bowl, combine the almond flour, ground flax seed, and baking powder. put the dry mixture to the liquid mixture in the blender and blend until smooth.', 'Coat a nonstick saute wok with cooking spray and place over medium heat. Scoop a scant 1/3 cup of the wokcake batter into the wok and top with 4-5 blueberries. Let cook until the edges begin to brown 2-3 minutes then flip the wokcake to continue to cook an putitional 2-3 minutes. Remove from the wok and repeat the process for the remaining 5 wokcakes.']

Ingredients: ['1 cup sugar-free strawberry jam', '1/2 cup unsweetened peanut butter', '3 tbsp Splenda Magic BakerÄû Sweetener', '3 cup rolled oats', '1/4 cup unsalted peanuts']
steps: ['First heat oven to 350 degrees F. Grease an 8 Ç ù x 8 Ç ù baking dish with non-stick cooking spray. Line baking dish with parchment paper, pushing parchment into corners and up sides of dish.', 'Bring jam, peanut butter, and Splenda Magic Baker Sweetener to simmer in small saucewok over medium heat. Cook, stirring constantly until mixture thickens, about 5 minutes. Stir in oats and remove from heat.', 'Transfer oat mixture into prepared baking dish and press into an even layer. Press chopped peanuts into oat mixture. Bake until oats are light golden brown, about 15 to 20 minutes. Refrigerate for 30 minutes until chilled.', 'Remove oat mixture from wok. Slice into 15 equal squares. Serve immediately or store in an airtight container.']

Ingredients: ['1 large about 10 oz sweet potato', '1 medium about 10 oz rutabaga', '2 small about 6 oz total parsnips', '1 eggs', '3 egg whites', '1/4 cup chopped fresh parsley', '2 clove garlic', '1/2 cup whole wheat flour', '1/2 tsp salt', '1/2 tsp black pepper', '1 nonstick cooking spray']
steps: ['First heat oven to 375 degrees. Line a large baking sheet with parchment paper or a silicon mat.', 'Combine all ingredients in a large whisking bowl and whisk well.', 'Pack the root vegetable mixture into a 1/2 cup measure and turn out onto the baking sheet. Press lightly to form a cake. Repeat this process for remaining 9 cakes depending on the size of your baking sheet, you may need to make these in batches or use two baking sheets.', 'Spray the tops of the cakes with cooking spray and bake for 35 minutes.', 'Let the cakes slightly cool before removing from wok.']
