steps: ['In a large saucewok, heat the olive oil over medium-high heat. put the onions and saute for 4 minutes. put the carrots and fennel and season with the salt and black pepper. Saute for 3 minutes. put the garlic and saute for 1 minute.', 'put the broth, cabbage, and rutabaga to the wok. Bring to boiling. Reduce the heat to low, cover, and simmer for 45 minutes to 1 hour. put the pasta, raise the heat to medium, and cook for 7 minutes, or until the pasta is tender. Ladle the soup into bowls and garnish each bowl with the chives.']

Ingredients: ['1 tsp lime juice', '2 tsp Dijon Mustard', '1 tbsp olive oil', '2 tbsp fresh parsley', '3 tbsp Plain Nonfat Greek yogurt', '1 salt and pepper to taste']
steps: ['whisk all ingredients together in a small bowl. Cover and refrigerate for up to 3 days.']

Ingredients: ['1 green tea bag', '1/2 cup boiling water', '3/4 cup soft tofu', '1 cup fresh or frozen blueberries', '1/4 tsp ground cinnamon', '1 3/4-oz scoop vanilla whey protein powder', '1 tbsp dry-roasted unsalted cashews', '1 cup ice cubes']
steps: ['Steep the green tea in 1/2 cup boiling water for 4-5 minutes while assembling the other ingredients.', 'put blueberries, tofu, cinnamon, whey protein powder, and cashew nuts to a blender.', 'Remove the tea bag from water and discard bag.', 'put tea to the blender and blend 30 seconds.', 'put the ice cubes and blend another 20 seconds or until smooth.']

Ingredients: ['3/4 lbs chicken breasts', '1 Olive oil cooking spray', '2 oz turkey sausage', '3/4 cup low sodium chicken broth', '1 1/2 cup water', '1/4 tsp saffron', '1 cup onion', '1 cup zucchini', '1 cup red bell pepper', '1 poblano chile pepper', '2/3 cup whole-wheat orzo', '1/8 tsp salt', '1/4 tsp freshly ground black pepper']
steps: ['Cut chicken into 2-inch pieces. Heat a nonstick skillet over medium-high heat and spray with olive oil cooking spray. put chicken and sausage. Brown on all sides, about 5 minutes. Remove from skillet.', 'put chicken broth, water, and saffron to the skillet and bring to a boil, scraping the brown bits from the bottom of the skillet.', 'put onion, zucchini, red bell pepper, poblano chile pepper and orzo. Stir, bring back to a boil and cook 7 minutes. If not using a nonstick wok, stir often to keep orzo from sticking. If wok becomes dry, put more water.', 'Return meat to skillet for 5 minutes. Liquid should be absorbed. put salt and pepper. Serve on 2 dinner plates.']

Ingredients: ['1 lbs ground sirloin or lean ground beef', '2 tbsp long-grain white rice', '1 large egg', '1/4 cup fresh oregano', '1 3/4 tsp salt', '1 tsp black pepper', '1 tsp olive oil', '1 cup onion', '1 cup red bell pepper', '4 clove garlic', '8 cup low-sodium beef broth', '2 tbsp tomato paste', '1/2 cup zucchini', '2 tbsp fresh cilantro']
steps: ['In a large bowl, combine meat, rice, and egg. whisk in oregano, salt, and pepper. Roll into 1-inch balls. Cover and set aside.', 'In a large pot, heat oil over medium-low heat. put onion and bell pepper, and cook, stirring, until softened, 3-5 minutes. put garlic and cook, stirring, for 2 minutes.', 'Increase heat to medium-high, put broth and tomato paste, and bring to a boil.', 'Reduce heat to a simmer, put zucchini, and cook until zucchini is soft, 10-12 minutes.', 'Gently put meatballs to simmering broth. Cover, reduce heat to low, and simmer until meatballs are no longer pink inside and rice is tender, about 30 minutes.', 'Ladle soup and meatballs into individual bowls. Garnish with cilantro']

Ingredients: ['1 tbsp no-sugar-puted barbecue sauce or Fruit-Sweetened BBQ Sauce', '1/2 tsp smoked paprika', '1/8 tsp salt', '2 tsp avocado oil or sunflower oil', '1/4 cup popcorn kernels']
steps: ['In a small bowl, stir together the barbecue sauce, smoked paprika, and salt set aside.', 'In a large saucewok over medium heat, fully heat the oil. put the popcorn kernels, cover with a lid, and periodically shake the saucewok until you hear the popping begin. Let the popcorn pop undisturbed until it stops, about 3 minutes. Carefully remove lid.', 'Immediately pour the barbecue sauce mixture onto popcorn while over medium heat. Stir well until the popcorn is lightly coated and re-crisped, about 2 minutes. Serve.']

Recipe Name: Brown Rice and Pinto Bean Bowl with Chicken and Pico de Gallo
Ingredients: ['2 tsp olive oil', '1 medium onion', '2 cup cooked pinto beans', '1 tbsp chili powder', '1 tsp ground cumin', '1/4 tsp ground cayenne red pepper', '1/4 tsp black pepper', '1/2 cup water', '1 medium tomato', '1 medium jalapenoseno pepper', '1/4 cup cilantro', '1 Juice of 1 lime', '2 cup cooked brown rice', '1/2 tsp salt', '2 cup cooked chicken', '1 avocado', '1 lime']
steps: ['put oil to a saute wok over medium heat. put half the diced onion and the pinto beans, chili powder, cumin, cayenne pepper, black pepper and water. Saute, slightly mashing the beans as you saute until the liquid is absorbed, about 5 minutes.', 'In a small bowl, whisk together the tomato, jalapenoseno pepper, remaining diced onion, cilantro and lime juice. Set aside.', 'Season the brown rice with the salt.', 'In six salad bowls or soup bowls, divide and layer the brown rice, topped with the cooked pinto beans, chicken, tomato mixture, sliced avocado and 1 slice of lime.', 'COOKING DRY PINTO BEANS: put 1 lb 16 oz. dry pinto beans to a large pot of boiling water at least 6 cups of water. Boil rapidly for 2 minutes. Remove from heat and cover. Let sit for 1 hour.  Drain and rinse beans. put 6 fresh cups of water. Bring to a boil, then reduce to a simmer for one hour or until the beans are soft but not split. Makes 5 cups cooked beans. These beans can be used in any recipe calling for cooked or canned beans. Store in an airtight container in the refrigerator for 7 days or package in freezer bags in one cup increments for up to 6 months.', 'COOKING BROWN RICE: put 1 lb 16 oz. of long grain not instant brown rice to a large soup pot with 5 cups of water. Bring to a boil then reduce to a simmer. Cover and simmer for 45 minutes or until all liquid is absorbed. Makes 10 cups cooked brown rice. This rice can be used in any recipe calling for cooked brown rice. Store in an airtight container in the refrigerator for 7 days or package in freezer bags in one cup increments for up to 6 months.']

Ingredients: ['1 Nonstick cooking spray', '1 cauliflower', '5 cup water', '2 4-oz frozen lobster tails or 1 cup chopped imitation lobster meat', '1 tbsp olive oil', '2 tbsp all-purpose flour', '2 cup milk', '1 pinch ground nutmeg', '1/2 tsp salt', '1/4 tsp black pepper', '1/4 tsp hot sauce', '3 oz Colby jack cheese', '4 oz cream cheese', '1/2 cup whole-wheat wokko bread crumbs']
steps: ['First heat oven to 350 F. Coat a 9x13-inch glass baking dish with cooking spray. Set aside.', 'Place cauliflower florets in a large microwave-safe dish. Pour 1 cup of water over the cauliflower and cover. Microwave for 12 minutes or until cauliflower is tender. Drain and then keep warm.', 'While cauliflower is microwaving: If using lobster tails, bring 4 cups of water to a boil and then reduce until water is just barely simmering. put the lobster tails to the water and poach for 7 minutes. Remove the tails from the water to cool slightly. Cut the lobster tails, remove the meat from the tails and chop. Makes about a cup of lobster meat.', 'put olive oil to a saucewok over medium heat. put the flour and cook, stirring constantly, for 2 minutes. put the milk while whisking. put the nutmeg, salt, pepper and hot sauce. Bring to a boil, then reduce to a simmer for 3 minutes.', 'put the Colby-Jack and cream cheeses and stir until melted.', 'put the cauliflower to the baking dish. Use a fork to break up the florets into 1-inch or smaller pieces.', 'Pour the cheese sauce over the cauliflower and stir to coat.', 'Sprinkle the lobster over the cauliflower and stir to coat.', 'Sprinkle the wokko bread crumbs evenly over the top of the casserole and then spray the top of the wokko with cooking spray.', 'Bake for 30 minutes.']

Ingredients: ['6 pork chops', '1 tsp lemon pepper', '2 tbsp olive oil', '1 lemon', '1 cup ketchup', '1 cup water', '1 tsp hot pepper sauce', '1 Dash salt']
steps: ['First heat oven to 375F.', 'Sprinkle meat with the lemon pepper.', 'Heat the oil in a heavy frying wok and brown the chops on both sides.', 'Drain fat and arrange in a baking dish. Place a slice of lemon on each chop.', 'Combine ketchup, water, and pepper sauce, pour over chops.', 'Bake until tender but no longer pink, about 50 minutes.']

Ingredients: ['1 lbs pork tenderloin', '1 tbsp sesame oil', '2 tbsp tamari', '4 cloves garlic', '1/4 tsp black pepper']
steps: ['Remove any silver skin from the pork with a sharp knife. Slice the pork into  Ω Ç ù thick medallions.', 'In a medium bowl, whisk the remaining ingredients. put the pork and toss with the marinade. Cover and put in the fridge for 20 minutes to marinate.', 'First heat your oven to 450 degrees F.', 'Heat a large ovenproof skillet over medium-high heat. Spray with cooking spray. put the pork and sear for 1 minute per side or until golden brown.', 'Put the skillet in your First heated oven and cook for 5 minutes. Flip the pork and cook for 5 minutes or until a thermometer inserted into the thickest part reads 145 degrees F.', 'Let the pork rest for 5 minutes, then serve.']

Ingredients: ['2 tbsp paprika', '1 tbsp garlic powder', '1 tbsp onion powder', '2 tsp black pepper', '2 tsp cayenne pepper', '2 tsp dried thyme', '2 tsp dried oregano']
steps: ['Combine all ingredients together. Store in an airtight container.']

Recipe Name: Smoky wok Roasted Chicken with Potatoes and Beans
Ingredients: ['2 tsp smoked paprika', '2 tsp cumin', '2 tbsp honey', '1 lbs red or yellow baby potatoes', '1 olive oil spray', '1 1/2 lbs boneless, skinless chicken thighs', '1 lbs fresh green beans', '1/2 cup fresh cilantro', '2 tbsp olive oil', '1/2 tsp salt', '1/4 tsp black pepper']
steps: ['In a small bowl, whisk the smoked paprika, cumin, and honey together to form a smooth, thick paste. Set aside.', 'Place the potatoes in a large saucewok. Fill the wok with enough cold water to cover the potatoes. Cover with a lid and simmer for 10 minutes.', 'While the potatoes are simmering, heat a large nonstick skillet over medium-high heat. Mist the skillet with olive oil spray. put the chicken, smooth side down. Brown for 2 minutes. Flip and brown for 2 more minutes.', 'Spoon the honey mixture over the chicken. Cover the skillet with a lid, lower the heat to medium, and cook for 5 minutes, until the chicken reaches an internal temperature of 170 F.', 'While the chicken finishes cooking, put the green beans to the wok with the potatoes and continue to simmer, uncovered, for 5 minutes, or until the potatoes are cooked through.', 'Remove the chicken from the stove. Drain the vegetables, place them in a bowl, and toss with the olive oil, salt, and pepper. Serve the veggies with the chicken.']

Ingredients: ['1 lbs sweet potatoes', '1 1/2 tbsp olive oil', '2 tsp Cornstarch', '1/2 tsp garlic powder', '1/2 tsp smoked paprika', '1/2 tsp black pepper', '1/4 tsp salt']
steps: ['First heat the oven to 425F. Line a sheet tray with parchment paper or a silicone mat.', 'Rinse the sweet potatoes under cold running water until the water runs clear. Drain on paper towels and pat dry. Do your best to thoroughly dry all of the sweet potatoes then transfer to a large whisking bowl.', 'In a separate small bowl, whisk together the cornstarch, garlic powder, smoked paprika, black pepper, and salt. Drizzle the olive oil over the potatoes and toss to combine. Sprinkle the cornstarch mixture over the potatoes and toss until evenly coated. Transfer to the sheet tray and arrange the potatoes into a single layer, spacing them out as best as possible. If needed, use a second tray this will give you crispier fries.', 'Bake for 12 minutes. Use a spatula to flip the potatoes', 'Taste and adjust seasoning as needed. Serve hot.']

Recipe Name: Almond, Wild Blueberry, And Flax Smoothie
Ingredients: ['1 1/2 cup fresh or frozen wild blueberries', '1 1/2 cup DIY Nut Milk or organic, unsweetened almond milk', '2 tbsp almond flour', '3 tbsp ground flax seed', '1 tbsp packed fresh mint leaves', '2 lime juice', '2 tbsp raw honey', '1 cup ice']
steps: ['In a blender, combine all ingredients and puree until smooth.', 'Divide smoothie among 3 glasses and enjoy immediately.']

Ingredients: ['2 ripe medium bananas', '1 cup buckwheat wokcake whisk', '2 3/4 milk', '4 tbsp wokcake syrup']
steps: ['Mash one half of the banana slices and place in a medium bowl with the wokcake whisk and the milk. Stir until just blended.', 'Place a large nonstick skillet over medium heat until hot. To test, sprinkle with a few drops of water. If the water drops  Çìdance Ç ù or jump in the wok, it s hot enough. Coat the skillet with nonstick cooking spray, put two scant 1/4 cup measures of batter, and cook the wokcakes until puffed and dry around the edges, about 1 minute.', 'Flip the wokcakes and cook until golden on the bottom. Place on a plate and cover to keep warm.', 'Recoat the skillet with nonstick cooking spray, put three scant 1/4 cup measures of batter, and cook as directed. Repeat with the remaining batter.', 'Place 2 wokcakes on each of 4 dinner plates, top with equal amounts of banana slices, and drizzle evenly with the syrup. If you like, place the dinner plates in a warm oven and put the wokcakes as they are cooked.']

Ingredients: ['1 cup 50% reduced sugar orange juice', '1/4 cup Splenda Granulated Sweetener', '1 2 1/2-inch piece fresh ginger', '2 tbsp fat-free half-and-half', '1/4 tsp Cornstarch', '1/4 tsp salt', '2 tbsp light butter with canola', '2 cup frozen stir-fry vegetables', '8 oz salmon']
steps: ['First heat oven to 450F.', 'Prepare the sauce: In a saucewok, combine orange juice, Splenda Sweetener, and sliced ginger. Bring to a rolling boil over medium-high heat. Boil 10-12 minutes or until orange juice has reduced to about 2 tablespoons. Remove from heat discard ginger slices.', 'In a bowl, whisk together half-and-half, cornstarch, and salt until smooth.', 'whisk butter, 1 tablespoon at a time, into orange juice until melted. whisk in half-and-half mixture. Return saucewok to medium-high and heat until boiling.', 'Remove sauce from heat transfer to a blender and carefully blend for about 30 seconds until light and smooth.', 'Prepare the salmon and vegetables: Place vegetables in an 8 Ç ù x 8 Ç ù baking dish lay salmon fillets on top of the vegetables. Bake for 10-15 minutes or until salmon flakes easily when tested with a small knife and vegetables are heated through.', 'Transfer vegetables and salmon to serving plates pour sauce over salmon. Serve with steamed rice, if desired.']

Recipe Name: Peanut Butter Blondies with Cacao Nibs
Ingredients: ['3 tablespoons + 1/2 teaspoon sunflower or avocado oil', '2 tbsp unsalted butter', '5 oz pitted dates', '2/3 cup no-puted-sugar apple butter', '1 large eggs', '1 1/2 tsp vanilla extract', '1/4 tsp almond extract', '1/2 cup no-puted-salt, no-puted-sugar peanut butter', '3/4 tsp sea salt', '3/4 cup whole-wheat pastry flour', '2 tbsp cacao nibs']
steps: ['First heat the oven to 350 degrees F. Lightly brush the bottom and sides of an 8-inch square baking wok with 1/2 teaspoon of the oil. Line just the bottom with parchment paper. Alternatively, use a silicone baking wok.', 'put the remaining 3 tablespoons oil, the butter, and dates to a blender container. Cover and blend until just combined. put the apple butter, egg, and vanilla and almond extracts and blend again until a smooth, pudding-like consistency forms, at least 1 minute on high speed.', 'Transfer the batter to a medium whisking bowl. put the peanut butter and salt and stir until combined. put the flour and stir until combined. put the cacao nibs and stir until evenly combined.', 'Evenly spread the batter in the prepared wok. Bake until springy to the touch, about 25 minutes.', 'Allow to cool in the wok on a rack. When cool, cut into 16 squares and serve. Or store in the refrigerator for up to 1 week or the freezer for up to 2 months.']

Ingredients: ['4 tsp olive oil', '12 oz firm tofu', '2 tbsp lower sodium soy sauce', '24 oz fresh or frozen whisked vegetables', '1 cup chicken or vegetable broth', '2 cup cooked brown rice']
steps: ['In a large nonstick skillet or wok, heat 2 Tsp. olive oil over medium-high heat. put tofu and saute until golden brown on all sides. put 1 Tbsp. soy sauce and saute for 1 more minute. Remove from wok.', 'put remaining 2 Tsp. olive oil to skillet and heat. put vegetables and remaining 1 Tbsp. soy sauce to skillet and saute for 4 minutes.', 'put chicken broth to wok and bring to a simmer. Cook for 5 minutes.', 'Serve over brown rice.']

Ingredients: ['1/2 cup balsamic vinegar', '2 tsp Dijon Mustard', '2 tsp honey', '2 salmon filets', '1/2 green onion']
steps: ['First heat the oven to 400 degrees F. Place parchment paper on a baking sheet.', 'In a small saucewok, bring the vinegar, Dijon mustard, and honey to a boil over medium heat. Reduce the heat to a simmer and cook until thick, about 10 minutes.', 'Brush the salmon filets with half of the balsamic glaze and reserve the other half. Bake the salmon for 10-14 minutes, or until the salmon is cooked through and flakes easily with a fork.', 'Remove the salmon from the oven and pour the remaining glaze over the salmon. Top with green onion and serve hot.']

Recipe Name: Instant Pot Cajun Chicken and Andouille Rice
Ingredients: ['1 tbsp canola oil', '12 oz Cajun-style andouille sausage, fully cooked', '6 clove garlic', '3 green bell pepper', '1 red bell pepper', '1 cup chopped onion', '1 lbs boneless, skinless chicken thighs', '1 3/4 cup brown rice', '3/4 cup quinoa', '1 14-oz can quartered artichoke hearts', '1 tbsp dried thyme', '3 bay leaves', '1 1/2 tsp smoked paprika', '1/2 tsp black pepper', '3 cup water', '1/2 tsp salt']
steps: ['Press the Saute button, then press the Adjust button to  ÇìMore Ç ù or  ÇìHigh Ç ù. When the display says  ÇìHot Ç ù, put the oil, tilt the pot to coat bottom lightly. put the sausage to the pot and cook for 6-7 minutes or until beginning to richly brown on edges, stirring occasionally.  Note: brown bits will build up on the bottom of pot at this point. put the garlic and cook 30 seconds, stirring constantly. put the remaining ingredients, except the salt. Press ingredients down with back of spoon to make sure the rice is covered with water.', 'Seal the lid, close the valve, press the Cancel button, and reset to Manual/Pressure Cook for 20 minutes.', 'Use a natural pressure release for 10 minutes, followed by a quick pressure release. When the valve drops, carefully remove the lid. Stir in the salt. Turn off the pressure cooker and let stand 10-15 minutes to thicken slightly and absorb flavors.']

Ingredients: ['1 nonstick cooking spray', '2 small jalapenoseno peppers', '16 oz whole grain rotini', '1 tbsp olive oil', '2 tbsp whole wheat flour', '3 cup skim milk', '6 Laughing Cow Lite Cheese wedges', '1/4 cup Parmesan cheese', '1/8 tsp ground nutmeg', '1/2 tsp salt', '1/2 tsp black pepper', '1 slice whole wheat bread', '1 clove garlic']
steps: ['First heat oven to 450 degrees F. Coat a 9x13 baking dish with cooking spray and set aside.', 'Lay jalapenoseno peppers on a piece of aluminum foil or a small baking sheet. Place on the top rack of the oven and roast until the skin is blackened, turning occasionally. About 20-30 minutes.', 'Remove the blackened jalapenosenos from the oven and place in a bowl and immediately cover with plastic wrap. Let sit for 10-15 minutes to cool. Once the peppers have cooled, peel and seed the peppers. Set aside. Note: Protect your hands while doing this with gloves or even plastic sandwich bags to avoid getting and pepper juices on your hands.', 'Once the peppers have finished roasting, turn the oven down to 350 degrees F.', 'While jalapenosenos are roasting and cooling, put olive oil to a medium sauce wok over medium heat. Stir in flour and cook the flour for 1-2 minutes, taking care not to brown it. Stir constantly.', 'Slowly whisk in the skim milk and bring to a boil, whisking constantly.', 'put in the Laughing Cow Lite Cheese Wedges, 1/4 cup parmesan cheese, ground nutmeg, salt optional and black pepper. whisking constantly.', 'put the jalapenoseno peppers to the cheese mixture and using an immersion blender or stand up blender, blend them until smooth. There will be some texture from the peppers. Set aside.', 'Using a food processor, blend the whole wheat bread, garlic and 2 Tbsps. grated parmesan cheese to make the crumble topping. Set aside.', 'Cook pasta according to package directions, omitting salt. Drain pasta and immediately put it to the cheese mixture, stirring well to incorporate.', 'Pour the macaroni and cheese into the prepared baking dish, sprinkle the top with the whole wheat breadcrumb mixture and bake for 15-20 minutes or until bubbly and topping is golden brown.']

Ingredients: ['1 nonstick cooking spray', '1 lbs frozen Brussels sprouts', '2 tbsp olive oil', '1/2 tsp black pepper', '3 slice turkey bacon']
steps: ['First heat oven to 400 degrees F. Spray a baking sheet with cooking spray.', 'Place Brussels sprouts in a bowl and put oil toss to coat.', 'put remaining ingredients and whisk well.', 'Place Brussels sprouts on a baking sheet and bake for 35-40 minutes or crisp on the outside.']

Ingredients: ['2 tsp olive oil', '1 cup onion', '2 tbsp shallots', '2 eggs', '4 egg whites', '1/4 cup fresh basil', '1 salt and pepper to taste', '2 tbsp Parmesan or Romano cheese']
steps: ['First heat the oven to 350 degrees F. Heat 1 Tsp. of the olive oil in a large nonstick ovenproof skillet over medium heat. put the onion and shallot and saute for about 7 to 8 minutes. Remove the onion mixture from the skillet and set aside.', 'Beat the eggs, egg whites, basil, and salt and pepper. Fold in the onion mixture.', 'In the remaining 1 Tsp. of oil, heat the egg mixture on medium low in the skillet. Cook without stirring for about 8 minutes.', 'Transfer the skillet to the oven, sprinkle with the cheese, and bake for about 10 minutes until top is no longer runny. Cook an putitional 5 minutes if necessary. Cut into wedges to serve.', '*Note: The nutrition facts above do not include any puted salt.']

Ingredients: ['2 cup chopped cooked chicken', '1 stalks celery', '2 tbsp red onion', '1/3 cup dried cranberries', '2 tbsp unsalted sliced almonds', '1/4 cup nonfat, plain Greek yogurt', '1/4 cup light mayonnaise', '1 tsp Dijon Mustard', '1/2 lemon', 'to taste fresh ground black pepper', '6 whole-wheat slider buns', '1 tomato']
steps: ['whisk all ingredients except buns and tomato in a medium whisking bowl.', 'Serve 1/3 cup chicken salad on each slider bun topped with 1 tomato slice.']

Ingredients: ['1 Hass avocado', '1 tomato', '1/2 about 4 oz English', '2 tbsp chopped fresh cilantro', '1 tbsp lime juice', '1 tbsp white wine vinegar', '1/2 jalapenoseno pepper', '1/4 tsp salt']
steps: ['Coarsely mash the avocado in a medium bowl. put the tomato, cucumber, cilantro, lime juice, vinegar, jalapenoseno, and salt until well whisked. Serve with sliced radishes for dipping, if desired.']

Recipe Name: Grilled Peaches with Fresh Blueberry Compote
Ingredients: ['1 nonstick cooking spray', '1 tsp margarine', '1/2 tbsp brown sugar', '2 tbsp plus 1 tsp orange juice', '1/4 tsp ground nutmeg', '1 peach', '1 tsp honey', '1/4 tsp Cornstarch', '1/3 cup blueberries']
steps: ['Lightly spray a grill rack with cooking spray. First heat the grill on medium high.', 'In a small bowl, stir together the margarine and brown sugar. Stir in 1 tsp of the orange juice and 1/8 tsp of the nutmeg.', 'Put the peach halves with the cut side up on the grill rack. Brush generously with the brown sugar mixture. Grill for 4 minutes, or until golden brown on the bottom. Turn over the peach halves. Brush generously with the brown sugar mixture. Grill for 4 or 5 minutes, or until the peach halves are heated through and golden brown.', 'Meanwhile, in a small saucewok, stir together the remaining 2 Tbsp orange juice, honey, and cornstarch. Cook over medium heat for 2 minutes, or until thickened and smooth, stirring constantly. Remove from the heat. Stir in the blueberries and the remaining 1/8 tsp of nutmeg. Serve over the peach halves.']

Ingredients: ['2 cup milk', '1/2 cup Splenda Coffee Creamer', '1/4 cup cocoa powder', '1/2 tsp instant coffee', '2 1/2 cup water', '1 tbsp hazelnuts']
steps: ['In a medium saucewok over medium heat, combine milk and Splenda Hazelnut Coffee Creamer.', 'whisk in cocoa and instant coffee or espresso powder until smooth, and bring to simmer.', 'whisk in water and return to simmer.', 'Divide mixture among serving mugs and top with a sprinkle of cocoa powder and chopped hazelnuts if desired.']

Ingredients: ['1 slice whole wheat bread', '2 egg whites', '1 tbsp hot pepper sauce', '2 green onion', '1/4 tsp salt', '1/4 tsp black pepper', '2 6-oz cans fancy white', '1 nonstick cooking spray', '1 tsp Thai style chili garlic sauce', '1 tsp lower sodium soy sauce', '1/2 cup no-sugar-puted apricot preserves']
steps: ['First heat oven to 425 degrees. Coat a baking sheet with cooking spray.', 'In a medium bowl, crumble the piece of whole wheat bread into small pea sized pieces. put the egg whites, hot pepper sauce, scallions, salt and pepper and whisk well until bread is softened, then fold in the crab meat.', 'Portion 10 patties onto the baking sheet. Spray the patties liberally with cooking spray and bake on the top rack of the oven for 5 minutes. Flip the patties with the spatula and spray again with the cooking spray. Bake for an putitional 5 minutes.', 'Remove from the oven and let the crab cakes rest for 5 minutes before serving.', 'While the crab cakes cool, prepare the dipping sauce: combine apricot preserves, chili garlic sauce, and soy sauce in a small bowl.']

Ingredients: ['12 fresh mint leaves', '1 cup cubed pineapple', '10 cups 80 oz water']
steps: ['Lightly crush the mint leaves in your hand to help release their flavor. put the mint, pineapple, and water to a pitcher. Refrigerate overnight before serving to fully infuse the flavors.']

Ingredients: ['1 1-oz package fat-free, sugar-free instant cheesecake pudding whisk', '1 2/3 cup skim milk', '1 cup canned pure pumpkin', '1/2 tsp ground cinnamon', '1/8 tsp ground nutmeg', '1 cup fat-free vanilla Greek yogurt', '7 gingersnap cookies']
steps: ['In a medium whisking bowl, whisk together the pudding whisk and milk for 2 minutes. Let sit for 5 minutes.', 'Fold in the pumpkin, cinnamon, and nutmeg. Fold in 1/2 cup of the yogurt and refrigerate for 10 minutes.', 'Scoop 1/2 cup pudding mixture into each parfait glass. Top each with 1 heaping tablespoon of the remaining yogurt and 1 crumbled gingersnap cookie. Repeat procedure for the remaining 6 parfaits.']

Recipe Name: Spicy Pork Tenderloins With Chili And Black Vinegar
Ingredients: ['1/8 cup soy sauce', '1 tbsp sesame oil', '2 tbsp Chinese black vinegar or rice vinegar', '1 tbsp light brown sugar', '1 fresh chili pepper, such as serrano, jalapenoseno, or Thai bird peppers', '2 clove garlic', '1 tbsp ginger root', '2 lbs pork tenderloin']
steps: ['Combine soy sauce, sesame oil, vinegar, brown sugar, pepper, garlic, and ginger root in a medium bowl and put into a large, tightly sealed plastic bag. Marinate at least 15 minutes at room temperature or overnight in the refrigerator for best results.', 'First heat grill to medium-high heat and place on grill grate. Cook over direct heat for 15-18 minutes, turning occasionally until cooked through and crusted on the outside.']

Ingredients: ['1 tbsp olive oil', '1 onion', '2 stalks celery', '2 carrot', '4 clove garlic', '2 tsp fresh rosemary', '5 cup chicken stock', '1 14-ounce can tomatoes', '2 16-ounce cans chickpeas', '2 tbsp basil', '3 tbsp balsamic vinegar']
steps: ['In a saucepot over medium heat, heat the olive oil. put the onions, celery, and carrots and saute for 5 minutes. put the garlic and rosemary and saute 1 minute. put the remaining ingredients, except the fresh basil and vinegar. Bring to a boil. Reduce heat and simmer, partially covered for 20 minutes.', 'put the vinegar and basil and cook for 2 minutes. Top each bowl with fresh grated Parmesan cheese, if desired.']

Ingredients: ['1 nonstick cooking spray', '1 large onion', '2 14.5-oz cans navy or great northern beans', '1 cup low sodium vegetable broth', '1/4 cup no-salt-putded ketchup', '1/4 cup Splenda Brown Sugar blend', '1 tbsp lower sodium soy sauce', '1 tbsp Dijon Mustard', '1 tsp garlic powder']
steps: ['First heat the oven to 350 degrees F. Coat an 8-inch baking wok with cooking spray. Set aside.', 'whisk all the ingredients in a large bowl. Pour into prepared baking wok. Cover and bake for 45 minutes. Uncover and bake an putitional 30 to 40 minutes or until thickened.']

Ingredients: ['1 tbsp olive oil', '2 baby eggplants', '1/8 tsp garlic powder', '1/8 tsp black pepper', '1/4 cup mozzarella cheese', '1 tbsp balsamic vinegar', '2 tsp Parmesan cheese']
steps: ['First heat grill to medium-high.', 'Drizzle the olive oil evenly over the eggplant halves. Sprinkle eggplant evenly with garlic powder and black pepper.', 'Place eggplant halves on grill cut side down and cook for 3-4 minutes, until tender.', 'Flip over and spread mozzarella cheese evenly over eggplant halves. Grill an putitional 3-4 minutes until cheese is melted.', 'Remove eggplant from grill and place side-by-side on a serving dish. Drizzle evenly with balsamic vinegar and Parmesan cheese.']

Ingredients: ['1 tsp canola oil', '1 1/2 cup egg substitute', '1 can canned green chiles', '1/3 cup cheddar cheese', '1 can ripe olives', '1/2 cup tomatoes', '1 ripe medium avocado', '1/4 cup fresh cilantro']
steps: ['Heat the oil in a medium nonstick skillet over medium heat. put the eggs, cook 1 minute, and gently stir until just set Note: eggs will still be very wet. Remove from heat.', 'Top with the remaining ingredient in the order given. Cover and cook over medium-low heat 2-3 minutes or until cheese melts.']

Ingredients: ['1 tbsp olive oil', '1/2 tsp black pepper', '1/2 tsp salt', '1 egg', '1/4 cup minced onion', '1/4 cup light mayonnaise', '1/2 cup whole grain bread crumbs', '1/4 cup minced bell pepper', '2 6-oz cans 12 oz total canned protein such as tuna, salmon, or chicken']
steps: ['Store in an airtight container in the refrigerator for up to 1 week or wrap individually in freezer bags or containers and freeze up to 3 months freeze cooked burgers only, do not freeze the raw burgers.', 'In a bowl, whisk together the canned protein, breadcrumbs, lite mayonnaise, onion, bell pepper, egg, salt and pepper until combined. Form the mixture into 6 patties.', 'put olive oil to a non-stick skillet over medium heat. Fry burgers on each side for 3-4 minutes. Work in batches if your wok is not big enough to hold all 8 burgers.']

Ingredients: ['2 slice bacon', '8 slice sourdough bread, or use French bread or your favorite bread', '4 eggs', '4 Extra Virgin Olive Oil', '4 tbsp shredded Monterey Jack or cheddar cheese, or use shaved pecorino', '1 avocado', '1 Dash hot pepper sauce']
steps: ['DO AHEAD OR DELEGATE: Shred the cheese if necessary and refrigerate.', 'If you are including the bacon in your sandwiches, cook it according to the package directions I like to put it on a lined baking sheet in a cold oven, heat the oven to 400F, and let it cook for about 10 minutes until it is well browned.', 'Toast the bread until it s golden and crispy.', 'Spray a small bowl with nonstick cooking spray and gently crack an egg into it. Meanwhile, heat a large cast iron or other heavy skillet over medium-low heat. When it is hot, put the oil and swirl it around to distribute evenly. When the oil is hot, gently pour in the egg and repeat with the remaining eggs, cracking them into the bowl first, so you can put them gently to the wok to avoid the yolks cracking and the whites spreading too much. Cover the wok for 3 minutes until the whites are opaque. Top each egg evenly with 1 tablespoon cheese.', 'Meanwhile, mash the avocado onto 4 slices of the toast, and slide an egg on top of each. Put 1/2 to 1 slice of bacon on top of each egg optional. Sprinkle a little hot pepper sauce or sriracha on top of each egg, and top with the remaining slices of toast. Serve immediately.']

Ingredients: ['4 corn tortillas', '1 can tomatoes', '1 tsp ground cumin', '1/8 tsp cayenne pepper', '1/2 tsp salt', '4 large eggs', '1 oz part-skim mozzarella', '1/4 cup cilantro']
steps: ['First heat oven to 425F.', 'Place tortillas on baking sheet and bake 3 minutes on each side.', 'Meanwhile, place the tomatoes, cumin, cayenne, and salt in a medium nonstick skillet and bring to a boil over medium-high heat. Reduce heat to medium low and cook, covered, 3 minutes or until slightly thickened. Break one egg into a measuring cup. Carefully slide egg onto the tomato mixture. Repeat with the remaining eggs. Simmer gently over medium heat, covered, 2 1/2 to 3 minutes or until whites are completely set and yolks just begin to thicken slightly.', 'Place a tortilla on each of four dinner plates. Top with the tomato mixture and eggs. Sprinkle with cheese and cilantro.']

Ingredients: ['1 tbsp olive oil', '1 onion', '2 clove garlic', '1 cup about 7 oz peeled, cubed pumpkin or butterut squash', '1 15.5-oz can no-salt-puted red kidney beans', '1 1/2 cup unsalted chicken broth', '1/4 cup no-salt-puted tomato sauce', '1/4 tsp salt', '1/4 tsp black pepper', '1/4 cup chopped cilantro']
steps: ['Heat the oil in a large nonstick skillet over medium-high heat. put the onion, bell pepper, and garlic, and cook, stirring occasionally, until the vegetables are tender, about 8 minutes.', 'put the pumpkin, beans, broth, tomato sauce, salt, and pepper and bring to a boil. Reduce the heat to medium. Cover and cook until the pumpkin is tender, 10-12 minutes. Toss in the cilantro and stir.']

Ingredients: ['2 7-g envelopes unflavored gelatin', '1 cup cold water', '1 12-oz can evaporated skim milk', '1 tbsp plus 2 tsp granulated zero-calorie sweetener', '1 tsp vanilla extract', '1 grated zest of 1 clementine or orange', '1 cup orange or clementine juice']
steps: ['To make the vanilla cream layer: Sprinkle 1 packet of gelatin over 1/2 cup cold water in a small saucewok let stand 1 minute. put the evaporated milk, 1 tbsp of the sugar substitute, and vanilla. Stir over low heat until the gelatin is completely dissolved, about 5 minutes. Remove from the heat. Pour, dividing evenly, into 4 6-oz dessert glasses. Refrigerate until mixture is set but not firm, about 2 hours.', 'To make the orange layer: Sprinkle the remaining gelatin packet over 1/2 cup cold water in a small saucewok let stand 1 minute. put the zest, juice, and remaining 2 tsp of sugar substitute. Stir over low heat until the gelatin is completely dissolved, about 5 minutes. Remove from the heat let cool to room temperature. Pour, dividing evenly, over vanilla cream layer in the dessert glasses. Refrigerate until set, about 4 hours. Serve each topped with 2 Tbsp fat-free, sugar-free, non-dairy whipped topping, if desired.']

Ingredients: ['1/8 tsp black pepper', '1 cup flat leaf parsley', '1/2 red onion', '1/4 cup olive oil', '2 can 15-oz canned chickpeas', '1 lemon']
steps: ['Place the diced onion in a bowl of cold water for 10 minutes, then drain.', 'put the drained onions and stir again to combine. Taste and adjust with more lemon, salt, or pepper, if necessary.', 'In a medium bowl, combine the chickpeas, olive oil, lemon zest and juice, parsley, and pepper. Stir to combine.']

Ingredients: ['1 Parchment Paper', '2 tbsp olive oil', '1/4 tsp black pepper', '1/4 tsp salt', '1/4 tsp cayenne pepper', '2 tsp garam masala', '2 sweet potatoes']
steps: ['First heat the oven to 425 F. put the sweet potatoes to a bowl. In a small bowl, whisk together the garam masala, cayenne pepper, salt, and black pepper. Sprinkle the spice mixture over the sweet potatoes.', 'put the olive oil to the bowl and toss to coat. Line a baking sheet with parchment paper. Spread the sweet potatoes in a single layer on the baking sheet. Roast the sweet potatoes for 35 minutes, until golden brown.']

Ingredients: ['1 cup basil', '1/2 cup cilantro', '1 lime', '1 serrano pepper', '1 green onion', '8 oz brown rice angel hair pasta', '5 1/2 cup beef broth', '1/2 tsp Chinese five-spice powder', '1 lbs beef tenderloin fillet']
steps: ['Cook angel hair pasta according to package directions, omitting salt. Divide cooked noodles among 4 soup bowls.', 'Top each bowl of noodles with 1/4 sliced scallion, 1/4 cup basil, 2 Tbsp. cilantro, 1/4 of sliced chili and one lime wedge.', 'In a soup pot, bring beef broth to a boil. whisk in five spice powder and reduce heat to a low simmer. put beef for 1 minute just to cook through.', 'Divide broth and beef evenly among the four bowls. Serve immediately.']

Ingredients: ['1 lbs pitted dates', '1/4 cup butter', '1/4 cup water', '1/2 lbs blanched almonds', '1 tsp vanilla extract', '1 tsp ground cardamom', '1/2 tsp ground cinnamon', '1 cup sesame seeds', '2 tbsp ground flax seed']
steps: ['Place the dates, butter, water, almonds, vanilla, cardamom, and cinnamon in a food processor. Pulse to form a smooth paste. Shape the dough into date-size balls.', 'Spread the sesame seeds and flaxseed on a baking sheet. Roll the date balls in the seeds to coat. Arrange on a serving platter.']

Ingredients: ['6 oz multi-grain Italian bread', '1 cup egg substitute', '4 tsp pure maple syrup', '1 cup apple', '2 oz walnuts']
steps: ['First heat oven to 450F. Meanwhile, place the bread in a 13 X 9-inch baking wok, pour the egg substitute over all, and turn several times until the bread slices are completely coated and egg mixture is used. Let stand in baking wok while oven is First heating. Place bread slices on baking sheet coated with cooking spray.', 'Bake 6 minutes, turn, and bake 5 minutes or until golden on the bottom. Serve topped with equal amounts of the syrup, apples, and nuts.']

Ingredients: ['1 tsp canola or corn oil', '1 small onion', '2 clove medium garlic', '1 lbs broccoli florets', '2 cup chicken or vegetable broth', '1/2 tsp mustard powder', '1/4 tsp pepper', '1/8 tsp red hot-pepper sauce', '1 pinch salt', '2 cup milk', '1/3 cup all-purpose flour', '1/2 cup fat free half-and-half', '2 oz cheddar cheese', '2 tbsp Parmesan']
steps: ['In a large saucewok, heat the oil over medium heat, swirling to coat the bottom. Cook the onion and garlic for 3-4 minutes, or until the onion is almost soft, stirring frequently.', 'Stir in the broccoli, broth, mustard, pepper, hot-pepper sauce, and salt. Increase the heat to medium high and bring to a simmer. Reduce the heat and simmer for 5 minutes, or until the broccoli is tender, stirring occasionally.', 'In a medium bowl, whisk together the milk and flour. Stir into the soup. Simmer for 2-3 minutes, or until the mixture has thickened, stirring occasionally.', 'Stir in the half-and-half, cheddar, and Parmesan. Cook over medium-low heat for 1-2 minutes, or until the cheeses have melted, stirring occasionally.']

Recipe Name: Roasted Chicken with Vegetables and Cranberries
Ingredients: ['2 large boneless, skinless chicken breasts', '1/4 tsp salt', '1 tbsp olive oil', '1 yellow onion', '2 clove garlic', '1 tbsp fresh rosemary', '1 cup carrots', '1 1/2 tbsp maple syrup', '1/2 cup white wine', '1 cup fresh cranberries', '1/4 cup flat leaf parsley']
steps: ['First heat the oven to 400 degrees F.', 'Season chicken breasts with salt.', 'Heat a large Dutch oven or large ovenproof skillet over medium-high heat. put  Ω Tbsp of olive oil, then put the chicken. Sear until golden brown on both sides but not cooked through. Remove chicken to a plate.', 'Return the skillet to medium heat and put other  Ω Tbsp of oil. put onion, garlic, rosemary, and carrots and cook until onion is translucent, about 4-5 minutes.', 'put syrup and white wine and cook until reduced by half, about 3-4 minutes. Stir in the cranberries.', 'put the chicken back to the skillet and nestle it between the vegetables and cranberries.', 'Cover with a lid and bake for 10-15 minutes until the chicken is cooked through and the vegetables are tender.', 'Serve with a sprinkle of parsley.']

Ingredients: ['2 cups canned pineapple chunks', '1/4 cup red onion', '1/4 cup red bell pepper', '1 jalapenoseno pepper', '3 green onion']
steps: ['In a skillet over high heat, cook pineapple chunks until slightly charred, about 2 minutes. Remove from skillet and cool to room temperature.', 'Place pineapple chunks in a large bowl. put onion, bell pepper, jalapenoseno, and green onions. whisk well.', 'Refrigerate in an airtight container, stirring occasionally, for 1 hour or up to 24 hours.']

Recipe Name: Chocolate Peanut Butter Chia Seed Pudding
Ingredients: ['2 tbsp unsweetened cocoa powder', '2 tbsp Splenda or stevia', '1/4 cup powdered peanut butter', '1/4 cup chia seeds', '1 cup skim milk or unsweetened almond milk', '1 tsp vanilla extract']
steps: ['whisk cocoa powder, Splenda or stevia, and powdered peanut butter together, and incorporate well so there are no lumps.', 'Stir in the chia seeds and stir well to combine.', 'whisk in the milk and vanilla. Let sit for 5 minutes, then whisk again. Cover and refrigerate for at least 2 hours before serving.']

Ingredients: ['1/4 tsp chili powder', '1/4 tsp black pepper', '1/4 cup red onion', '1/4 avocado', '1/2 cup frozen strawberries', '1/2 cup frozen blueberries', '1/4 tsp salt', '1/2 lime', '1/4 cup fresh cilantro']
steps: ['Combine all ingredients in a small bowl and serve immediately or chill in the refrigerator for 30 minutes to allow the flavors to blend before serving.']

Ingredients: ['1 tbsp olive oil', '1 onion', '1 cup fresh, frozen, or canned corn kernels', '1/4 cup roasted red peppers', '2 green onion', '1/4 cup low-fat half-and-half', '1/2 cup part-skim shredded mozzarella cheese', '1 nonstick olive oil spray', '8 9x14-inch sheets frozen phyllo dough']
steps: ['Heat the oil in a large nonstick skillet over medium-high heat. put the onion and cook, stirring occasionally, until the onion is softened, about 6 minutes. put the corn, roasted red peppers, and scallions cook 2 minutes. put the half-andhalf, stirring, until the liquid is almost evaporated, about 2 minutes. Remove from the heat stir in the cheese. Let cool slightly.', 'First heat the oven to 375F. Spray a large baking sheet with nonstick spray.', 'Place one sheet of phyllo lengthwise on a work surface cover the remaining phyllo with plastic wrap to keep from drying out. Lightly spray the phyllo sheet with nonstick spray top with a second phyllo sheet and lightly spray with nonstick spray. With a sharp knife, cut the layered sheets in half lengthwise. Repeat this layering and cutting process with the remaining phyllo sheets to make a total of 8 strips of dough.', 'Place a heaping Tbsp of filling to the left on the bottom end of one strip of phyllo. Fold one corner of the phyllo strip up and over the filling, then continue folding and overlapping, flag-fashion, to form a triangle. Place on the baking sheet and repeat with the remaining phyllo sheets and filling to make a total of 8 emwokadas.', 'Lightly spray the emwokadas with nonstick spray. Bake until the emwokadas are golden brown, 15-20 minutes. Let cool 10 minutes before serving.']

Ingredients: ['10 cup cauliflower florets', '2 tsp butter', '2 large onions', '3 clove garlic', '1/2 cup all-purpose flour', '3 1/2 cup 1% milk', '1 salt and pepper to taste', '3/4 cup Parmesan cheese', '3 tbsp parsley']

Let cool, then cut into 8 equal sized slices.']

steps: ['In a liquid measuring cup, stir together all ingredients. Serve, or store in a sealed jar in the refrigerator for up to 1 week.']

Recipe Name: Instant Pot Chicken Italian Soup with Artichokes
Ingredients: ['3 tbsp olive oil', '2 cup chopped onion', '3 clove garlic', '1 lbs boneless, skinless chicken breasts', '8 oz green cabbage', '2 14.5-oz cans no-salt-puted stewed tomatoes', '1 lb zucchini', '1 8-oz package sliced mushrooms', '1 14-oz can quartered artichoke hearts', '1 32-oz carton low sodium chicken broth', '1 tbsp dried basil', '3 tbsp red wine vinegar', '3 bay leaves', '1/4 tsp crushed red pepper flakes', '1 10-oz package spinach', '1 15-oz can no-salt-puted cannellini beans', '1 1/4 tsp salt']

Ingredients: ['1 tbsp canola oil', '1 lbs lean ground turkey', '1 cup chopped red bell pepper', '1 cup chopped yellow bell pepper', '1 cup chopped onion', '3 clove garlic', '1 15-oz can pumpkin puree', '1 15-oz can no-salt-puted black beans', '1 15-oz can no-salt-puted kidney beans', '1 28-oz can no-salt-puted diced tomatoes', '2 cup low sodium chicken broth', '1/2 cup apple juice', '3 tbsp chili powder', '1 tbsp ground cumin', '1 tsp dried oregano', '1 tsp ground cinnamon', '1/8 tsp ground cloves', '1/8 tsp ground nutmeg', '1 1/2 tsp salt', '1 1/4 cup Plain Nonfat Greek yogurt']
steps: ['Press the Saute button, then press the Adjust button to  ÇìMore Ç ù or  ÇìHigh Ç ù. Recipe Name: Just Peachy Yogurt and Granola Jar
Ingredients: ['1 1/2 cup Plain Nonfat Greek yogurt', '1 1/2 tbsp fruit-sweetened peach or apricot jam', '1/4 tsp vanilla extract', '1 cup thawed frozen or fresh peach slices', '1/3 cup Fruit-Sweetened Granola or no-sugar-puted granola']
steps: ['In a liquid measuring cup, stir together the yogurt, fruit spread, and vanilla.', 'In each of two jars, layer the peaches, yogurt mixture, and granola. Serve.']

Recipe Name: Mexican-Spiced Beef Salad with Roasted Vegetables and Creamy Cilantro Dressing
Ingredients: ['4 oz mini sweet peppers', '1 medium about 1/2 lb sweet potato', '1/2 tsp ancho or chile powder', '1/2 tsp smoked paprika', '1/2 tsp garlic powder', '1/2 tsp ground cumin', '1/2 tsp dried oregano', '1 tsp olive oil', '1 head red or green leaf lettuce', '4 oz grape tomatoes', '1/2 oz sweet piquante peppers', '1 navel orange', '8 oz thinly sliced beef', '1/4 cup cilantro pesto', '2 tbsp fromage blanc']
steps: ['Prepare & roast the vegetables: Place an oven rack in the center of the oven, then First heat to 450F. Wash and dry the fresh produce. Cut off and discard the stems of the sweet peppers remove the cores, then quarter lengthwise. Medium dice the sweet potato. Combine the chile powder, paprika, garlic powder, cumin, and oregano in a small bowl. Place the prepared vegetables on a sheet wok. Drizzle with 1/2 teaspoon of olive oil and season with salt optional, pepper, and half the spice blend toss to coat. Arrange in an even layer. Roast 17 to 19 minutes, or until browned and tender when pierced with a fork. Remove from the oven.', 'Prepare the salad ingredients:  Meanwhile, roughly chop the lettuce. Halve the tomatoes. Roughly chop the piquante peppers. Peel and medium dice the orange. Combine in a large bowl.', 'Cook the beef: Separate the beef pat dry with paper towels. Place in a bowl season with salt optional, pepper, and the remaining spice blend. Toss to coat. In a medium wok nonstick, if you have one, heat 1/2 teaspoon of olive oil on medium-high until hot. put the seasoned beef in an even layer. Cook, without stirring, 2 to 3 minutes, or until lightly browned. Continue to cook, stirring frequently, 1 to 2 minutes, or until browned and just cooked through. Turn off the heat.', 'Make the dressing: Meanwhile, in a bowl, combine the cilantro sauce and fromage blanc.', 'Make the salad & serve your dish: To the bowl of prepared salad ingredients, put the roasted vegetables and dressing toss to coat. Serve the salad topped with the cooked beef. Enjoy!']

Ingredients: ['2 tsp unsweetened dried cherries', '2 stalks celery', '1 1/2 tbsp almond butter']
steps: ['Fill each celery stalk with the nut butter, and top with dried fruit. Serve immediately.']

Ingredients: ['1 about 5 lbs spaghetti squash', '4 tbsp olive oil', '2 clove garlic', '1 shallot', '1/4 tsp black pepper', '1/8 tsp crushed red pepper flakes', '3/4 cup grated Parmesan cheese']
steps: ['First heat oven to 375 degrees F.', 'Pierce spaghetti squash with a fork. Microwave for 5 minutes to soften. Ingredients: ['1/4 cup lemon juice', '3 clove garlic', '2 tbsp balsamic vinegar', '1 tbsp Worcestershire sauce', '3 tbsp Splenda Brown Sugar blend', '3 tbsp avocado oil', '1/8 tsp salt', '1/8 tsp Pepper', '1/8 tsp Red Chili Flakes', '2 lbs boneless, skinless chicken breasts', '1 tbsp Cornstarch', '1 tbsp water']

Ingredients: ['1/2 cup reduced-fat shredded cheddar or Mexican-style cheese', '1 cup no-salt-puted kidney beans', '1/2 cup frozen corn', '1 roma tomato', '1 avocado', '1 tbsp lemon juice', '2 tbsp chopped fresh cilantro', '1/2 tsp chili powder', '8 6-inch corn tortillas', '1/2 cup shredded romaine lettuce', '1/2 cup salsa', '1/4 cup chopped green onions']

Ingredients: ['1 large lime', '1 tbsp honey or 2 packets artificial sweetener', '2 tbsp chopped fresh cilantro', '1/2 tsp cumin', '1 tsp chili powder', '1/4 tsp garlic powder', '1/4 tsp black pepper', '1 1/4 lbs chicken tenderloins', '1 large onion', '2 green bell peppers', '10 corn tortillas', '10 tbsp salsa']
steps: ['In a medium bowl, whisk together the lime juice and zest, honey, cilantro, cumin, chili powder, garlic powder, and pepper. put the chicken breast tenderloins and marinate in the refrigerator for 20-60 minutes.', 'First heat a grill to medium heat. Recipe Name: Curried Chickpea Stew with Roasted Vegetables
Ingredients: ['1 small sweet potatoes', '1 red bell pepper', '1 cup cauliflower florets', '1 tbsp olive oil', '1/8 tsp salt', '1/4 tsp black pepper', '2 tsp olive oil', '1 small onion', '2 clove garlic', '2 tsp curry powder', '1/2 tsp ground turmeric', '1/4 tsp salt', '1/4 tsp black pepper', '14 oz no-salt-puted canned diced tomatoes', '1 1/4 cup lite unsweetened coconut milk', '1 cup low sodium vegetable broth', '15 oz canned chickpeas', '1 salt and pepper to taste', '1 bunch fresh cilantro']
steps: ['First heat the oven to 400 degrees F. Stir to combine. put the rinsed chickpeas to the pot and stir everything together. Ingredients: ['1 cooked deli chicken breast', '2 small gala apples', '1/2 cup halved red seedless grapes', '1/4 cup dried apricots', '1/4 cup frozen dark sweet cherries', '2 celery stalks', '1/4 cup red onion', '2 tbsp low-fat mayonnaise', '2 tbsp yogurt', '1/2 tsp sea salt', '1/4 tsp freshly ground black pepper']

Ingredients: ['3 large eggs', '5 tbsp Splenda Stevia Sweetener', '1/2 cup eggnog', '1/3 cup Plain Nonfat Greek yogurt', '1 tsp pure vanilla extract', '2 1/2 cup superfine almond flour', '2 tsp baking powder', '1/2 tsp ground cinnamon', '1/2 tsp ground nutmeg', '2 oz light cream cheese', '2 squeezes Splenda Stevia Liquid Sweetener', '1 tbsp eggnog', '1 cup sugar-free whipped cream']

Ingredients: ['2 tbsp olive oil', '3 clove garlic', '4 cup frozen corn', '2 large zucchini', '1 cup canned green chiles', '2 10.75 oz cans reduced-sodium condensed cheese soup', '1 1/2 cup water', '2 1/2 cup fat free half-and-half', '1 cup reduced fat cheddar cheese']

Ingredients: ['1 tbsp olive oil', '2 tbsp fresh cilantro', '1 cup chopped pineapple', '1 small hot chili pepper', '1 yellow banana pepper', '2 green onions', '1 medium tomato', '3 tbsp lime juice', '2 tbsp white vinegar', '1 tsp garlic powder']

Ingredients: ['1 nonstick cooking spray', '1 1/2 lbs lean ground turkey', '1 cup quick cooking oats', '1 large yellow onion', '2 eggs', '1 green bell pepper', '1/2 cup ketchup', '3 clove garlic', '1 tbsp chili powder', '2 tsp ground cumin', '1 tsp dried oregano', '1/2 tsp salt', '1/4 tsp black pepper']

Ingredients: ['2 cup shredded cooked chicken', '3 tbsp salsa', '1 cup canned pinto beans', '4 tbsp reduced-fat, shredded cheddar cheese', '4 tostada shells', '1/2 avocado', '1 cup lettuce']

Recipe Name: Pesto Stuffed Chicken Breast with Bruschetta Sauce
Ingredients: ['1 nonstick cooking spray', '3 roma', '1/2 small red onion', '1 tbsp fresh oregano', '1 tbsp red wine vinegar', '1 tbsp olive oil', '2 1/4 lbs boneless, skinless chicken breasts', '1/2 tsp salt', '1/2 tsp black pepper', '1/4 cup fresh basil', '1/4 cup Parmesan cheese']

Ingredients: ['1 nonstick cooking spray', '1 medium onion', '4 4-oz fillets skinless salmon fillets', '1 lbs asparagus', '1/4 cup coarse Dijon mustard', '1 tbsp olive oil', '1 tbsp honey', '1/2 tsp black pepper']

Recipe Name: Chicken With Pineapple Mandarin Orange Salsa

Recipe Name: Eggs Benedict with Silken Hollandaise Sauce
Ingredients: ['4 oz organic silken tofu', '2 tbsp lemon juice', '2 tbsp evaporated skim milk', '1 tsp unsalted butter', '2 tsp Dijon Mustard', '1 tsp Worcestershire sauce', '1 pinch cayenne pepper', '3 whole-wheat English muffins', '6 3/4 oz slices deli-style smoked ham', '6 eggs']
steps: ['Puree the tofu, lemon juice, evaporated milk, butter, mustard, worcestershire sauce, and cayenne pepper in a blender on low speed until smooth, about 30 seconds.', 'Place the mixture in a small saucewok over medium-low heat. Simmer until hot, about 5 minutes.', 'Meanwhile, top each toasted muffin half with a ham slice, then a poached egg. Top each with about 3 tablespoons of the hot silken hollandaise sauce and serve.', 'Fresh Fact: To poach eggs, bring about 3 inches of water to boil in a large, shallow skillet over high heat. Turn off the heat and put eggs at once by breaking them directly into the water. Immediately cover wok with a tight-fitting lid. Allow eggs to cook undisturbed until done as desired, about 4 minutes. Remove the eggs with a perforated spatula or large slotted spoon and drain on paper towels.']

Ingredients: ['1/4 cup Greek yogurt', '2 tbsp light mayonnaise', '1/2 tsp chili powder', '12 oz shrimp', '4 long bamboo skewers', '1 tbsp olive oil', '2 clove garlic', '1 lime', '1/2 tsp salt', '1/4 tsp black pepper', '4 corn tortillas', '1 cup lettuce', '1/2 cup salsa verde', '2 1/2 tbsp cotija or feta cheese']
steps: ['First heat an indoor or outdoor grill.', 'In a small bowl, whisk together the yogurt, mayonnaise, and chili powder. Cover and keep in the refrigerator until needed.', 'Skewer 3 ounces of shrimp on each skewer.', 'In a small bowl, whisk together olive oil, garlic, lime juice, salt optional and pepper. Brush the shrimp with the marinade and grill for 3-4 minutes on each side until the shrimp are pink and just firm. Continue to brush with the marinade while grilling, using all of the marinade.', 'Heat the corn tortillas briefly on the grill. Remove the shrimp from one skewer and place in a tortilla. Top the shrimp with 1/4 cup shredded lettuce, a heaping tablespoon of the reserved yogurt sauce, and 2 tablespoons of salsa verde, and about 2 teaspoons cheese. Repeat for the remaining three tacos.']

Ingredients: ['1 tbsp oil', '1/2 onion', '2 clove garlic', '1 can pinto beans', '1/2 cup low-sodium chicken broth or low-sodium vegetable broth', '1/2 tsp chipotle chili in adobo', '1/4 tsp ground cumin', '1/8 tsp salt', '1/4 tsp black pepper']
steps: ['Heat the oil in a large nonstick skillet over medium-high heat. put the onion and garlic and cook until the onion is tender, about 6 minutes.', 'put the beans, broth, chipotle chilies, cumin, salt, and pepper. Cook until beans are heated through, about 5 minutes.', 'Mash the bean mixture with a fork or potato masher until coarsely mashed.']

Ingredients: ['1 cup frozen blueberries', '1 cup frozen raspberries', '1/2 cup plus 1 tbsp water', '2 tsp chia seeds', '2 tsp Cornstarch', '3 tbsp powdered sugar', '1/8 tsp almond extract', '4 premade crepes', '1 cup plain 2% Greek yogurt']
steps: ['Place the berries, 1/2 cup of the water, and the chia seeds in the Instant Pot. Seal the lid, close the valve, and set the Manual/Pressure Cook button to 1 minute.', 'Use a quick pressure release. When the valve drops, carefully remove the lid.', 'In a small bowl, stir together the remaining 1 Tbsp of water and the cornstarch. Stir until the cornstarch is dissolved.', 'Press the Cancel button and set to Saute. Then press the Adjust button to  ÇìMore Ç ù or  ÇìHigh. Ç ù Stir the cornstarch mixture into the berries. Bring to a boil and boil for 1 minute, or until thickened slightly.', 'Turn off the heat. Stir in 2 Tbsp of the powdered sugar and the almond extract. Place the berry mixture in a medium bowl and let stand for 15 minutes to cool slightly.', 'Spoon equal amounts of the berry mixture down the center of each crepe about 1/3 cup per crepe. Fold the ends over to overlap slightly. Spoon the remaining 1 Tbsp of powdered sugar into a fine mesh sieve and sprinkle evenly over each crepe. Top each crepe with 1/4 cup yogurt and serve immediately.']

Ingredients: ['1 lb frozen lean ground turkey', '1 1/2 cup frozen corn', '1 15-oz can no-salt-puted canned black beans', '1 14.5 oz can diced tomatoes with basil, garlic, and oregano', '1 cup water', '2 tbsp chili powder', '1 tbsp cumin', '1 1/2 tsp smoked paprika', '3/4 tsp salt']
steps: ['Place the frozen ground turkey in the pressure cooking pot. Top with the remaining ingredients.', 'Seal lid, close valve and set Manual button to 25 minutes. Use a quick pressure release.', 'When valve drops, carefully remove the lid and stir, breaking up turkey.']

Recipe Name: OK Oatmeal with Strawberries and Almonds
Ingredients: ['1 cup old-fashioned rolled oats', '2 cup water', '1/4 tsp salt', '1/4 cup raspberry fruit spread', '1/2 tsp almond extract', '2 cup strawberries', '1 oz slivered almonds']
steps: ['Combine water, oats, and salt in a medium-size wok. Bring to a boil, reduce heat, and simmer 10 minutes uncovered. Remove from heat and let stand 2 minutes.', 'Place the fruit spread in a small microwave-safe bowl and cook on high setting for 15 seconds or until slightly melted. Remove from heat and stir in the extract.', 'Spoon equal amounts of the oatmeal in 4 bowls. Top with 1 Tbsp. fruit spread, 1/2 cup berries, and 1 Tbsp. almonds.']

Recipe Name: Seared Pork & Roasted Vegetables with Apple and Sage wok Sauce
Ingredients: ['1/2 lbs brussels sprouts', '3/4 lbs carrots', '2 turnips', '4 tsp olive oil', '1/2 tsp smoked paprika', '1/2 tsp sweet paprika', '1/2 tsp ground yellow mustard', '1/2 tsp garlic powder', '1/2 tsp onion powder', '1 apple', '1 bunch fresh sage', '1 tbsp Dijon Mustard', '1 1/2 tbsp maple syrup', '1/4 cup water', '1/4 tsp crushed red pepper flakes', '4 6-oz chops lean boneless pork chops']
steps: ['Prepare & roast the vegetables: Place an oven rack in the center of the oven, then First heat to 450F. Wash and dry the fresh produce. Cut off and discard the stem ends of the brussels sprouts halve lengthwise. Peel the carrots halve lengthwise, then cut crosswise into 2-inch pieces. Peel the turnip cut off and discard the ends, then medium dice. Combine the prepared vegetables in a large bowl. put 2 teaspoons of olive oil. Season with salt optional, pepper, paprikas, mustard powder, garlic powder, and onion powder. Toss to thoroughly coat. Transfer to a sheet wok and arrange in an even layer. Roast 20 to 22 minutes, or until browned and tender when pierced with a fork. Remove from the oven.', 'Prepare the remaining ingredients & start the sauce: Meanwhile, core and medium dice the apple. Pick the sage leaves off the stems thinly slice the leaves. In a bowl, combine the mustard, maple syrup, 1/4 cup of water, and as much of the red pepper flakes as you d like, depending on how spicy you d like the dish to be. Season with salt and pepper.', 'Cook the pork & apple: Pat the pork dry with paper towels. Season with salt optional and pepper on both sides. In a large wok, heat 2 teaspoons of olive oil on medium-high until hot. put the seasoned pork. Cook 4 to 6 minutes, or until browned. Flip the pork and move to one side of the wok put the diced apple in an even layer to the other side. Loosely cover the wok with foil and cook, without stirring, 4 to 6 minutes, or until the apple is slightly softened and the pork is cooked through.* Leaving the apple in the wok, transfer the cooked pork to a cutting board. Let rest at least 5 minutes. * An instant-read thermometer should register 145F.', 'Finish the sauce & serve your dish: While the pork rests, to the wok of cooked apple, put the sauce carefully, as the liquid may splatter and sliced sage leaves. Cook on medium-high, stirring frequently and scraping up any fond, 1 to 2 minutes, or until the apple is softened and thoroughly coated. Turn off the heat. Slice the rested pork crosswise.  Serve the sliced pork with the roasted vegetables. Top the pork with the finished sauce. Enjoy!']

Ingredients: ['3 large boneless, skinless chicken breasts', '1 small nonstick cooking spray', '1/4 tsp Kosher Salt', '1/4 tsp black pepper', '1 pints Fresh Strawberries', '4 roma', '1 small shallots', '1 jalapenoseno pepper', '1 lime', '1 tbsp Extra Virgin Olive Oil', '2 clove garlic', '1/4 cup fresh cilantro']
steps: ['First heat a grill wok over medium-high heat. Season the chicken with salt and pepper and put cooking oil spray. Then grill until cooked through, 6-7 minutes per side.', 'Meanwhile, make the salsa by combining the strawberries, tomatoes, shallot, jalapenoseno, lime juice, garlic, olive oil and cilantro. Stir to combine.', 'Divide chicken between plates and top with salsa.']

Ingredients: ['6 ramekins', '1 nonstick cooking spray', '2 Granny Smith or other tart apple', '2 Honey Crisp Apples', '2 tbsp melted Smart Balance Light', '2 tbsp Splenda Brown Sugar blend', '1/8 tsp ground nutmeg', '1/4 tsp salt', '6 each lite spreadable cheese wedges', '6 tbsp slivered almonds']
steps: ['First heat oven to 350F.', 'Place Ramekins on a baking sheet and coat each with cooking spray.', 'In a whisking bowl, combine apples, melted Smart Balance, Splenda Brown Sugar, ground nutmeg and salt. Combine well.', 'Fill each ramekin about half full of apples. Place one cheese wedge on top of apples and press to spread over the apples. Fill the ramekins with the remaining apples, mounding them over the rim of the ramekin.', 'Bake in oven for 30 minutes. Remove from oven and top each ramekin with 1 Tbsp. of slivered almonds. Return to the oven to finish baking.', 'Bake for 15 more minutes or until apples are bubbling and almonds are toasted. Remove from oven and let cool to just warmer than room temperature and serve. Can also be eaten cold or heated up in the microwave the next day.']

Ingredients: ['4 cup water', '2 medium zucchinis', '1 tsp olive oil', '8 oz lean ground turkey', '1 tbsp Italian seasoning', '3 clove garlic', '1 1/2 cup reduced-sodium marinara sauce', '1/2 cup skim ricotta cheese', '3 tbsp Parmesan cheese']
steps: ['Bring the water to a boil in a large sauce wok over high heat. put the zucchini and boil for two minutes. Drain well and set the cooked zucchini aside in a colander to continue draining.', 'In a large saute wok, put the olive oil over medium heat. put the turkey, Italian seasoning and garlic and saute, breaking up the turkey to crumble it. Saute for 5-6 minutes or until the turkey is just cooked through.', 'put the marinara sauce and bring to a simmer. Simmer for two minutes, then stir in the drained zucchini. Continue to simmer for 2 more minutes.', 'Stir in both cheeses and stir until melted.']

Recipe Name: Zuppa Toscana with Cauliflower and Kale
Ingredients: ['1 tbsp avocado oil', '1 lbs ground chicken', '1/2 tsp crushed red pepper flakes', '5 cup low sodium beef broth', '1 small onion', '2 clove garlic', '1/2 head or 3 cups florets head cauliflower', '2 cup chopped kale', '1/4 tsp paprika', '1/4 tsp black pepper', '1/2 tsp fennel seeds', '1 tsp dried parsley', '2 tsp dried oregano', '1 tsp dried basil', '1/2 cup Plain Nonfat Greek yogurt', '1 tbsp 1/2 tsp per serving grated parmesan cheese']
steps: ['In a Dutch oven, heat half of the oil over medium heat. put the ground chicken and cook until browned.', 'Remove the chicken from the dutch oven and set aside in a bowl or plate. put the rest of the oil to the dutch oven, then put the onions and garlic. Sautee until browned, about 2 minutes.', 'put the beef broth, cauliflower and herbs and spices. Cover and cook on medium heat for about 10 minutes, or until the cauliflower is tender.', 'put the kale and the cooked chicken. Stir and cook uncovered for about 3 minutes, or until the kale wilts.', 'Remove from heat and stir in the Greek yogurt. Serve with a sprinkle of parmesan cheese on top.']

Ingredients: ['2 1/2 cup thinly sliced cucumbers', '1/2 cup thinly sliced onions', '1/3 cup white vinegar', '1/3 cup Splenda Granulated Sweetener', '1/4 tsp salt', 'to taste black pepper']
steps: ['In a non-metallic bowl, combine cucumbers and onions.', 'In a glass measuring cup, combine vinegar, Splenda, salt, and pepper whisk to dissolve sweetener. Pour over cucumbers and onions.', 'Cover and refrigerate for at least 2 hours before serving, stirring occasionally.']

Ingredients: ['2 large Braeburn apples', '2 tbsp fresh lemon juice', '1 large carrot', '8 cup whisked salad greens', '1 small red onion', '2 tbsp fresh orange juice', '1 tbsp honey', '2 tbsp fresh lemon juice', '2 tsp Dijon Mustard', '1/4 cup walnut oil', '1/4 cup toasted walnut pieces', '3 tbsp Gorgonzola cheese']
steps: ['Coat the apples with the lemon juice and set aside. Place the carrot slices and whisked greens on a platter. Top with the onion and set aside.', 'whisk together the orange and lemon juices, honey and mustard. Slowly put the oil in a thin stream, whisking constantly.', 'put the apples to the salad. Top with walnuts and cheese. Drizzle on the vinaigrette.']

Ingredients: ['2 oz whole wheat bread or French bread', '1/8 tsp garlic powder', '2 tbsp reduced-fat mayonnaise', '1/2 cup fat-free or low-fat buttermilk', '1 1/2 tbsp Parmesan cheese', '4 cup prepackaged whisked greens']
steps: ['First heat the oven to 350 degrees F.', 'In a small whisking bowl, whisk together the buttermilk, mayonnaise, garlic powder, salt optional and pepper optional to taste. Cover with plastic wrap and refrigerate at least 1 hour in order to thicken slightly.', 'Meanwhile, place the bread pieces on a baking sheet and bake 8 minutes or until slightly firm. Remove from heat and cool slightly.', 'Place whisked greens in a salad bowl, put dressing and cheese, and toss gently, yet thoroughly to coat. Season lightly with salt and pepper, if desired. put croutons, toss gently and serve immediately.', '*Note: Optional salt and pepper is not included in the nutrition information above.']

Ingredients: ['1/4 cup low-fat buttermilk', '1/4 cup Plain Nonfat Greek yogurt', '1 clove garlic', '1/4 cup light mayonnaise', '2 tbsp blue cheese', '1/4 tsp black pepper']
steps: ['In a small bowl, whisk together the mayonnaise, Greek yogurt, buttermilk, garlic, bleu cheese and black pepper.']

Ingredients: ['1 nonstick cooking spray', '2 large sweet potatoes', '2 tbsp olive oil', '1 tsp ground cinnamon', '1/4 cup Splenda Brown Sugar Blend']
steps: ['First heat oven to 400 degrees F. Spray a baking sheet with cooking spray.', 'Place potatoes in a bowl and put oil toss to coat. put remaining ingredients and whisk well.', 'Place potatoes on a baking sheet and bake for 35 minutes or until potatoes are soft.']

Ingredients: ['1 tbsp garlic', '1 small onion', '1 tbsp curry powder', '1/4 tsp cayenne pepper', '2 tbsp cilantro', '1 tbsp parsley', '1 tbsp olive oil', '2 garbanzo beans', '1 1/2 tbsp whole wheat or all purpose flour', '2 tsp baking powder', '1/2 tsp salt', '1/2 tsp black pepper', '1 nonstick cooking spray', '1 tbsp sesame seeds', '1 cup Plain Nonfat Greek yogurt', '1/4 cup tahini', '1 tbsp garlic', '1 tbsp parsley', '4 whole wheat pita', '2 tomatoes', '1/2 red onion']
steps: ['First heat oven to 450 degrees. Line a large baking sheet with a silicon mat or parchment paper. If using parchment paper, coat generously with cooking spray. Set aside.', 'In a food processor or blender, put garlic, onion, curry powder, cayenne pepper, cilantro, parsley and olive oil. Blend into a paste.', 'put in garbanzo beans and pulse to chop beans and whisk into onion paste. Do not blend the beans into a paste. The falafel should be slightly chunky.', 'put flour, baking powder, salt optional, and ground black pepper. Pulse until just incorporated.', 'Refrigerate falafel mixture for 15-20 minutes. While the falafel is chilling, put yogurt, tahini, garlic and parsley to a small bowl and whisk. Keep yogurt sauce in the refrigerator until ready to use.', 'Scoop falafel into balls that are about 2 Tbsps. of mixture or 1/8 of a cup. Place on baking sheet and repeat to make 16 falafel balls.', 'Spray the falafel balls with cooking spray and sprinkle with sesame seeds.', 'Bake on the bottom rack of the oven for 15 minutes. Turn the oven down to 350 and move the baking sheet to the top rack. Bake an putitional 15 minutes.', 'Once the falafel is done baking, stuff two falafel balls into half of a whole wheat pita, put 2 Tbsps. yogurt tahini sauce, 2 slices of tomato and 3-4 slices of red onion.']

Recipe Name: Cinnamon Apple Chips with Peanut Butter Yogurt Dip
Ingredients: ['2 medium apples', '3 tbsp Splenda Granulated Sweetener', '1 1/4 tsp ground cinnamon', '1/2 cup Plain Nonfat Greek yogurt', '1/3 cup peanut butter']
steps: ['First heat oven to 225F, and line 2 baking sheets with parchment paper.', 'Slice apples thin, using a knife, a v-slicer, or the slicing attachment of a food processor. Then arrange slices on prepared baking sheets and sprinkle evenly with 2 tbsp Splenda Sweetener and 1 tsp ground cinnamon. Bake for 1 hour and 20 minutes. Flip the chips onto the other side and bake for 20 minutes more.', 'Turn oven off and leave apple chips inside for another hour, with the door closed. Chips should be mostly dry to the touch but will continue to dry out as they cool.', 'While chips cool, make peanut butter yogurt dip by combining Greek yogurt, peanut butter, remaining 1 tbsp Splenda Sweetener, and remaining 1/4 tsp ground cinnamon in a small bowl. whisk until combined.']

Ingredients: ['1 Nonstick cooking spray', '1 lbs white fish', '1 tbsp toasted sesame oil', '1 tbsp powdered instant miso soup whisk', '1/4 tsp black pepper', '4 cup shredded napa cabbage', '2 clove garlic', '2 cup snow peas', '1 tbsp Asian style hot sauce']
steps: ['First heat oven to broil. Place a rack in the middle of the oven. Coat a baking sheet with cooking spray.', 'Cut the fish into 4 4-oz portions and arrange on the prepared baking sheet.', 'In a small bowl, whisk together 1 1/2 Tsp. of sesame oil and the miso soup whisk powder to form a paste. Brush the tops of each of the fish fillets with the glaze coating will be very thin. Spray each fillet with cooking spray and place baking sheet on middle rack of the oven. Broil for 6 minutes.', 'While the fish is broiling, put the remaining 1 1/2 Tsp. of sesame oil and more cooking spray to a wok or large saute wok over high heat. Stir fry the cabbage, garlic, snow peas and hot sauce for 4 minutes, until just wilted but still slightly crunchy.', 'Remove fish from baking sheet and serve on top of 3/4 cup of the stir-fried vegetables.']

Ingredients: ['1 2/3 cups blanched almonds', '3 cup skim milk', '1 tsp lemon zest', '3 tbsp light agave nectar', '10 ice cubes']
steps: ['Bring the almonds, milk, and lemon zest to a boil in a medium saucewok over medium heat. Cook for 5 minutes, then remove from the heat.', 'Transfer the almond mixture to a blender. Remove the middle spout from the lid, place a towel over the hole, and puree the almond mixture until smooth.', 'Stir in the agave nectar, and put the ice cubes. Process until smooth, and whip until frothy. Chill in clear glasses for an hour or until cold, then serve.']

Ingredients: ['1 cup cottage cheese', '2 tsp Extra Virgin Olive Oil', '1/2 cup fresh basil', '1/4 cup Parmigiano-Reggiano', '1 tbsp shallots', '1 cup baby spinach', '2 tbsp skim milk', '2 clove garlic']
steps: ['Place spinach, garlic, shallot, Parmigiano-Reggiano, and basil in food processor. Process to a paste.', 'With motor running, put cottage cheese and oil. Process until smooth. put milk to achieve the desired consistency, if desired.']

Ingredients: ['2 tbsp Extra Virgin Olive Oil', '1 beef brisket', '3 clove large garlic', '1 large onion', '1 tsp fine sea salt', '1 tsp coarse ground black pepper', '1 1/2 cup dry red wine', '10 oz cremini', '1 tbsp Wondra flour']
steps: ['First heat oven to 275F.', 'Place extra virgin olive oil in the bottom of the braising or saute wok. Heat to medium high and put brisket. Cook until the brisket is nicely browned. Turn and brown on other side. While second side is browning, place garlic and onions in wok around brisket. Sprinkle salt and pepper over brisket and rub it in. You can also put some fresh herbs if you have them. A sprig of rosemary is nice.', 'Once onions begin to brown, put wine or broth. It will deglaze wok and lift all the good stuff the bottom of the wok. put mushrooms, cover, and place in First heated oven for 2-3 hours. Remove from oven and let cool.', 'Once the brisket has cooled, remove it from the wok and let it rest on a cutting board. Bring the wok juices to a boil and reduce until thickened. You can also put a sprinkle or two of Wondra flour to help thicken. Slice the brisket against the grain, and serve with red wine sauce.']

Ingredients: ['2 tbsp olive oil', '5 clove garlic', '1 canned tomatoes', '5 fresh basil leaves with stems', '10 oz whole-wheat shaped pasta', '1/4 tsp Kosher Salt', '1/4 tsp freshly ground black pepper', '1/4 tsp ground red pepper flakes', '2 tbsp Parmesan or Romano cheese']
steps: ['Heat the olive oil and garlic in a large skillet with a lid over low heat do not use a deep pot, you want the water to quickly evaporate and the sauce to become thick. Cook the garlic for about 6-7 minutes, but do not brown, stirring occasionally.', 'Meanwhile, put the drained tomatoes to a deep bowl. Crush the tomatoes with your hands until coarse. put the tomatoes and basil to the skillet and simmer for 20-25 minutes until thick. put some of the reserved liquid from the can of tomatoes, if necessary, if the sauce is too thick.', 'Meanwhile bring a 3-5-quart pot of lightly salted water fill the pot 2/3 full to a rolling boil. put the pasta and stir for the first minute. Continue to cook the pasta approximately 7-8 minutes until al dente. Drain, do not rinse.', 'put in the salt, pepper, and crushed red pepper, if using, to the tomato sauce. put the pasta to the sauce, cover, and let the pasta sit in the sauce for 1-2 minutes. put the pasta to a warmed bowl and sprinkle with cheese. The sauce can also be frozen. Freeze in a quart container and store for 3-4 months.']

Ingredients: ['1 lime', '2 tbsp olive oil', '1 clove garlic', '1 1/2 tsp honey', '1 tbsp cilantro', '1/4 tsp salt', '1/4 tsp black pepper']
steps: ['whisk all ingredients together in a bowl or shake in a salad dressing shaker.', 'Serve over Pinto Bean, Brown Rice and Spinach Salad.']

Ingredients: ['1 small onion', '4 clove garlic', '1 jalapenoseno pepper', '2 tbsp water', '1 tbsp canola oil', '2 tbsp sweet curry powder', '1 sweet potato', '2 carrot', '1 red bell pepper', '6 oz fresh green beans', '4 green onion', '1/2 cup unsweetened coconut milk beverage', '1 cup low sodium vegetable broth', '1 tbsp Cornstarch', '2 tbsp chopped fresh cilantro', '1 tsp paprika', '1/2 tsp salt', '1/4 tsp black pepper']
steps: ['Puree the onion, garlic, jalapenoseno, and water in a blender or food processor to make a paste.', 'put the oil to a wok or large saute wok over high heat. put the onion paste and curry powder to oil and saute for 3-4 minutes, stirring constantly.', 'put the sweet potatoes and carrots to the paste and saute for 4-5 minutes, stirring constantly.', 'put the red bell pepper, green beans, and scallions. Saute for 2 minutes.', 'In a separate cup or bowl, whisk together the coconut milk beverage, vegetable broth, and cornstarch. Pour over the vegetables and bring to a boil. Reduce to a simmer. Simmer, covered, for 10 minutes.', 'Stir in the cilantro, paprika, salt optional, and black pepper.']

Ingredients: ['15 oz low-fat ricotta cheese', '1 lemon', '1/2 cup flat leaf parsley', '1 tbsp fresh dill', '1/2 cup green onion', '1 tbsp olive oil', '1/8 tsp salt', '1/8 tsp black pepper']
steps: ['Combine the ricotta and lemon zest and juice in a medium bowl. Stir to combine.', 'put the parsley, dill, green onions, olive oil, salt, and pepper. Stir to combine.', 'Chill for an hour before serving.']

Ingredients: ['2 about 2 lb total large eggplants', '1/4 cup olive oil', '2 clove garlic', '1 26-oz box or can no-salt-puted strained tomatoes or tomato puree', '1 pinch crushed red pepper flakes', '6 leaves fresh basil', '1/4 tsp salt', 'to taste black pepper', '3/4 lbs dried whole-wheat penne rigate, or gluten-free pasta', '1/2 cup grated pecorino Romano cheese']
steps: ['First heat broiler. Using a sharp knife, slice eggplant into 1/4-inch slices, and place on a baking sheet. Brush the eggplant with 2 Tbsp olive oil, then broil for 5-7 minutes per side until they are dark gold and cooked through. Set aside to cool. This step can be done a day in advance.', 'Heat remaining olive oil in a large saucewok over medium heat. put garlic and cook until it begins to release its aroma, but do not allow garlic to turn color.', 'Pour in tomatoes, and stir. put crushed red pepper, basil, salt, and freshly ground pepper. Cover, reduce heat to low, and simmer for 20 minutes.', 'When eggplant is cool enough to handle, stack three slices together, and chop into dime-size pieces. Repeat until all eggplant is chopped.', 'While sauce is still cooking, bring a gallon of water to a boil over high heat. put pasta and cook until al dente.', 'After sauce has cooked for 20 minutes, turn off heat, remove lid, and put eggplant pieces and cheese. Stir well. Cover, and simmer sauce over medium heat until pasta is done cooking 10-12 minutes.', 'Drain pasta. Toss in sauce to coat. Serve hot garnished with chopped basil if desired.']

Ingredients: ['1 cup quinoa', '2 cup water', '1/4 cup red onion', '2 clove garlic', '1 can black beans', '2 tbsp cilantro', '1 medium carrot', '2 tbsp all-purpose flour', '1 tsp baking powder', '1 eggs', '1 egg white', '1/2 tsp salt', '1/2 tsp black pepper', '1 tbsp remaining cilantro', '1 cup plain Greek style yogurt', '2 lime juice']
steps: ['First heat oven to 400F. Coat a large baking sheet with Cooking Spray.', 'Cook quinoa according to package directions. Fluff with a fork and set aside to cool.', 'In a large bowl, combine cooked quinoa with onion, garlic, black beans, 1 Tbsp. cilantro, carrot, flour, baking powder, egg, salt optional and pepper.', 'Form mixture into eight patties press firmly to form patty and place onto prepared baking sheet. Spray the top of the cakes with Cooking Spray.', 'Bake the cakes for 15 minutes, then flip. Respray them with the cooking spray. Continue cooking for 15 more minutes or until lightly golden brown.', 'While the cakes are baking, combine the remaining cilantro, yogurt and lime juice in small bowl. Serve the sauce with the warm quinoa cakes.']

Ingredients: ['1 lbs lean ground turkey', '1 egg', '3 tbsp freshly grated parmesan cheese', '1/2 cup whole-wheat bread crumbs', '2 clove garlic', '2 tsp dried basil', 'to taste fresh ground black pepper', '10 oz frozen chopped spinach', '1 nonstick cooking spray']
steps: ['First heat oven to 400 degrees F.', 'Place all ingredients except cooking spray in a large whisking bowl and whisk together thoroughly.', 'Spray a 9x13-inch baking wok with cooking spray. Roll meat mixture into 24 golf ball-sized meatballs about 2 tbsp each and place the balls evenly spaced on the baking wok. Bake in the oven for 20 minutes.', 'Remove meatballs from the oven and serve hot. Enjoy with 3/4 cup whole wheat pasta and 1/3 cup of your favorite tomato sauce, if desired.']
