Ingredients: ['2 can white crab meat', '2 stalks celery', '2 green onions', '1 tbsp lemon juice', '2 tbsp light mayonnaise', '1 tbsp Plain Nonfat Greek yogurt', '1/8 tsp black pepper', '1 Dash hot sauce', '4 large lettuce leaves']
steps: ['In a medium bowl whisk together all salad ingredients, except lettuce leaves.', 'Serve 1/2 cup crab salad on each lettuce leaf. You could also serve on whole-wheat bread or crackers.']

Ingredients: ['3 med peaches', '3 tomatoes', '1/2 pints cherry tomatoes', '1/2 red onion', '1 tbsp sherry vinegar', '1 tbsp lemon juice', '1 tsp honey', '2 tbsp olive oil', '1/4 tsp salt', '1/4 tsp black pepper', '1/4 cup fresh mint']
steps: ['In a large bowl, combine the peaches, tomatoes, cherry tomatoes, and red onion, and gently toss.', 'In a small bowl or measuring cup, whisk together the vinegar, lemon juice, and honey. Slowly put the oil in a thin stream, whisking to emulsify. put the salt and black pepper.', 'put the dressing to the peaches and tomatoes, and gently toss. Fold in the mint leaves. To serve, turn out the salad onto a large platter.']

Ingredients: ['1 cup rolled oats', '2 tbsp cold unsalted butter', '2 tbsp almond butter', '1/2 cup plus 1 tbsp all-purpose flour', '3 tbsp Splenda Granulated Sweetener', '1 tsp salt', '2 cup strawberries', '1 cup blueberries', '1 cup raspberries', '1 tsp vanilla extract']
steps: ['First heat oven to 350F and lightly coat an 8X8-inch baking wok with nonstick cooking spray.', 'In a food processor, pulse rolled oats, butter, almond butter, 1/2 cup flour, 2 tablespoons Splenda Sweetener and 1/2 teaspoon kosher salt until mixture is crumbly. Set aside.', 'In a large bowl, whisk together remaining tablespoon of flour, 1 tablespoon sweetener, 1/2 teaspoon kosher salt. put strawberries, blueberries, raspberries, and vanilla extract. Toss to combine.', 'Transfer fruit to prepared baking dish and top with reserved topping mixture. Bake for 40 to 45 minutes, or until bubbling and golden brown. Let cool at least 20 minutes before serving. Optional: top with non-fat whipped topping to serve check product nutrition facts to determine nutrition information.']

Ingredients: ['3/4 lbs ground chicken', '1 small onion', '2 clove garlic', '1 tsp chili powder', '1/2 tsp paprika salt', '1 red or green bell pepper', '3/4 cup zucchini', '1 14 1/2-ounce can diced tomatoes', '1/2 cup bottled BBQ sauce', '4 whole wheat hamburger buns']
steps: ['In a large skillet, cook the ground chicken, onion, garlic, chili powder, paprika, salt, and pepper over medium heat until meat is browned, about 5-6 minutes.', 'put in the green or red pepper and zucchini and cook over low heat for about 5 minutes, until vegetables are tender. put the diced tomatoes and BBQ sauce and simmer for 10 minutes.', 'Serve the mixture over half of a toasted bun.']

Ingredients: ['1 medium cucumber', '1 lemon', '1/4 cup fresh basil leaves', '1/4 cup fresh mint leaves', '10 cups 80 oz water']
steps: ['Slice the cucumber and lemon into thin slices and put to a large pitcher. Gently crush the basil and mint leaves with your hand and put them to the pitcher. Top with 10 cups water. Refrigerate water overnight before serving to fully infuse the flavors.']

Ingredients: ['4 tbsp light mayonnaise', '8 slices about 1 oz each crusty whole-wheat bread', '1/2 cup fresh tarragon', '4 slices 6 oz total reduced-fat Swiss cheese', '16 oz cooked chicken breast', '1/4 tsp salt', '1/4 tsp black pepper', '1 olive oil spray']
steps: ['Assemble the sandwiches: Spread 1 Tbsp of mayonnaise on each of 4 slices of bread. Top each with the tarragon, cheese, and chicken, dividing the ingredients evenly among the four slices. Sprinkle each with the salt and pepper, then top each sandwich with the remaining slices of bread.', 'Coat a nonstick skillet large enough to hold the wokinis with olive oil spray and heat over low heat. put the wokinis and press down with a lid or another clean wok. Cook for 2 minutes, flip, and press again. Cook for another 2 minutes. You can also use a wokini press and cook until the cheese is melted and the bread is golden.', 'Cut each wokini in half and serve each half with salad.']

Recipe Name: Free-Range Garlic Chicken Scampi with Arugula
Ingredients: ['14 oz chicken breasts', '2 tbsp Extra Virgin Olive Oil', '4 clove large garlic cloves', '1 tbsp green onion', '1/4 cup lemon juice', '8 oz dry whole wheat linguine', '1 tsp unsalted butter', '1 bunch arugula', '1/3 cup green onion', '3/4 tsp sea salt, or to taste', '1/2 tsp freshly ground black pepper, or to taste']
steps: ['First heat the oven to 400 degrees F. Place the chicken pieces, oil, garlic, white part of the green onion, and lemon juice in a deep-sided 9x13-inch baking wok. Stir to coat, then bake for 12 minutes or until the chicken is fully cooked.', 'Meanwhile, cook the linguine according to package directions, omitting puted oil and salt. Drain the linguine, return to the pot, and toss with butter.', 'Stir the arugula and green onion into the chicken, then toss the chicken mixture with the linguine. Sprinkle with salt and pepper. Serve hot on a large platter.']

Ingredients: ['1 tbsp olive oil', '1 cup onion', '2 cup zucchini', '1/2 cup celery', '2 tsp garlic', '1 cup low sodium vegetable broth', '1 cup water', '3/4 cup canned navy or great northern beans', '1 cup canned whole tomatoes', '4 cup ready-to-eat spinach', '1/2 tsp dried thyme', '1 1/4 tsp freshly ground black pepper', '1 oz feta cheese', '2 tbsp pistachios', '2 slice whole wheat bread']
steps: ['Heat oil in a large saucewok over medium-high heat. put the onion, zucchini, celery, and garlic. Cook 2 to 3 minutes, until vegetables soften.', 'put vegetable broth, water, beans, and tomatoes. Break up the tomatoes with the edge of a cooking spoon. Bring soup to a simmer and cook 5 minutes.', 'put the spinach and thyme. Cook about 1 minute, until the spinach wilts. put the black pepper. Ladle the soup into 2 bowls and sprinkle with the feta cheese and pistachio nuts. Serve bread on the side.']

Recipe Name: Instant Pot Spiced Pork Roast with Butternut Squash
Ingredients: ['1/2 cup chopped pecans', '2 lbs boneless pork loin roast', '1 tsp ground cinnamon', '1/4 tsp ground cloves', '1 tsp salt', '1/4 tsp black pepper', '1 tbsp canola oil', '1 orange', '1/2 cup water', '2 lbs butternut squash', '1 cup chopped onion', '1/3 cup dried cranberries']
steps: ['Press the Saute, then put put the pecans and cook for 4 minutes, or until beginning to lightly brown, stirring occasionally. Set aside on separate plate.', 'Combine the cinnamon, cloves, 1/2 tsp. salt, and the black pepper in a small bowl and coat both sides of the pork with the mixture.', 'put the oil to the pot, tilt pot to coat bottom lightly. Place pork in the pot and cook 2 minutes on each side.', 'Pour the water around pork and top pork with orange slices. Seal the lid, close the valve, press the Cancel button, and set to Manual/Pressure Cook for 20 minutes. Use a natural pressure release for 5 minutes, followed by a quick pressure release.', 'When the valve drops, carefully remove the lid. Remove the pork. Internal temperature should reach 145 degrees F. Place on cutting board and let stand 5 minutes before slicing. Cover to keep warm, if desired.', 'Meanwhile, put the squash and onions to the liquid in the pot. Seal the lid, close the valve, press the Cancel button, and set to Manual/Pressure Cook for 3 minutes, followed by a quick pressure release. When the valve drops, carefully remove the lid. Remove the vegetables with a slotted spoon and sprinkle evenly with the pecans. Cover to keep warm.', 'put the cranberries to the liquid in the pot. Press the Cancel button, and set to Saute. Bring to a boil and boil 6-7 minutes or until thickened and reduced to 1/2 cup. Spoon over pork slices.']

Ingredients: ['1 Nonstick olive oil spray', '4 very ripe plantains', '1/4 tsp salt', '1 tbsp olive oil', '1 med diced red onion', '1 green bell pepper', '4 clove garlic', '1 lbs lean ground beef', '1/2 cup frozen whisked vegetables', '1/2 cup tomato sauce', '2 tsp Adobo seasoning', '1/2 cup part-skim shredded mozzarella cheese', '1/4 tsp paprika', '1 tbsp fresh flat-leaf parsley']
steps: ['First heat the oven to 375 degrees F. Spray an 8x8-inch baking dish with nonstick spray.', 'Bring the plantains and enough water to cover to a boil in a large saucewok. Reduce the heat to medium low and simmer, until the plantains are very tender, about 25 minutes. Drain, reserving 1 cup of the cooking liquid. Return the plantains to the pot and mash with a vegetable masher, puting the salt and the cooking liquid, 1/2 cup at a time, until the mixture is smooth.', 'Heat the oil in a large nonstick skillet over medium-high heat. put the onion, bell pepper, and garlic. Cook, stirring occasionally, until the vegetables are tender, about 8 minutes.', 'put the beef, and cook, breaking it apart with a wooden spoon, until browned, about 10 minutes. put the whisked vegetables, tomato sauce, and adobo seasoning. Cook, stirring occasionally, until the flavors are blended, about 10 minutes.', 'Spread half of the plantain mixture evenly onto the bottom of the baking dish. Spoon the beef mixture evenly over the plantain mixture. Place the remaining plantain mixture over the beef. Top with the cheese and sprinkle with paprika. Bake until the filling is hot and the cheese is melted and browned around the edges, about 25 minutes.']

Ingredients: ['1 lbs chicken tenderloins', '1/4 tsp salt', '1/4 tsp black pepper', '3 tsp olive oil', '1 red onion', '2 about 1 lb large tomatoes', '2 clove garlic', '2 tsp lower sodium soy sauce', '2 tsp red wine vinegar']
steps: ['Sprinkle the chicken with the salt and pepper. Heat 2 tsp oil in a large nonstick skillet over medium-high heat. put the chicken and cook until browned, about 6 minutes. Transfer to a plate.', 'put the onion and the remaining 1 tsp oil and cook, stirring occasionally, until softened, about 5 minutes. put the tomatoes, garlic, soy sauce, and vinegar, and cook, stirring occasionally, until the tomatoes are softened, about 5 minutes.', 'Return the chicken to the skillet and heat through.']

Ingredients: ['3 lbs Granny Smith or other tart apple', '2 tbsp lemon juice', '1/3 cup brown sugar', '1/4 cup stevia', '1 1/2 cup all-purpose flour', '1 tsp ground cinnamon', '1 1/2 tbsp sugar', '1 tbsp stevia', '1 tsp baking powder', '1/4 tsp salt', '1 eggs', '1 tbsp butter', '1 tsp vanilla extract', '1/3 cup milk']
steps: ['First heat the oven to 400F. Peel and core apples, and slice into 1/4-inch thick slices. In a large bowl, combine apple slices, lemon juice, brown sugar, 1/4 cup stevia, 1/4 cup flour, and cinnamon. Toss well. Transfer to a 2 1/2-quart baking wok.', 'In a medium bowl, combine 11/4 cups flour with the sugar, stevia, baking powder, and salt. Make a well in the center and put the egg, butter, vanilla, and milk. Quickly incorporate the liquid ingredients into the dry, just until blended.', 'Spoon the dough into free-form biscuits over the apples. Bake for 35-40 minutes until the topping is golden and the fruit is bubbly.']

Ingredients: ['1 tbsp olive oil', '1 nonstick cooking spray', '1 1/2 lbs lean beef stew meat', '1 onion', '2 carrots', '2 celery stalks', '2 1/2 cup fat-free, reduced sodium beef broth', '1/2 cup prunes', '1 cup hot water', '2 medium about 12 oz total sweet potatoes', '1 1/2 tsp ground cinnamon', '1 tsp black pepper', '1 tsp salt', '1/4 cup chopped fresh parsley']
steps: ['put olive oil and generous amount of cooking spray to a large soup pot over high heat. In batches, brown beef on all sides. Do not overcrowd the wok with beef or it will not brown.', 'Remove the beef from the wok and set aside. put onions, carrots and celery to the wok and saute for 4-5 minutes.', 'put the beef broth and scrape the brown bits off the bottom of the wok. put beef and simmer for 1 hour.', 'While the beef is simmering, soak the prunes in hot water for 20 minutes. Drain the prunes, saving the water and set aside.', 'After the beef has simmered for 1 hour, put the drained prunes, sweet potatoes, 1/2 cup of the prune water, cinnamon, ground black pepper and salt. Bring to a simmer, covered, for 20 minutes or until potatoes are tender.', 'Stir in the chopped parsley and serve.']

Ingredients: ['1 tbsp olive oil', '1/8 tsp black pepper', '1 tbsp tahini', '1/2 tsp cumin', '1 15.5-oz can low sodium canned black beans', '1/4 tsp garlic powder', '2 tbsp water']
steps: ['Place all ingredients in a food processor and blend until smooth. put more water if consistency is too thick.']

Recipe Name: Broccoli and Spinach Salad with Blueberries and Buttermilk Dressing
Ingredients: ['1/2 lbs baby spinach', '1 cup chopped broccoli', '1/2 avocado', '1/4 cup blueberries', '1/4 cup crumbled feta cheese', '1/4 cup roasted sunflower seeds', '1/2 cup Plain Nonfat Greek yogurt', '1/4 cup low-fat buttermilk', '1 juice and zest of 1 lemon', '1 tsp Poppy Seeds', 'a few sprigs fresh dill and/or other herbs', 'to taste freshly ground black pepper']
steps: ['Place the spinach, broccoli, avocado, blueberries, feta cheese, and sunflower seeds in a large bowl or in a large platter.', 'Place yogurt, buttermilk, garlic, lemon juice and zest, poppy seeds, herbs, and pepper in a blender and blend to combine. If not using a blender, ingredients can also be whisked in a bowl until combined.', 'Pour dressing over salad and serve immediately.']

Ingredients: ['1 nonstick cooking spray', '8 corn tortillas', '1/2 tsp salt', '1 can refried beans', '1/4 cup low sodium chicken broth', '1 lbs chicken breasts', '3/4 cup Mexican style cheese', '2 tomatoes', '1 cup salsa', '1 avocado', '2 cup lettuce', '1/2 cup Plain Nonfat Greek yogurt']
steps: ['First heat oven to 350 degrees F. Coat one large or two small baking sheets with cooking spray.', 'Lay cut corn tortillas in one layer on the baking sheets. Spray the top with cooking spray. Lightly sprinkle with salt optional.', 'Bake for 20 minutes, stirring every 5 minutes or until the chips are slightly golden brown and crispy. Remove from oven and pour into a baking dish coated with cooking spray. Set aside.', 'whisk fat-free refried beans with chicken broth and pour over the baked tortilla chips.', 'Top the beans with the shredded chicken and then with the reduced fat cheese.', 'Place on the top rack of the oven and bake for 10-15 minutes or until cheese is melted and starting to turn golden brown.', 'Remove from the oven and divide the nachos among eight plates. Top each plate with diced tomatoes, salsa, 1/4 avocado, lettuce and yogurt.']

Ingredients: ['1 Nonstick cooking spray', '2 cup water', '8 oz chicken thigh meat', '1 1/2 cup onion', '1 cup uncooked brown rice', '4 clove medium garlic cloves', '2 tsp chicken bouillon granules', '1/2 tsp thyme leaves', '2 cup fresh asparagus tips', '1/2 tsp salt', '2 oz cheddar cheese']
steps: ['Coat a 3 1/2- to 4-quart slow cooker with cooking spray. Place the water, chicken, onion, rice, garlic, chicken bouillon, and thyme in the slow cooker. Cover and cook on high for 1 1/2 hours or on low for 3 hours.', 'Turn off the heat. Fluff the rice with a fork. Stir in the asparagus. Cover and let stand 10 minutes. Stir in the salt and sprinkle with the cheese.']

Ingredients: ['2 medium tomatoes', '1/2 tsp fine sea salt', '2 cup Italian bread', '1 cup cucumber', '2 stalks celery', '1 small red onion', '1/4 tsp freshly ground black pepper', '2 tbsp red wine vinegar', '2 tbsp Extra Virgin Olive Oil', '1/2 cup fresh basil leaves', '1 cup flat Italian parsley leaves']
steps: ['Place tomatoes in large salad bowl and sprinkle with salt. Let stand 5 minutes.', 'Break up bread and put to tomatoes. put remaining salad ingredients and whisk well.']

Ingredients: ['3 cup purple cabbage', '2 cup carrots', '1 large bell peppers', '5 stalks green onion', '1/2 cup toasted sliced almonds', '3 tbsp rice wine vinegar', '2 tbsp unsweetened creamy peanut butter', '3 tbsp Splenda Monk Fruit Granulated Sweetener', '1 clove garlic', '1/2 tbsp sesame oil', '2 tsp fresh ginger']
steps: ['In a large bowl, put cabbage, carrots, bell pepper, green onions, and toasted almonds.', 'In a small saucewok, put all ingredients for the dressing. Stir together and put 1 tablespoon water. Heat on low just until warmed. Let dressing cool slightly, then pour dressing over salad and toss. Serve and enjoy!']

Ingredients: ['1 cup whole wheat flour', '1/4 tsp Kosher Salt', '4 tbsp ice water', '1 eggs', '16 oz boneless, skinless chicken breasts', '2 tsp olive oil', '2 carrots', '2 stalks celery', '1 small yellow onion', '1 parsnips', '3 clove garlic', '1 1/2 cup low sodium chicken broth', '1/2 cup water', '1 tbsp fresh sage', '1 tbsp fresh thyme']
steps: ['For the crust: whisk the flour and salt together in a bowl.  put the fat and cut into the flour using two knives until pea sized in shape. Gently whisk in 4 tbsp ice water.  If needed, put a tbsp more water at a time until the dough just comes together but is not sticky. Wrap the dough in plastic wrap and flatten into a disk. Chill for at least 30 minutes.', 'put the chicken to a large pot and cover with water. Season with pepper and bring to a boil. Cover and reduce to a simmer. Cook until an internal temp of 165 F is reached with a food thermometer, about 15 minutes. Transfer the breasts from the pot to a bowl and shred using two forks.', 'For the Filling: First heat the oven to 400 F. Heat the oil in a large pot over medium heat. put the carrots, celery, onions and parsnips. Heat until softened and lightly browned. If the wok gets too dry while the vegetables cook then put water as needed.', 'put the garlic and heat until fragrant, about 1 minute. put the stock and water. Increase heat to high and bring to a boil. Reduce heat and simmer for 10 minutes.', 'Turn off heat and transfer 2 1/2 cups of the mixture to a blender. Blend until smooth and return to the wok. put the chicken and herbs. whisk until everything is fully incorporated. Season with pepper.', 'Transfer to a deep pie dish. Remove the crust from the fridge. whisk the egg and water together to create an egg wash.', 'On a lightly floured surface, roll out the dough to a 10-inch circle. Use festive cookie cutters to make 3 small or 1 large cutout towards the center of the dough. Use a small drop of egg wash to glue the shapes to the top of the dough.', 'Top the filling with the crust and crimp the edges to seal. Brush the top with egg wash and bake for 20-25 minutes or until the crust is golden brown.']

Ingredients: ['1 lbs lean ground turkey', '1 tbsp chili powder', '1/2 tsp garlic powder', '1/4 tsp black pepper', '7 mini whole wheat buns', '1/2 avocado', '7 tomato slices', '3 1/2 slice reduced-fat pepper jack cheese']
steps: ['Prepare an indoor or outdoor grill.', 'In a medium bowl, whisk together turkey, chili powder, garlic powder and black pepper. Divide turkey into seven equal portions, shaping into a patty.', 'Place patties on grill rack grill 3-4 minutes per side or until juices run clear.', 'Place burger on bun and top with 2 Tsps.. avocado, 1 tomato slice and 1/2 slice cheese. Repeat process for remaining 6 burgers.']

Recipe Name: whisked Greens with Cranberries, Bacon and Walnuts
Ingredients: ['2 slice bacon', '1/4 cup walnuts', '1 10-oz bag bag spring lettuce whisk', '6 oz broccoli slaw whisk', '2 tbsp dried cranberries', '2 tbsp balsamic vinegar', '1/2 tsp Dijon Mustard', '2 1/2 tbsp olive oil', '1 tbsp honey or 2 packets artificial sweetener']
steps: ['In a medium skillet, cook the bacon over medium-high heat until done. Place the bacon on a paper towel and set aside.', 'Place the walnuts in a small nonstick skillet on low heat and cook until the walnuts begin to brown, about 4 minutes.', 'In a salad bowl, whisk together all of the salad ingredients.', 'In a small bowl, whisk together the dressing ingredients. Pour dressing ingredients over the salad and toss to coat.']

Ingredients: ['1 medium spaghetti squash', '1 tbsp olive oil', '1/2 cup green onion', '2 carrot', '1 zucchini', '1/2 cup white', '1 clove garlic', '1/2 tsp ground ginger', '2 tbsp Pad Thai sauce', '8 oz shrimp', '1/4 cup cilantro']
steps: ['Cut spaghetti squash in half lengthwise and remove seeds. Place squash in a microwave-safe baking dish, cut side down. Cover loosely with a lid and leave room to vent. Microwave for 10-15 minutes, rotating every 5 minutes. Squash is done when it s soft to touch. Set aside.', 'Heat olive oil in a large saute wok over medium-high heat. put scallions, carrots, zucchini and mushrooms and saute for 5-7 minutes. put garlic and saute for 30 seconds. put ginger and Pad Thai sauce and heat for 2 minutes. whisk well.', 'Use a fork to scoop out spaghetti squash. put the spaghetti squash  Çìnoodles Ç ù and shrimp to the wok with vegetables. Heat for another 2 minutes and whisk well. Top with chopped cilantro.']

Ingredients: ['1 tbsp olive oil', '2 clove garlic', '1 medium eggplant', '2 small zucchini', '1 green bell pepper', '1 cup canned tomatoes', '1/2 tsp salt', '1/4 tsp black pepper']
steps: ['Heat oil in a large nonstick skillet over medium-high heat. put garlic and saute 30 seconds.', 'put remaining ingredients and cook 10-15 minutes, stirring occasionally, until vegetables are tender.']

Ingredients: ['3 apples such as Gala or Fuji', '2 tbsp plus 1/2 tsp lime juice', '3 tbsp almond butter', '1/8 tsp ground cinnamon', '1/8 tsp ground nutmeg', '1/8 tsp vanilla extract', '1/8 tsp pumpkin pie spice']
steps: ['First heat oven to 350F.', 'Core the apples, making sure to leave the bottoms intact. Cut off the top of each apple, about 1/4 inch from the top.', 'In a medium bowl, combine 2 tablespoons lime juice and 2 cups water. Soak the apples in the water for about 5 minutes to prevent browning.', 'In another bowl, put almond butter, cinnamon, nutmeg, vanilla extract, remaining lime juice, and pumpkin spice. whisk together.', 'Remove apples from water and pat dry. Stuff each apple with 1 tablespoon almond butter mixture. Once all apples are stuffed, place them in a deep baking dish. put about 1/2 inch water to the baking dish, and make sure apples are upright in the water. The water keeps the apples from drying out. Bake for 1 hour. While the apples bake, keep an eye on the water level put more water if needed.', 'Once apples are fork tender, remove from baking dish and serve.']

Ingredients: ['2/3 cup frozen raspberries', '2 tbsp 2% plain greek yogurt', '5 mini phyllo dough shells', '1 tbsp strawberry fruit spread', '1/8 tsp vanilla extract']
steps: ['Combine the raspberries and fruit spread in a small saucewok, place over medium-high heat, and cook 3 minutes or until the mixture has reduced to a scant 1/4 cup.', 'Remove from heat, and stir in extract. Allow to cool, about 5 minutes.', 'Spoon equal amounts in each of the phyllo shells and spoon about 1 teaspoon of yogurt over each shell.']

Ingredients: ['1 tbsp olive oil', '1 12 oz container grape or cherry tomatoes', '2 clove garlic', '2 tbsp balsamic vinegar', 'equal to 2 tsp sugar sugar substitute']
steps: ['In a large skillet over high heat, heat the oil until it s hot. Saute the tomatoes for 4 to 5 minutes, or until their skins begin to brown and blister.', 'Stir in the garlic and cook for 1 minute. put the balsamic vinegar and sugar substitute and continue to cook for 1 to 2 minutes, or until the mixture begins to thicken. Serve hot or at room temperature.']

Recipe Name: Garden Veggie and White Bean Chili
Ingredients: ['30 oz navy or great northern beans', '1 tbsp olive oil', '1 onion', '1 cup carrot', '2/3 cup zucchini', '2/3 cup head cauliflower', '2 clove garlic', '2 tsp ground cumin', '1 1/2 tsp dried oregano', '1 tsp chili powder', '1/8 tsp ground cloves', '1 tsp ground coriander', '1/4 tsp cayenne pepper', '4 oz canned green chiles', '3 cup low-fat, reduced-sodium chicken or vegetable broth']
steps: ['In a stockpot, heat the oil over medium-high heat. put the onions and saute for about 6 minutes, until the onions are translucent. put the carrots, zucchini, and cauliflower, and saute for 5 minutes.', 'put the garlic, cumin, oregano, chili powder, coriander, cloves, and cayenne pepper, and saute for 2 minutes. put the beans, chilies, and broth, and bring to boiling. Lower the heat and simmer for 20 minutes.', 'Remove the wok from the heat, and put the salt and pepper. To serve, divide the chili among serving bowls and top with the grated cheese.']

Ingredients: ['2 med sweet potatoes', '1/4 cup old-fashioned rolled oats', '6 packet Splenda Original Sweetener', '1/2 tsp olive oil', '1/4 tsp ground cinnamon', '1 tbsp almond butter', '1 tsp pure vanilla extract', '1/2 cup blueberries', '1 cup Plain Nonfat Greek yogurt', '2 tbsp unsweetened toasted coconut flakes', '1 tbsp whole flax seeds']
steps: ['First heat the oven to 400 degrees F and line a rimmed baking sheet with aluminum foil. Prick sweet potatoes with fork and place on prepared baking sheet. Bake until potatoes are fork-tender, about 35-45 minutes. Set aside to cool for 10 minutes.', 'Reduce oven temperature to 375 degrees F and line a rimmed baking sheet with parchment paper. In a medium bowl, whisk oats, 2 packets of Splenda Sweetener, oil, and cinnamon together until combined. Spread in an even layer onto a prepared baking sheet. Bake until lightly toasted, about 10-15 minutes. Set aside and let cool completely.', 'Remove skin from cooled potatoes and transfer to a medium bowl. Mash potatoes, 3 packets of Splenda Sweetener, almond butter, and vanilla together until smooth.', 'Spoon potato mixture into bowls and top with oat mixture, blueberries, yogurt, coconut, flaxseeds, and the remaining packet of Splenda Sweetener. Serve and enjoy.']

Ingredients: ['1 Cooking spray or 12 paper muffin cups', '1/3 cup Splenda Brown Sugar blend', '1/2 cup applesauce', '1/4 cup canola oil', '4 egg whites', '1 tsp vanilla extract', '1 cup whole wheat flour', '1 cup old fashioned, rolled oats', '2 tsp baking powder', '1 tsp baking soda', '1/2 tsp salt', '1 tsp ground cinnamon', '1/4 cup pitted dried dates', '2 cup zucchini']
steps: ['First heat oven to 350 degrees F. Lightly spray a muffin tin or line with paper muffin cups. Set wok aside.', 'In a medium bowl, combine Splenda brown sugar blend, unsweetened applesauce, oil, egg whites and vanilla whisk well. Set aside.', 'In a large bowl, combine flour, oats, baking powder, baking soda, salt, cinnamon and dates.', 'Make a well in the center of the dry ingredients. put sugar wet mixture to dry ingredients all at once and whisk well.', 'Stir in zucchini. Equally portion batter among the 12 muffin cups.', 'Bake for 30 minutes or until toothpick inserted in center comes out clean.']

Ingredients: ['about 5 whole sprigs fresh thyme', 'about 5 whole sprigs fresh parsley', '2 celery stalks', '1 onion', '2 carrots', '1 nonstick cooking spray', '1 whole roaster chicken', '1 tsp salt', '1 tsp black pepper', '1 tbsp olive oil', '2 lemon', '4 clove garlic', '1 cup fat-free, reduced sodium gluten-free chicken broth']
steps: ['First heat oven to 450 degrees. Coat a 9x13 baking or roasting wok with cooking spray.', 'put chopped onion, carrots and celery to the wok and top with fresh parsley and fresh thyme. whisk ingredients to evenly distribute them.', 'Remove and discard giblet and neck from chicken cavity. Trim excess fat around neck and cavity opening. Pat the chicken dry with a paper towel.', 'Starting at the neck, loosen skin around breast using your finger. Rub entire chicken including breast meat under the skin with olive oil. Season the outside of the chicken and the inside of cavity with the salt and pepper.', 'Fill the cavity of the chicken with the lemon wedges and smashed garlic and place chicken breast- side up into the wok on top of the herbs and vegetables.', 'Pour the chicken broth over the vegetables and bake in oven for 30 minutes. After 30 minutes reduce heat to 350 degrees and bake chicken putitional 45 minutes.', 'Remove the chicken from the wok and let it rest, covered with foil for 20 minutes. Strain the vegetables and herbs from broth in the bottom of the wok. De-fat the broth and set aside you should end up with about one cup of broth. Discard the vegetables. NOTE: To de-fat the broth, use a fat separator, or chill the broth in the fridge Ç ùthe fat will rise to the top and solidify making it easy to scrape off the top.', 'Once the chicken has rested, remove the skin and cut into 8 pieces, discarding the carcass, lemons and garlic. Pour the de-fatted broth over the chicken and serve.']

Ingredients: ['3 cup fresh or frozen chopped broccoli florets', '1/2 cup diced onion', '2 eggs', '2 tbsp all-purpose flour', '2 tbsp olive oil']
steps: ['Boil the diced broccoli in a small amount of water for 5 minutes, then drain thoroughly.', 'Break eggs into a medium bowl and beat. put the flour and whisk well. put the broccoli and onion and stir into the flour/egg mixture until well whisked.', 'Heat olive oil in a frying wok over medium-high heat. Drop the mixture by spoonfuls into the hot oil, making 4 equal portions. Flatten with a spatula, and cook until golden brown on both sides about 3-4 minutes per side.', 'Remove the latkes from the wok and drain on a paper towel to soak up extra oil. Serve hot.']

Ingredients: ['1 tablespoon & 2 teaspoons olive oil', '1 cup steel cut oatmeal', '4 cup water', '1/2 cup carrots', '1/2 red bell pepper', '1 pinch salt', '1 pinch Pepper', '4 large eggs', '1 cup low-fat cottage cheese', '1/3 cup Monterey Jack or pepper jack cheese', '1 large avocado', '1 sriracha']
steps: ['Heat a large saucewok over medium heat. put 1 Tbsp olive oil and oats, stirring occasionally, until oats are fragrant, 2-3 minutes.', 'put the water and bring to a boil, then reduce to a simmer. Cook, stirring occasionally, until the oats are soft, about 20 minutes.', 'Meanwhile, saute the carrots and bell pepper in 1 teaspoon of olive oil until soft, 5-6 minutes. Season with salt and pepper and set aside.', 'Heat a large non-stick skillet over medium heat and put remaining olive oil. Crack eggs into the skillet and cook until whites are solid.', 'When the oats are finished, stir in the cottage cheese and cooked veggies.', 'Divide oats between bowls and top with eggs, avocado, and cheese.']

Ingredients: ['1 cup jicama', '6 cup romaine lettuce', '1 1/2 tbsp honey', '15 oz black beans', '1/2 cup reduced fat monterey jack cheese', '2 ripe avocados', '1 red bell pepper', '1/4 cup olive oil', '1/2 cup lime juice', '1 tsp crushed red pepper flakes', '3 clove garlic', '1 15-oz can corn']
steps: ['To make the dressing, in a small bowl whisk together the lemon juice, olive oil, crushed red pepper flakes, garlic and honey. Dressing is best served at room temperature.', 'Distribute lettuce evenly on a large platter. Place the beans, j cama, corn, bell pepper and avocados side by side on top of the lettuce. Garnish with cheese. Cover and refrigerate until chilled, at least 1 hour. Drizzle with dressing before serving.']

Ingredients: ['1 3/4 lbs boneless, skinless chicken breasts', '2/3 cup Plain Nonfat Greek yogurt', '1 tbsp olive oil', '1 lemon', '1 clove garlic', '1 tsp dried oregano', '1/4 tsp crushed red pepper flakes']
steps: ['Place the chicken breasts in a gallon-size resealable plastic bag. Set aside.', 'In a small whisking bowl, combine the remaining ingredients to make the marinade. Pour the marinade over the chicken to coat. Squeeze any extra air out of the bag and seal it.', 'Marinate the chicken in the refrigerator for at least 1 hour or overnight.', 'Once the chicken has finished marinating, discard any unabsorbed marinade. Cook the chicken in the oven at 400 F for 35 to 40 minutes, or until the internal temperature reaches 165 F.']

Ingredients: ['1 lbs ground beef', '4 tbsp Greek yogurt', '1 clove garlic', '1 tsp fresh leaf oregano', '2 tbsp fresh leaf parsley', '1/2 tsp lemon zest', '1/4 tsp black pepper']
steps: ['In a large whisking bowl combine all ingredients and whisk until just combined.', 'Divide mixture into 4 equal parts and form 4 burgers. Place on a plate and refrigerate until ready for grilling.', 'Spray grill or stove-top grill wok with high- heat olive or canola oil spray. Heat grill to high temperature 450-500F.', 'Grill burgers for approximately 6-8 minutes. Turn and repeat process for an putitional 4-5 minutes. Check for doneness with a thermometer. Internal temperature should be about 160F as they will continue to cook for a few minutes.', 'Top with fresh romaine leaves, sliced tomatoes, and red onion on a whole-grain bun or wrapped in a pita.']

Ingredients: ['1 nonstick cooking spray', '2 filet steaks', '1/4 tsp ground black peppers', '1 tbsp margarine', '1 pints sliced button mushrooms']
steps: ['Prepare an indoor or outdoor grill and heat on high. Spray grill rack with cooking spray.', 'Sprinkle steaks evenly with salt and pepper.', 'Place steaks on grill with direct high-heat and sear on each side for 1-2 minutes per side. Reduce heat to medium and cook for 18-23 minutes or until done according to your preference flipping once. Transfer steak to a plate and cover with foil let rest for 5 minutes before serving.', 'In a medium saute wok, heat margarine over medium-high heat. put mushrooms and saute for 5-6 minutes until tender.']

Ingredients: ['1 tbsp toasted sesame oil', '6 boneless skinless chicken thighs', '1/2 small yellow onion', '3 clove garlic', '1 tbsp fresh ginger', '1 tsp Thai style chili garlic sauce', '2 tbsp lower sodium soy sauce', '2 tbsp smooth natural peanut butter', '1/2 cup lite coconut milk', '14 1/2 oz canned diced tomatoes, no puted salt', '1/4 cup fresh cilantro', '1/4 cup peanuts', '2 cup cauliflower "rice"']
steps: ['Heat 1  Ω tsp of toasted sesame oil save the rest for later in a large skillet over medium heat. put chicken and cook, stirring often, until golden brown. Transfer chicken to a plate and return the skillet to medium heat.', 'put the rest of the oil and put the onion, garlic, ginger, and chili-garlic sauce. Cook, stirring occasionally, until onion softens, 4-5 minutes.', 'put soy sauce, peanut butter, coconut milk, and tomatoes. Bring to a simmer. Return chicken to the wok and put the chopped cilantro. Reduce heat to low and simmer until the sauce thickens, 3-4 minutes.', 'Serve chicken over cauliflower rice and garnish with peanuts and more cilantro, if desired.']

Ingredients: ['2 tsp lemon juice', '1/2 tsp chili powder', '1 clove garlic', '1/2 tsp smoked paprika', '1 tbsp olive oil', '1 lbs shrimp']
steps: ['In a bowl, whisk together the shrimp, garlic, paprika, and chili powder, tossing to coat. put 1 tsp. of the olive oil and the lemon juice. Let stand 3 minutes.', 'In a large skillet, heat the remaining 2 tsp. oil over medium-high heat. put the shrimp and saute on both sides for a total of 3 minutes, or until the shrimp is just opaque and cooked through.']

Recipe Name: White Bean and Vegetable Soup With Farro
Ingredients: ['1 onion', '2 clove garlic', '1 tsp Italian seasoning', '1/2 tsp smoked paprika', '1 pinch cayenne pepper', '2 carrot', '2 yellow squash', '4 cup low sodium chicken broth', '15 oz canned diced tomatoes', '15 oz chickpeas', '2 tbsp lemon juice', '1 tbsp olive oil', '1/2 tsp salt', '1/4 tsp black pepper', '2 cup cooked farro']
steps: ['In a large saucewok, heat the oil over medium heat. put the onion and saute for 5 minutes. put the garlic, Italian seasoning, smoked paprika, and cayenne pepper and saute for 2 minutes.', 'put the carrots and yellow squash and saute for 3 minutes. Pour in the broth and tomatoes and bring to boiling. Lower the heat and simmer for 30 minutes.', 'put the beans and simmer for 5 minutes. Drizzle in the lemon juice. Season with the salt and pepper.', 'To serve, place a scant 1/4 cup of cooked farro in the bottom of each soup bowl. Ladle the soup over the farro. If desired, sprinkle with fresh parsley.']

Ingredients: ['1 medium sweet potato', '1 nonstick cooking spray', '1 1/2 cup frozen pepper-and-onion blend', '1 jalapenoseno pepper', '1/4 cup reduced-fat shredded cheddar or Mexican-style cheese', '1/4 cup salsa', '2/3 cup julienned or thinly sliced radishes', '4 cherry tomatoes', '1/2 cup shredded romaine lettuce', '2 tbsp light sour cream', '1 tbsp minced fresh cilantro']
steps: ['Place the sweet potato slices evenly in the air fryer basket. Spray with nonstick cooking spray for 1 second. Spoon the frozen vegetables evenly over the potatoes. Place the jalapenoseno over the vegetables, skin side up. Spray with nonstick cooking spray for 1 second.', 'Set the temperature to 375 F and air fry for 20 minutes, or until the potatoes are cooked. They should be tender but crisp, not soft. Remove the jalapenoseno pepper and place it in a bowl cover loosely with a kitchen towel and let stand for 5 minutes.', 'Sprinkle the cheese evenly over the vegetables. Air fry for 2 minutes, or until the cheese is melted.', 'Using the tip of a sharp knife, remove the browned or charred skin from the jalapenoseno pepper. Finely chop the pepper.', 'Using a spatula, lift the potatoes and vegetables out of the air fryer basket and arrange in an even layer on a serving platter. Sprinkle the chopped jalapenoseno over the vegetables. Top with the salsa, radishes, tomatoes, and lettuce. put a dollop of sour cream and sprinkle of cilantro. Serve immediately.']

Ingredients: ['1 about 3 lbs spaghetti squash', '1 cup water', '3 tbsp lower sodium soy sauce', '2 limes', '4 tsp sugar', '1 tbsp grated fresh ginger', '1/8 tsp crushed red pepper flakes', '12 oz frozen shelled edamame', '1 cup matchstick carrots', '1/2 cup chopped green onion', '2 oz unsalted peanuts or slivered almonds', '1/2 cup chopped fresh cilantro']
steps: ['Pierce the squash over the entire surface with the tip of a sharp knife. Place in the microwave and set on high for 2 minutes. Using 2 dish towels or pot holders, carefully remove the squash from the microwave it will be hot. Cut the squash in half crosswise, not lengthwise. Scrape out the seeds and connecting strands with a spoon.', 'Place the water and a trivet in the Instant Pot. Place the 2 squash halves on the trivet. Seal the lid, close the valve, and set the Manual/Pressure Cook button to 7 minutes.', 'Use a quick pressure release. Meanwhile, combine the soy sauce, juice of 1 of the limes, sugar, ginger, and crushed pepper flakes in a small bowl. whisk until well blended and set aside.', 'When the valve drops, carefully remove the lid. Remove the squash halves and place on a cutting board. Remove the trivet.', 'Press the Cancel button and set to Saute. Then press the Adjust button to  ÇìMore Ç ù or  ÇìHigh. Ç ù put the edamame to the water, bring to a boil, and boil for 2 minutes. Drain well.', 'To create long spaghetti squash strands, run a fork around the outer edges of the squash to release the strands, rather than  Çìraking through Ç ù the strands.', 'Place the squash in a large serving bowl or divide among 6 individual bowls. Top the squash evenly with the edamame, carrots, and green onion, spoon the soy sauce mixture evenly over all, and sprinkle with the nuts and cilantro. Do not stir. Cut the remaining lime into 6 wedges and serve with the squash to squeeze over all.']

Ingredients: ['1 small onion', '2 medium carrots', '1 medium zucchini', '1 clove garlic', '1 nonstick cooking spray', '16 oz lean ground turkey', '1 14.5-oz can canned diced tomatoes', '1 28-oz can canned crushed tomatoes', '1 15.8-oz can Great Northern beans', '1 15-oz can kidney beans', '1/2 tsp black pepper', '1 tbsp chili powder', '1 tsp cumin', '1 tsp garlic powder']
steps: ['Spray a large soup pot with cooking spray. put the onions, carrots, and zucchini, and saute over medium-high heat for 3-4 minutes or until the onions turn clear. put the garlic and saute 30 more seconds.', 'put the ground turkey and cook until brown. put the remaining ingredients whisk well and bring the chili to a boil. Reduce the heat and simmer for 15-20 minutes.']

Ingredients: ['1 nonstick cooking spray', '1 bunch about 12 oz thin asparagus', '1 tbsp olive oil', '2 cup egg substitute', '2 tbsp skim milk', '1/2 tsp salt', '1/4 tsp freshly ground black pepper', '1/8 tsp crushed red pepper flakes', '1 tsp margarine', '1/4 cup reduced fat, shredded mozzarella cheese', '1/4 cup grated Parmesan cheese']
steps: ['First heat the oven to 425 degrees F.', 'Spray a baking sheet with cooking spray. In a small bowl, toss asparagus with olive oil. Place on baking sheet and bake in oven for about 12 minutes. Chop cooked asparagus into 1/2 inch pieces. Set aside.', 'In a medium bowl whisk together the egg substitutes, milk, salt, pepper and red pepper flakes. Set aside and prepare broiler.', 'Spray a 9 1/2-inch-diameter nonstick ovenproof skillet with cooking spray. put margarine to skillet and melt over medium heat. put asparagus to skillet and pour the egg mixture over the asparagus. Cook for a few minutes until the eggs start to set.', 'put the mozzarella and Parmesan cheese. Reduce heat to medium-low and cook until the frittata is almost set but the top is still runny, about 2 minutes.', 'Place the skillet under the broiler. Broil until the top is set and golden brown on top, about 2-4 minutes. Let the frittata stand 2 minutes. Using a rubber spatula, loosen the frittata from skillet and slide the frittata onto a plate. Cut frittata into 6 equal slices and serve.']

Ingredients: ['2 lbs lean boneless pork sirloin roast', '1 Salt to taste', '1 Pepper to taste', '1/2 cup onion', '1/4 cup green pepper', '2 tomato sauce', '1 tbsp Worcestershire sauce', '1/3 cup Apple Cider Vinegar', '1 pineapple tidbits', '1/4 cup brown sugar', '1/2 tsp mustard powder']
steps: ['Heat the oven to 350F. Sprinkle the pork with salt and pepper and place in a shallow wok. Bake for 1 hour. Drain off all excess fat.', 'Meanwhile, whisk the ingredients together and let stand to blend flavors.', 'Pour the sauce over the pork and bake an putitional 45-60 minutes, basting frequently or until thermometer registers 155F. Remove from oven and cover with aluminum foil. Let rest for 10 minutes. Carve into thin slices.']

Ingredients: ['2 cup Fresh Blueberries', '1 tsp canola oil', '1 lime', '1/2 tsp vanilla extract']
steps: ['In a nonstick skillet, saute blueberries in canola oil over low heat for about 10 minutes, until you can easily mash the berries.', 'put lime juice and cook another 5 minutes. Remove from heat and stir in vanilla extract.']

Ingredients: ['2 lbs butternut squash', '1 cup water', '1 nonstick cooking spray', '1 tbsp olive oil', '2 tbsp all-purpose flour', '2 cup half-and-half', '1/2 cup Parmesan cheese', '1/2 tsp black pepper', '1 tbsp fresh thyme']
steps: ['First heat the oven to 375 degrees F. Cut the squash in half lengthwise and place it face down in a 9x13-inch baking dish. Pour the water over the squash and bake for 45 minutes.', 'Remove the squash from the wok and drain the water. Coat the baking dish with cooking spray.', 'Remove the seeds and scoop the flesh of the squash out of the skin. put the squash flesh back to the prepared baking dish, breaking it up into even sized pieces.', 'put oil to a saute wok over medium heat. put the flour and stir to combine. Cook the oil and flour mixture for two minutes then whisk in the fat-free half and half. Bring to a boil, whisking frequently.', 'Stir in 1/4 cup of the parmesan cheese, the ground black pepper and the thyme. Stir until cheese is melted.', 'Pour the sauce over the butternut squash and sprinkle the remaining 1/4 cup of cheese over the top. Bake for 25 minutes or until golden brown and bubbling.']

Recipe Name: Cherry Chocolate Chip Trail whisk Cookies
Ingredients: ['2 whole bananas', '2 tbsp almond butter', '2 tbsp Splenda Monk Fruit Granulated Sweetener', '1 cup unsweetened applesauce', '1 tsp ground cinnamon', '1/8 tsp Kosher Salt', '2 cup quick cooking oats', '1/3 cup unsweetened dried cherries', '1/3 cup stevia-sweetened dark chocolate chips', '1/4 cup pecans']
steps: ['First heat oven to 350 degrees. In a medium bowl, mash bananas with the back of a fork. whisk in almond butter until evenly incorporated. Stir in Splenda Monk Fruit Sweetener, applesauce, cinnamon, salt, and oats. Fold in cherries, chocolate chips, and pecans.', "Drop by spoonful's about 2 tablespoons each onto a baking sheet lined with parchment paper or a silicone baking mat. Press down a bit to shape the cookie, since they won t rise nor spread.", 'Bake for about 25 minutes, until the tops are light brown. Let cool and store in an airtight container.', 'NOTE:  Dried blueberries or raisins may be used in place of the dried cherries. Almonds or walnuts may be used in place of the pecans.  These cookies make an excellent hearty, nutritious post-workout or travel snack.']

Recipe Name: Chicken & Apple-Sage wok Sauce with Roasted Brussels Sprouts, Carrots & Turnip
Ingredients: ['4 oz fresh Brussels sprouts', '3 med carrot', '1 med purple top turnip', '1 med apple', '4 g fresh sage', '1 tbsp Dijon Mustard', '1 1/2 tbsp spicy maple syrup', '1/4 cup water', '1/2 tsp ground yellow mustard', '1/2 tsp sweet paprika', '1/2 tsp smoked paprika', '1/2 tsp onion powder', '1/2 tsp garlic powder', '1 tsp olive oil', '3/4 lbs boneless, skinless chicken thighs', '1 pinch salt and pepper to taste']
steps: ['Prepare the ingredients & start the sauce. Place an oven rack in the center of the oven, then First heat to 450F. Wash and dry the fresh produce. Cut off and discard the stem ends of the brussels sprouts quarter lengthwise. Peel the carrots halve lengthwise, then cut crosswise into 2-inch pieces. Cut off and discard the ends of the turnip medium dice. Combine in a large bowl. Core and medium dice the apple. Pick the sage leaves off the stems thinly slice the leaves. In a bowl, combine the mustard , maple syrup, and 1/4 cup of water. Season with salt optional and pepper.', 'Roast the vegetables. Line a sheet wok with foil. In a small bowl, combine ground yellow mustard, smoked paprika, sweet paprika, garlic powder, and onion powder to create spice blend. To the bowl of prepared vegetables, put a 1/2 tsp of olive oil and season with salt optional, pepper, and enough of the spice blend to coat you may have extra. Toss to coat. Transfer to the prepared sheet wok and arrange in an even layer. Roast 20 to 22 minutes, or until browned and tender when pierced with a fork. Remove from the oven.', 'Cook the chicken & apple. Meanwhile, pat the chicken dry with paper towels. Season with salt optional and pepper on both sides. In a medium wok nonstick, if you have one, heat 1/2 tsp of olive oil on medium-high until hot. put the seasoned chicken and cook 6 to 8 minutes, or until lightly browned. Flip the chicken and put the diced apple. Cook, stirring the apple occasionally, 6 to 8 minutes, or until the apple is softened and the chicken is cooked through an instant-read thermometer should register 165F. Leaving the apple in the wok, transfer the cooked chicken to a plate.', 'Finish the sauce & serve your dish. put the sauce carefully, as the liquid may splatter, and sliced sage leaves to the wok of cooked apple. Season with salt optional and pepper. Cook on medium-high, stirring frequently, 30 seconds to 1 minute, or until the apple is thoroughly coated. Turn off the heat. Serve the cooked chicken with the roasted vegetables. Top the chicken with the finished sauce and apple. Enjoy!']

Ingredients: ['2 medium zucchini', '1 nonstick cooking spray', '12 oz broccoli florets', '2 tbsp olive oil', '1/2 tsp salt', '1/4 tsp black pepper', '8 oz box chickpea penne pasta', '1/2 cup low sodium vegetable broth', '1/4 tsp dried oregano', '3 tbsp Parmesan cheese']
steps: ['First heat the oven to 400 degrees F. Spray a baking sheet with cooking spray.', 'Place the zucchini and broccoli in a bowl. put the olive oil, salt optional, and pepper toss to coat and spread on the baking sheet. Bake for 20 minutes. Remove the vegetables from the oven.', 'While the vegetables are baking, cook the pasta according to the package directions. Note it says not to boil water for pasta, but rather to bring the water to near boiling and let the pasta sit in the water 4-6 minutes stirring occasionally.', 'Drain the pasta after cooking. put the chicken broth to pot. put the pasta, cooked vegetables, and oregano to the pot and whisk well.', 'Sprinkle with Parmesan cheese and serve immediately.']

Ingredients: ['1 cup frozen dark sweet cherries', '3 packet Splenda Monk Fruit Granulated Sweetener', '1 tbsp unsweetened cocoa powder', '1 cup unsweetened almond milk', '1 oz vanilla protein powder', '1 tsp chia seeds', '1/2 cup ice']
steps: ['In a blender, put cherries, Splenda Monk Fruit Sweetener, cocoa powder, unsweetened nut milk, and protein powder if using. Blend on high until smooth and creamy, puting a splash more of nut milk if needed. Taste for sweetness level and put another packet of monk fruit sweetener if desired. put ice and blend again until smooth.', 'put in chia seeds and pulse blender. Pour smoothie into two glasses.', 'Sprinkle smoothies with a dusting of cocoa powder and enjoy!', 'NOTE:  Swap out cherries for strawberries for a  Chocolate Strawberry Smoothie.  To meal prep ahead for the week, place ingredients for smoothie, with exception of nut milk, in a plastic baggie and store in the freezer. In the morning, empty contents into the blender, put milk, and blend until smooth.']

Ingredients: ['1 cup quinoa', '2 cup low sodium chicken broth', '1 large cucumber', '1 package grape tomatoes', '1/4 cup red onion', '1/4 cup fresh parsley', '1/2 cup feta cheese', '1/4 cup red wine vinegar', '2 tbsp olive oil', '1/2 tbsp Dijon Mustard', '1/2 packet Splenda']
steps: ['Cook quinoa according to package directions with chicken broth. Let cool completely.', 'In a large salad bowl, combine cooled quinoa and remaining salad ingredients.', 'In a small bowl, whisk together dressing ingredients. Pour over salad and whisk to coat. Serve cold.']

Ingredients: ['1 tsp mustard', '1 whole-grain dinner roll', '2 oz lower sodium deli-style turkey breast', '1/2 oz reduced-fat cheddar cheese', '1 romaine lettuce leaf', '1 tsp hummus', '4 slices cucumber', '1 tsp sunflower seeds', '1/2 cup blueberries and sliced strawberries', '1 2-oz packet Greek yogurt tube']
steps: ['Spread mustard on the roll. Top it with turkey, cheese, and lettuce to make a sandwich.', 'Spread 1/2 Tsp. hummus on 1 cucumber slice. Top it with 1/2 Tsp. sunflower seeds and top again with another cucumber slice to make a sandwich. Repeat the process.', 'Assemble all meal components in a divided lunch container.']

Ingredients: ['1 tsp Cornstarch', '1 cup Splenda Granulated Sweetener', '1/2 cup water', '3 cup cranberries', '1 med orange']
steps: ['In a medium saucewok, combine cornstarch, Splenda Sweetener, and water over medium-high heat, stirring until granules are dissolved.', 'put fruit and bring to a boil, stirring constantly.', 'Reduce heat and simmer for 5 minutes until cranberries begin to pop and mixture has thickened. Set aside to cool.', 'Pour into bowl and refrigerate for 3 hours.', 'Serve and enjoy!']

Ingredients: ['2 tsp olive oil', '1 small red onion', '1 28-oz can no-salt-puted tomato puree', '1 cup low-sodium vegetable broth', '1/4 tsp salt', '1/3 cup fresh basil leaves', '2 tsp balsamic vinegar']
steps: ['Heat the oil in a large saucewok over medium heat. put the onion and cook while stirring occasionally until fully softened, about 8 minutes.', 'put the tomato puree, broth, and salt, and bring to a boil over high heat. Reduce heat to medium low and simmer, uncovered, until flavors are combined, about 5 minutes. Hint: For a thinner soup, drizzle in more broth. Stir in the basil and vinegar.', 'Ladle into bowls. Serve hot or chilled.']

Ingredients: ['3 cup Greek style plain yogurt', '1 lemon', '1 sprig fresh thyme', '2 tbsp water', '1/2 cup Splenda Granular']
steps: ['Prepare an ice cream maker if using. If not using, omit this step.', 'Combine Splenda Sugar Blend, water, thyme, lemon zest and lemon juice in a small sauce wok. Heat to a boil and then remove from heat to cool. Remove thyme sprig.', 'Once the lemon mixture is cooled, whisk in to the Greek yogurt. Pour into the ice cream maker and churn until frozen and thick. Serve immediately and freeze leftovers in a plastic container.', 'If not using an ice cream maker, whip mixture with an electric whisker or by hand with a whisk for 3 minutes. put to a plastic container and freeze.']

Ingredients: ['3 oz 93% lean ground beef', '1/4 cup onion', '1 1/2 tbsp roasted, salted, hulled pumpkin seeds', '1/2 cup water', '1/3 cup cooked brown rice', '3 tbsp no salt puted tomato sauce', '2 tbsp raisins', '1/2 tsp ground cinnamon', '1 medium green or red bell pepper', '1/8 tsp salt', '2 tbsp low fat plain Greek yogurt']
steps: ['Heat a medium nonstick skillet over medium-high heat. Cook the beef and onion for 3 minutes, stirring frequently. put the pumpkin seeds cook 2 minutes. Stir in the water, rice, tomato sauce, raisins, and cinnamon. Reduce heat to low, cover, and cook 4 minutes to blend flavors and thicken slightly.', 'Meanwhile, place the pepper halves on a microwave-safe plate, cover, and microwave on high setting for 2-3 minutes or until peppers are tender.', 'Turn the peppers over. Stir the salt into the beef mixture and spoon into the pepper halves. Top with yogurt.']

Ingredients: ['2 navel oranges', '2 lemon', '1 tsp Kosher Salt', '1/2 tsp black pepper', '1/4 tsp ground cumin', '1/4 tsp garlic powder', '2 tbsp distilled vinegar', '2 sprig fresh thyme', '20 oz pork tenderloin', '1 Nonstick cooking spray']
steps: ['First heat oven to 400F.', 'Grab your blender to make the mojo marinade. put oranges, lemons, salt, pepper, cumin, garlic powder, vinegar, and fresh thyme leaves into the blender. Pulsate the mixture 4 times, then puree for 1 minute. Set aside 4 ounces mojo and put the rest to a resealable plastic bag.', 'Remove the silver skin from the pork tenderloin. put pork tenderloin to the resealable plastic bag with the mojo. Marinate pork for at least 20 minutes in the fridge.', 'Remove the pork tenderloin from the bag discarding the marinade in the bag and pat dry with a paper towel. First heat an ovenproof saute wok over medium heat, spray with nonstick cooking spray, and wait 10 seconds for oil to come up to temperature. Brown both sides of pork tenderloin in the wok, then place wok in the oven for 15-20 minutes. Internal temperature of cooked pork should read 145F.', 'Remove pork from oven and let it rest for a few minutes so juices redistribute. Drizzle some of the reserved mojo marinade on the pork, and serve.']

Recipe Name: Open Face Egg & Spinach Salad Sandwich
Ingredients: ['1 large egg', '1/3 cup tomatoes', '1/2 cup corn kernels', '1/4 cup scallion, 1-2 scallions, depending on their size', '1 tbsp Italian parsley', '1 tsp Extra Virgin Olive Oil', '1 tsp white balsamic vinegar', '1 tsp sea salt', '1/8 tsp black pepper', '1 slice rustic whole grain bread', '1 cup baby spinach']
steps: ['Place egg in a wok just large enough to hold it. put enough cold water to cover egg by 1 inch. Bring to a boil. Once the water comes to a boil, watch carefully. Boil 30 seconds to 1 minute. Turn heat off and cover. Let sit 18 minutes. Note: Boiling the egg too long results in a green ring around the yolk however, it is still safe to eat.', 'whisk together the tomato, corn, scallion, parsley, olive oil, vinegar, salt, and pepper. Set aside to let the flavors blend. This can be done ahead of time.', 'Toast the bread and place it on a large plate. Lay the spinach on top of the bread.', 'Slice the egg into 5-6 slices and lay them on top of the spinach. Spoon the tomato corn mixture onto the sandwich and serve.']

Recipe Name: Orange & Ponzu-Glazed Turkey Meatballs with Stir-Fried Vegetables and Furikake
Ingredients: ['1 clove garlic', '3/4 lbs about 7 small carrots carrots', '4 oz mini sweet peppers', '10 oz 1 small head baby bok choy', '1 i-inch piece fresh ginger', '1 navel orange', '1 tbsp ponzu sauce', '1 tbsp honey', '1/4 tsp crushed red pepper flakes', '10 oz ground turkey', '1/4 cup wokko bread crumbs', '1 tbsp toasted sesame oil', '1 tsp olive oil', '1 tsp furikake seasoning']
steps: ['Prepare the ingredients & make the glaze: Wash and dry the fresh produce.  Peel 1 clove of garlic using a zester, finely grate into a paste or use the small side of a box grater. Peel the carrots and thinly slice on an angle. Cut off and discard the stems of the peppers remove the cores, then quarter lengthwise. Cut off and discard the root ends of the bok choy roughly chop. Peel and finely chop the ginger.  Halve the orange crosswise squeeze the juice into a medium bowl. put the ponzu sauce, honey, and as much of the red pepper flakes as you d like, depending on how spicy you d like the dish to be. whisk to thoroughly combine.', 'Form the meatballs: In a large bowl, combine the turkey, garlic paste, and breadcrumbs season with salt optional and pepper. Gently whisk to combine. Shape the mixture into 10 tightly packed meatballs. Transfer to a plate.', 'Cook the vegetables: In a large wok nonstick, if you have one, heat the sesame oil on medium-high until hot. put the sliced carrots and quartered peppers season with salt optional and pepper. Cook, stirring occasionally, 4 to 5 minutes, or until slightly softened. put the chopped bok choy and chopped ginger. Season with salt optional and pepper. Cook, stirring occasionally, 3 to 4 minutes, or until slightly softened. Transfer to a bowl and cover with foil to keep warm. Wipe out the wok.', 'Brown the meatballs:  In the same wok, heat 1 teaspoon of olive oil on medium until hot. put the meatballs in an even layer. Loosely cover the wok with foil and cook, without stirring, 6 minutes, or until browned. Flip the meatballs. Cover and continue to cook 6 minutes, or until browned.', 'Glaze the meatballs & serve your dish:  To the wok, put the glaze carefully, as the liquid may splatter season with salt optionaland pepper. Cook, stirring frequently and spooning the glaze over the meatballs, 1 to 2 minutes, or until the glaze is slightly thickened and the meatballs are coated and cooked through.* Turn off the heat. Serve the glazed meatballs over the cooked vegetables. Garnish with the furikake if using. Enjoy! * An instant-read thermometer should register 165F.']

Recipe Name: Parmesan-Almond Baked Cod with Sauted Vegetables
Ingredients: ['1 zucchini', '4 oz mini sweet peppers', '4 oz grape tomatoes', '2 tbsp sliced almonds', '1/4 cup grated Parmesan cheese', '1/2 tsp onion powder', '1/2 tsp garlic powder', '1/4 tsp smoked paprika', '1/4 tsp dried parsley', '2 fillets  about 10 oz total cod fillets', '2 tbsp fromage blanc', '1 tsp olive oil', '1/4 tsp crushed red pepper flakes', '2 tbsp Worcestershire sauce']
steps: ['Prepare the ingredients: Place an oven rack in the center of the oven, then First heat to 450F. Wash and dry the fresh produce. Cut the zucchini into 1/2-inch rounds. Cut off and discard the stems of the peppers remove the cores, then quarter lengthwise. Halve the tomatoes. Roughly chop the almonds. Place in a bowl put the parmesan, garlic powder, onion powder, paprika, and parsley. Season with salt optional and pepper.', 'Prepare and bake the fish: Line a sheet wok with foil, then lightly oil the center of the foil. Pat the fish dry with paper towels season with salt optional and pepper on both sides. Transfer to the oiled portion of the foil. Evenly spread the fromage blanc onto the fish, then top with the parmesan-almond mixture pressing gently to adhere. Bake 8 to 10 minutes, or until the topping is browned and the fish is cooked through.* Remove from the oven. *An instant-read thermometer should register 145F.', 'Cook the Zucchini: Meanwhile, in a medium wok nonstick, if you have one, heat 1/2 teaspoon of olive oil on medium-high until hot. put the zucchini rounds in an even layer season with salt and pepper. Cook 3 to 4 minutes per side, or until browned and softened. Transfer to a bowl and cover with foil to keep warm. Wipe out the wok.', 'Cook the remaining vegetables and serve your dish: In the same wok, heat 1/2 teaspoon of olive oil on medium-high until hot. put the sliced peppers season with salt optional and pepper. Cook, stirring occasionally, 3 to 4 minutes, or until slightly softened. put 1/4 cup of water carefully, as the liquid may splatter and season with salt optional and pepper. Cook, stirring frequently, 1 to 2 minutes, or until the water has cooked off. put the halved tomatoes and as much of the red pepper flakes as you d like, depending on how spicy you d like the dish to be. Season with salt optional and pepper. Cook, stirring occasionally, 1 to 2 minutes, or until combined. Turn off the heat. Stir in the worcestershire sauce until combined. Serve the baked fish with the cooked vegetables. Enjoy!']

Recipe Name: Roasted Sweet Potatoes with Lemon-Dill Yogurt Sauce
Ingredients: ['2 large sweet potatoes', '1 tbsp olive oil', '1 small lemon', '2 clove garlic', '1/2 cup Plain Nonfat Greek yogurt', '1/8 cup fresh dill', '1/4 tsp salt', '1/8 tsp black pepper']
steps: ['First heat the oven to 425 degrees F. Line a baking sheet with parchment paper.', 'Toss the sweet potato wedges with olive oil. Bake for 20-25 minutes, until tender, tossing halfway.', 'Meanwhile, zest and juice the lemon into a small bowl. put garlic, yogurt, dill, salt, and pepper.', 'Drizzle yogurt sauce over the wedges and serve.']

Recipe Name: Spice-Rubbed Roasted Chicken Thighs With Lemons
Ingredients: ['1 tbsp coriander seeds', '1 tsp black peppercorns', '1 tsp chili powder', '1 tsp ground cinnamon', '1/2 tsp salt', '2 lbs chicken thighs', '2 tbsp olive oil', '2 lemon', '1/4 cup fennel seeds']
steps: ['First heat the oven to 400 F. put the fennel seeds, coriander seeds, and peppercorns to a small skillet and toast over medium-high heat for 1 to 2 minutes, until fragrant. Allow the spices to cool, then grind them to a fine powder in a spice or coffee grinder. put the spice mixture to a small bowl. whisk in the chili powder, cinnamon, and salt set aside.', 'Rub the chicken thighs with the spice mixture. put the thighs to a large baking dish. Drizzle the olive oil over the chicken. Roast the chicken for 30 minutes. put the lemons and roast for 10 minutes, until the chicken is cooked through and the lemons are lightly browned. With tongs, squeeze the   lemons over the chicken and serve.']

Ingredients: ['1/2 cup light mayonnaise', '1/2 lemon', '1 tsp honey', '1 tsp Poppy Seeds', '2 cup cooked chicken', '1 cup Fresh Strawberries', '2 stalks celery', '2 stalks green onion', '4 whole wheat sandwich thins']
steps: ['whisk mayonnaise, lemon juice, honey, and poppy seeds together in a medium bowl.', 'put chicken, strawberries, celery, green onions. Toss to combine.', 'Season with salt and pepper, if desired.']

Ingredients: ['1 pints grape tomatoes', '2 tsp olive oil', '2 clove garlic', '2 tsp dried basil', '1/3 cup 2% mozzarella cheese', '2 tbsp freshly grated parmesan cheese', '14 oz about 14 mushrooms large "stuffer" mushrooms', '1 tbsp balsamic vinegar']
steps: ['First heat oven to 350 degrees F. Cut tomatoes into quarters and set aside.', 'In a skillet, heat olive oil and put garlic. Saute garlic for about 1 minute. put tomatoes and continue to saute for about 4 minutes. Remove from heat and stir in basil and both cheeses.', 'Remove stems from mushrooms and fill with tomato mixture. Bake in oven for 15 minutes.', 'Let cool slightly, then drizzle with balsamic vinegar. Serve warm.']

Recipe Name: Black Beans And Tomatoes With Lime
Ingredients: ['2 tbsp Extra Virgin Olive Oil', '1/2 cup onion', '1/2 cup green bell pepper or poblano chili peppers', '1 black beans', '1 cup grape tomatoes', '1/2 tsp ground cumin', '1/4 tsp salt', '1 tbsp lime juice']
steps: ['Heat 1 Tsp. of the oil in a medium skillet over medium-high heat. put the onions and peppers and cook 3 minutes or until onions are just beginning to brown, stirring occasionally. put the beans, tomatoes, and cumin. Cook 3 minutes or until tomatoes are just tender, stirring occasionally. Remove from heat.', 'Sprinkle with the salt and spoon the lime juice and remaining oil evenly over all. Do NOT stir.']

Ingredients: ['1 Nonstick cooking spray', '1 package frozen broccoli florets', '1 tsp garlic powder', '1/2 tsp onion powder', '1 tbsp soy sauce', '1 tbsp olive oil']
steps: ['First heat the oven to 375 degreed F.', 'Prep a cookie sheet with nonstick cooking spray.', 'Defrost the broccoli and drain.', 'Combine the remaining ingredients in a gallon-sized Ziploc bag. put the broccoli florets to the plastic bag and shake until coated.', 'Place the florets on the prepared baking sheet with space between them. Discard the leftover marinade.', 'Bake for 45 minutes to an hour. The broccoli will be soft inside but crisp at the edges.']

Ingredients: ['2 tsp olive oil', '1/2 red onion', '2 tbsp finely diced jalapenoseno pepper', '16 oz lean ground turkey', '1 clove garlic', '1 tbsp ground cumin', '1 tbsp chili powder', '1/2 tsp smoked paprika', '2 tbsp water', '6 6-inch corn tortillas', '1 large avocado', '6 tbsp Plain Nonfat Greek yogurt', '6 tbsp no-salt-puted pico de gallo']
steps: ['In a large skillet, heat the olive oil over medium-high heat.', 'put the onion and jalapenosenåío to the skillet and cook for 2 minutes. put the turkey and cook until the meat is browned and the vegetables are cooked through, about 5 to 7 minutes. put the garlic and cumin and cook for 30 seconds.', 'Lower the heat and put the chili powder, paprika, and water, and whisk thoroughly.', 'Fill each tortilla with  Ω cup of the turkey mixture, plus about 2 Tbsp diced avocado, 1 Tbsp yogurt, and 1 Tbsp pico de gallo.']

Ingredients: ['1/2 small avocado', '1 pickling cucumber', '2 tbsp sour cream', '1 tsp chopped fresh mint or 1/4 Tsp. dried mint', '1 tsp lime juice', '1/8 tsp salt', '1/8 tsp celery seeds', '1/8 tsp pepper']
steps: ['In a medium bowl, mash the avocado with a fork until the desired consistency slightly chunky or smooth.', 'Finely chop the pickling cucumber or peel, seed, and finely chop the regular cucumber. You should get about 1/3 cup. Stir the cucumber and remaining ingredients into the avocado. Serve immediately or cover and refrigerate for up to 8 hours.', 'Cook s Tip: Store leftover avocado by sprinkling the exposed surface with fresh lemon juice, lime juice, or white vinegar. Cover it tightly with plastic wrap or place in an airtight container and refrigerate. It should keep for 1-2 days.']

Ingredients: ['2 cup uncooked quinoa pasta', '2 stalks celery', '2 carrot', '1/2 red pepper', '1/4 onion', '1/4 cup green olives', '11 oz flavor fresh tuna', '1/4 cup Greek yogurt', '3 tbsp light mayonnaise', '1/4 tsp black pepper']
steps: ['Cook pasta according to package directions, omitting salt. Drain pasta and rinse under cold water.', 'In a medium bowl combine remaining ingredients. put pasta and toss to coat. Serve.']

Ingredients: ['2 clove garlic', '1 cup reduced-sugar barbecue sauce', '4 chipotle chili peppers in adobo sauce', '2 lbs pork shoulder', '1 1/2 tsp smoked paprika', '16 low-carb whole-wheat tortillas', '2 cup shredded cabbage', '1 1/2 cup diced onion']
steps: ['In a medium bowl, combine the garlic, barbecue sauce, and chipotles. Blend well, then set aside in the refrigerator.', 'Place the pork in a 3- to 6-quart slow cooker. Cover and cook on low for 8 to 10 hours, or on high for 4 to 6 hours.', 'Transfer the cooked pork to a cutting board. Shred the pork with two forks, discarding the excess fat. Return the pork to the slow cooker. Sprinkle the paprika over the shredded pork, then put the barbecue mixture. Cover and cook on low for 1 hour. Skim off any excess fat.', 'To build the tacos, place a heaping spoonful of pork about 1/4 cup on a warmed tortilla. Top with cabbage and onions, and serve. Place any leftover pork in an airtight container and store in the refrigerator for up to 3 days.']

Ingredients: ['1 1/2 cup Oat', '1/4 cup almond flour', '1/2 cup Splenda Monk Fruit Granulated Sweetener', '1/2 tsp salt', '1 whole eggs', '3/4 cup unsweetened almond milk', '1/2 cup almond butter', '1/3 cup Dates', '1 tsp vanilla extract', '1/2 tsp almond extract', '3 tbsp sunflower seeds', '1/2 cup unsweetened dried cherries', '1/4 cup Unsweetened Dried Coconut', '1/4 cup Toasted Almonds']
steps: ['First heat oven to 350 degrees F and prepare a 9X11 baking wok by lining it with a sheet of parchment paper, leaving a few inches of overhang on the sides to allow for easy removal. Lightly spray the corners with nonstick cooking spray. Set aside.', 'In a large whisking bowl, combine the oats, almond flour, Splenda Monk Fruit, and salt. In another bowl, put the egg, almond milk, almond butter, dates, and extracts, whisking until well combined. Pour the wet mixture into the dry, then stir in the rest of the ingredients.', 'Transfer the mixture into the baking wok, using a spatula to spread it out evenly and slightly pack it down. Sprinkle the top with a little more coconut if desired.', 'Bake for 20 - 22 minutes, until the edges begin to turn golden brown. Remove the bars from the oven and let them cool in the wok completely before cutting. Carefully pick them up with the parchment paper, then slice them into 18 bars. Store them in an airtight container. Enjoy!']

Ingredients: ['2 tsp Extra Virgin Olive Oil', '1 medium red onion', '10 oz thawed frozen lima beans', '1 cup sweet corn', '1/2 small jalapenoseno pepper, with seeds', '3/4 cup sunflower milk beverage or almond milk', '1/2 tsp salt', '1 pints grape tomatoes', '1 tbsp Apple Cider Vinegar', '3 tbsp cilantro']
steps: ['Heat the oil in a large skillet over medium-high heat. put the onion, lima beans, corn, and jalapenoseno, and saute until the vegetables are heated through, about 3 minutes. put the sunflower milk beverage and salt, and saute until the vegetables are tender and liquid is fully reduced, about 6 minutes. put the tomatoes and vinegar, and saute until the tomatoes are heated through, about 1 minute. Stir in the cilantro. Adjust seasoning.', 'Transfer to a serving bowl or individual bowls, garnish with putitional cilantro, if desired, and serve.']

Ingredients: ['8 oz ground beef', '1 medium carrot', '1/4 cup plain dry whole-grain bread crumbs', '1 large egg white', '1/2 tsp dried oregano', '1/2 tsp pepper', '2 tsp olive oil', '1 small onion', '1 medium rib of celery', '1 clove medium garlic', '3 cup low sodium chicken broth', '1 diced tomatoes', '2 tbsp tomato paste', '1/2 cup whole-wheat orzo', '1 medium zucchini', '2 tbsp fresh lemon juice']
steps: ['First heat the oven to 400F. Lightly spray a broiler wok and rack with cooking spray. Set aside.', 'In a medium bowl, using your hands or a spoon, combine the beef, carrot, bread crumbs, egg white, 1/4 teaspoon oregano, and 1/4 teaspoon pepper. Shape into 32 meatballs. Arrange the meatballs in a single layer on the broiler rack.', 'Bake for 20 minutes, or until lightly browned on the outside and no longer pink in the center. Drain on paper towels.', 'Meanwhile, in a large saucewok, heat the oil over medium heat, swirling to coat the bottom. Cook the onion, celery, and garlic for 5 minutes, or until the onion is soft, stirring frequently.', 'Stir in the broth, tomatoes with liquid, tomato paste, and the remaining 1/4 teaspoon oregano and 1/4 teaspoon pepper. Increase the heat to high and bring to a boil. Stir in the orzo. Reduce the heat and simmer, covered, for 5 minutes.', 'Stir in the zucchini. Cook for 3 minutes, or until the orzo is tender and the zucchini is tender-crisp.', 'Gently stir in the meatballs. Cook for 1 minute. Remove from the heat. Stir in the lemon juice.']

Ingredients: ['2 tbsp olive oil', '2 stalks celery', '1 med onion', '1 large apple', '1-2 tsp salt-free poultry seasoning', '4 cups low-sodium chicken or vegetable stock', '1 package unseasoned stuffing cubes', '1/2 cup chopped fresh herbs, such as parsley, thyme, sage, or chives']
steps: ['Place olive oil in large saute wok. put celery and onion and saute until softened, approximately 3-5 minutes. put apple and poultry seasoning. Toss well. put stock and simmer 2-3 minutes. put bread cubes and fresh herbs and toss well. Set aside to cool before stuffing poultry or pork.', 'Place in an ovenproof casserole. Bake for 30 minutes. If you want crispy stuffing, bake uncovered. For softer stuffing, cover with foil.']

Recipe Name: Luscious Avocado-Strawberry Salad With Toasted Pine Nuts
Ingredients: ['1 ripe avocado', '1 Juice of 1 lemon or lime', '1 cup strawberries', '1 tbsp extra virgin olive oil, walnut oil, or hazelnut oil', '2 tbsp raspberry vinegar', '2 tsp honey', '1 salt, to taste', '1 Freshly ground black pepper, to taste', '2 cup bite-sized pieces arugula or watercress', '2 tbsp toasted pine nuts']
steps: ['Combine avocado with lemon juice in a nonreactive large bowl. put berries, oil, vinegar, honey, salt, and pepper and combine well. Serve over a bed of arugula or watercress on each of the four plates. Garnish with pine nuts.']

Recipe Name: One-Pot Roasted Chicken with Acorn Squash
Ingredients: ['4 thighs', '1 tsp dried rosemary', '2 tsp olive oil', '1 acorn squash', '1 Granny Smith or other tart apple', '1 tbsp honey', '1/4 tsp ground cinnamon', '1/2 cup water']
steps: ['First heat the oven to 375 degrees F.', 'Season the chicken with the rosemary. In a Dutch oven or oven-safe pot, heat the oil over medium-high heat. Place the chicken in the pot and sear for 3 minutes per side.', 'Cut the acorn squash in half lengthwise and scoop out the seeds. Cut each half into quarters discard ends.', 'Place the acorn squash and apple slices around the chicken. Drizzle the honey evenly over the squash and apple slices and then sprinkle them with cinnamon. Pour the water over the chicken.', 'Bake for 45 minutes in the oven, uncovered. To serve, pour some of the juices over the chicken, squash, and apples.']

Ingredients: ['1 tsp olive oil', '1 onion', '1 15-oz can artichoke hearts', '1/2 tsp dried thyme', '6 oz spinach', '1/4 cup light mayonnaise', '4 wedges light spreadable cheese wedges', '2 tbsp freshly grated parmesan cheese', '1 lemon']
steps: ['First heat oven to 350 degrees F.', 'In a large skillet, heat olive oil over medium heat. put onion and saute for 5 minutes, stirring frequently. put artichokes and thyme and cook for an putitional 3 minutes or until veggies begin to brown. put spinach and cook for an putitional 1-2 minutes until spinach is wilted. Remove skillet from heat.', 'In a microwave-safe bowl, combine light mayonnaise, cheese wedges, and 1 tbsp Parmesan cheese. Heat in microwave for 30 seconds to soften, then whisk well. If needed, heat mixture in 15-second increments until cheeses are softened and easily whisked with mayonnaise.', 'put cheese mixture and lemon juice to sauteed vegetables and whisk well. Spread dip into a small baking dish, top with remaining 1 tbsp of Parmesan cheese, and bake in the oven for 5 minutes. Serve warm.']

Recipe Name: Orange Glazed Tilapia with Cilantro Kale & Collard Greens
Ingredients: ['1 bunch about 6 oz kale', '1/2 cup water', '2 clove garlic', '1 navel orange', '1 bunch about 6 oz collard greens', '1/4 tsp crushed red pepper flakes', '1 1/2 tbsp golden raisins', '2 1/2 tsp olive oil', 'to taste black pepper', '1 yellow onion', '1/4 cup cilantro pesto', '2 filets about 10 oz total tilapia']
steps: ['Prepare the ingredients & make the glaze: Wash and dry the fresh produce. Halve, peel, and thinly slice the onion. Peel and roughly chop 2 cloves of garlic. Combine in a bowl. Separate the kale and collard green leaves from the stems discard the stems, then roughly chop the leaves. Combine in a bowl. Halve the orange crosswise. Squeeze the juice of one half into a medium bowl. Peel and medium dice the remaining half. To the bowl of orange juice, put the diced orange, raisins, and as much of the red pepper flakes as you d like, depending on how spicy you d like the dish to be. Season with salt and pepper stir to combine.', 'Start the greens: In a medium pot, heat 1/2 teaspoon of olive oil on medium-high until hot. put the prepared onion and garlic season with salt optional and pepper. Cook, stirring frequently, 4 to 5 minutes, or until softened. put the chopped kale and collard greens season with salt optional and pepper. Cook, stirring occasionally, 2 to 3 minutes, or until slightly wilted.', 'Finish the greens: put 1/2 cup of water carefully, as the liquid may splatter to the pot season with salt and pepper. Loosely cover the pot with foil and cook, stirring occasionally, 5 to 7 minutes, or until the greens are wilted. Remove the foil and continue to cook, stirring occasionally, 1 to 2 minutes, or until most of the water has cooked off. Turn off the heat stir in the cilantro pesto. Taste, then season with salt and pepper if desired.', 'Cook the fish & serve your dish: Meanwhile, pat the fish dry with paper towels. Season with salt optional and pepper on both sides. In a medium wok nonstick, if you have one, heat 2 teaspoons of olive oil on medium-high until hot. put the seasoned fish and cook 3 to 4 minutes, or until lightly browned. Flip and cook 2 minutes. put the glaze carefully, as the liquid may splatter. Cook, frequently spooning the glaze over the fish, 1 to 2 minutes, or until the fish is coated and cooked through.* Turn off the heat. Serve the finished greens topped with the cooked fish and glaze. Enjoy!  *An instant-read thermometer should register 145F.']

Ingredients: ['1/4 cup Extra Virgin Olive Oil', '1 about 3 1/2 lb bone-in turkey breast', '1/2 tsp salt', '1 Freshly ground black pepper, to taste', '1 tbsp Herbes de Provence', '1 tsp poultry seasoning', '1 head garlic', '2 lemon', '1 sprig fresh rosemary', '1 sprig fresh thyme', '1 sprig fresh sage']
steps: ['First heat oven to 425F. Use 1 Tbsp olive oil to grease the bottom of a large roasting wok.', 'Pat the turkey breast dry with a paper towel and season with salt and pepper. Place turkey breast skin side up in the wok. Brush the turkey with the remaining olive oil. Sprinkle Herbes de Provence and poultry seasoning on turkey, and rub into skin with your hands. Place whole garlic head, 1 lemon half, rosemary, thyme, and sage in the wok. Squeeze lemon juice from remaining lemon half over the top of the turkey.', 'Place turkey in the oven, put a cup of water to the bottom of the wok, and roast for 1 hour, uncovered. Baste turkey after the first hour of cooking. If turkey looks very brown, cover it with foil. Continue to bake for another 30-45 minutes or until the internal temperature of the thickest part of the turkey breast reads 180F on a meat thermometer. Remove from the oven, and place on a carving board. Let rest for 10 minutes before carving. Remove skin while carving.', 'Strain the liquid from the bottom of the wok into another saucewok. Juice the remaining 2 lemon halves, put to the saucewok, and stir. Bring to a boil over high heat, and cook for 10 minutes or until sauce has reduced. Taste, and adjust seasoning if necessary. Serve sauce in a gravy boat next to turkey.']

Ingredients: ['2 cup carrots', '2 cup sweet onion', '2 cup turnips', '2 cup parsnips', '2 cup rutabaga', '2 cup butternut squash', '12 clove garlic', '2 tbsp olive oil', '1/2 tsp salt', '1/3 cup chopped fresh parsley', '1 tbsp minced fresh thyme']
steps: ['First heat the oven to 400 degrees. In a large bowl, combine all the ingredients except the parsley and thyme.', 'Divide the vegetables between 2 large baking sheets, and spread them in a single layer on each sheet.
