Sprinkle the top of each muffin with Parmesan.', 'Bake the lasagna muffins for 18-20 minutes until bubbly and browned. Remove from the oven and let cool for 5 minutes. Run a knife around each cup to loosen. Remove from the wok and serve.']

Ingredients: ['1/2 cup brown lentils', '2 cup hot water', '2 medium tomatoes', '1 medium red bell pepper', '1/2 cup red onion', '1/2 English cucumber', '1 clove garlic', '1 tbsp fresh cilantro', '2 tbsp red wine vinegar', '1 tbsp olive oil', '1/4 tsp crushed red pepper flakes', '1/4 cup feta cheese', '1/2 tsp black pepper', '1 lbs multigrain baguette', '1 nonstick cooking spray']
steps: ['First heat oven to 350 degrees.', 'In a medium sauce wok, combine lentils and hot water. Bring to a boil over high heat, then reduce to a simmer, uncovered, for 20 minutes.', 'While the lentils are cooking, combine tomatoes, red bell pepper, red onion, cucumber, garlic, cilantro, red wine vinegar, olive oil, crushed red pepper flakes, feta cheese and ground black pepper. Stir to incorporate and set aside.', 'Arrange sliced baguette pieces on a large baking sheet. Spray the tops of the bread slices lightly with cooking spray. Bake on the top rack of the oven for 10 minutes. Set aside to cool. See note in step 6.', 'When the lentils are done cooking, drain and rinse them under cold water. Shake the colander to get rid of all of the water on the lentils, then put them to the bruschetta mixture and stir to incorporate.', 'To serve, either put the bruschetta mixture to a serving bowl and arrange the toasted baguette around the bowl for self-serve bruschetta, or top each toasted baguette slice with 2 heaping Tbsps. of bruschetta mixture. Note: If you plan to serve the bruschetta on the baguette, you may want to toast the bread a little longer to avoid sogginess.']

Ingredients: ['1 lemon', '1/3 cup reduced-fat crumbled feta cheese', '1 tbsp capers', '2 1/2 tsp dried oregano', '3 clove garlic', '1 lbs boneless, skinless chicken breasts', '1 tbsp paprika', '1 tsp garlic powder', '1/2 tsp salt', '1/2 tsp black pepper', '2 medium zucchini', '8 oz cremini', '10 oz cherry tomatoes', '1 15-oz can cannellini beans', '1 tbsp olive oil']
steps: ['First heat oven to 375 degrees F. Coat a 9x13 baking/casserole dish with cooking spray.', 'In a small bowl, combine lemon zest, feta cheese, capers, 1/2 tsp of the dried oregano and 1 clove minced garlic.', 'Slice a pocket in the side of each chicken breast with a sharp knife. Be sure not to slice all the way through the chicken breast, just far enough to make a pocket about 3-4 inches long. Divide the filling mixture evenly among the four breasts and fill each pocket. Do not overfill. Press down on the breast to slightly seal the pocket opening.', 'In a small bowl, combine paprika, remaining 2 tsp dried oregano, garlic powder, salt and ground black pepper. Rub each chicken breast on both sides with the spice rub so that the entire breast is coated. Set aside.', 'Toss together zucchini, mushrooms, tomatoes, cannellini beans, remaining minced garlic, olive oil and 1/4 cup lemon juice in the prepared baking dish.', 'Place the chicken breasts on top of the vegetables and put in the oven to bake.', 'Bake for 30-40 minutes depending on the size of the chicken breast or until the internal temperature of the chicken and filling is 165 degrees Fahrenheit. Check the temperature after 30 minutes and every five minutes after until it reaches 165 degrees.', 'Remove the chicken from the wok and place on a cutting board. Cover with foil and let it rest for 15 minutes.', 'Turn the oven temperature up to 400 degrees F. Return the vegetables to continue to bake in the oven for 15 minutes while chicken is resting.', 'Slice chicken and serve over the vegetables.']

Recipe Name: Mediterranean Stuffed Chicken and Vegetable Ragout
Ingredients: ['1 spaghetti squash', '2 tbsp olive oil', '1/2 cup finely chopped onion', '2 clove garlic', '1/2 8-ounce package cream cheese', '1 eggs', '1/2 tsp poultry seasoning', '1/8 tsp black pepper', '1/2 cup dried cranberries']
steps: ['Fill a soup pot with 1 inch water place squash in water. Bring to a boil over high heat, cover, and cook 25 to 30 minutes or until tender when pierced with a knife. Remove squash to a cutting board and allow to cool slightly. Cut squash in half, lengthwise. Remove and discard seeds with a spoon. With a fork, scrape the inside of one half, shredding it into noodle-like strands. Place shredded squash in a large bowl. Reserve remaining half for later use.', 'Meanwhile, in a small skillet over medium-low heat, heat oil until hot. Cook onion and garlic 3 to 4 minutes or until softened, stirring occasionally put to squash.', 'put cream cheese to squash mixture and whisk until thoroughly combined. Stir in egg, poultry seasoning, and pepper.', 'First heat oven to 400 degrees F. Coat 1 24-cup mini muffin tin with cooking spray. Spoon equal amounts of squash mixture into each muffin cup and lightly press 2 to 3 dried cranberries on top of each. Bake 25 to 30 minutes or until lightly browned. Let cool slightly, then remove from muffin tin and serve.']

Ingredients: ['1 tbsp. olive oil', '1 onion', '1 red pepper', '1 green pepper', '4 cloves garlic', '1 tbsp. tomato paste', '1 tsp saffron filaments', '1 cup uncooked quinoa', '2 cups unsalted chicken broth', '1 10 oz can diced tomatoes', '1/4 tsp coarse salt', '1 lb approx. 30 shrimp large fresh wild shrimp', '1 lbs squid', '3 tbsp. fresh flat-leaf parsley', '1 limn']
steps: ['Heat the oil in a large non-stick frying wok or paella wok over medium high heat. put the onion, red pepper and garlic, and sautÈ, stirring occasionally, until softened, about 8 minutes.', 'put the tomato paste and saffron to the wok, stirring until well blended. put the quinoa, broth, tomatoes and salt, and bring to a boil. Reduce heat to medium-low. Cover and simmer until the liquid is absorbed and the quinoa is soft, about 20 minutes.', 'put the shrimp and squid to the quinoa. Cover and cook until cooked through, about 5 minutes. Remove from heat Top with the parsley and garnish with lemon wedges.']

Ingredients: ['1 pinch Pinch of nutmeg', '3 medium green onions', '2 clove medium garlic', '2 tbsp port', '1 cup frozen spinach', '3/4 cup milk', '1 tsp corn starch', '1/8 tbsp pepper', '1/4 cup plus 2 tbsp shredded part-skim mozzarella cheese', '1 tsp canola or corn oil', '1 tbsp Parmesan cheese', '1/2 cup egg substitute', '6 oz Portobello mushrooms']
steps: ['First heat the oven to 350F 177degreesC. Lightly spray two 10 oz flan woks or individual cake woks with cooking spray. Place them on a shallow tray.', 'In a large non-stick frying wok, heat the oil over medium heat, stirring to coat the bottom. Cook the mushrooms and chives for 2 minutes, stirring occasionally. A put the port. Reduce heat to medium-low and cook for 3 to 4 minutes, or until all liquid is absorbed. Stir in garlic and cook for 30 seconds to 1 minute, or until fragrant. Remove the saucewok from the heat. A put the spinach. Using a spoon, separate them into small pieces.', 'Put the cornstarch in a medium bowl. Pour in the milk, whisking to dissolve. put the rest of the ingredients. Stir in mushroom mixture. Pour into cups of flan.', 'Bake for 30 minutes or until the centers are puffy and set do not move when gently shaken. Let sit for 5 minutes before serving.']

Ingredients: ['8 oz rigatoni', '1 Olive oil cooking spray', '1/2 cup onion', '2 clove garlic', '1/2 cup rehydrated sun-dried tomatoes', '1/2 cup dry white wine', '4 tbsp pesto sauce', '2 tbsp toasted pine nuts', '1/4 cup Kalamata olives', '2 tsp fresh lemon zest', '1 freshly ground black pepper to taste']
steps: ['Bring a large pot of lightly salted water to a boil. put the rigatoni and cook for 8-10 minutes until al dente.', 'Meanwhile coat a large skillet with cooking spray. Saute the onion and garlic over medium heat for about 6 minutes. put the sun-dried tomatoes and saute for 2 minutes. put the wine and cook until wine is almost evaporated.', 'Drain the pasta, reserving about 1/3 cup pasta water. Set the pasta aside. put the pasta water to the onion mixture and cook for 1 minute. put in the pesto, pine nuts, olives, and lemon zest. Season with pepper. put the rigatoni and toss well.']

Recipe Name: Rigatoni With Sun-Dried Tomatoes, Pesto, And Olives
Ingredients: ['1 3-inch piece English cucumber', '3/4 cup Plain Nonfat Greek yogurt', '1 tbsp olive oil', '1/8 tsp salt', '16 leaves fresh mint']
steps: ['Slice the 3-inch-long piece of cucumber into quarters lengthwise. Then slice the four 3-inch-long pieces into thin slices crosswise.', 'Scatter half the cucumber pieces onto a plate or shallow bowl. Dollop the yogurt onto the cucumbers. Spread it with the back of a spoon. Attractively arrange the remaining cucumber on the yogurt.', 'Drizzle with the oil. Sprinkle with the salt and mint leaves. Serve.']

Ingredients: ['1 tbsp honey', '1 oz goat cheese', '3/4 lbs golden potatoes', '6 oz about 3 whole carrots carrots', '4 oz mini sweet peppers', '1 tsp onion powder', '1 tsp garlic powder', '1/2 tsp smoked paprika', '1/2 tsp dried parsley', '5 tsp olive oil', '2 12 oz total boneless, skinless chicken breasts', '1 tbsp red wine vinegar', '1 1/2 tbsp golden raisins', '1/4 tsp crushed red pepper flakes']
steps: ['Prepare the ingredients & make the sauce:  Remove the honey and cheese from the refrigerator to bring to room temperature. Fill a medium pot 3/4 of the way up with salted water cover and heat to boiling on high. Wash and dry the fresh produce. Medium dice the potatoes. Peel the carrots halve lengthwise, then cut crosswise into 2-inch pieces. Cut off and discard the stems of the peppers remove the cores, then quarter lengthwise. In a bowl, whisk together the cheese and 2 tablespoons of hot water. Prepare the spice blend: combine the onion powder, garlic powder, paprika, and parsley in a small bowl.', 'Cook & mash the potatoes:  put the diced potatoes to the pot of boiling water. Cook 16 to 18 minutes, or until tender when pierced with a fork. Turn off the heat. Drain thoroughly and return to the pot. put 2 teaspoons of olive oil. Using a fork or potato masher, mash to your desired consistency. Taste, then season with salt and pepper if desired. Cover to keep warm.', 'Cook the chicken:  Meanwhile, pat the chicken dry with paper towels. Season on both sides with salt optional, pepper, and enough of the spice blend to coat you may have extra. In a medium wok nonstick, if you have one, heat 2 teaspoons of olive oil on medium-high until hot. put the seasoned chicken. Cook 6 to 7 minutes per side, or until browned and cooked through.* Leaving any browned bits or fond in the wok, transfer to a cutting board. Cover with foil to keep warm. * An instant-read thermometer should register 165F.', 'Make the carrot-pepper agrodolce:  In the wok of reserved fond, heat 1 teaspoon of olive oil on medium-high until hot. put the carrot pieces season with salt optional and pepper. Cook, stirring occasionally, 4 to 6 minutes, or until lightly browned and slightly softened. put the quartered peppers. Cook, stirring occasionally, 3 to 4 minutes, or until slightly softened. put the honey, vinegar carefully, as the liquid may splatter, raisins, and as much of the red pepper flakes as you d like, depending on how spicy you d like the dish to be. Cook, stirring frequently, 30 seconds to 1 minute, or until the vegetables are coated. Turn off the heat.', 'Slice the chicken & serve your dish: Slice the cooked chicken crosswise. Serve the sliced chicken with the mashed potatoes and carrot-pepper agrodolce. Top the chicken with the sauce. Enjoy!']

Recipe Name: Seared Chicken & Goat Cheese Sauce with Mashed Potatoes & Carrot-Pepper Agrodolce
Ingredients: ['2 cup fresh basil leaves', '5 tbsp olive oil', '1 clove garlic', '1/4 cup Plain Nonfat Greek yogurt', '1 tbsp red wine vinegar', '1/8 tsp salt', '3/4 lb about 16 scallops sea scallops', '1/4 tsp black pepper', '1 tbsp unsalted butter']
steps: ['Make the pesto: put the basil, 3 Tbsp of the olive oil, and the garlic to a blender pulse until a rough paste forms. put the yogurt, vinegar, and salt and puree until smooth.', 'Dry the scallops with a paper towel and sprinkle with the pepper.', 'Heat the remaining 2 Tbsp of olive oil and the butter in a large saucewok over medium-high heat. put the scallops and cook until browned, 1 Ω to 2 minutes per side. Using tongs, remove the scallops and place them on a plate to cool.', 'Spoon 2 Tbsp of the pesto sauce onto each of 4 plates and top with the warm scallops.']

Ingredients: ['8 chicken tenderloins', '1 cup Greek yogurt', '1 Grated rind and juice of a large lemon', '1 tbsp paprika', '1 tbsp gingerroot', '1 tsp ground cumin', '1/2 tsp garlic powder', '1/2 tsp salt', '1 medium lemon']
steps: ['Combine all ingredients, except the lemon quarters, in a gallon resealable plastic bag. Seal tightly and toss back and forth until well coated. Refrigerate 8 hours.', 'Heat a grill wok liberally coated with cooking spray over medium-high heat. Remove chicken from marinade, discarding marinade, and grill 3 minutes on each side or until no longer pink in center. Serve with the quartered lemon, if desired.']

Ingredients: ['4 tbsp olive oil', '2 cup white', '4 cup baby spinach', '1 clove garlic', '1 nonstick cooking spray', '1/2 cup reduced-fat, shredded mozzarella cheese', '4 gluten-free tortillas or whole-wheat flour tortillas', '2 tbsp lime juice', '1 tbsp honey or 2 packets artificial sweetener', '8 cup chopped romaine lettuce']
steps: ['Heat 1 tbsp of the olive oil in a non-stick wok over medium-high heat. put the mushrooms and spinach, and saute for about 5 minutes, until the spinach wilts and most of the liquid has cooked off. put the garlic and saute for 30 seconds. Remove the mixture from the wok and set aside in a bowl.', 'Spray the wok with cooking spray. Place 1 tortilla in the wok and spread 1/4 of the spinach-mushroom mixture on one half of the tortilla. whisk the two types of cheese together and spread 1/4 cup cheese over the spinach-mushroom mixture. Fold the tortilla in half. Cook for 1-2 minutes. Flip the tortilla and cook for 1-2 more minutes, until golden brown. Cut your quesadilla into triangles.', 'Repeat procedure for remaining 3 quesadillas.', 'Prepare the salad: whisk together the remaining 3 tbsp olive oil, lime juice, and honey or combine in a shaker. Toss the dressing in a large bowl with the romaine lettuce. Serve each quesadilla along with 2 cups salad.']

Ingredients: ['1 nonstick cooking spray', '1 lbs boneless, skinless chicken breast', '1/2 tsp black pepper', '1 tsp basil', '3 cup baby spinach', '2 tbsp pine nuts', '2 tbsp fresh lemon juice', '1/4 cup light mayonnaise', '1 tbsp olive oil', '2 tbsp Parmesan cheese', '1/4 tsp garlic powder', '5 6-inch corn tortillas']
steps: ['First heat the oven to 350 degrees F. Spray a baking sheet with cooking spray.', 'Season the chicken breasts with 1/4 Tsp. black pepper and dried basil. Bake for 35 minutes or until done. Put the chicken breasts in the refrigerator to cool.', 'In a food processor, combine the spinach, pine nuts, lemon juice, and mayonnaise. Lightly pulse. With the machine running, put the olive oil, blending until the mixture is creamy. Stir in the Parmesan cheese, garlic powder, and 1/4 Tsp. black pepper.', 'Cut the cooked chicken into 1/2-inch pieces and shred. In a medium bowl, combine the chicken and pesto sauce whisk well.', 'Serve 1/2 cup chicken salad in each tortilla. Fold in the two sides of the tortilla and roll like a burrito. You can serve these immediately or wrap tightly in plastic wrap and refrigerate.']

Ingredients: ['6 clove garlic', '1 cup balsamic vinegar', '1 1/2 lbs strip, flank, or skirt steak', '1 olive oil spray', '1/2 lbs Portobello mushrooms', '4 whole-wheat hoagie rolls', '1/2 tsp salt', '1/4 tsp freshly ground black pepper']
steps: ['whisk the garlic and balsamic vinegar in a small bowl. Set aside.', 'Remove visible fat from the steak. Heat a skillet to medium-high heat. Place the steak in the skillet and sear for 2 minutes. Turn the steak over and cook for 2 more minutes, or until they reach desired doneness. Remove from the skillet and set aside.', 'Coat the skillet with the olive oil spray. put the mushrooms and cook for 5 minutes, turning over once. Remove the mushrooms to a cutting board.', 'put the garlic-vinegar mixture to the skillet and boil for 3 to 4 minutes, until reduced by half. Divide the sauce among 4 small bowls and set aside.', 'Slice open the rolls, then mist each side with the olive oil spray. Toast the rolls in a toaster oven for 1 minute.', 'Slice the steak and mushrooms into thin strips. Arrange about 5 oz of steak and 3/4 cup of mushrooms on the bottom half of each roll. Top with salt and pepper. Cover each sandwich with the top half of the roll, cut in half, and serve with the dipping sauce.']

Ingredients: ['1 medium green bell pepper', '1 can stewed tomatoes with Italian seasonings', '1 cup water', '1 lbs tilapia', '1/2 tsp seafood seasoning']
steps: ['Place a large saucewok over medium heat until hot. Coat the wok with nonstick cooking spray, put the bell pepper, and cook 5 minutes or until beginning to lightly brown, stirring frequently.', 'put the tomatoes and water, increase to high heat, and bring to a boil. Reduce the heat, cover tightly, and simmer until the tomatoes are tender. Using the back of a spoon, break up the larger pieces of tomato.', 'put the fish and seasonings and stir very gently. Increase the heat to high and bring just to a boil. Reduce the heat, cover tightly, and simmer 3 minutes or until the fish is opaque in the center. Remove from the heat and let stand, covered, 10 minutes to develop flavors.']

Ingredients: ['1/2 lbs red cabbage', '1 tbsp rice vinegar', '4 tsp olive oil', '2 persian cucumber', '1 zucchini', '6 oz about 3 whole carrots carrots', '1 1-inch piece fresh ginger', '1 tbsp ponzu sauce', '3 tbsp ranch dressing', '3/4 lbs boneless, skinless chicken thighs', '1 tbsp togarashi']
steps: ['Prepare the ingredients & make the dressing: Wash and dry the fresh produce. Cut out and discard the core of the cabbage medium dice the leaves. Place in a large bowl put half the vinegar and 1 teaspoon of olive oil. Season with salt optional and pepper stir to coat. Halve the cucumbers lengthwise, then thinly slice crosswise. Place in a separate bowl put the remaining vinegar and season with salt optional and pepper. Stir to coat. Medium dice the zucchini. Peel the carrots. Halve lengthwise cut crosswise into 1-inch pieces. Peel and finely chop the ginger. In a bowl, whisk together the ponzu sauce and ranch dressing.', 'Cook the chicken: Pat the chicken dry with paper towels season with salt optional and pepper on both sides. In a large wok nonstick, if you have one, heat 2 teaspoons of olive oil on medium-high until hot. put the seasoned chicken. Cook 5 to 7 minutes per side, or until browned and cooked through.* Leaving any browned bits or fond in the wok, transfer to a cutting board. * An instant-read thermometer should register 165F.', 'Cook & finish the vegetables: In the wok of reserved fond, heat 1 teaspoon of olive oil on medium-high until hot. put the diced zucchini and carrot pieces in an even layer. Cook, without stirring, 3 to 4 minutes, or until lightly browned. put the chopped ginger and half the togarashi season with salt optional and pepper. Cook, stirring occasionally, 3 to 4 minutes, or until softened. Transfer to the bowl of dressed cabbage stir to combine.', 'Slice the chicken & serve your dish: Slice the cooked chicken crosswise. Serve the finished vegetables topped with the sliced chicken and dressing. Garnish with the dressed cucumbers and remaining togarashi. Enjoy!']

Recipe Name: Togarashi Vegetables & Chicken Thighs with Creamy Ponzu-Ranch Dressing
Ingredients: ['2 tbsp Extra Virgin Olive Oil', '1 Juice of 1 lemon', '2 clove garlic', '2 tsp fennel seeds', '1/2 tsp crushed red pepper flakes', '1 tbsp fresh oregano', '1 tbsp balsamic vinegar', '1 lbs chicken breasts']
steps: ['Combine oil, lemon juice, garlic, fennel seeds, red chili flakes, oregano, and vinegar in a medium bowl and put into a large tightly sealed plastic bag. Marinate at least 15 minutes room temperature or overnight in the refrigerator for best results.', 'Thread the chicken cubes on skewers, either alone or with chunks of your favorite vegetables such as red onion, bell pepper, or zucchini.', 'First heat grill to medium-high heat and place on grill grate. Cook as per directions for direct heat method page 3 for 10-12 minutes, turning occasionally, until cooked through and crusted on the outside.']

Recipe Name: Tuscan Spiedini With Fresh Herbs, Lemon, And Cracked Fennel Seeds
Ingredients: ['2 tbsp vegetable oil', '2 tbsp all-purpose flour', '1 small onion', '1 green bell pepper', '1 red bell pepper', '2 stalks celery', '3 clove garlic', '1 tsp salt', '1/2 tsp black pepper', '2 tbsp salt-free cajun seasoning', '3 cup low sodium vegetable broth', '9 oz baby spinach', '1 14.5-oz can black-eyed peas']
steps: ['put the vegetable oil to a large pot over medium-high heat. put the flour and cook, stirring, until golden, about 3 minutes.', 'put the onion, bell peppers, celery, and garlic. Reduce the heat to medium and cook, stirring frequently, until the vegetables soften, about 5-7 minutes.', 'put the salt optional, ground black pepper, and Cajun seasoning. Cook for another minute.', 'Pour in the vegetable broth, scraping up any browned bits from the bottom of the pot. Bring to a boil, then reduce to a simmer and cover.', 'Simmer, covered, for 40 minutes, stirring occasionally.', 'put the spinach and black-eyed peas. Continue to simmer until the spinach is wilted.']

Ingredients: ['3 cup seedless watermelon', '1/3 cup reduced-fat crumbled feta cheese', '7 oz arugula', '1/4 small red onion', '2 tbsp balsamic vinegar', '1 tbsp olive oil', '1/4 tsp salt', '1/4 tsp black pepper']
steps: ['In a large bowl, toss together the watermelon, feta, arugula, and onion.', 'In a medium bowl, whisk together the balsamic vinegar, olive oil, salt, and pepper.', 'Drizzle the dressing over the salad and toss gently to coat.']

Ingredients: ['1 3-inch piece English cucumber', '1 tbsp olive oil', '3/4 cup Plain Nonfat Greek yogurt', '16 leaves fresh mint', '1/8 tsp salt']
steps: ['Cut the 3-inch-long piece of cucumber into quarters lengthwise. Next, cut the four pieces 3 inches long into thin slices crosswise.', 'Scatter half of the cucumber pieces on a shallow plate or bowl. Spoon the yogurt over the cucumbers. Spread it out with the back of a spoon. Place the rest of the cucumbers attractively on top of the yoghurt.', 'Drizzle it with the oil. Sprinkle with salt and mint leaves. Serve.']

Ingredients: ['2 tsp Extra Virgin Olive Oil', '1/3 cup wokko bread crumbs', '1 cup water', '1 lbs asparagus spears', '1/4 cup sour cream', '3 tbsp light mayonnaise', '2 tbsp milk', '1 1/2 tsp prepared mustard', '1/4 tsp dried tarragon', '1/4 tsp salt']
steps: ['Heat the oil in a large skillet over medium-high heat. put the breadcrumbs and cook 1-2 minutes or until golden, stirring constantly. Set aside on separate plate.', 'Bring the water to a boil in the skillet over medium-high heat. put the asparagus, return to a boil, reduce heat, cover, and simmer 3 minutes or until just tender. Drain well, discarding water. Place the asparagus on a serving plate.', 'Meanwhile, in a small bowl, whisk together the sour cream, mayonnaise, milk, mustard, tarragon, and salt. Place in the skillet over medium-low heat and cook 1 minute or until heated, stirring constantly. Spoon over the asparagus and sprinkle with the breadcrumbs.']

Ingredients: ['1/3 cup sugar', '1/4 cup water', '2 cups skim milk', '1 can 12 oz evaporated skim milk', '3 tbsp. granulated baking sugar substitute', '1/4 tsp cinnamon powder', '2 3-inch cinnamon sticks', '2 tsp vanilla extract', '5 large eggs', '2 2/3 cups raspberries']
steps: ['Heat the oven to 350∞F.', 'whisk the sugar and water in a small, heavy-bottomed pot. Bring to a boil over medium high heat and stir occasionally, until honey is lightly browned, about 12 minutes. Immediately pour the honey into a half-gallon baking dish, tilting it so that it coats evenly. Let sit until honey cools and hardens, about 10 minutes.', 'Meanwhile, whisk milk, evaporated milk, sugar substitute, cinnamon powder and cinnamon sticks in a medium pot. Cook over medium-low heat, stirring occasionally, for 6 minutes. Remove from heat. put the vanilla, whisk and let stand 15 minutes. Remove the cinnamon sticks.', 'Beat the eggs in a medium bowl. Slowly put them to the milk pot and whisk well. Pour into the caramel baking dish.', 'Place the baking dish with the flan mixture in a 9 "13-inch roasting wok and pour hot water into the roasting wok until it reaches one-third of the way through. Bake until the flan sets but moves in the centre when shaking, 50-55 minutes.', 'Transfer the dish to a wire rack Cool 1 hour. Refrigerate until thoroughly cooled, about 3 hours or overnight. To unmold, run the tip of a small knife around the edge of the flan. Place a large flat dish on top of the flan and flip it over. Cut the flan into triangles and serve each with 1/3 cup raspberries.']

Ingredients: ['1 tbsp lime juice', '1 tbsp olive oil', '1 tsp red wine vinegar', '1/8 tsp zero-calorie sweetener', '1/4 tsp salt', '1/8 tsp black pepper', '2 oranges', '4 cup whisked greens', '1 avocado', '1/4 small red onion', '2 tbsp chopped fresh cilantro']
steps: ['In a small bowl, whisk together the lime juice, olive oil, red wine vinegar, sweetener, kosher salt, and black pepper.', 'Remove the peel and the white pith from around the oranges. Using a paring knife, cut in between the membranes to release the orange segments, and slice them into thirds. Place the orange pieces into a medium bowl.', 'put the whisked greens, avocado cubes, and red onion to the bowl and drizzle with the lime juice mixture. Toss to combine. Sprinkle with the cilantro and serve.']

Recipe Name: Green Salad with Orange, Avocado, and Onion
Ingredients: ['1 tsp garlic', '1 tsp basil', '2 medium tomatoes', '1/2 tsp salt', '1/8 tsp black pepper']
steps: ['whisk ingredients and let set at room temperature for at least 1 hour.', 'Serve plain or on a lettuce leaf']

Ingredients: ['1 cup parsnips', '1 cup turnips', '1 tbsp hazelnut or olive oil', '1 small onion', '1 clove garlic', '1 tbsp brown sugar', '3/4 cup malt vinegar', '1/2 cup fresh cilantro or parsley', '8 cup baby salad greens', '1/2 cup walnut pieces', '1 cup radish', '1 Salt and pepper']
steps: ['Bring a large pot of salted water to a boil. put parsnips and turnips and simmer until vegetables are just tender, 8-10 minutes. Drain well.', 'While the parsnips and turnips are cooking, make the dressing. Heat oil in a large skillet over medium heat. put onions and cook until golden brown, 5-7 minutes. put garlic and cook for 30 seconds more. Stir in vinegar and sugar and bring just to a simmer. Remove from heat and keep dressing warm.', 'Arrange parsley, cilantro, and salad greens and top with hot vegetables, then garnish with walnuts and radish. Drizzle with warm dressing, and serve immediately.']

Ingredients: ['4 medium sweet potatoes', '3 cup broccoli florets', '4 tsp margarine', '4 tbsp slivered almonds']
steps: ['Pierce each sweet potato with a fork in a few spots. Arrange the potatoes on a microwave-safe plate and microwave until soft, about 12 minutes.', 'Place 3/4 to 1 inch of water in a saucewok with a steamer and bring to a boil. If you don t have a steamer, you can simply put the broccoli directly into 1 inch of boiling water. put the broccoli to the steamer and cover reduce the heat to medium and let it cook for 6 minutes.', 'Using a knife, slit each sweet potato in half and pinch the sides to open it up. Fill each sweet potato with 1 Tsp. margarine, 2/3 cup broccoli and 1 Tbsp. toasted almonds.']

Ingredients: ['1 tsp dried oregano', '1 tbsp ground cumin', '3 tbsp chili powder', '2 cup low sodium chicken broth', '1 28-oz can no-salt-puted diced tomatoes', '1 15-oz can no-salt-puted kidney beans', '1 15-oz can no-salt-puted black beans', '3 clove garlic', '1 15-oz can pumpkin puree', '1 cup chopped onion', '1 cup chopped yellow bell pepper', '1 cup chopped red bell pepper', '1 lbs lean ground turkey', '1 1/2 tsp salt', '1 1/4 cup Plain Nonfat Greek yogurt', '1 tbsp canola oil', '1/2 cup apple juice', '1 tsp ground cinnamon', '1/8 tsp ground cloves', '1/8 tsp ground nutmeg']
steps: ['Press the SautÈ button.  When the display says Hot, put the oil, tilt the pot to lightly coat the bottom. put the turkey and cook for 4 minutes or until not pink, stirring occasionally. put the peppers and onions and cook for 4 minutes. put garlic, cook for 30 seconds, stirring constantly. put the remaining chili ingredients, except the salt, and stir until well blended.', 'Seal the lid, close the valve, press the Cancel button, and set to Manual Cooking Pressure for 20 minutes.', 'Use a quick release of pressure. When the valve drops, carefully remove the lid and stir in the salt. Spoon the yogurt over each portion.']

Recipe Name: Chili with Turkey Seasoned with Large Butternut Squash in the Instant Pot
Ingredients: ['2 tbsp extra virgin olive oil', '2 links 6 oz total fully cooked Italian-style chicken sausage links, such as Al Fresco', '2 cup water', '1 zucchini', '1 cup green onion', '1/2 tsp dried oregano', "1 tsp hot sauce, such as Frank's", '4 8-oz each russet or baking potatoes', '1/8 tsp salt', '1/4 tsp black pepper', '1 oz reduced-fat blue cheese']
steps: ['Press the Saute/Browning button. When hot, put 1 Tbsp. oil, tilt the pressure cooker pot to coat bottom lightly. put sausage and cook 3 minutes or until beginning to brown on edges. put 1/3 cup of the water, the zucchini, 3/4 cup of the onion and oregano, cook 3 minutes or until zucchini is tender crisp, scraping up browned bits.  Place in a medium bowl with hot sauce and remaining 1 Tbsp. oil. Cover to keep warm.', 'Put a steamer basket in the pressure cooking pot and put the remaining water. Top with the potatoes. Lock the lid in place and close the seal valve. Press the Cancel button and reset to Manual for 18 minutes. When time ends, use a 10-minute natural pressure release, then a quick pressure release.', 'When valve drops, carefully remove the lid. Remove potatoes with tongs or a fork. Split potatoes almost in half and fluff with a fork. put the salt and pepper to the sausage mixture and spoon equal amounts over each potato. Top with the cheese and remaining 1/4 cup green onion.']

Recipe Name: Instant Pot Chicken Sausage and Zucchini Stuffed Potatoes

Ingredients: ['1/4 tsp black pepper', '7 mini whole wheat buns', '1/2 tsp garlic powder', '1/2 avocado', '1 tbsp chili powder', '3 1/2 slice reduced-fat pepper jack cheese', '1 lbs lean ground turkey', '7 tomato slices']
steps: ['Prepare a grill for internal or external use at home.', 'In a medium bowl, whisk together turkey, chili powder, garlic powder and black pepper. Divide the turkey into seven equal portions, molding them into a flat meatball.', 'Place the flat meatballs on a grill rack grill for 3-4 minutes per side or until juices run clear.', 'Place the burger on a bun and cover with 2 Tbsp. avocado, 1 slice of tomato and 1/2 slice of cheese. Repeat the process for the remaining 6 patties.']

Ingredients: ['6 eggs', '1 tbsp white vinegar', '6 tbsp plain yogurt', '1 tbsp light mayonnaise', '1 tbsp fresh chives', '2 tsp Dijon Mustard', '1/2 tsp horseradish', '1/4 tsp turmeric', '1 pinch paprika']
steps: ['To prepare the eggs: put the eggs to a saucewok that is large enough so they are not crowded. put water to cover about 1 inch over the eggs. Cover the pot and bring to a boil. Once the water comes to a boil, about 6 to 7 minutes, remove the pot from the heat and set it on an unused burner. put the vinegar to the water to help in peeling the eggs. Let the eggs stand in the hot water for 20 to 30 minutes.', 'Prepare a large bowl of ice water. Using a slotted spoon, transfer the eggs to the ice water bath, letting them cool for 15 to 20 minutes. Gently remove each egg from the ice water, and gently tap its shell until it is cracked all over but do not peel. put the cracked eggs back to the ice water bath prepare a new ice bath if necessary for 10 minutes. Remove the eggs from the ice water, and gently roll them between your palms. The shells should slip off easily. Discard the shells.', 'Halve each egg and remove the yolks. Discard one yolk and put the remaining five to a bowl. Set the egg whites on a platter, with the cut sides up.', 'Mash the yolks with the yogurt, mayonnaise, chives, mustard, horseradish, turmeric, salt, and pepper. Spoon or pipe the egg yolk mixture back into the egg whites. Sprinkle lightly with paprika.']

Ingredients: ['1 1/2 cup grape tomatoes', '16 Kalamata olives', '2 tbsp chopped fresh basil leaves, or 2 Tsps. dried basil leaves', '1/2 tsp rosemary leaves', '1/8 tsp crushed red pepper flakes', '1 clove medium garlic', '4 oz uncooked whole-grain penne or rotini pasta', '8 oz fresh or frozen shelled edamame', '1 medium lemon', '2 oz feta cheese']
steps: ['Cook the pasta according to package directions, omitting any salt or fats and puting the edamame for the last 2 minutes of the cooking time.', 'In a small bowl, combine the tomatoes, olives, basil, rosemary optional, garlic, and pepper flakes. Stir to whisk and set aside.', 'Drain the pasta and edamame in a colander, place them on a serving platter or pasta bowl, squeeze the lemon over everything, top with the feta cheese, and pile the tomato mixture in the center.']

Ingredients: ['1 tsp chili powder', '1 tbsp paprika', '1 tsp cumin', '1 tbsp vegetable oil', '4 cup low sodium chicken broth', '8 oz chicken breasts', '1 medium yellow onion', '1 nonstick cooking spray', '1 lbs premade whole wheat pizza dough', '1 eggs', '1 tbsp water', '16 green Swokish olives']
steps: put the chicken breasts and chicken broth to a large saucewok over high heat. Bring to a boil, then reduce the heat and simmer for 15 to 20 minutes, until the chicken is cooked through. Remove the saucewok from the heat and let the chicken cool to the touch in the broth about 20 minutes.', 'Shred the chicken into small pieces and put 2 Tbsp. from the chicken broth to the saucewok mixture set aside.', 'A put the oil to a saucewok over medium heat. put the onion, paprika, cumin, chili powder, and 1/2 cup of the chicken broth. Reduce the heat to low and cook for 10 to 15 minutes, until the onions are soft and translucent, and the liquid is evaporated. Stir in chicken to produce 2 cups of filling.', 'First heat oven to 400F 204C. Coat a large baking sheet with cooking spray.', 'Separate the whole wheat pizza dough into 16 golf ballsized pieces, and roll each into a soft ball.', 'Using a rolling pin, roll each ball of dough into a 6-inch-diameter circle.']

Ingredients: ['1/2 cup Prepared or deli coleslaw', '2 tbsp no-sugar-puted salsa', 'to taste black pepper', '4 slices whole wheat bread']
steps: ['Drain the coleslaw in a colander.', 'Toss the drained coleslaw with the sauce and put black pepper to taste.', 'Place half of the turkey on each of the two slices of bread. Place the coleslaw on top of the turkey and then top each sandwich with the remaining slices of bread. Serve with more coleslaw on the side.']

Ingredients: ['1 tbsp fresh lime juice', '2 tsp sugar', '4 ice cubes', '2 sprig fresh mint', '1/2 cup orange juice', '2 cup 2 cups honeydew or cantaloupe chunks']
steps: ['Blend all ingredients in a blender and process for 30 seconds to 1 minute until smooth. Pour into tall glasses and serve. Garnish each glass with a sprig of fresh mint.']

Ingredients: ['2 stalks celery', '1 medium Jonagold apple', '2 green onions', '3 tbsp walnuts', '1/4 cup yogurt', '1/4 cup light mayonnaise', '1/8 tsp black pepper', '2 cup cooked chicken breast', '1/2 lemon']
steps: ['In a medium bowl, combine chicken, celery, chives, apple and walnuts.', 'In a small bowl, whisk together mayonnaise, yogurt, lemon juice and pepper. Pour over the chicken mixture and stir gently to coat.', 'Serve the salad over lettuce leaves, bread or crackers of your choice.']
